NK065(cu)001:1946: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK065(cu)001:1947: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK065(cu)001:1949: de'ang sngags phyi pas lha'i sku gsung thugs su bltas te bsgom pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:1950: nang pa ltar na chos thams cad sku gsung thugs
NK065(cu)001:1951: kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du rtogs nas goms
NK065(cu)001:1952: par byed pa'i phyir na 'bras bu lam byed dang
NK065(cu)001:1953: rdo rje theg pa'i nges tshig grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:1954: bang mdzod 'phrul gyi lde mig las /
NK065(cu)001:1955: 'bras bu rdo rje'i theg pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:1956: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor lam byas nas //
NK065(cu)001:1957: 'bras bu de nyid lam du khyer //
NK065(cu)001:1958: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum ni //
NK065(cu)001:1959: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rjer sbyor //
NK065(cu)001:1960: de rigs rdo rje theg par btags //
NK065(cu)001:1962: khyad par gzhan yang yod de /
NK065(cu)001:1964: don gcig na'ang ma rmongs dang //
NK065(cu)001:1965: thabs mang dka' ba med pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:1966: dbang po rnon po'i dbang byas pas //
NK065(cu)001:1967: sngags kyi theg pa khyad par 'phags //
NK065(cu)001:1969: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa chen po gnyis ka sems
NK065(cu)001:1970: can gyi don la dmigs nas byang chub 'dod par
NK065(cu)001:1971: gcig na'ang / sngags khyad par bzhis 'phags te /
NK065(cu)001:1972: lha bsgom sngags bzla ba sogs thabs kyi cha la ma rmongs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:1973: de'ang thabs kyi cha'i sgo gcig ma yin par dbang
NK065(cu)001:1974: po'i rim pa dang mthun par bya spyod la sogs
NK065(cu)001:1975: pa'i rgyud sde'i sgo mtha' yas pa'i phyir mang ba
NK065(cu)001:1976: dang / de dag kyang rgyu'i lam ltar bskal pa
NK065(cu)001:1977: grangs med gsum sogs su dka' bas bgrod mi dgos
NK065(cu)001:1978: par tshegs chung ngus 'grub pa'i phyir dka' med pa
NK065(cu)001:1979: dang / dang / de nyid sngags kyi theg pa'i
NK065(cu)001:1980: dngos kyi gdul bya dbang rnon la dgongs nas gsungs
NK065(cu)001:1981: pa'i phyir tshul bzhi po des 'phags pa yin no
NK065(cu)001:1983: dpyal lo mkhas pa kun dga' rdo rje ni /
NK065(cu)001:1986: thob bya 'bras bu'i khyad par phye ste 'phags tshul gsung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:1988: gnubs chen gyis rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan gyi rang 'grel du /
NK065(cu)001:1989: pha rol tu phyin pa las sngags nang pa khyad par bcu gnyis kyis 'phags par gsungs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:1990: rje zur chung ba dang rog bder gshegs chen pos /
NK065(cu)001:1995: 'bras bu rang gi ngo bo rnams la khyad par
NK065(cu)001:1996: yod tshul rgyas par gsungs kyang 'dir yi ges 'jigs
NK065(cu)001:2000: bla na med pa'i theg pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:2003: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK065(cu)001:2004: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK065(cu)001:2005: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK065(cu)001:2006: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK065(cu)001:2009: phyi thub pa rgyud kyi theg pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:2010: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2011: de gnyis kyi khyad par la snga rabs pa rnams kyi bzhed pa mi mthun pa mang na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:2012: 'dir thugs sras ka ba bzhi'i dgongs pa rje sgro phug pas bsdus nas lngar gsungs te /
NK065(cu)001:2013: dang po lta ba'i khyad par ni /
NK065(cu)001:2014: sngags kyi theg pa gang zhig sems nyid bdag nyid chen por rtogs pa nang pa /
NK065(cu)001:2015: ma rtogs pa phyi ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:2016: in+d+ra b+h+au ti'i lam rnam bkod las /
NK065(cu)001:2017: rigs gsum rigs lngar 'dod pa dag /
NK065(cu)001:2018: bdag nyid chen por ma rtogs phyir //
NK065(cu)001:2019: thun mong mnyam par nga smra'o //
NK065(cu)001:2021: gnyis pa dngos grub len tshul gyi khyad par ni /
NK065(cu)001:2022: ye shes kyi lha la re zhing bka' la sdod pas dngos grub zhu ba ni phyi pa /
NK065(cu)001:2023: bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas sems nyid sku dang
NK065(cu)001:2024: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:2025: dngos grub rang la yod par mthong ba ni nang
NK065(cu)001:2026: pa ste / rdo rje sems pa'i zhus lan las /
NK065(cu)001:2027: sngags phyi nang gi rnal 'byor pa gnyis dngos grub len pa la khyad par ci mchis /
NK065(cu)001:2029: dper na rgyal pos blon por bsgos pa ltar //
NK065(cu)001:2030: grub pa gong nas 'byin pa phyi pa'i tshul //
NK065(cu)001:2031: 'bangs kyis rgyal srid phul nas dbang bsgyur ltar //
NK065(cu)001:2032: rang byung rdzogs chen bla na med pa'i tshul //
NK065(cu)001:2035: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK065(cu)001:2036: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK065(cu)001:2037: gsum pa dbang gi khyad par ni /
NK065(cu)001:2038: mchog dbang gong ma gsum bskur thob mi nus na phyi pa /
NK065(cu)001:2039: de gsum la gtso bor 'dzin pa ni nang pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2040: bzhi pa spyod pa'i khyad par ni /
NK065(cu)001:2041: 'khor ba'i chos nyi shul thabs kyis zin nas spyod nus pa nang pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:2043: lnga pa 'bras bu'i khyad par ni /
NK065(cu)001:2044: mi tshe bdun dang lnga dang gsum sogs nas sbyor nus pa phyi pa /
NK065(cu)001:2045: tshe 'di la sbyor nus pa nang pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2047: lha rje kha rag pa dang rog ni /
NK065(cu)001:2049: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu phyi nang gis bsgyur ba'i khyad par dang /
NK065(cu)001:2050: bye brag dbang gi skabs su zab dbang gsum ston nus mi nus dang /
NK065(cu)001:2051: lta ba'i skabs su rang byung gi ye shes smra nus mi nus dang /
NK065(cu)001:2052: bsgom pa'i skabs su lha zhal sbyor du bsgom nus mi nus dang /
NK065(cu)001:2053: spyod pa'i skabs su dam rdzas lnga la spyod nus mi nus dang /
NK065(cu)001:2054: lha dang bdag tha mi dad du bltas nas 'jug nus mi nus dang /
NK065(cu)001:2055: dngos grub kyi skabs su dus nye ring dang phyi nang nas re ba'i khyad par yod ces gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:2056: lha rje dpyal pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:2057: khyad par de rnams kyang phyogs re ba tsam yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:2059: shes byed lam gyi khyad par /
NK065(cu)001:2060: thob bya 'bras bu'i khyad par gsum du phye na 'thad gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:2061: rje sgrol g.yung gnyis kyi zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:2062: lta spyod dang ting nge 'dzin gsum dbyer med du 'dod pa sngags nang pa /
NK065(cu)001:2064: 'o na rgyu'i theg pa dang sngags phyi pa la khyad par med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:2066: kun rdzob lam du byed nus mi nus kyi khyad par yod pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:2068: dang bo phyir thub pa brgyud kyi theg pa la dbye na /
NK065(cu)001:2070: phyi pa rgyud la rnam gsum ste //
NK065(cu)001:2071: kri ya u pa yo ga'o //
NK065(cu)001:2081: don dam par mtha' bzhi dang bral ba'i dag par
NK065(cu)001:2082: rtogs pas kun rdzob tu dngos grub gzhan la re
NK065(cu)001:2083: zhing rtsol ba'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2085: gnyis med mnyam par ma shes pas //
NK065(cu)001:2086: don dam dag pa chos nyid tsam //
NK065(cu)001:2087: ye shes bzhi yon kun rdzob lha //
NK065(cu)001:2088: res bsgom bya ba las kyi sa //
NK065(cu)001:2091: kri ya'i sgra bya ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:2092: phyi'i bya ba gtso bor ston pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:2093: de ltar yang bsam gtan phyi ma'i 'grel pa las /
NK065(cu)001:2094: rgyud 'di ni lus ngag gi bya ba gtso bor ston pas na bya ba'i rgyud ces bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:2096: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK065(cu)001:2098: thog ma'i 'jug sgo smin byed dang /
NK065(cu)001:2101: chu dang cod pan gyi dbang 'khor bcas bskur bas slob ma snod rung du byed pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2103: chu'i dbang bskur dbu rgyan dag /
NK065(cu)001:2104: bya ba'i rgyud la rab tu grags //
NK065(cu)001:2107: khrus dang gtsang sbra dang dag pa gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK065(cu)001:2109: 'jug pa'i sgo ni dag pa gsum //
NK065(cu)001:2112: de yang dag pa gsum ni /
NK065(cu)001:2114: dag pa rnam gsum gang zhe na //
NK065(cu)001:2115: lha dang dkyil 'khor dag pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:2116: rdzas dang longs spyod dag pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:2121: kri ya don dam chos nyid blta //
NK065(cu)001:2122: kun rdzob rang rig yon tan lha //
NK065(cu)001:2123: rigs gsum dkyil 'khor snang ba la //
NK065(cu)001:2125: ces pas bden pa gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:2127: sems nyid dag pa stong gsal gyi ye shes yod
NK065(cu)001:2128: med snang stong gi mtha' bzhi dang bral bar 'dod
NK065(cu)001:2130: rang sems mtha' bzhi yongs bral ba //
NK065(cu)001:2131: rig phyir ye shes gzhan las min //
NK065(cu)001:2136: dbu ma pa man chad kyis yang dag dang log par brtags pa'i kun rdzob thams cad yin la /
NK065(cu)001:2138: chos nyid rtogs pa'i yon tan rigs gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du snang bar 'dod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2140: skyen bslad snang ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK065(cu)001:2141: snang ba'i dngos po mtho 'jam rtsub //
NK065(cu)001:2142: drug phyed rigs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK065(cu)001:2143: mthong ba rnam par dag ces bya //
NK065(cu)001:2147: dkon mchog gsum dang byang chub sems //
NK065(cu)001:2148: sngags dang phyag rgya mi spang zhing //
NK065(cu)001:2149: rdo rje dril bu spang mi bya //
NK065(cu)001:2150: lha dang bla ma de bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:2151: de ni yan lag dam tshig yin //
NK065(cu)001:2152: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po ni //
NK065(cu)001:2153: khri la nyal bar mi bya zhing //
NK065(cu)001:2154: sha mi za zhing chang mi btung //
NK065(cu)001:2155: sgog pa la phug bza' mi bya //
NK065(cu)001:2156: zhes dam tshig bcu gcig tu gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:2157: gsang ba spyi rgyud las spyi'i dam tshig gsum dang /
NK065(cu)001:2158: bye brag gi dam tshig bcu gsum du bshad pa la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2163: he ru ka gal po las /
NK065(cu)001:2164: chos nyid sgra dang yid gzugs thugs //
NK065(cu)001:2165: ye shes yongs rdzogs skur sgrub bsgom //
NK065(cu)001:2166: zhes pas kri ya don gyi lha drug gi sgo nas dam tshig pa bskyed par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:2167: de'ang stong pa nyid kyi lha dang /
NK065(cu)001:2174: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK065(cu)001:2175: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin te //
NK065(cu)001:2176: zhes rnam 'joms kyi rgyud rgyas pa las gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:2177: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs te /
NK065(cu)001:2178: mchod bstod dang bzlas pa sogs byas la /
NK065(cu)001:2179: rje khol gyi tshul du bltas nas dngos grub blang ste /
NK065(cu)001:2181: lha dang rnal 'byor dag pa gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:2182: rje dang 'bangs kyi tshul du blta //
NK065(cu)001:2184: rigs thams cad pa'i dngos grub len pa'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:2185: rje dpon rgyal po'i tshul bltas la //
NK065(cu)001:2186: rang nyid bran gyi 'du shes kyis //
NK065(cu)001:2187: sngags bsgrub dngos grub snying po ni //
NK065(cu)001:2188: bla na med pa'i mchog tu blang //
NK065(cu)001:2191: mtshan bcas lha dang yig 'bru la sogs par bsgom
NK065(cu)001:2192: pa'i snang ba de'ang mi dmigs pa dag pa mtha'
NK065(cu)001:2193: bzhi dang bral ba'i ngang du 'jog pas bden gnyis
NK065(cu)001:2194: res bsgom ste / la shan las /
NK065(cu)001:2195: snang stong rim gyis brtan par byed //
NK065(cu)001:2204: bzlas brjod sngags kyi bya ba rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:2207: gza' skad dus tshigs zas gos gtsang //
NK065(cu)001:2208: brtul zhugs dka' thub spyad pa spyod //
NK065(cu)001:2216: mi tshe bdun na rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i
NK065(cu)001:2217: sa sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can 'thob
NK065(cu)001:2220: mi tshe bdun na sangs rgyas pa //
NK065(cu)001:2223: gnyis pa u pa ya'i theg pa la /
NK065(cu)001:2229: spyod pa bya ba ltar spyod pas dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs su gyur pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2231: gnyis ka la brten pa las grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2235: phyi lus ngag gi bya ba dang nang gi rnal 'byor gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:2236: cha mnyam du spyod pa'i phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:2238: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK065(cu)001:2239: lta ba yo gar blta ba la //
NK065(cu)001:2240: spyod pa kri yar spyod pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2241: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK065(cu)001:2243: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK065(cu)001:2244: dang po 'jug sgo la'ang gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:2246: chu cod pan gnyis kyi steng du rdor dril ming gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:2248: rdo rje dril bu de bzhin ming //
NK065(cu)001:2249: spyod pa'i rgyud du rab tu gsal //
NK065(cu)001:2253: lnga pa spyod pa rnams bya rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:2255: bzhi pa sgom pa'i ting nge 'dzin ni yo ga dang shas cher mthun pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2257: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:2258: spyod pa bya ba'i rjes mthun yang //
NK065(cu)001:2259: lta ba rnal 'byor rjes mthun phyir //
NK065(cu)001:2260: rigs dang lta bas khyad par 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:2263: gnyis ka rgyud kyi 'dod pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:2264: lta spyod gong 'og rjes su mthun //
NK065(cu)001:2266: 'on kyang rgyal ba rigs bzhir blta zhing bsgom pa sogs khyad par cung zad snang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:2268: mi tshe lnga na rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob par 'dod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2269: rigs bzhi ni las kyi rigs rin chen rigs la bsdus pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2271: rigs bzhi rdo rje 'chang bar gnas //
NK065(cu)001:2274: gnyis su med la mi tshe lngas sgrib gol //
NK065(cu)001:2276: gsum pa yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK065(cu)001:2281: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid kyi byin
NK065(cu)001:2282: rlabs kun rdzob rdo rje dbyings kyi lhar brtags te
NK065(cu)001:2283: rtog pa bzang ngan blang dor gyi rtsol bas 'bras
NK065(cu)001:2286: lhun grub mnyam pa ma mthong bas //
NK065(cu)001:2287: chos kun rnam dag ye shes kyi //
NK065(cu)001:2288: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings sprul ba //
NK065(cu)001:2292: yo ga'i sgra las nang gi rnal 'byor gtso bor
NK065(cu)001:2293: byed pa'am ston pas na rnal 'byor rgyud ces bya
NK065(cu)001:2295: rnal 'byor gtso bor byas pas 'grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2297: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK065(cu)001:2298: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:2300: rig pa'i dbang lnga'i steng du rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang drug bskur te /
NK065(cu)001:2302: phyir mi ldog pa bum pa'i dbang //
NK065(cu)001:2303: rnal 'byor rgyud du gsal bar byas //
NK065(cu)001:2304: de ni drug gi bye brag dbang //
NK065(cu)001:2305: de ni slob dpon dbang zhes bya //
NK065(cu)001:2307: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni //
NK065(cu)001:2308: mtshan bcas mtshan med kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK065(cu)001:2310: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pa //
NK065(cu)001:2311: mtshan ma yod med sgor zhugs nas //
NK065(cu)001:2316: chos thams cad spros pa'i mtshan ma dang bral ba'i rang bzhin 'od gsal stong pa nyid de /
NK065(cu)001:2318: chos rnams rang bzhin 'od gsal bas //
NK065(cu)001:2319: ngo bo nyid kyis gdod nas dag /
NK065(cu)001:2322: log pa'i kun rdzob sngar dang 'dra /
NK065(cu)001:2324: cir snang thams cad chos nyid rtogs pa'i byin rlabs
NK065(cu)001:2325: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:2326: / skye bos snang ba rang rgyud du brtags pa 'di med par 'dod do //
NK065(cu)001:2327: de ltar yang gal po las /
NK065(cu)001:2328: yo ga'i theg par gnas 'dod pas //
NK065(cu)001:2329: 'og min rdo rje dbyings su blta //
NK065(cu)001:2332: yo ga don dam rnam dag pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:2333: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su //
NK065(cu)001:2334: rtogs pa'i byin rlabs lhar snang ba //
NK065(cu)001:2335: de phyir skye bo ltar mthong 'khrul //
NK065(cu)001:2338: rang rig dngos mthong mtshan ma gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:2339: dbyer med dbyings dag ye shes las //
NK065(cu)001:2340: byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi lha //
NK065(cu)001:2341: shar lta grogs po'i tshul du ltar //
NK065(cu)001:2344: rtse mor gsungs pa'i rigs lnga spyi'i dam tshig /
NK065(cu)001:2345: byang chub kyi sems dang por bskyed cing /
NK065(cu)001:2346: de'i rjes su tshul khrims gsum gyi bslab pa la nan tan byed pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:2348: snang mdzad kyi dam tshig gsum /
NK065(cu)001:2349: mi bskyod rin 'byung gnyis la bzhi bzhi /
NK065(cu)001:2351: don grub gyi gnyis te bcu bzhir gsungs la /
NK065(cu)001:2353: bya rgyud kyi dam tshig bcu gcig po'i steng du
NK065(cu)001:2354: thun min gnyis bsnan nas bcu gsum du bcad de
NK065(cu)001:2356: rnal 'byor rgyud kyi bsrung mtshams ni //
NK065(cu)001:2357: gong gi bsrung mtshams steng du ni //
NK065(cu)001:2358: lung gcig chu la mi btung zhing //
NK065(cu)001:2359: nyams dang kha mi bsre ba bsrung //
NK065(cu)001:2365: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo nas lha
NK065(cu)001:2366: dang lha mo'i rnal 'byor phyag rgya bzhi ldan du
NK065(cu)001:2367: bsgom pa ste / lta phreng las /
NK065(cu)001:2368: phyir yo byad la gtso bor mi 'dzin par don
NK065(cu)001:2369: dam par skye 'gag med pa'i lha dang lha mo
NK065(cu)001:2370: dang / de dang 'dra ba'i rgyud yongs su dag
NK065(cu)001:2371: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'phags pa'i gzugs kyi sku
NK065(cu)001:2372: phyag rgyas bzhi dang ldan par bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor
NK065(cu)001:2375: de'ang dam tshig pa bskyed la /
NK065(cu)001:2376: ye shes pa spyan drangs nas /
NK065(cu)001:2377: spun nam grogs po'i tshul du bzang ngan med par bltas te /
NK065(cu)001:2378: mchod bstod bzlas pa la sogs pa bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:2379: de ltar yang rang shar las /
NK065(cu)001:2380: lha dang rnal 'byor bdag nyid kyang //
NK065(cu)001:2381: spun dang grogs po'i tshul du 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:2383: de la mngon byang lnga ni /
NK065(cu)001:2388: sku yongs su rdzogs pa las mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2394: de dag kyang gal po las /
NK065(cu)001:2395: mi rtog zla ba gsung rdo rje //
NK065(cu)001:2396: spro bsdus bsgom pa'i sku ru gsal //
NK065(cu)001:2397: ting 'dzin byin rlob dbang bskur mchod //
NK065(cu)001:2398: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK065(cu)001:2399: bsgom zhing mchod pa bya ba yang //
NK065(cu)001:2400: bsod nams ldan phyir bya ba yin //
NK065(cu)001:2403: lus ngag yid dang bya ba bzhi la /
NK065(cu)001:2416: phrin las las rgya rnams kyis rgyas btab nas bsgom pa'i phyir phyag rgya ste /
NK065(cu)001:2417: me long lta bu la sogs pa'i ye shes bzhi mngon du bya ba dang sbyar zhir /
NK065(cu)001:2418: chos dbyings ye shes ni de thams cad kyi rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2420: don dam mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo nyid dang
NK065(cu)001:2421: de'i byin rlabs lhar snang ye shes kyi snang cha
NK065(cu)001:2422: gnyis gnyis su med pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog
NK065(cu)001:2423: pa ste / rdo rje 'byung ba las /
NK065(cu)001:2424: gnyis su med pa'i chos dbyings dang //
NK065(cu)001:2425: bla med dngos grub dam pa blang //
NK065(cu)001:2428: gtsang spra sogs phyi'i kun spyod kyi grogs dang ldan
NK065(cu)001:2429: pa'i sgo nas gtso bor lha'i rnal 'byor la gnas
NK065(cu)001:2430: pas rang gzhan gyi don spyod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2432: lha yi ting 'dzin la gnas te //
NK065(cu)001:2433: sems can thams cad yongs mi gtong //
NK065(cu)001:2434: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK065(cu)001:2435: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pa mchog /
NK065(cu)001:2438: mi tshe gsum na stug po bkod pa'i sa la
NK065(cu)001:2439: sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can du 'tshang
NK065(cu)001:2442: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK065(cu)001:2443: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:2446: gzung 'dzin bag chags lnga byang nas //
NK065(cu)001:2447: ye shes lnga yi rtsal dag gis //
NK065(cu)001:2448: stug po bkod pa'i sa non nas //
NK065(cu)001:2450: skye med chos sku dag pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:2451: skye med sgo nas 'gro don mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:2452: phyag rgya rigs lnga longs spyod rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:2453: byang chub sems dpa'i 'gro don rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:2454: sprul pa bye ba sa ya yis //
NK065(cu)001:2455: rigs drug ngo la cir yang ston //
NK065(cu)001:2457: gnyis pa nang pa thabs kyi theg pa la /
NK065(cu)001:2458: bskyed rdzogs gsum so so'i dbye ba bshad pa /
NK065(cu)001:2459: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid de gsum gang yin la dpyad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2462: nang pa ma h+aa yo ga'i bkol mdo ni gzhung
NK065(cu)001:2463: hril bo yin pas sbyar mi dgos par bzhed la
NK065(cu)001:2464: / a nu dang a ti yo ga'i bkol mdo ni 'dir ma sbyar kyang chog mod kyi /
NK065(cu)001:2466: 'og tu gzhung 'di nyid bskyed rdzogs gsum gang yin
NK065(cu)001:2467: ngos 'dzin pa'i tshe so so'i mtshan nyid phyed pa
NK065(cu)001:2468: la mkho bar 'gyur ba'i phyir cung zad bri bar
NK065(cu)001:2470: nang pa la ni gsum du 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:2471: ma h+aa a nu a ti'o //
NK065(cu)001:2475: man ngag a ti yo ga'o //
NK065(cu)001:2476: de gsum gyi khyad par la /
NK065(cu)001:2477: glan chab par bas rje zur chung pa la zhus pa'i lan du /
NK065(cu)001:2478: rig pa'i cho 'phrul du snang ba ma h+aa /
NK065(cu)001:2479: rang rig pa'i rtsal du snang ba a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2480: rig pa rang snang ba a ti ste /
NK065(cu)001:2482: cho 'phrul rtsal dang rang snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:2483: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gsungs skad /
NK065(cu)001:2485: chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med kyi cho 'phrul du rtogs pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK065(cu)001:2486: chos thams cad sems nyid dbyings ye gnyis su med pa'i rtsal du rtogs pa a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2487: chos thams cad sems nyid ye nas skye 'gag med
NK065(cu)001:2488: pa'i rang byung gi ye shes rang snang bar rtogs
NK065(cu)001:2489: pa a ti ste lta ba'i sgo nas khyad par
NK065(cu)001:2490: phye ba'o // de la mda' glan gnyis ka gces nor du bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:2491: yang skyo gong bu pa'i zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:2493: spyod pa gtso che ba ma h+aa /
NK065(cu)001:2494: ting nge 'dzin gtso che ba a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2495: lta ba gtso che ba a ti'o gsung /
NK065(cu)001:2497: ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis lha rim par bskyed pa'i phyir bskyed pa ma h+aa /
NK065(cu)001:2498: de la mi brten par lha rdzogs tshul du bskyed pa rdzogs pa a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2499: bskyed rdzogs gnyis las grol bas bskyed du med pa ni rdzogs pa chen po a ti'am /
NK065(cu)001:2501: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu la ched 'dzin che ba ma h+aa /
NK065(cu)001:2502: de bas chung ba a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2503: ched 'dzin las grol a ti'o gsung //
NK065(cu)001:2504: me nyag 'byung grags kyi zhal nas yod bskyed rdzogs gsum ga yod kyang /
NK065(cu)001:2505: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa ma h+aa /
NK065(cu)001:2506: rdzogs rim gtso bor ston pa a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2507: de gnyis kyi rtsol ba dang bral ba rdzogs pa chen po ste /
NK065(cu)001:2508: dpyal lo kun rdor yang nges tshig gi khyad par la 'di legs par bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:2510: gdul bya zhe sdang shas che zhing rtog pa mang
NK065(cu)001:2511: ba'i don du snang ba thabs kyi rang bzhin pha
NK065(cu)001:2513: 'dod chags shas che zhing sems gnas pa la dga'
NK065(cu)001:2514: ba'i don du stong pa de kho na nyid kyi
NK065(cu)001:2515: rdzogs rim shes rab ma'i rgyud a nu /
NK065(cu)001:2516: gti mug shas che zhing bya rtsol can gyi don
NK065(cu)001:2517: du gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin a ti yo
NK065(cu)001:2518: ga bstan te / bkod pa chen po las /
NK065(cu)001:2519: sems yas pa la bskyed pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:2520: sems bcud can la rdzogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2521: mchog gsang rab la rdzogs pa che //
NK065(cu)001:2522: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir gsung zhing /
NK065(cu)001:2523: sems nyid ngal gso las kyang /
NK065(cu)001:2524: ma h+aas rlung dang bskyed rim thabs gtso la //
NK065(cu)001:2525: a nus khams dang rdzogs rim shes rab gtso //
NK065(cu)001:2526: a tis thams cad gnyis med ye shes gtso //
NK065(cu)001:2529: dang po ma h+aa yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK065(cu)001:2534: thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa la gtso bor brten pa'i
NK065(cu)001:2535: sgo nas lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi don
NK065(cu)001:2536: la rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba thob pa'i
NK065(cu)001:2537: rang bzhin no // gnyis pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:2538: ma h+aa yo ga'i sgra las rnal 'byor chen po ste /
NK065(cu)001:2539: gnyis med kyi don la blo 'byor bas yo ga phyi pa las ches 'phags pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:2540: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK065(cu)001:2541: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:2543: thun mong pa bum dbang gi steng du thun min
NK065(cu)001:2544: mchog dbang gong ma gsum bsnan pas dbang bzhi bskur
NK065(cu)001:2546: rtsa rgyud kyi phyi ma las /
NK065(cu)001:2547: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK065(cu)001:2548: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:2550: de yang bum dbang la phan nus gnyis su phye bas lngar 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:2552: dbyee ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:2553: bdag phan nus pa gnyis ka'i las //
NK065(cu)001:2555: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK065(cu)001:2556: shes rab stong pa chen po'i rnal 'byor dang //
NK065(cu)001:2557: thabs snying rje sgyu ma dang phyag rgya phra rags te ting 'dzin gsum gyi sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK065(cu)001:2558: bskyed rim gtso bor ston pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:2559: de ltar yang rang shar las /
NK065(cu)001:2560: 'jug pa'i sgo ni ting 'dzin rnam pa gsum //
NK065(cu)001:2563: ma h+aa yo ga'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK065(cu)001:2567: rig pa spros bral la snang ba ngo bo nyid
NK065(cu)001:2568: kyi rgyur lhun grub tu 'dod pa'i don dam bden
NK065(cu)001:2569: pa dang / de nyid kyi rtsal rtog tshogs thams
NK065(cu)001:2570: cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang
NK065(cu)001:2571: snang ba kun rdzob kyi bden par 'dod la /
NK065(cu)001:2572: de gnyis kyang snang stong phyogs re ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:2573: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed par mnyam pa nyid du snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:2574: tha snyad du dbyer med ces brjod na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:2575: der 'dzin pa'i bsam brjod kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:2576: dbyer med spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:2577: de ltar yang rnam bkod las /
NK065(cu)001:2578: lhag pa'i mnyam nyid dbyer med don //
NK065(cu)001:2579: ming grangs cir yang bstan mod kyang //
NK065(cu)001:2580: don du smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK065(cu)001:2583: de ming zhen pa grol phyir las //
NK065(cu)001:2584: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK065(cu)001:2588: bsrung bya'i dam tshig rtsa ltung bcu bzhi la sogs pa rnams dang /
NK065(cu)001:2589: spyad bya'i dam tshig sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i rang bzhin shes nas spyod pa gnyis su bzhed /
NK065(cu)001:2591: rnal 'byor chen po'i dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad gsungs te /
NK065(cu)001:2593: rnal 'byor chen po'i bsrung mtshams ni //
NK065(cu)001:2594: rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum po dang //
NK065(cu)001:2595: yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga bsrung //
NK065(cu)001:2598: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig gsum mo //
NK065(cu)001:2601: spyad dang mi spang dang du blang //
NK065(cu)001:2602: shes dang bsgrub par bya ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:2608: sgrub sde gtso bor byas pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:2609: rgyud sde gtso bor byas pa'i lugs gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:2611: 'jam dpal gyi sku 'khor lo bzhi la brten nas bde gshegs sku'i sgrub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:2612: rta skad thengs gsum la brten nas pad+ma gsung gi sgrub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:2613: thugs rig par rang byung gi ye shes yang dag
NK065(cu)001:2614: sgrub pa gcig pu la brten nas thugs rdo rje'i
NK065(cu)001:2615: sgrub pa dang / 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad
NK065(cu)001:2616: yon tan du rdzogs par ston pa bdud rtsi yon
NK065(cu)001:2618: mngon spyod kyi las kyi gdug pa can 'dul ba'i
NK065(cu)001:2619: thabs gtso bor ston pa phur pa phrin las kyi
NK065(cu)001:2620: sgrub pa ste ye shes lha'i sgrub sde lnga dang
NK065(cu)001:2623: 'jig rten mchod bstod kyi sgrub pa ste thun mong gi sgrub sde gsum mo //
NK065(cu)001:2625: spyir ma h+aa yo ga la'ang pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum gyi dbye bas /
NK065(cu)001:2626: gsang 'dus la sogs pa pha rgyud du bskyed rim thabs kyi cha dang /
NK065(cu)001:2627: de'i rdzogs rim kyang rlung gtso bor byed pas gsal
NK065(cu)001:2628: stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i tshul gyis nyams su
NK065(cu)001:2629: len par 'dod / bde dgyes yang dag sogs ma
NK065(cu)001:2630: rgyud rnams su bskyed rim gyi spros pa shas chung
NK065(cu)001:2631: len par 'dod / zhing / shes rab rdzogs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:2632: rim pa khams byang chub kyi sems thig le gtso
NK065(cu)001:2633: bor byed pa'i bde stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK065(cu)001:2634: tshul gyis nyams su len par 'dod /
NK065(cu)001:2635: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs ma ning gi rgyud rnams su bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug cing /
NK065(cu)001:2636: de'ang rdzogs rim rtsa thig rlung gsum las skyes pa'i bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK065(cu)001:2637: khyad par 'od gsal ye shes chen po la gtso
NK065(cu)001:2638: bor byed pa'i tshul gyis nyams su len par 'dod
NK065(cu)001:2639: do // 'dir rgyud gzhung 'di nyid kyi dbang du byas te bshad na /
NK065(cu)001:2641: mtshan ma bsgom pa'i rim pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:2642: de bzhin nyid ni bsgom pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:2643: bye brag rnam pa gnyis su gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:2650: ting nge 'dzin gsum la brten nas dkyil 'khor rim
NK065(cu)001:2651: gyis bskyed pa gtso bor byed pa'i sgo nas lha
NK065(cu)001:2652: rtog dbyer med du bsgom pa'i nyams len /
NK065(cu)001:2657: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang rnam
NK065(cu)001:2658: pa tsam bsgom pa nub gcig la bskyed rim gyi
NK065(cu)001:2659: cho ga'i yan lag tshang ba nyams su len pa
NK065(cu)001:2661: zag bcas tshogs sbyor gyi rnal 'byor lnga dang /
NK065(cu)001:2662: zag med rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi'o //
NK065(cu)001:2664: steng sgo 'ju 'dul gyi man ngag dang /
NK065(cu)001:2665: 'og sgo khams gsum rol pa'i man ngag gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:2667: gdams ngag steng dang 'og gi sgo //
NK065(cu)001:2670: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2672: thabs la mkhas pa'i gding gis zin pas 'khor ba'i chos ci la'ang ma chags par spyod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2674: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni //
NK065(cu)001:2675: ta na dang ni ga na dang //
NK065(cu)001:2676: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga po la //
NK065(cu)001:2677: thabs chen lta ba'i spyod pa'i spyad //
NK065(cu)001:2680: tshe 'adi'am bar dor sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag nyid mngon du byed pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2682: 'di ni bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK065(cu)001:2683: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK065(cu)001:2684: ye shes rgya mtsho rnam par brgyan //
NK065(cu)001:2688: yang na lus ni spangs ma thag /
NK065(cu)001:2689: brtson pa mi ldan pas kyang 'grub //
NK065(cu)001:2691: gnyis pa lung a nu yo ga'i theg pa la //
NK065(cu)001:2696: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa la gtso bor brten
NK065(cu)001:2697: pa'i sgo nas dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med
NK065(cu)001:2698: pa'i don la rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas grol ba
NK065(cu)001:2701: a nu yo ga ste shes rab rjes chags kyi
NK065(cu)001:2702: lam gtso bor ston pa'i phyir rjes su rnal 'byor
NK065(cu)001:2703: ro // gsum pa dbye ba drug gi /
NK065(cu)001:2704: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:2706: a nu'i dkyil 'khor du phyi nang sgrub gsang bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang chog sum cu rtsa drug ste /
NK065(cu)001:2708: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK065(cu)001:2709: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK065(cu)001:2710: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK065(cu)001:2711: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:2714: de ltar smos pa'i rtsa ba so drug las yan
NK065(cu)001:2715: lag gi dbang brgyad brgya po gcig tu phye ba
NK065(cu)001:2716: ni theg pa dgu ka'i dbang yin te /
NK065(cu)001:2718: yo ga la sogs theg drug las /
NK065(cu)001:2719: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK065(cu)001:2721: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK065(cu)001:2722: bcu yis byang chub rigs can 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:2723: bcu gcig gsang ba nang bar 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:2724: bcu gsum bla ma chen por grags //
NK065(cu)001:2725: gnyis kyi theg dgu'i dbang rdzogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2727: a nu'i dgos dbang du ji ltar 'gyur zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:2729: theg rim dgu dang tshul mthun pas theg dgu'i dbang
NK065(cu)001:2730: du ming btags par bla ma mkhas pa rnams bzhed
NK065(cu)001:2732: mdo dbang 'chad pa po phal gyi 'dod pa ltar ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:2734: a nu yo ga'i dbang gi nang du gong ma
NK065(cu)001:2735: a ti yo ga'i dbang 'du bar khas len dgos
NK065(cu)001:2736: pa'i phyir ha cang thal te /
NK065(cu)001:2737: phyi rgyud kyi nang du nang pa'i thun min gyi chos skad mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:2739: bdag gi rje bla ma thams ca da mkhyen pa'i zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:2740: rtsa ba a nu'i cho ga la //
NK065(cu)001:2741: theg brgyad sgos chos bye brag tu //
NK065(cu)001:2742: sbyar ba nyid la stos dgos na //
NK065(cu)001:2743: a nu'i mtshan gzhir ji ltar nges //
NK065(cu)001:2744: zhes gsungs pa'i phyogs snga ma nyid du gnas pa'i phyir skyon yod pa ma yin no //
NK065(cu)001:2745: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK065(cu)001:2746: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK065(cu)001:2748: a nu dbyer med pa 'dod pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:2749: dbyings dang ye shes sgor zhugs nas //
NK065(cu)001:2752: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis te /
NK065(cu)001:2754: skye med dbyings nyid ye shes te //
NK065(cu)001:2755: ye shes rig pa dbyings nyid tshul //
NK065(cu)001:2756: gnyis med rol pa bde ba che //
NK065(cu)001:2757: rim par 'jug pa ma yin te //
NK065(cu)001:2758: snang srid phyag rgya thams cad la //
NK065(cu)001:2759: chu la nya ldang ji bzhin du //
NK065(cu)001:2760: thugs phrad snang srid phyag rgya che //
NK065(cu)001:2763: chos thams cad rang gi sems yin la /
NK065(cu)001:2764: de nyid skye med spros pa dang bral ba'i rang
NK065(cu)001:2765: bzhin yum kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par
NK065(cu)001:2766: dag pa ste / ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:2767: de ltar yang spyi mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:2768: sems las byung ba stong nyid pas //
NK065(cu)001:2769: de las byung ba thams cad stong //
NK065(cu)001:2771: skye med de nyid thams cad du mi 'gag bar
NK065(cu)001:2772: rig pa rang byung 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK065(cu)001:2773: ba ni / ye shes kun tu bzang po'am /
NK065(cu)001:2774: rang bzhin lhun grub dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:2776: brtags na ma mthong cir yang snang ba nyid //
NK065(cu)001:2778: de gnyis ngo bo tha mi dad par gsal ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:2779: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde ba
NK065(cu)001:2780: chen po ste rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK065(cu)001:2781: 'khor ro // de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK065(cu)001:2782: gsang sngags zhes bya ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:2783: snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis su med pa /
NK065(cu)001:2784: gnyis kyi ngo bo las grol ba /
NK065(cu)001:2785: dbu mar mi dmigs pa gang yin pa de kho na nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:2788: chos thams cad dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum dbyer med
NK065(cu)001:2789: pa'i rang bzhin rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK065(cu)001:2790: 'khor du ye nas sangs rgyas par blta ba ste
NK065(cu)001:2792: thams cad de nyid der gcig pas //
NK065(cu)001:2793: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK065(cu)001:2794: skyes 'gag med pa'i snying po yin //
NK065(cu)001:2795: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK065(cu)001:2796: ye nas grub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK065(cu)001:2799: snang srid bzang mo'i mkha' klong las //
NK065(cu)001:2800: ma bskyed dkyil 'khor kun bzang shar //
NK065(cu)001:2801: shar ba nyid na shar ba med //
NK065(cu)001:2802: yab yum sras bcas bde chen po //
NK065(cu)001:2805: de'ang kun tu bzang po'i rol pa ma 'gags pa'i rtsal lha skur 'char bar 'dod de /
NK065(cu)001:2807: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK065(cu)001:2808: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK065(cu)001:2809: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK065(cu)001:2812: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni //
NK065(cu)001:2813: phung po khams dang skye mched rnams //
NK065(cu)001:2814: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK065(cu)001:2815: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:2819: gzhi 'dzin pa ni dam tshig ste //
NK065(cu)001:2820: sgo gsum sdom par gnas pa'i don //
NK065(cu)001:2821: rtsa ba yan lag la sogs pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:2822: bsrung dang bsgrub pa de nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:2823: zhes pas sgo gsum gyis rtsa ba dang yan lag la sogs pa'i dam tshig bsrung zhing /
NK065(cu)001:2824: bsgrub par bya ba rnams te /
NK065(cu)001:2826: gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig bzhi /
NK065(cu)001:2827: thun mong gi nyi shu rtsa brgyad //
NK065(cu)001:2834: lta ba'i dam tshig ste rnam grangs dgur spyi mdo'i le'u re drug par gsungs mod kyang /
NK065(cu)001:2836: bsrung mtshams med par cig car ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK065(cu)001:2837: bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i dam tshig gnyis su 'du ste /
NK065(cu)001:2839: bsrung bya bsrung du med pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:2840: chos nyid dam tshig dam pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:2842: dam tshig 'di na rmad po che //
NK065(cu)001:2843: kun gyi thun mong ma yin phyir //
NK065(cu)001:2844: mos pa chung ngu thams cad la //
NK065(cu)001:2845: bsrung ba'i mtshams dag bzung bar bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:2849: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab ste //
NK065(cu)001:2854: steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi'am drug bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK065(cu)001:2855: 'og sgo mkha' gsang gnyis kyi snyoms 'jug la brten
NK065(cu)001:2856: nas lhan skyes kyi ye shes bskyed pa'i thabs te
NK065(cu)001:2858: rol pa'i ka ra la sogs pa //
NK065(cu)001:2859: man ngag thabs kyis der 'jug dang //
NK065(cu)001:2865: spros med rnam par mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK065(cu)001:2866: chos nyid snying po ji bzhin pa'i ngang las sgom byed kyi blo ma bcos par 'jog pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2869: ji bzhin pa yi chos nyid la //
NK065(cu)001:2870: de bzhin pa yi blo bzhag nas //
NK065(cu)001:2871: brjod pa med pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK065(cu)001:2872: ma yengs rgyun du dran pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2875: spros bcas lha yi ting nge 'dzin te /
NK065(cu)001:2876: sngags brjod pa tsam gyis chu las nya ldang ba ltar //
NK065(cu)001:2877: snod bcud lha'i dkyil 'khor gsal la ma 'dres par
NK065(cu)001:2878: cig car du bsgom pa gtso bor byed pa'i nyams
NK065(cu)001:2879: len no // de ltar yang bang mdzod 'phrul lde las /
NK065(cu)001:2880: a nu yo ga'i theg par ni //
NK065(cu)001:2881: snying po tsam zhig brjod byas nas //
NK065(cu)001:2882: ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i lha ru bsgom //
NK065(cu)001:2885: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK065(cu)001:2886: 'byung dang 'byung gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK065(cu)001:2888: de'ang spyir nges rdzogs bsgom pa'i lam la /
NK065(cu)001:2889: zag bcas dang zag med gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:2896: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor ro //
NK065(cu)001:2898: spyir mnyam pa nyid la gtso bor spyod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2900: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga ni //
NK065(cu)001:2901: dbyings dang ye shes longs spyod rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:2906: thabs kyi spyod pa gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:2908: byin gyis rlob kyi spyod pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:2909: dbang sgyur thabs kyi spyod pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:2910: dper na nam mkha' rgyal po'am //
NK065(cu)001:2911: ji ltar me dpung chu bo 'dra //
NK065(cu)001:2914: tshe gcig gis 'bras chos nyer lnga dbyer med lhun
NK065(cu)001:2915: grub gyi ngo bo sku bzhi'i bdag nyid bde ba
NK065(cu)001:2916: chen po'i sku mngon du byed de /
NK065(cu)001:2917: thig le mchog gi rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:2918: 'od gsal ba yi sems nyid ni //
NK065(cu)001:2919: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med par //
NK065(cu)001:2920: bde ba che de su bsgom pa //
NK065(cu)001:2924: a nu yo ga'i theg pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:2925: bar ma chod pa'i tshe gcig gis //
NK065(cu)001:2926: sangs rgyas sa la nges par 'gro //
NK065(cu)001:2928: gsum pa man ngag a ti yo ga'i theg pa la /
NK065(cu)001:2933: ye sangs rgyas ba'i don rang thog tu grol bar byed pa'i thabs /
NK065(cu)001:2934: spang blang re dogs dang bral ba'i rang bzhin can no //
NK065(cu)001:2937: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i rdzogs rim mthar thug pa yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:2938: theg pa thams cad kyi rtse mor gyur pa'i phyir shin tu rnal 'byor ro //
NK065(cu)001:2939: gsum pa dbye na drug gi /
NK065(cu)001:2940: dang po 'jug sgo la gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:2942: rig pa'i rtsal dbang la sogs pas smin par byas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:2943: gnyis pa bya ba'i 'jug sgo ni /
NK065(cu)001:2944: ci yang 'jug tu med pa'i sgo nas 'jug ste /
NK065(cu)001:2946: chos la bya ru med pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:2947: rtsol ba med pa'i sgo nas 'jug /
NK065(cu)001:2950: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK065(cu)001:2951: thig le chen po chos kyi sku rang byung gi
NK065(cu)001:2952: ye shes chen po'i ngo bor bya rtsol med par
NK065(cu)001:2953: ye nas sangs rgyas par 'dod de /
NK065(cu)001:2955: rang byung ye shes rtsol med las //
NK065(cu)001:2956: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK065(cu)001:2959: rang byung ye shes mi rtog kun tu ji bzhin gnas //
NK065(cu)001:2962: med pa dang phyal ba la sogs pa'i dam tshig las mi 'da' bar bya ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:2964: a ti yo ga'i dam tshig ni //
NK065(cu)001:2965: med pa dang ni phyal ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:2966: gcig pu dang ni lhun gyis grub //
NK065(cu)001:2967: de yi don las 'da' mi bya //
NK065(cu)001:2970: a ti bkod pa chen po las /
NK065(cu)001:2971: yid can rnams la sems kyi sde //
NK065(cu)001:2972: nam mkha' can la klong gi sde //
NK065(cu)001:2973: rim rtsol bral la man ngag sde //
NK065(cu)001:2975: rig stong chos sku'i ngang du 'jog pa sems sde /
NK065(cu)001:2976: chos nyid bya rtsol med pa'i ngang du 'jog pa klong sde /
NK065(cu)001:2977: ye grol spang blang bral ba'i chos nyid kyi ngang du 'jog pa man ngag sde'o //
NK065(cu)001:2978: de'ang spyir rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs kyi bsgom pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:2982: nyams blangs khregs chod thod rgal lo //
NK065(cu)001:2985: ka dag gi lta ba'i ngang las ma g.yos par 'jog pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:2987: lhun gyi gnas pas bzhag pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:2989: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK065(cu)001:2990: sems kyi rang bzhin ye nas bud+d+ha ste //
NK065(cu)001:2991: sems la skye 'gag med pa nam mkha' 'dra //
NK065(cu)001:2992: chos kun mnyam nyid yang dag don rtogs nas //
NK065(cu)001:2993: de nyid ma btsal bzhag na bsgom pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:2994: zhes a ti zab don snying por gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:2995: de ltar bsgoms pas lam gyi bskyed rim bzhi ste /
NK065(cu)001:2996: gnas dang mi g.yo mnyam nyid lhun gyis grub //
NK065(cu)001:2999: gnad drug la brten nas snang bzhi rim par 'char ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:3003: chos nyid zad pa'i snang bas mthar phyin pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3005: cir snang chos nyid kyi rol par shar bas blang dor med par spyod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3007: bya ba med bas las rnams zin //
NK065(cu)001:3010: a ti yo ga'i spyod pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:3011: lta sgom srog dang ldan pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:3012: shugs las byung ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:3013: ji ltar smyon pa'i spyod pa bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:3014: gang la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK065(cu)001:3017: lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i sa la da lta nyid nas gnas pa mthar phyin pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3018: gding bzhi tshad du phyin pas 'khor ba myang 'das su grol ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:3021: rdzogs chen a ti'i 'bras bu ni //
NK065(cu)001:3022: gdod nas snying po byang chub tu //
NK065(cu)001:3023: thob med 'bras bu rang la smin //
NK065(cu)001:3026: gong ma rnams kyi bzhed gzhung dgod pa /
NK065(cu)001:3027: de dag gi dgongs pa la brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:3028: rang gi rtogs pa brjod pa dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:3030: dgongs pa mi mthun pa mang ste /
NK065(cu)001:3032: man ngag rdzogs pa chen por bkral ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:3033: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo gar bkral ba'i lugs gnyis su 'du ba las /
NK065(cu)001:3035: slob dpon nyi 'od seng ge dang kun mkhyen chos rje'i dgongs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3037: rgyud 'di'i gnas skabs su rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rang bzhin las /
NK065(cu)001:3038: gang yang dbyer med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3040: ston pa po so sor ma phye ste /
NK065(cu)001:3045: 'grel ba 'dir rgyud don phal cher brjod bya'i tshig re'ang ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK065(cu)001:3046: a ti yo ga'i dbang du byas nas 'grel tshul gnyis gnyis snang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:3048: rdzogs chen la'ang bskyed rdzogs gnyis med sems dang ye
NK065(cu)001:3049: shes rang snang ba'i dkyil 'khor du bstan pa dang
NK065(cu)001:3050: / bskyed pa dang rdzogs pa la mi ltos par
NK065(cu)001:3051: sems nyid ye sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du bstan
NK065(cu)001:3052: / pa dang / ye shes rang snang ba'i ngo
NK065(cu)001:3053: bor sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du bstan pa gsum
NK065(cu)001:3054: / pa dang / las / 'dir dang po nyid do zhes bzhed /
NK065(cu)001:3059: zur ba'i bka' srol 'dzin pa phal che ba'i dgongs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3060: de'ang sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim che chung la sogs par ma h+aa ltar bkral zhing /
NK065(cu)001:3061: gnubs kyi rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan gyi 'grel
NK065(cu)001:3062: bar ma h+aa'i 'dod gzhung 'chad pa'i tshe'ang rgyud 'di
NK065(cu)001:3063: la brten nas bshad pa mdzad la /
NK065(cu)001:3064: slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje ni /
NK065(cu)001:3065: ma h+aa la pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum du phye ba las /
NK065(cu)001:3066: de gsum ka'i spyi rgyud du bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:3068: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:3069: dpal bde ba'i mchog la sogs pa shes rab rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:3070: dpal sangs rgyas 'byung ba la sogs pa ma ning gi rgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:3071: de las dpal gsang ba'i snying po 'di ni /
NK065(cu)001:3072: thams cad kyi don dang rgyu 'bras tshang bar 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3073: rgyud thams cad kyi spyi yin par gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:3075: rje sgro phug pa dang sgrol g.yung rnam gnyis kyi khog dbub las kyang de ltar 'byung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:3077: rdzogs pa ston du rung yang bskyed pa'i rim pa shas che bas ma h+aa yo ga ste /
NK065(cu)001:3080: ma h+aa yo ga la gsum du phye ba'i gnyis med kyi rgyud du bzhed /
NK065(cu)001:3084: rgya che ba gnyis su med par ston pa'i phyir gnyis med do gsung /
NK065(cu)001:3086: lta phreng ltar rnal 'byor chen po'i tshul la'ang gsum du phye ba'i 'di ma h+aa'i a ti'o gsung /
NK065(cu)001:3087: de ltar na 'grel ba nyi seng gis a tir bkral ba'ang der 'gyur ram snyam te /
NK065(cu)001:3088: de dang lta phreng gi a tir 'jog pa'i dgongs pa shas cher mthun pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3090: a ti dang ma h+aar 'dod pa'i phyogs gnyis la log rtog bsal ba /
NK065(cu)001:3091: nang tshan gyi dbye ba phra mos spyi'i lus kyi
NK065(cu)001:3092: dbye ba phye na thug med du 'gyur bar bstan
NK065(cu)001:3094: gong ma rnams kyi a tir bkral ba phal cher
NK065(cu)001:3095: ma h+aa'i nang gses kyi gsum du phye ba la
NK065(cu)001:3096: dgongs pa'am / yang na sher phyin sngags lugs su
NK065(cu)001:3097: bkral ba ltar ma h+aa'i gzhung a ti'i lugs su
NK065(cu)001:3099: gzhan du rgyud lung man ngag gsum spyi'i dbye bas
NK065(cu)001:3100: phye ba'i a tir bzhed pa'o snyam du rtogs na
NK065(cu)001:3101: mi rigs te / rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan las /
NK065(cu)001:3103: rang rig pa gnyis su med pa de bzhin nyid kyi ngang du gsal ba la /
NK065(cu)001:3104: snang na snang du zad de phung po khams dang
NK065(cu)001:3105: skye mched lha'i dkyil 'khor lags pa'i don de las
NK065(cu)001:3109: de bzhin nyid du gnyis su med pa la //
NK065(cu)001:3110: skur byed don byed rtsol ba bcug pas nor //
NK065(cu)001:3111: bya med ting 'dzin don la nam yang reg mi nus //
NK065(cu)001:3112: de phyir lhun grub rgyal po nga nyid gcig pur byung //
NK065(cu)001:3116: thabs dang shes rab sgor zhugs nas //
NK065(cu)001:3117: rang rgyud dag pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK065(cu)001:3118: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis sgrub par byed //
NK065(cu)001:3119: a ti yo ga'i bde chen ni //
NK065(cu)001:3120: rtsol bsgrub 'das pa'i byang chub sems //
NK065(cu)001:3121: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs pas gnod pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:3122: so so'i bkol mdor smos pa ltar kyi a ti'i
NK065(cu)001:3123: sgos chos rnams kyang gzhung 'dis gtso bor mi ston
NK065(cu)001:3124: pa'i phyir dang / slob dpon brgya byin sdong po'i
NK065(cu)001:3125: mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel pa rgyud don rnams bshad las
NK065(cu)001:3126: pa'i phyir dang / kyang / gsang sngags kyi rgyud mtha' dag bsdu na /
NK065(cu)001:3128: mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:3134: de la bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum du phye ste /
NK065(cu)001:3135: dang po rgyud kyi rnams grangs bco brgyad du gsungs pa las /
NK065(cu)001:3136: zhes tan+t+ra bco brgyad po rgyud lung man ngag gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:3137: rgyud du gsungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:3138: bskyed rdzogs gsum mi yul du babs pas gnas tha dad par gsungs pa las /
NK065(cu)001:3139: ma h+aa ni rgyal po dzah'i khang steng du glegs bam dang bcas te babs par grags pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:3140: 'adi'ang der babs par bshad pa sogs kyis gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:3141: yang ma h+aa yo ga nyid du bzhed pa'i phyogs
NK065(cu)001:3142: kyi dgongs pa 'grel tshul la'ang brtag par bya ba
NK065(cu)001:3143: 'di yod de / spar khab las pha ma gnyis med kyi rgyud gsum ka'i spyir bzhed pa nyid /
NK065(cu)001:3144: gnyis med kyi rgyud kyi go don pha ma gnyis cha mnyam par ston pa la bzhag pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:3145: de gnyis kyi don tshang bar bstan pas gnyis med
NK065(cu)001:3146: kyi rgyud kyi don kyang bstan par 'gyur ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:3147: / che ba'i ngos nas de gsum gyi spyi rgyud ces smos pa las /
NK065(cu)001:3148: ngo bo gnyis med kyi rgyud yin par dgongs so zhes bshad na legs par mngon la /
NK065(cu)001:3149: gzhan du na rgyud thams cad kyi spyi zhes pa'ang /
NK065(cu)001:3150: nang rgyud sde gsum kho na'i spyi rgyud du bzhed pa ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:3152: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi /
NK065(cu)001:3155: lung gi spyi 'di shin tu zab pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:3158: lung gi spyi ru grags pa yi /
NK065(cu)001:3159: rnam par dbye ba lnga ru 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:3160: zhes sogs dang dgongs pa mthun pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3161: thams cad kyi don dang rgyu 'bras tshang bar 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3164: che ba'i ngos nas lung thams cad kyi spyi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3165: rang gi ngo bo gnyis med kyi rgyud du gzhag par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:3166: dper na gsang 'dus kyi rgyud nyid /
NK065(cu)001:3167: mdo sde dang rgyud sde thams cad kyi snod dang rtsa bar gsungs shing /
NK065(cu)001:3168: ngo bo pha rgyud du bzhed pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:3170: rgyud 'di ma h+aar 'dod pa mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:3171: lta phreng las bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi rdzogs pa chen po'i skabs su rgyud 'di dang sbyar nas /
NK065(cu)001:3172: rtog tshogs lhar dag tshul dang /
NK065(cu)001:3173: rtogs pa bzhi yi gtan tshigs dang /
NK065(cu)001:3174: mtshan nyid gsum sogs ston pas gnod pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:3176: lta phreng gi rdzogs pa chen po'i don ni /
NK065(cu)001:3177: ma h+aa la gsum du phye ba'i a ti yin
NK065(cu)001:3178: par nyang t+aika pa bzhed pa ltar 'chad pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:3179: dang / der bzhag pa'i rdzogs chen gyi don de
NK065(cu)001:3180: dag shas cher 'dus pa sogs las kyang ston pa'i
NK065(cu)001:3181: dang / phyir dang / lta phreng ni ma h+aa'i
NK065(cu)001:3182: grol lam cig car ston pa'i gzhung du rje sgro
NK065(cu)001:3183: phug bzhed par grags shing grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:3185: ma h+aa la nang gses kyi bskyed rdzogs gsum du phye ba de 'dra mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:3186: de ltar 'byed rigs pa'i tshad ma med pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:3188: kun khyab kyi tshad ma gsum gyis 'grub pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3191: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3194: dbang sgyur thabs kyi theg pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:3195: yul gyis rnam par gsum snang ste //
NK065(cu)001:3196: bskyed dang rdzogs dang yongs su rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:3199: bde 'dus sgrub pa lung gi bka' 'go las /
NK065(cu)001:3200: yo ga rnam gsum la dgu dgur bka' stsal ba'i /
NK065(cu)001:3201: ma h+aa'i ma h+aa ni lha'i dkyil 'khor rim pas bskyed pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3202: ma h+aa'i a nu ni rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3203: ma h+aa'i a ti ni don dam ngo bo ma skyes pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3205: gsang sngags bka'i lde mig las kyang gsang sngags thams cad rgyud lung man ngag gsum du phye /
NK065(cu)001:3206: de re re la'ang gsum gsum dgur phye ste /
NK065(cu)001:3212: rgyud 'dir bstan gyi a nu a ti dang /
NK065(cu)001:3214: de dang de'i nang gses kyi a nu dang a tir bzhag dgos te /
NK065(cu)001:3215: gzhan du 'og mas gong ma'i don mi mthong bar
NK065(cu)001:3216: bzhed pa'i bstan pa spyi skad kyi phyag rgya las
NK065(cu)001:3218: gsang sngags phyi 'gyur ba la grags pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:3221: gnyis med kyi rgyud dus 'khor la sogs pa de dag kyang /
NK065(cu)001:3222: snga 'gyur rang skad kyi ma h+aa la gsum du
NK065(cu)001:3223: phye ba'i ma rgyud sogs ma yin no zhes 'dod
NK065(cu)001:3226: dus 'khor sogs a tir thal ba bzlog tu med do //
NK065(cu)001:3228: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa /
NK065(cu)001:3229: zhes pa'i skabs kyi 'grel chung bin tar+thara /
NK065(cu)001:3230: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub dang //
NK065(cu)001:3231: bya ba'i rgyud dang gnyis ka'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3232: rnal 'byor bskyed dang rdzogs pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:3233: rnam thar brgyad phyir rta babs brgyad //
NK065(cu)001:3234: ces rdzogs pa man chad bgrod nas thob bya don gyis rdzogs chen du bshad pa'ang /
NK065(cu)001:3235: ma h+aa'i rdzogs chen rgyud 'di nyid la dgongs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:3237: lta sgom spyod pa sogs la mi 'dra ba'i khyad
NK065(cu)001:3238: par sngar smos pa ltar bskyed rdzogs gsum ka la
NK065(cu)001:3239: yod pa'i phyir / de rnams gang gtso bor ston pa'i sgo nas dbye bar bya bar yin gyi /
NK065(cu)001:3240: phyogs re nas bzung ste bskyed rdzogs gsum spyi'i lus
NK065(cu)001:3241: kyi dbye ba phye na thug med du 'gyur te
NK065(cu)001:3242: / bskyed rdzogs gsum 'gal ba ma yin pa'i gnad
NK065(cu)001:3243: kyis bka' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba lta bu gcig gi
NK065(cu)001:3244: nang du'ang de gsum ka tshang bar nges pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:3245: / / de ltar yang bdud rtsi bam brgyad las /
NK065(cu)001:3246: rgyud dang lung dang man ngag gsum //
NK065(cu)001:3247: dmangs dang rje dang rgyal po'i tshul //
NK065(cu)001:3248: gcig la gcig brten gcig gi ngang //
NK065(cu)001:3250: gsum pa rang gi rtogs pa brjod pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:3251: rgyud gzhung 'di nyid ma h+aa yo ga la gsum
NK065(cu)001:3252: du phye ba'i gnyis med kyi rgyud du ngos bzung
NK065(cu)001:3255: khyad par ci zhig yod ce na /
NK065(cu)001:3258: khyad par bstan pa gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:3260: dur khrod bde ba'i dpe chung rang gnas las /
NK065(cu)001:3261: thabs dang shes rab ma ning rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3262: bstan pa'i yig lam rkyen du gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:3263: zhes pa'i 'grel bar bi ma las /
NK065(cu)001:3265: de b+ai dz+aa la sogs shes rab kyi rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:3266: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa la sogs pa rnal 'byor thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:3267: dpal gsang ba'i snying po sogs ma ning gi rgyud
NK065(cu)001:3268: yi ger bkod pa dag ni ngo bo'i rkyen du
NK065(cu)001:3270: bde 'dus gsang sngags bka'i lde mig tu rgyud lung
NK065(cu)001:3271: man ngag gsum dgu phrugs su phye ba'i skabs su
NK065(cu)001:3274: sems dang ye shes rang snang dbyer med gsang ba'i snying po la rgyas 'bring lnga ste /
NK065(cu)001:3281: de la bskyed pa'i tshul ni /
NK065(cu)001:3282: ting 'dzin rnam gsum rim gyis bskyed nas /
NK065(cu)001:3283: dkyil 'khor rim gyis bkod cing bsgoms pas 'grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3285: don dam par skye 'gag med pa'i lha dang lha mo dang /
NK065(cu)001:3286: rnam par mi rtog pa'i don dbu ma chos kyi dbyings las kyang ma g.yos la /
NK065(cu)001:3287: kun rdzob tu 'phags pa'i gzugs kyi sku yang gsal
NK065(cu)001:3288: bar bsgom zhing mnyam la ma 'dres par bsgoms pas
NK065(cu)001:3289: 'grub pa'o // rdzogs pa chen po'i tshul ni /
NK065(cu)001:3290: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK065(cu)001:3291: cad dbyer med par sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK065(cu)001:3292: rang bzhin ye nas yin par rtogs nas bsgom pa
NK065(cu)001:3294: 'dir chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis dkyil 'khor du
NK065(cu)001:3295: rtogs nas bsgom pa gtso bor ston pa'i phyir dang
NK065(cu)001:3297: gsang dbang gi lam thabs lam sna tshogs gtso bor ston pa pha rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3298: shes rab ye shes kyi lam 'og sgo las rgya'i rnal 'byor gtso bor ston pa ma rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3299: dbang bzhi pa'i lam rdzogs pa chen po gtso bor
NK065(cu)001:3300: ston pa gnyis med kyi rgyud du bzhed pa las
NK065(cu)001:3301: / 'dir thabs lam steng 'og gi sgo gnyis kyang cha snyoms par ston cing /
NK065(cu)001:3302: khyad par dbang bzhi pa'i lam gtso bor ston pa'i phyir gnyis med kyi rgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:3304: thabs kyi de kho nyid rgya che ba gtso bor ston pa pha rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3305: shes rab kyi de nyid zab pa gtso bor ston pa ma rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:3306: 'dir dbang dang phrin sgrub sogs rgya che ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:3307: rdzogs rim sogs zab lam dag gnyis su med par ston pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:3308: lha rnams kyi rnam pa'ang cha lugs kyi khyad par
NK065(cu)001:3309: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du pha rgyud ltar ston kyang
NK065(cu)001:3310: / khro dkyil du ma rgyud ltar ston pa'i phyir gnyis med kyi rgyud du gzhag par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:3311: gsum pa rjod byed rgyud kyi khyad par la phyi nang gi rgyud sde spyir bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3312: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3314: kri ya'i rgyud la spyi bye brag gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:3321: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i rigs gsum dang /
NK065(cu)001:3322: 'jig rten pa'i rigs la nor bu'i /
NK065(cu)001:3327: rigs drug gi so so'i rgyud mang du bzhugs pa rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3331: rjo rje sa 'og gi rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3333: rtsa rgyud de nyid bsdus pa /
NK065(cu)001:3334: bshad rgyud rtse mo dang dpal mchog /
NK065(cu)001:3335: cha mthun gyi rgyud spyod rgyud la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3341: ma h+aa ni spyir tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad las kha cig ma gtogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3344: sku 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs gnyis med kyi rgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:3349: sems lung chen mo ste mdo bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3350: dems su grags pa spyi mdo dgongs 'dus la sogs pa rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3354: sems sde ma bu bco brgyad sogs sems sde /
NK065(cu)001:3355: ye shes gsang ba sogs klong sde /
NK065(cu)001:3356: rgyud bcu 'dun la sogs pa man ngag gi sde'o //
NK065(cu)001:3358: bka' brgyad spyi sgos kyi rgyud rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3360: rgyud kyi mtshan gzhi'i dbye ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:3361: de dag gi yan lag rtsi tshul lo //
NK065(cu)001:3365: bshad rgyud sde bzhir dbyer bar mdzad de /
NK065(cu)001:3367: sems dang ye shes rang snang du ston pa rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba snying po /
NK065(cu)001:3368: rol pa mngon par brjod pa lha mo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK065(cu)001:3369: dkyil 'khor rdzogs par ston pa sgyu 'phrul brgyad pa /
NK065(cu)001:3370: phrin las rdzogs par ston pa bzhi bcu pa /
NK065(cu)001:3371: dbang gtso bor ston pa bla ma /
NK065(cu)001:3372: yon tan mthar phyin par ston pa brgyad cu pa /
NK065(cu)001:3373: sde snod yongs la khyab par ston pa 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa /
NK065(cu)001:3374: dam tshig mchog tu ston pa le lag dang brgyad do //
NK065(cu)001:3376: grol lam rim cig car du ston pa ye shes snying po dang /
NK065(cu)001:3378: thabs lam rim cig car du ston pa rgya mtsho dang /
NK065(cu)001:3381: rol pa chen po bshad rgyud bzhi'i gras su bgrangs nas /
NK065(cu)001:3382: ye shes snying po de bzhi ga'i bsdus rgyud du bzhed /
NK065(cu)001:3386: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rang snang dbyer med
NK065(cu)001:3387: du ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa
NK065(cu)001:3388: ba / las tshogs rgyas par ston pa rnam par snang mdzad sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK065(cu)001:3389: sde snod yongs la khyab par ston pa 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa /
NK065(cu)001:3390: rol pa mngon par brjod pa lha mo sgyu d+r+wa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3391: rdor sems sgyu d+r+wa la'ang nang gses kyi dbye na /
NK065(cu)001:3393: bshad rgyud sde brgyad du bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:3394: gzhan yang rdo rje gsang ba'i snying po dang /
NK065(cu)001:3396: khro bo stobs kyi rgyud sogs rgyud phran mang du bzhugs shing /
NK065(cu)001:3397: spyir rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba la
NK065(cu)001:3398: rgya gar la le'u 'bum phrag gcig bzhugs par grags
NK065(cu)001:3400: yan lag bdun ldan du dbye ba de rtsa bshad gnyis su bsdu ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:3402: he ru ka gal po las /
NK065(cu)001:3403: rtsa ba'i rgyud dang bshad pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3404: phyi ma phyi mar gyur pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:3405: ma tshang kha skong dka' ba gcod //
NK065(cu)001:3406: kalpa rtog pa dum bu rnams //
NK065(cu)001:3408: khyad par gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK065(cu)001:3411: thog mar byung zhing bshad gzhir gyur pa ni rtsa rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3414: 'khrugs pa sdebs pa la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid can ni bshad pa'i rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3415: rgyud snga mar gab pa mngon du phyung ba ni rgyud phyi ma /
NK065(cu)001:3416: der yang mi gsal ba gsal bar byed pa phyir ma'i phyi ma /
NK065(cu)001:3417: ma tshang ba logs su gsungs pa kha skong gi rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3418: dka' ba logs su bkral ba dka' ba gcod ba /
NK065(cu)001:3419: rtsa bshad nas logs su phyung ba kalpa dum bu'i rgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:3421: rtsa ba'i rgyud ni le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis pa 'adi'o //
NK065(cu)001:3423: bshad rgyud sde bzhi la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3425: glegs bam de nyid kyi phyi ma ni rtsa rgyud
NK065(cu)001:3426: kyi phyi ma le'u nyer gsum pa dang nyer bzhi
NK065(cu)001:3427: pa lta bu / glegs bam gzhan gyi phyi ma ni rgyas pa'i phyi ma dang /
NK065(cu)001:3428: phyi ma'i phyi ma lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3429: de dag ni phyima'ang yin la bshad rgyud kyang yin no //
NK065(cu)001:3430: ma tshang ba kha skong gi rgyud ni /
NK065(cu)001:3436: phyi ma ni kalpa dum bu'i rgyud kyang yin no //
NK065(cu)001:3438: snying po'i phyi ma dang khro bo stobs po che'i rgyud lta bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:3440: de dag kyang rtsa ba'i rgyud ni le'u nyer gnyis pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3441: gzhan thams cad bshad rgyud du bsdu'o //
NK065(cu)001:3442: de gnyis po'i khyad par gyi mtshan nyid la /
NK065(cu)001:3443: snga rabs pa rnams dgongs pa mi mthun te /
NK065(cu)001:3445: brjod bya mi gsal ba mun pa ltar gnas pa ni rtsa rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3446: gsal byed snang ba ltar ston pa ni bshad rgyud do gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:3448: snang mun dang mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3449: rtsa bshad gnyis phan tshun 'gal bar thal bas mi 'thad do //
NK065(cu)001:3450: yang zur lugs pa phal cher /
NK065(cu)001:3451: ston pa'i bdag nyid kyis gsungs pa rtsa rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3452: 'chad pa'i skyes bus gsungs pa bshad rgyud do gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:3453: de ltar na brgyad cu pa sogs kyang rtsa rgyud du 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:3454: rgyud gsungs pa'i gleng gzhi rtsa rgyud dang tshig don khyad par med pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:3455: spar khab tu rtsa rgyud nyid kyang 'chad pa'i skyes bus gsungs par bzhed pas gnod do //
NK065(cu)001:3456: yang nyang t+aika pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:3457: gzhung gzhan la ma brten par don gzhan bskyed nus pa rtsa rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3458: rgyud kyis rgyud kyi don 'grol bar byed pa bshad rgyud do gsungs pa mi 'thad do //
NK065(cu)001:3459: dang po ltar na rim gyis 'jug pa dag lam
NK065(cu)001:3460: stegs kyi theg pa gzhan la brten mi dgos par
NK065(cu)001:3461: thal / 'di nyid kyis bskyed nus pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3463: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:3464: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK065(cu)001:3466: gnyis pa ltar na rtsa ba'i rgyud 'di nyid kyang bshad rgyud du 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:3470: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK065(cu)001:3471: zhes sogs kyis bkral ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:3472: rog bde gshegs chen po ni /
NK065(cu)001:3473: thog mar byung zhing bshad gzhir gyur pa ni rtsa rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:3474: rjes la byung zhing 'chad byed du gyur pa'i rgyud
NK065(cu)001:3475: kyi dngos po gzhan du grub pa ni bshad rgyud
NK065(cu)001:3476: ces gsungs te / legs par dgongs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3477: de ltar yang dur khrod rmad byung gi rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:3478: thog mar gsungs pa rtsa ba'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3479: phyis nas gsungs pa bshad pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3480: mdo tsam brjod pa rtsa ba la //
NK065(cu)001:3481: gsal bar byed pa bshad pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:3488: lta ba khyad par 'phags pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:3489: rdzogs pa chen po mchog go lo //
NK065(cu)001:3490: sngags kyi khyad chos blta ba min //
NK065(cu)001:3491: dbu ma las lhag ga la yod //
NK065(cu)001:3494: theg chen thams cad blta ba spros bral du 'dod pa'i phyir zer ram /
NK065(cu)001:3495: dbu ma dang sngags gnyis lta ba spros bral du 'dod par gcig pa'i phyir zer /
NK065(cu)001:3497: dbu sems gnyis kyang lta ba khyad med du 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:3498: gnyis ka theg chen du bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3500: sems tsam pa spros bral du mi 'dod pas gsal /
NK065(cu)001:3502: don dam spros bral dang kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam
NK065(cu)001:3503: du blta bar mthun na'ang de tsam gyis sngags kyi
NK065(cu)001:3504: lta ba gtan la phebs pa ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:3506: bden gnyis dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin can du 'dod pas /
NK065(cu)001:3507: de'i mthus kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid can de
NK065(cu)001:3508: dag kyang yongs su dag pa'i lha'i mtshan nyid du
NK065(cu)001:3510: des na khyed cag sngags la dbu ma las 'phags pa'i lta ba mi 'dod pa mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:3512: chos nyid sangs rgyas yin na /
NK065(cu)001:3513: chos can sangs rgyas ma yin pa mi rung ste /
NK065(cu)001:3514: chos can gyi ngo bo chos nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3515: zhes 'khor 'das dbyer med kyi lta ba khas len pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3517: sngags kyi kun rdzob lhar snang ba de dag chos can /
NK065(cu)001:3518: don dam la dmigs pa'i lta ba ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:3519: kun rdzob la dmigs pa'i sgom pa yin pa'i phyir zer na /
NK065(cu)001:3520: kun rdzob lta ba'i dmigs yul du mi 'dod pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:3521: bden gnyis la bzang ngan blang dor du blta ba mdo'i lugs yin la /
NK065(cu)001:3522: sngags su bden gnyis kyi skya bar nas mi 'don bar mnyam pa'i lta ba khas len pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3523: sgom pa yin pa lta ba min pa sogs lta sgom 'gal bar 'dzin pa yang mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:3524: lta ba gtan la phab nas rtogs don sgom bar mkhas grub kun la grags pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:3525: gal te phung khams sogs gzod nas lhar dag par
NK065(cu)001:3526: gsungs pa ltar rtogs pa gnas lugs kyi lta ba
NK065(cu)001:3529: der sgro btags te sgom pa yin na logs pa'i lta sgom du 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3531: bong ba gser du bsgom pa la ji tsam 'bad kyang der mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:3532: de'i phyir lta ba la khyad par yod par grub la /
NK065(cu)001:3533: de ltar grub pa nyid kyis /
NK065(cu)001:3534: de rtogs byed theg pa'i rim pa la'ang khyad par yod par dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3535: theg rim dgu ka la lta ba so sor snang zhing /
NK065(cu)001:3536: kun gyi rtse mo mchog tu gyur pa ni a ti yo ga ste /
NK065(cu)001:3538: mchog go lo zhes ma rangs pa'i tshig gis bsnyad pa ni bla col tsam du zad de /
NK065(cu)001:3540: de la kha cig na re /
NK065(cu)001:3543: sangs rgyas sa la bzhi pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3544: lnga pa thub pa'i dgongs pa min //
NK065(cu)001:3545: zhes pas theg pa bzhi pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3546: grub mtha' lnga ba med par gsungs pas theg pa ni gsum kho nar nges pa'i phyir zer /
NK065(cu)001:3549: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK065(cu)001:3550: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK065(cu)001:3551: zhes bzhir phye ba'ang mi 'thad par thal /
NK065(cu)001:3552: gsum kho nar nges pa'i phyir byas pa la /
NK065(cu)001:3554: gsum du phye ba ni nyan rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa gsum yin la /
NK065(cu)001:3555: de'i phyi ma la rgyu 'bras gnyis su phye nas bzhir gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3556: dbye bsdu'i khyad tsam ste skyon med do zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:3557: de 'dra rim dgu la'ang mtshungs te /
NK065(cu)001:3558: phyi nang gi rgyud sde drug po 'bras theg tu 'du la /
NK065(cu)001:3559: de'ang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'i nang du 'du bas 'dir yang dbye bsdu'i khyad do //
NK065(cu)001:3560: gal te lha mi'i theg pa ma 'dus so zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:3562: lha mi'i theg pa ni mngon mtho'i theg pa yin la /
NK065(cu)001:3563: rdo rje snying 'grel las gsum du bsdus pa ni
NK065(cu)001:3564: rnam grol gyi theg pa la dgongs pa'i phyir ro
NK065(cu)001:3565: // de bas na khyed cag theg pa gsum kho nar zhen pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:3567: theg pa bsam gyis mi khyab par gsungs pa sogs kyi don la rmongs par zad do //
NK065(cu)001:3568: gzhan yang phyi 'gyur gyi rgyud sde rnams su a
NK065(cu)001:3569: nu dang a ti'i chos skad ma byung ba rgyu
NK065(cu)001:3571: 'gog pa ni smad mi mkhas kyi bstod sgrar 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:3572: rgyal bas gdul bya la ltos nas gsung rab la
NK065(cu)001:3573: mchog dman mdzad pa'i 'og ma 'og ma'i nang du
NK065(cu)001:3574: gong ma gong ma'i chos skad dang bshad pa rgyas
NK065(cu)001:3575: par mi 'byung ba spyi lugs yin pa'i phyir te
NK065(cu)001:3576: / dper na nyan thos kyi sde snod du phar theg dang /
NK065(cu)001:3577: de'i nang du sngags phyi rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:3578: de dag tu gsang bde sogs kyi chos skad mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:3579: de'i phyir gsang bde sogs su a nu dang a
NK065(cu)001:3580: ti'i chos skad dang bshad pa rgyas par mi 'byung
NK065(cu)001:3581: ba nyid kyis rdzogs pa chen po ni theg pa
NK065(cu)001:3582: kun gyi rtse mor grub pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:3585: rnam gzhag spyir bstan pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3586: bye brag rgyud 'di'i dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos ngos gzung ba gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3592: gtso bor bstan bcos rtsom pa'i bsam pas kun nas
NK065(cu)001:3593: bslang ste rang gi zhe 'dod kyi grub mtha' gzhan
NK065(cu)001:3594: la brtan pa'i phyir bsdebs pa'i lung chos gang zhig
NK065(cu)001:3595: / khyad chos gsum dang ldan pa bstan bcos rnam dag gi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3596: de gsum gang rung dang bral ba ltar snang gi mtshan nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:3598: rgyal ba'i bka' la brten nas de'i dgongs 'grel du byas pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3599: rtsom pa po rnam g.yeng med pa'i yid can gyis bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3600: byed las thar ba thob pa'i lam dang rjes su mthun pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3602: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gi /
NK065(cu)001:3603: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK065(cu)001:3604: thar ba thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK065(cu)001:3605: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blang //
NK065(cu)001:3610: t+r+aa ya skyob pa la 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3611: 'chos skyob kyi yon tan gnyis dang ldan pas na bstan bcos te /
NK065(cu)001:3613: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:3614: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyob byed gang yin pa //
NK065(cu)001:3615: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK065(cu)001:3616: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK065(cu)001:3619: mchog dman gyi sgo nas dang /
NK065(cu)001:3621: rtsom byed gang zag gi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3622: ji ltar brtsam tshul gyi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3624: bshad bya bka'i sgo nas dbye ba dang drug /
NK065(cu)001:3626: bde 'dus kyis gcod tshoms kyi chings las /
NK065(cu)001:3627: bstan bcos don med don dman dang //
NK065(cu)001:3628: don log don ldan bzhir shes bya //
NK065(cu)001:3630: don med par bya rog so brtag gi bstan bcos lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3631: don dman pa thun mong gi rig gnas bzhi'i bstan bcos lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3632: don log pa phyi rol pa'i bstan bcos lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3633: don dang ldan pa sangs rgyas pa'i nang rig pa'i bstan bcos lta bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:3634: sa sde las dgur bshad de /
NK065(cu)001:3636: don med don log don dang ldan //
NK065(cu)001:3637: ngan g.yon brtse bral sdug bsngal spong //
NK065(cu)001:3638: thos rtsod bsgrub pa lhur len pa //
NK065(cu)001:3639: bstan bcos rnam pa dgu yin no //
NK065(cu)001:3641: snga ma gnyis gnyis ltar snang dang /
NK065(cu)001:3642: phyi ma re re bstan bcos yang dag go //
NK065(cu)001:3644: bka'i don rgya chen po sdud pa'i /
NK065(cu)001:3646: zab mo rnam par 'byed pa'i bstan bcos gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:3650: bi ma la'i thugs thig lta bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:3652: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa la bstan bcos su byas
NK065(cu)001:3653: pa rdo rje chos kyis mdzad pa'i bde 'dus kyi
NK065(cu)001:3654: lung lnga dang / byams pa'i chos lnga lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3655: dgra bcom pas gsungs pa la bstan bcos su byas pa mngon pa sde bdun lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3656: sa non pa'i byang 'phags kyis brtsam pa la bstan
NK065(cu)001:3657: bcos su byas pa slob dpon chen po pad+ma dang
NK065(cu)001:3658: 'od 'phro'i sa la bzhugs pa gnubs chen gyi bstan
NK065(cu)001:3659: bcos lta bu / yi dam lha'i lung bstan thob
NK065(cu)001:3660: nas brtsam pa la bstan bcos su byas pa sgeg
NK065(cu)001:3661: rdor dang phyogs glang gi bstan bcos lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3662: rang gi grub mtha' la zlos shing gzhan gyi grub
NK065(cu)001:3663: mtha' sun 'byin pa la mkhas pa'i skye bos brtsam
NK065(cu)001:3664: pa thugs sras ka ba bzhi'i bstan bcos lta bu'o
NK065(cu)001:3666: bka' nyid la 'grel bar btab pa'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:3667: bka'i don rang rgyud du brtsam pa'i bstan bcos gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:3668: rim bzhin 'grel pa spar khab dang /
NK065(cu)001:3669: kun mkhyen chen po'i sems nyid ngal bso lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:3673: thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa thob pa'i thabs ston pa'i bstan bcos gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:3679: sngags kyi dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3681: mdzod dang mdo rtsa lta bu 'khor lo dang po'i /
NK065(cu)001:3682: dbu ma rigs tshogs lta bu 'khor lo bar pa'i /
NK065(cu)001:3683: rgyud bla dang klu sgrub kyi bstod tshogs lta bu
NK065(cu)001:3684: 'khor lo gsum pa'i dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos rnams
NK065(cu)001:3686: phyi nang gi rgyud sde drug gi dgongs pa 'grel par byed pa'i bstan bcos rnams te /
NK065(cu)001:3689: rgyud spyi la 'jug pa'i man ngag dang /
NK065(cu)001:3690: rgyud gnas skabs la 'jug pa'i man ngag gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3692: thos bsam gyi shes rab la brten te rgyud drang
NK065(cu)001:3693: thad du gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i man ngag
NK065(cu)001:3699: bi ma la'i khog gzhung gsal sgron la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3701: rtsa rgyud la sgeg pa'i rin po che'i spar khab /
NK065(cu)001:3703: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rnam dbye 'grel /
NK065(cu)001:3705: bi ma la'i 'grel chung bin tar+tha /
NK065(cu)001:3706: tsan+d+ra go mi'i rgya mdud 'grel rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3707: bshad rgyud la bi ma las mdzad pa'i bla ma'i 'grel pa mun sel /
NK065(cu)001:3709: brgyad cu pa'i bsdus 'grel la sogs pa rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3711: bsgom pa'i shes rab la gtso bor brten nas rgyud
NK065(cu)001:3712: mngon rtogs su bslab cing nyams su len pa'i man
NK065(cu)001:3713: ngag ste / yongs shes kyi dngos po kha yar bstod pa phra mo'i skor ro //
NK065(cu)001:3715: dang po lta ba gtso bor ston pa'i man ngag ni /
NK065(cu)001:3718: bi ma la'i shes rab spyan 'byed sgron me'i skor /
NK065(cu)001:3720: dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3721: gnyis pa spyod pa gtso bor ston pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:3723: rdo rje 'jam mgon la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3725: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rdo rje las rim gnyis kyi stod dang /
NK065(cu)001:3727: bi ma la'i thig gi bin tar+tha la sogs pas ston no //
NK065(cu)001:3729: rdo rje las rim gnyis kyi smad dang /
NK065(cu)001:3732: thigs pa gsum la sogs pas ston no //
NK065(cu)001:3733: lnga pa dam tshig gi sgeg pa'i gsal bkra dang /
NK065(cu)001:3734: phra rgyas la sogs pas ston no //
NK065(cu)001:3736: bi ma la'i sbyin sreg dang ro sreg /
NK065(cu)001:3738: dur khrod bde ba'i dpe chung rang gnas la sogs pas ston no //
NK065(cu)001:3740: thun mong gi sgrub pa rgyud las mang du gsungs mod kyi /
NK065(cu)001:3741: de dag la man ngag gi yi ge zur bkol ma mthong ngo //
NK065(cu)001:3743: nges rdzogs sgom pa'i man ngag ni /
NK065(cu)001:3744: in+d+ra b+h+au ti'i lam rnam bkod dang rim pa gnyis pa /
NK065(cu)001:3745: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim che chung /
NK065(cu)001:3747: bi ma la'i rim gsum sogs bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka ston pa'i gzhung rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3748: mos sgom gyi man ngag ni /
NK065(cu)001:3749: bi ma'i 'od rim dang d+r+wa chen /
NK065(cu)001:3750: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i d+r+wa chung dang /
NK065(cu)001:3751: dam pa rgyan la sogs pas ston no //
NK065(cu)001:3753: bi ma la'i phyag rgya bsam gtan /
NK065(cu)001:3754: khro bo phyag rgya gcig pa /
NK065(cu)001:3756: phyag rgya bzhi pa'i bsam gtan la sogs pa mtshan bcas gtso bor ston pa'i man ngag dang /
NK065(cu)001:3757: spyod yul bzhi pa'i bsam gtan /
NK065(cu)001:3758: spyod yul sbyong ba'i bsam gtan sogs mtshan med gtso bor ston pa'i man ngag rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3761: dur khrod bde ba'i gtor chung /
NK065(cu)001:3765: bi ma la'i thab mchog dpag gis mi lang ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:3766: dbyig gi sgron ma la sogs pas ston no //
NK065(cu)001:3767: bcu pa sngags dang phyag rgya'i man ngag la /
NK065(cu)001:3768: yi ge zur ba med pas sgrub thabs kyi khongs nas ston pa yin gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:3769: de dag kyang mdo tsam brjod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3770: rgyas par rma 'gyur la phra mo drug cu rtsa bzhi yod par grags shing /
NK065(cu)001:3771: spyir 'grel bshad sgrub thabs phra mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3772: se ston rin chen rgyal mtshan gyis gzigs pa la'ang brgya re bzhi yod par gsungs la /
NK065(cu)001:3773: de rnams la rgyud sgrub thabs dang 'brel ba zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:3774: sgrub thabs lag len dang 'brel ba'i man ngag la phrin las shar sde brgyad de /
NK065(cu)001:3775: zhi ba dang khro bo gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3778: ro sreg dang sbyin sreg gnyis te brgyad do //
NK065(cu)001:3779: lnga pa skabs don ngos bzung ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:3780: de ltar bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:3781: 'dir gang bshad par bya ba'i dam chos ni /
NK065(cu)001:3782: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK065(cu)001:3783: de'i nang nas kyang rtsa ba'i rgyud gsang ba snying po ste /
NK065(cu)001:3784: bshad rgyud rnams la gtso bor brten cing /
NK065(cu)001:3785: dgongs 'grel man ngag rnams kyi legs cha blangs nas bshad par bya ba yin no //
NK065(cu)001:3786: gang bshad bya'i chos ngos bzung ba bshad zin to //
NK065(cu)001:3787: gnyis pa gang gis 'chad pa'i man ngag la /
NK065(cu)001:3788: rgyal bas gsungs pa'i rgyud bshad thabs dang /
NK065(cu)001:3789: de la brten te mdzad pa'i man ngag bshad thabs gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3791: spyir ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams rgyan bdun dang /
NK065(cu)001:3792: a nu rnams lung bdun dang /
NK065(cu)001:3793: a ti rnams spyi don drug gi sgo nas blo
NK065(cu)001:3794: kha dbye bar he ru ka gal por gsungs shing
NK065(cu)001:3795: / bla med kyi rgyud 'ga' zhig la ni /
NK065(cu)001:3797: rton pa bzhir bshad pa dag yod do //
NK065(cu)001:3800: bde 'dus kyi rgyud kyi spyi chings las /
NK065(cu)001:3801: bshad thabs man ngag nyi shul /
NK065(cu)001:3802: spyi sdoms lnga dang rgyud chings lnga //
NK065(cu)001:3803: lung sdoms lnga dang sgrub thabs kyi //
NK065(cu)001:3804: sbyor lugs lnga yis gtan la dbab //
NK065(cu)001:3806: de ltar bshad thabs kyi man ngag mtha' yas na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:3808: gzhan rnams btang snyoms su byas te /
NK065(cu)001:3810: spyi'i bshad thabs rgyan bdun dang /
NK065(cu)001:3811: khyad par 'di nyid kyi bka' srol spyi don lnga bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3814: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyan bdun yang //
NK065(cu)001:3815: gleng bslang ba dang sangs rgyas tshul //
NK065(cu)001:3816: rgyas bshad mtha' dang bshad pa'i tshul //
NK065(cu)001:3817: dbye ba'i rnam pa gang zag snod //
NK065(cu)001:3818: bden pa'i dgongs pa shes par bya //
NK065(cu)001:3819: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdun las /
NK065(cu)001:3825: gleng bslang ba yi grangs lnga ni //
NK065(cu)001:3826: rgyud 'di'i ming ni ci zhig yin //
NK065(cu)001:3827: rgyud 'di su zhig don du mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:3828: byed po ston pa su zhig yin //
NK065(cu)001:3829: rgyud 'di'i ldang tshad ji lta bu //
NK065(cu)001:3830: dgos pa ci zhig yod par shes //
NK065(cu)001:3832: gnyis pa lan la'ang lnga las /
NK065(cu)001:3834: 'di'i ming ni gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:3836: gdul bya dbang po rnon po 'dod chags can gtso
NK065(cu)001:3837: bor gyur pa'i dug lnga'i skye bo rnams 'dul ba'i
NK065(cu)001:3840: byed pa bo rigs drug pa kun tu bzang po'o //
NK065(cu)001:3843: cho ga de bzhin le'u dang //
NK065(cu)001:3844: rim par phye dang dum bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:3849: las gzhi'i phrin las sogs rgyas par ston /
NK065(cu)001:3852: thun mong gi sgrub pa rnams mdo tsam /
NK065(cu)001:3855: gnas lung rnams cha mthun gyi rgyud gzhan las kha bskang ste man ngag tu bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:3856: le'u ni nyi shu rtsa gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:3857: phyi ma dang bcas na nyi shu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK065(cu)001:3861: gnyis par phye ba rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:3863: rtsa ba'i dum bu le'u nyer gnyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:3864: bshad pa'i dum bu le'u nyer gsum pa dang nyer bzhi pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3866: tshe dang rkang mgyogs sogs thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK065(cu)001:3867: mchog gi dngos grub gnas skabs rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3868: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa'i ched du'o //
NK065(cu)001:3871: sangs rgyas pa yi tshul bzhi ste //
NK065(cu)001:3872: rgyud dang gleng gzhi nges tshig rgyu //
NK065(cu)001:3874: chags bral gyi tshul bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:3877: mi'i skye bar 'khrungs pa ni chags bral gyi chos kyi rten du gyur pa'i phyir rgyud ces bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:3878: khyim nas khyim med par rab tu byung ba ni
