NK065(cu)001:3879: chags bral gyi rnam pa la nges pa ster bas
NK065(cu)001:3881: rab tu byung nas kyang 'dul sdom bsrung ba ni
NK065(cu)001:3882: nges par bsten pa'i gnas su rigs pas nges tshig
NK065(cu)001:3883: ces bya'o // de ltar gsungs nas kyang 'bras bu
NK065(cu)001:3884: byang chub 'dod pas lam la bslab pa ni rnam
NK065(cu)001:3885: grol thob pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir rgyu zhes bya'o
NK065(cu)001:3886: ces bya'o // // 'dir chags bral gyis sangs rgyas tshul smos pas ci bya zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:3887: bcom ldan 'das thub pa'i dbang po ni /
NK065(cu)001:3888: ji skad bshad pa'i tshul bzhi'i sgo nas sangs rgyas par 'jig rten du grags shing /
NK065(cu)001:3889: rgyud kyi ston pa rigs drug pa'ang /
NK065(cu)001:3890: de las rgyud tha mi dad du shes pa'i sgo
NK065(cu)001:3891: nas byed pa po tshad mar sgrub pa yin no
NK065(cu)001:3892: // de la bla ma dbus gru smon lam seng ge na re /
NK065(cu)001:3893: 'dir sngags dang mtshan nyid kyi 'dod pa 'byed pa'i
NK065(cu)001:3894: phyir chags bral gyi tshul bzhi bkod pa yin gyi
NK065(cu)001:3895: / sngags su 'dod pa ni ma yin no gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:3897: bdag nyid rang rigs dang mthun par rigs lnga'i sangs
NK065(cu)001:3898: rgyas su bskyed pa ni gsang sngags kyi rten du
NK065(cu)001:3900: de nas slar yang rigs lnga gcig tu 'dus pa'i
NK065(cu)001:3901: rnam par gyur pa ni chags lam gyi rnam pa
NK065(cu)001:3902: la nges pa ster bas gleng gazhi'o //
NK065(cu)001:3903: rdo rje la sogs pa'i rigs kyi sdom pa bzung
NK065(cu)001:3904: ba dang khyad par rdo rje dang pad+ma mnyam par
NK065(cu)001:3905: sbyor bas tshangs spyod kyi brtul zhugs bzung ba ni
NK065(cu)001:3906: nges par brten pa'i gnas su rigs pas nges tshig
NK065(cu)001:3907: go // de nas 'dod chags lam du bsgyur ba'i
NK065(cu)001:3908: gsang chos la spyod pa ni 'bras bu myur du
NK065(cu)001:3909: 'byin pa'i nye rgyud yin pas na rgyu'o //
NK065(cu)001:3911: tshig don 'di las mi 'da' bas na mtha' ste /
NK065(cu)001:3913: rgyas bshad mtha' ni rnam pa drug /
NK065(cu)001:3914: drang don nges don dgongs pas bshad //
NK065(cu)001:3915: dgongs min sgra ni ji bzhin pa //
NK065(cu)001:3916: ji bzhin ma yin nyid du bshad //
NK065(cu)001:3919: rdo rje'i tshig gcig gis gdul bya yang dag pa'i skal ba dngos su med pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3920: yod pa gnyis la don tha dad du ston pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3921: bskyed rim yan lag dang bcas pa ston pa drang don dang /
NK065(cu)001:3922: rgyu rgyud dang rdzogs rim ston pa'i phyogs ni nges don no //
NK065(cu)001:3924: rdo rje'i tshig tha dad pas bskyed rdzogs kyi don gcig /
NK065(cu)001:3925: de dang 'gal ba'i tshig gi sbyor bas bcings te
NK065(cu)001:3926: brjod don dgongs gzhi la ltos nas go dgos pa
NK065(cu)001:3928: rjod byed dgongs bstan gyis brjod don dgongs gzhi la
NK065(cu)001:3929: ltos mi dgos par gsal bar go ba ni dgongs
NK065(cu)001:3930: pa can min pa'i bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3931: phyi dkyil dang sbyin sreg sogs cho ga rnams 'jig
NK065(cu)001:3932: rten dang bstan bcos la grags pa'i tshig gis gsungs
NK065(cu)001:3933: pa ni sgra ji bzhin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3934: ko t+aa kh+y+aahl sogs pa'i sgra dang /
NK065(cu)001:3935: 'dir sbyor sgrol la +aa li k+aa li zhes pa
NK065(cu)001:3936: lta bu 'jig rten dang bstan bcos gzhan la ma
NK065(cu)001:3937: grags pa'i brdas bcings te gsungs pa ni sgra ji
NK065(cu)001:3941: bshad pa'i tshul bzhi khyed la bstan //
NK065(cu)001:3942: tshig spyi sbas dang mthar thug yin //
NK065(cu)001:3945: yi ge'i 'bru non tsam la gzhol ba'i bshad pa
NK065(cu)001:3946: sgra tshad kyi gzhung dang mthun par bkod pa ste
NK065(cu)001:3947: / gzhan dag yi ge'i don zhes zer ro //
NK065(cu)001:3950: bskyed rim pa'i spyi don gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3952: mdo sogs la zhugs pa'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:3953: sngags nang pa la zhugs pa'i 'gyod pa bzlog pa gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:3955: sngags nang pa'i lam bde zhing myur ba 'di lta
NK065(cu)001:3956: bu la ma zhugs par sngar mado'am bya spyod sogs
NK065(cu)001:3957: la zhugs pa ni ma legs so snyam du 'gyod
NK065(cu)001:3958: na / de dag kyang 'di'i lam stegs te /
NK065(cu)001:3960: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:3961: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK065(cu)001:3964: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK065(cu)001:3965: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:3966: zhes pas dbang rnon thabs shes khyad par can dang
NK065(cu)001:3967: ldan na tshogs kyi bya ba rlabs chen gcig gis
NK065(cu)001:3968: bskal pa mang po'i tshogs bzlums pa sogs bde myur
NK065(cu)001:3969: gyi lam mdo sogs kyang bzhed pas spyi'i don zhes
NK065(cu)001:3971: 'dir khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs gtsang sme med par spyod pa khyi phag lta bu dang /
NK065(cu)001:3972: spyor sgrol sogs 'tshe ba chos su smra bas mu stegs kyi chos so snyam du 'gyod na /
NK065(cu)001:3973: gtsang sme'i zhen pa ma spangs na chos mnyam pa
NK065(cu)001:3974: nyid kyi don mi rtogs pas zhen pa spang phyir
NK065(cu)001:3975: ro snyam du spyod pa ni mdo sogs kyang bzhed
NK065(cu)001:3976: cing / mi nag mdung thung can bsad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:3977: ded dpon gyi bu mo la bsgrod pa sogs sems
NK065(cu)001:3978: dge bas sbyor sgrol la spyad kyang nyes pas mi
NK065(cu)001:3979: gos shing bsod nams dpag med 'phel bar mdo sogs
NK065(cu)001:3980: kyang bzhed pas bslab bya thun mong pa'i don zhes
NK065(cu)001:3982: rten gzhal yas khang dang brten pa lha bsgom pa sogs bskyed rim dang 'brel ba rnams te /
NK065(cu)001:3983: bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i thun mong gi bslab bya yin pa'i phyir spyi don no //
NK065(cu)001:3985: las rgya dang snyoms par 'jug pa'i cho ga ston
NK065(cu)001:3986: pa sogs tshogs su dbyung bar mi 'os pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:3988: rang byin gyis rlob pa rtsa rlung thig le'i rdzogs rim sogs kun rdzob bden pa'i sbas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:3989: spyi mthar gnyis kyi dbus su chud pas snying po lta bur gyur ba'i phyir sbas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:3991: de dag gi rgyas gdab tu gyur ba don dam
NK065(cu)001:3992: 'od gsal gyi rdzogs rim ni lam gyi mthar thug
NK065(cu)001:3993: dang / bden gnyis zung 'jug tu rtogs pa ni 'bras bu'i mthar thug ste /
NK065(cu)001:3994: tshul bzhi ka rdo rje'i tshig gcig la dbang po mi 'dra ba'i sgo nas 'chad dgos pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:3995: tshig de'i brjod bya lhag ma ma lus par mur thug pas na mthar thug go //
NK065(cu)001:3998: nyan bshad dbye ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:3999: tshogs dang slob ma dag tu 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:4001: tshogs bshad ni sgra ji bzhin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4002: de dang thun mong pa'i dgongs min /
NK065(cu)001:4005: spyi'i don rnams te 'dod chags chos sbas ma gtogs pa'i bskyed rim 'khor bcas so //
NK065(cu)001:4007: sgra ji bzhin ma yin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4011: mthar thug rnams te rdzogs rim 'khor bcas so //
NK065(cu)001:4012: 'dir thun mong ma yin pa'i dgongs min ni sbas mthar gnyis su 'dus pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:4015: snod kyi gang zag rnam pa lnga //
NK065(cu)001:4017: tsan+dana rin po che yi dpe //
NK065(cu)001:4019: slob dpon las thos nas lan cig 'dzin par nus
NK065(cu)001:4020: kyang 'du 'dzi la sogs pa'i rkyen gyis myur du
NK065(cu)001:4021: brjed par gyur pa ni ut+pala zhes bya ba'i gang
NK065(cu)001:4022: zag ste / dper na ut+pala chu nang du rtsi
NK065(cu)001:4023: bcud 'dzin pa sogs kyi yon tan kyang rna bar
NK065(cu)001:4024: 'jug pa sogs kyis myur du rnyid par 'gyur ba
NK065(cu)001:4025: zag ste / bzhin no // yang mang du thos
NK065(cu)001:4026: shing ma brjed kyang gzhan la 'chad mi nus pa
NK065(cu)001:4027: ni pad dkar zhes bya ba'i gang zag ste /
NK065(cu)001:4028: dper na pad+ma dkar po ni snga ma las rnying
NK065(cu)001:4029: dka' zhing rtsi bcud brtan na'ang nyi ma dang 'grogs
NK065(cu)001:4030: pa na kha zum par 'gyur ba'i phyir bung ba
NK065(cu)001:4031: sogs kyi rtsi bcud len mi nus pa bzhin no
NK065(cu)001:4033: dad brtse shes rab dang ldan pas blo kha bye
NK065(cu)001:4034: ste gzhan la 'chad nus kyang rgyud mi brtan pa'i
NK065(cu)001:4035: yon tan ring du mi gnas pa ni pad+ma dmar
NK065(cu)001:4036: po zhes bya ba'i gang zag ste /
NK065(cu)001:4037: dper na pad+ma dmar po ni nyi mas kha 'byed
NK065(cu)001:4038: cing rtsi bcud 'dzin pa sogs kyi yon tan yod
NK065(cu)001:4039: kyang 'jag rkyen pas rtsi bcud ring du mi gnas
NK065(cu)001:4040: pa bzhin no // yang thos pa chung zhing nga
NK065(cu)001:4041: rgyal che ba lung rigs kyi rtsa ba med kyang
NK065(cu)001:4042: mang du smra ba gdul bya rjes su 'dzin mi
NK065(cu)001:4043: nus pa ni tsan+da na zhes bya ba'i gang zag
NK065(cu)001:4044: pa bzhin no // ste / dper na tsan+dana sbrul
NK065(cu)001:4045: gyi snying po ni dngos po chung la dri che
NK065(cu)001:4046: ba rtsa ba rgya cher ma zug cing yal 'dab
NK065(cu)001:4047: rgyas pa sbrul gdug pas dkris pas gzhan gyis blang
NK065(cu)001:4050: khrims dag cing mkhas la sgrin pa rgyud brtan pa
NK065(cu)001:4051: rang gis thos nas gzhan la legs par ston nus
NK065(cu)001:4052: pa ni rin po che zhes bya ba'i gang zag
NK065(cu)001:4053: ste / dper na rin po che ni skyon med
NK065(cu)001:4054: cing yon tan dang ldan pa bzang po las mi
NK065(cu)001:4055: 'gyur ba dgos 'dod stsol ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:4056: de la rin po che rab /
NK065(cu)001:4060: gzhan bzhi po tshogs bshad kyi snod do //
NK065(cu)001:4063: bden pa'i dgongs pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:4064: kun rdzob don dam bshad par gyis //
NK065(cu)001:4065: zhes pas rgyan snga ma drug la brten nas rgyud
NK065(cu)001:4066: don bden pa gnyis su nges par byed pa ste
NK065(cu)001:4067: / bskyed pa'i rim pa 'khor bcas dang /
NK065(cu)001:4068: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i rdzogs rim rnams ni kun rdzob bden pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4069: mtshan med de bzhin nyid kyi rdzogs rim 'od gsal ba ni don dam bden pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4070: zung 'jug kyang thob bya yin pa'i phyir don dam du bzhag go //
NK065(cu)001:4071: de ltar rgyan bdun gyi 'chad tshul 'di ni /
NK065(cu)001:4072: rgyud 'di'i 'chad thabs kyi brgyud pa'i bka' srol ma yin kyang /
NK065(cu)001:4073: gal por ma h+aa spyi'i 'chad thabs su gsungs pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:4074: blo gsar rnams la mang du thos pa'i yan lag
NK065(cu)001:4075: tu bsams nas rnam grangs su bkod pa'i 'chad thabs
NK065(cu)001:4076: gzhan las tshul 'di cung zad spros te bshad pa
NK065(cu)001:4078: sngon gyi mkhan po rnams kyi bzhed pa tha dad pa mang yang /
NK065(cu)001:4079: 'dir bka' sde zur pa'i bshad srol gyi rjes su 'brangs te bshad pa la /
NK065(cu)001:4080: rang bzhin dngos po'i gnas tshul /
NK065(cu)001:4082: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs tshul /
NK065(cu)001:4083: brtse bas thugs rje skyes tshul /
NK065(cu)001:4084: 'gro don ji ltar mdzad tshul dang lnga /
NK065(cu)001:4086: rtogs rung ma rtogs rung snang srid 'khor 'das kyis
NK065(cu)001:4087: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad rang bzhin bden pa dbyer
NK065(cu)001:4088: med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por ye nas sangs
NK065(cu)001:4092: mtha' yas dkyil 'khor ma lus kun //
NK065(cu)001:4093: rgyal ba'i yum gyi dbyings su thim //
NK065(cu)001:4094: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK065(cu)001:4097: 'jig rten brtan g.yo la sogs pa //
NK065(cu)001:4098: snang ba nyid na ngo bo med //
NK065(cu)001:4099: de nyid chos sku chen po yin //
NK065(cu)001:4102: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang chos thams cad
NK065(cu)001:4103: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid du gcig
NK065(cu)001:4104: pa'i mtshan nyid yin pas dbyer med na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:4107: de ltar sangs rgyas kyang ma rtogs te /
NK065(cu)001:4109: lhan skyes kyi ma rig pas rang ngo rang gis ma shes la /
NK065(cu)001:4110: de'i steng du kun brtags kyi ma rig pas phyin ci log tu bzung ste /
NK065(cu)001:4111: las nyon la rang gar spyad pas yang dag pa'i
NK065(cu)001:4112: lam dang bral zhing 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sna tshogs
NK065(cu)001:4113: kyis nyam thag par gnas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4115: 'gro ba'i rnam par rtog pa ma rig pa las
NK065(cu)001:4116: 'gro ba lnga'i rigs bsam gyis mi khyab par smin
NK065(cu)001:4120: log par rtog brtags rnam dag cing //
NK065(cu)001:4121: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK065(cu)001:4122: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK065(cu)001:4123: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK065(cu)001:4125: dang po dbyings las mi gzhan pa'am ji lta ba
NK065(cu)001:4126: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis cir yang mi dmigs par
NK065(cu)001:4128: thams cad mkhyen pa'i thugs ldan pas //
NK065(cu)001:4129: gzhi rtsa med dbyings skad cig ma //
NK065(cu)001:4130: mtha' dang dbus kyang brtag tu med //
NK065(cu)001:4132: gnyis pa ye shes las mi gzhan pa'am ji snyed
NK065(cu)001:4133: pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gsal cha ma 'dres
NK065(cu)001:4135: mtho dman kun gyi gzugs snang dang //
NK065(cu)001:4136: bla med byang chub skur snang ba //
NK065(cu)001:4137: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK065(cu)001:4138: sna tshogs kha dog dbyibs su snang //
NK065(cu)001:4140: gsum pa dbyings ye'am ji lta ji snyed dbyer med
NK065(cu)001:4141: du mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis snang stong dbyer med
NK065(cu)001:4142: me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar gzigs te /
NK065(cu)001:4144: rnam par rtog pa mi mnga' ste //
NK065(cu)001:4145: de yis mi mkhyen gang yang med //
NK065(cu)001:4149: rtag rgyud rang bzhin shugs gsol dang //
NK065(cu)001:4150: yul dang 'phrad nas byung bar snang //
NK065(cu)001:4154: bskul zhing gsol ba btab pa'i /
NK065(cu)001:4155: yul dang 'phrad pa'i thugs rje skye tshul dang bzhi /
NK065(cu)001:4157: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rjes sems can gyi don nam
NK065(cu)001:4158: du'am mi 'dor ba'i phyir rgyun chad med par snang
NK065(cu)001:4159: ba ste / chu bo chen po'i rgyun bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:4161: rgyu rkyen dang rtsol rtog med par rang gis thugs rje 'char ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:4162: nyi ma dang 'od zer bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:4164: gang la gsol ba btab na thugs rje khyad par can mi 'gag pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4165: phongs pas gdung ba'i smre sngags 'don pa la snying rje can lhag par ster ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:4166: de'ang lhan cig pa'i 'khor gyis dbang thob pas rang don du rtogs na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:4167: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don du rton pa la
NK065(cu)001:4168: rgyud gsung bar gsol ba btab pas thugs rje skyes
NK065(cu)001:4169: te / 'di'i dngos kyi gdul byar gyur pa'i don du rgyud gsungs shing /
NK065(cu)001:4170: dngos su nyan pa'i skal ba med pa rnams la
NK065(cu)001:4171: lam stegs kyi theg pa gzhan ston pa'i phyir thub
NK065(cu)001:4172: drug sprul par mdzad pa ste le'u gnyis pa ltar
NK065(cu)001:4174: spyir sems can thams cad thugs rje skye ba'i yul yin mod //
NK065(cu)001:4175: khyad par du'ang ru dra lta bu gdul bya las
NK065(cu)001:4176: ngan can yal bar mi 'dor ba'i thugs rje khyad
NK065(cu)001:4177: par can te / mdzangs pa spyod log byed pa mthong ba lta bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:4179: thugs rje chen po sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas /
NK065(cu)001:4181: de'ang thugs rje chen po ni /
NK065(cu)001:4182: phan pa thams cad kyi gzhir gyur pa dmigs pa med pa'i snying rje ste /
NK065(cu)001:4183: bdag dang sems can dbyer med pa'i ngos nas skyes ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:4185: bzhed pa mi mthun pa mang ste /
NK065(cu)001:4186: rten can gyis don byed pa /
NK065(cu)001:4187: rten med kyis don byed pa /
NK065(cu)001:4188: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyis don byed par 'dod pa gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:4189: 'dir lha rje zur chung ba'i rjes su 'brangs te /
NK065(cu)001:4192: spyir bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4193: khyad par du gsang ba'i bstan pa rgyud 'di nyid kyis don mdzad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4196: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK065(cu)001:4197: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK065(cu)001:4198: 'gro ba'i phrin las bsam mi khyab //
NK065(cu)001:4201: 'di'i byin rlabs kyis don mdzad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4202: 'di nyid dngos kyis don mdzad pa gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:4204: ston pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs
NK065(cu)001:4205: las sprul sku thub drug spros te 'dul ba rnam
NK065(cu)001:4206: pa bzhis rigs drug gi don mdzad pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4207: le'u gsum pa'i stod ltar ro //
NK065(cu)001:4210: go phye ba'i 'khor gyi don mdzad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4212: ston bas 'og min du lhan cig pa'i 'khor rnams
NK065(cu)001:4213: la zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur bas ston 'khor dgongs
NK065(cu)001:4214: pa khyad med du gyur pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4215: le'u gnyis pa'i stod ltar ro //
NK065(cu)001:4217: ma 'ongs pa'i gdul bya khyad par can gyi ched
NK065(cu)001:4218: du lam gsang ba'i snying po lhan cig pa'i 'khor
NK065(cu)001:4219: gyis zhus te gsungs pa nyid brgyud nas da ltar
NK065(cu)001:4220: snang ba 'adi'o // de la'ang rgyud kyi brjod bya'i don ni /
NK065(cu)001:4221: rgyud gsum snang ba bzhi la sogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4222: 'og tu rgyud don dngos bshad pa'i skabs su shes par 'gyur ro //
NK065(cu)001:4223: rjod byed kyi sgra'i bshad thabs la'ang /
NK065(cu)001:4224: dor bya bshad tshul nye ba'i skyon ngos bzung ba /
NK065(cu)001:4225: blang bya legs pa'i yon tan shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4227: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa gnyis bsres nas bshad na
NK065(cu)001:4228: rdo rje theg pa na bab kyis bshad pa'i skyon
NK065(cu)001:4229: dang / yo ga phyi nang bsres na bsnyen sgrub
NK065(cu)001:4230: bzhi'i don las gol te yo ga 'brog 'chol ba'i
NK065(cu)001:4231: dang / dang / 'brel tshul gnyis dang ma ldan na smyon pa'i tshig lta bu'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:4232: spyi dang khyad par kyi dgos ched med 'chal ba'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:4233: rtog ges brtags pa'i the tshom gyi gegs sel ma shes na mdzangs pa lce sdum gyi dang /
NK065(cu)001:4234: mi mthun pa'i tshig don bsdebs ma shes na shes rab long ba'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:4235: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rim ma shes na bdud rtsi ro nyams lta bu'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:4236: rgyud gong 'og 'khrugs pa bsdebs ma shes na rin
NK065(cu)001:4237: po che rtsa 'chol ba lta bu'i skyon dang brgyad
NK065(cu)001:4239: rgyud gnas skabs dngos po re re'i 'chad thabs dang /
NK065(cu)001:4240: rgyud gzhung phyir tshig don 'chad thabs gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:4242: lta ba brgal brtag gis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4243: spyod pa rjes 'jug thabs kyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4246: dam tshig rnam grangs kyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4247: phrin las chog sgrigs kyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4248: sgrub pa phyag bzhes kyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4249: ting nge 'dzin bskyed rdzogs kyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4250: p+au dza phyi nang gis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4251: sngags sgra dang sdebs kyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:4252: phyag rgya bskyed rim gyis bshad pa dang bcu gcig go //
NK065(cu)001:4254: bshad thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu ste /
NK065(cu)001:4256: gang la blta dang sgo 'byed dang //
NK065(cu)001:4258: rkyen dang gzhan dang dmigs pa'i tshig /
NK065(cu)001:4259: ma bcos me long s+n+rel gzhi rnams //
NK065(cu)001:4260: me long bcu dang mthun sbyar bas //
NK065(cu)001:4261: tshig don rnam par sbyar ba yin //
NK065(cu)001:4263: dang po rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig khyung nam mkha' la lding ba ltar bshad pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:4265: ga ru da yi chos bzhi pos /
NK065(cu)001:4268: ji ltar khyung nam mkha' la lding ba'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:4269: mig gyen du blta ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4270: gshog pa g.yob pa'i rtsol ba med pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4271: ngam grog dang g.yang sar nyam mi nga ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4272: bya lam la rjes med pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4273: 'di'i gong na rtogs bya gzhan med pas rang bzhin
NK065(cu)001:4274: lta ba'i tshig gis theg pa thams cad khog 'og
NK065(cu)001:4276: lam bgrod pa'i rtsol ba dang bral ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4277: ltung gnas srid pa dang zhi ba'i mtha' la nyam ming ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4278: blta bya lta byed blo yul du byed pa'i rtog pa med pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4279: gnyis pa rnam par 'byed pa'i tshig stag gis mchongs pa lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4281: bya g+h+ri mchongs pa de bzhin pas //
NK065(cu)001:4282: tan+ta'i tshig don dum bur gcod //
NK065(cu)001:4284: ji ltar stag mchongs pa'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:4285: bgrod bya'i sa tshigs dum bu dum bur bcad nas mchongs pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4286: rnam par dbye ba'i tshig gis tshig don gyi dmigs
NK065(cu)001:4287: so sor phye nas ming 'dogs gsal bar ston pa'o
NK065(cu)001:4288: // gsum pa spyi don sdud pa'i tshig seng ge'i mchongs pa lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4290: seng chen mchongs pa'i chos gcig ltar //
NK065(cu)001:4291: rnam grangs tshig lam don gcig sdud //
NK065(cu)001:4293: ji ltar seng ge mchongs pa'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:4294: sa tshigs du ma khog 'og tu chud pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4295: tshig don gyi rnam grangs du ma rnams spyi don
NK065(cu)001:4296: bsdu ba'i tshig gis don gyi ngo bo gcig tu
NK065(cu)001:4297: sdud pa'o // bzhi pa 'brel ba mtshams sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4299: ngang mo'i 'gros chos rnam gnyis ltar //
NK065(cu)001:4300: gzhung don dbu zhabs le mtshams sbyor //
NK065(cu)001:4302: ji ltar ngang mo 'gro ba'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:4304: snga rjes phyi rjes kyis non par 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4306: tshig 'brel dang don 'brel ma chad par 'brel sbyong ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:4307: lnga pa rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig rus sbal gyi nur 'gros lta bur bshad pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:4309: rus sbal 'gros kyi chos gnyis pos //
NK065(cu)001:4310: 'bru stong mi bzhag gzer bu gdab //
NK065(cu)001:4312: ji ltar rus sbal 'gro ba la chos gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:4313: g.yo 'gul mi mngon par zhugs kyi 'gro ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4314: sa stong mi lus par rjes kyis khyab pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4315: rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig gis 'bru stong mi bzhag par tshig don brda 'phrod par byed ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:4316: drug pa ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig rna phrug brag la 'dzegs pa lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4318: rna phrug 'dzegs pa'i chos gnyis ltar //
NK065(cu)001:4319: ldem dgongs gsang ba brgyad kyi sbyar //
NK065(cu)001:4321: ji lta rna phrug brag la 'dzegs pa la chos gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:4322: skyes ma thag tu brag me long gi ngos lta bu la rtsed mo rtse zhing 'gro ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4323: de ri dwags gzhan la mi 'tshams kyang kho rang la 'tshams pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4324: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig zab lam sbas tshul du bstan pa rnams thabs kyis 'byin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4325: de theg pa 'og ma rnams la mi 'tshams kyang 'dir 'tshams pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4326: bdun pa gtar ga gegs sel gyi tshig bya glag khra mo gzan la bcum pa lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4328: glag gi gzan gyi chos gnyis ltar //
NK065(cu)001:4329: don gyi dmigs bzung gegs bsal lo //
NK065(cu)001:4331: ji ltar glag mo gzan la bcum pa'i tshe chos gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:4332: gang yid la btags pa'i zas dang /
NK065(cu)001:4333: de'i khong gi bcud 'byin pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:4334: gtar ga gegs sel gyi tshig gi gtan tshigs kyis
NK065(cu)001:4335: gtan la phab nas grub mtha'i don longs par byed
NK065(cu)001:4336: pa'o // brgyad pa tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig dus kyi 'brug sgra lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4338: dus kyi 'brug ltar chos gsum pos //
NK065(cu)001:4339: bka' yi tshad gzung skabs sbyar nas //
NK065(cu)001:4341: ji ltar 'brug gi sgra la'ang chos gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:4342: dus min du mi 'byung ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4344: des dbyar dgun la sogs pa'i dus kyi spros pa chod pas yid ches pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4345: bka' lung tshad ma nyid dang yul ma yin par mi drang zhing /
NK065(cu)001:4346: skabs dang mthun par drangs pas don gyi sgro 'dogs chod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4347: lung ni yid ches tshig yin te //
NK065(cu)001:4350: mtshon pa dpe'i tshig me long g.ya' dag pa lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4352: me long chos ltar mtshon pa'i dpe //
NK065(cu)001:4353: kun la dpes mtshon thog tu dbab //
NK065(cu)001:4355: ji ltar rang gi bzhin ras lkog tu gyur pa me long gis bsal ba bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:4356: shin tu lkog gyur gyi gzhung don rnams kyang dpes mtshon nges par byed pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4358: bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig seng phrug rtsal sbyong ba lta bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:4360: mi 'jigs phru gu rtsal sbyong ltar //
NK065(cu)001:4361: 'bru tshig don gyi go rim sdebs //
NK065(cu)001:4363: ji ltar seng ge'i phru gu rtsal sbyong ba'i tshe na /
NK065(cu)001:4364: bsnol mar mchongs nas drang por 'gro ba bzhin du bsnol mtshams 'phen sdud kyi tshig gis /
NK065(cu)001:4367: 'bru'i 'dugs bsgyur nas sgra ji bzhin pa ma yin /
NK065(cu)001:4368: don thun mong pa ma yin pa'i rgyud don phyin ci ma log par ston pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4369: de dag kyang rigs bsdus na /
NK065(cu)001:4370: rje sgro phug pa'i khog dbub las /
NK065(cu)001:4371: de la rnam par dbye ba /
NK065(cu)001:4373: rang rkyen gnyer gsum dkyus su sbyar /
NK065(cu)001:4374: gzhan le'u gang bshad kyi dkyus kyi thad kar ngo sprad do //
NK065(cu)001:4376: spyi 'gro rnam pa gsum ma gtogs le'u so so
NK065(cu)001:4377: dang sbyar tshul rags tsam sgrol g.yung gnyis kyi khog
NK065(cu)001:4381: dkyus dbu zhabs thams cad du khyab byed du 'jug pa gsum /
NK065(cu)001:4398: de dag kyang snga ma las /
NK065(cu)001:4399: tshig don mos par bshad pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:4400: rnam par phye bas ma 'dres gsal //
NK065(cu)001:4403: lha rje zur po che'i zhal snga nas /
NK065(cu)001:4404: mtshon dpe dang sbyar te bshad lugs gsum gyi sgo nas bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4405: rgyud 'brel man ngag rnams dang mi 'gal bar bya ba'i phyir bshad tshul bzhi'i sgo nas 'chad gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:4407: mda' ltar rtse mo nas bzung ste bshad pa /
NK065(cu)001:4408: mdung ltar sked pa nas bzung ste bshad pa /
NK065(cu)001:4409: ral gri ltar yu ba nas bzung ste bshad pa dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:4411: mtshan gyi skabs su chos thams cad gzhi lam 'bras gsum du dril nas 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:4413: le'u lnga par chos thams cad mtshan nyid gsum du dril nas 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:4415: le'u tha mar chos thams cad snang ba bzhir dril nas 'chad do //
NK065(cu)001:4416: gnyis pa bshad tshul bzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:4420: rgyud man ngag gis bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4422: rgyas pa sogs bshad rgyud rnams dang sbyar te 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:4424: rang rang gi 'dod gzhung so sos spar khab sogs
NK065(cu)001:4425: 'grel pa re re'am 'ga' zhig dbang btsan par byas
NK065(cu)001:4427: man ngag gi gzhung phra mo rnams kyis rgyud don dmigs phye ste skabs dang sbyar nas 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:4430: khyad par zab lam spas bshad rnams snyan brgyud dang
NK065(cu)001:4431: ldan pa'i bla ma dam pa'i gsung sgros kyis brgyan
NK065(cu)001:4432: te 'chad do // tshul bzhi po de ni rje
NK065(cu)001:4433: sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyis rgya cher 'grel gyi bshad
NK065(cu)001:4435: de ltar bshad thabs snams nges par byas nas //
NK065(cu)001:4437: phas kyi lan gdab 'bru mnan dang //
NK065(cu)001:4438: khog dbub sa bcad bzhi ru gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:4440: dang por spyi don gyis khog dbub //
NK065(cu)001:4443: gnas skabs khri'ura brgal lan gyis gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4448: bstan pa spyi'i rnam gzhag dang /
NK065(cu)001:4449: bye brag spyi don lngar bsdus te bshad pa sogs sngar smos pa rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:4451: 'chad 'gyur ltar rgyud gsum snang ba bzhi la sogs pa'i sogs nas gtan la 'bebs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4452: bar du dkyus kyis bcad pa la /
NK065(cu)001:4454: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK065(cu)001:4457: dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa sman pas lag
NK065(cu)001:4458: gi rtsal brten nas lus mgo mjug gi nad ngos
NK065(cu)001:4460: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba sman snod kyi kha byang lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4461: tha ma la 'bru res 'chad pa sman gcig kyang chos du mas gtan la 'bebs pa lta bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:4463: bshad lugs gsum las mda' ltar bzung bas 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:4464: 'bring la rnam par dbye ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:4467: yongs su shes par bya ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4469: gdams shing gtad pa dang lnga las /
NK065(cu)001:4471: rgyud gnas skabs kyi dngos por re re bshad thabs bcu gcig pos 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:4472: gdams pa ni ral gri ltar bzung bas dang /
NK065(cu)001:4473: gzhan rnams man ngag gi yi ge dang gsung sgros ci rigs pas 'chad do //
NK065(cu)001:4474: dbang po tha ma'i don ni /
NK065(cu)001:4476: tshig gi 'bru gzhon pa gnyis thun mong du bshad
NK065(cu)001:4477: thabs 'dren pa'i tshig bcu las bdun pa ma gtogs
NK065(cu)001:4478: pas 'chad cing / de dag gi gnas skabs khri'ura
NK065(cu)001:4479: brgal lan ni bdun pa gtar ga gegs sel gyi
NK065(cu)001:4482: le'u lnga pa kho na'i 'chad thabs so //
NK065(cu)001:4483: tshul bzhi'i sgo nas bshad pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:4487: tshul bzhi kas bshad pa'ang yod la /
NK065(cu)001:4488: phal che bar ci rigs pas bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:4489: de yang bshad thabs kyi man ngag 'di dag snyan
NK065(cu)001:4490: brgyud kyi srol ka mi nub pa'i ched du zlos
NK065(cu)001:4491: skyon sogs la ma bltas par bkod pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4492: spyi don lnga'i sgo nas bshad pa 'di ni /
NK065(cu)001:4493: 'jigs bral gyi slob dpon bud+d+ha gu h+ya la sogs
NK065(cu)001:4494: pa'i bshad srol rma med pa yin pas 'di tsam
NK065(cu)001:4495: du ma zad bla med kyi rgyud kun gyi 'chad
NK065(cu)001:4497: gnyis pa man ngag gi bshad thabs ni /
NK065(cu)001:4499: thos chung gsar bu yid ches bya ba'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:4500: man ngag spyi don rtsis 'gos klad nas gzhom //
NK065(cu)001:4502: khungs la yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:4503: slob dpon gang gis mdzad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4504: bka' dang mi 'gal zhing theg pa'i gzhung tshugs par
NK065(cu)001:4505: bya ba'i phyir rgyud gang nas bsdus shing phyogs gar
NK065(cu)001:4506: gtogs pa dang / bstan pa la mtshan nges shing
NK065(cu)001:4507: don gyi mdo tsam zhig rtogs par bya ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:4508: mtshan ci las btags pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4509: brtsams pa la don yon par bya ba'i phyir gang zag gang gi don dumadzada pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4510: brjod bya'i don khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:4511: dbu zhabs su bsdus pa'i don du bstan pa dang
NK065(cu)001:4513: spyir bstan pa la 'jug pa'i gang zag la rigs gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:4514: rtogs ldan chos kyi rjes su 'brang ba dag ni /
NK065(cu)001:4515: brjod bya'i don dang rjod byed sgra'i sdeb sbyor la skyon med par mthong na /
NK065(cu)001:4516: rtsom byed kyi gang zag su yin kyang 'jug par 'gyur bas rtsom pa po smos mi dgos mod /
NK065(cu)001:4517: de lta na'ang dbang rtul gang zag gi rjes su 'brang ba dag ni /
NK065(cu)001:4518: rtsom pa po'i yon tan thos pa na dang ste 'jug par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:4519: thog mar mdzad pa bo gang yin gyi mtshan dang /
NK065(cu)001:4520: de nyid kyi che ba'i yon tan brjod par bya ba ste skabs dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:4522: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud las btus la /
NK065(cu)001:4523: phyogs rnal 'byor chen por gtogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4530: don dang lnga las btags te /
NK065(cu)001:4532: lang kar gshegs pa'i mdo lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4534: swa lu ljang pa'i mdo lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4536: rtsom pa po las btags pa pad+ma'i lam rim lta bu dang /
NK065(cu)001:4537: zhu ba po las btags pa bam brgyad kyi stag 'grel lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4539: dbyig gnyen dang thu mi'i sum cu pa lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4541: don gyi ngo bo nyid las btags pa phyag rgya bsam gtan lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4542: rnam grangs las btags pa sgeg pa'i rim drug dang bi ma la'i rim gsum lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:4543: don gyi gtso bo las btags pa lam rim che chung lta bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:4544: de dag las gang yin ngos bzung ba skabs dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:4546: gang zag su zhig don du mdzad pa yang skabs dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:4548: brjod bya don gyis bsdus pa'i cha dang /
NK065(cu)001:4549: rjod byed tshig gis bsdus pa'i cha gnyis su shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4550: gang gis 'chad pa'i man ngag bshad zin to //
NK065(cu)001:4551: gsum pa des ji ltar 'chad pa'i tshul la /
NK065(cu)001:4552: slob dpon dang slob ma'i mtshan nyid /
NK065(cu)001:4554: de ltar 'chad nyan byas pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:4556: 'chad byed slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid dang /
NK065(cu)001:4557: bshad bya'i yul slob ma'i mtshan nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:4560: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi don la mkhas pas gsang ba'i mdzod gsum dang ldan pa /
NK065(cu)001:4561: phan nus zab mo'i dbang thob pas chu bo rdzogs pa /
NK065(cu)001:4562: gsang sngags bab 'chol du mi spyod pas gsang gnyer thub pa'am /
NK065(cu)001:4563: yang na snod ldan yal bar mi 'dor ba'i gnyer dang ldan pa /
NK065(cu)001:4564: rgyud don dngos po bcu la mkhas pas slob bu'i shes rgyud 'grol nus pa /
NK065(cu)001:4565: dkyil 'khor dang dbang gi rim pa dang zhi rgyas
NK065(cu)001:4566: sogs las tshogs sgrub pa'i mtha' la ma rmongs pa
NK065(cu)001:4567: / snyan brgyud kyi man ngag 'chang ba'am nyams myong
NK065(cu)001:4568: dang ldan pas man ngag gi gdeng thob pa ste
NK065(cu)001:4569: / / mdzod gsum so sor bgrangs pas brgyad do //
NK065(cu)001:4570: de'ang lta ba'i mdzod a ti /
NK065(cu)001:4572: spyod pa'i mdzod ma h+aa yo ga'o //
NK065(cu)001:4573: de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK065(cu)001:4574: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:4575: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK065(cu)001:4579: bla ma dam pa la bsten pa zhes 'bod pa gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:4580: mtshon bya don gyi rgyud rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po sems kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK065(cu)001:4581: mtshon byed tshig gi rgyud rtsa bshad man ngag dang
NK065(cu)001:4582: bcas pa'i tshig don ston par mdzad pa po yin
NK065(cu)001:4583: pa'i phyir de skad ces bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4584: rgyud sde rnams su slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid mang du gsungs na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:4585: re zhig brgyad po der 'dus so //
NK065(cu)001:4588: rtsod ldan dbang gis bla ma skyon dang yon tan 'dres //
NK065(cu)001:4589: rnam pa kun tu sdig pa med pa yod ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:4590: gang zhig yon tan lhag pa yang ni legs dpyad nas //
NK065(cu)001:4591: bu rnams kyis ni de la brten par 'gyur ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:4592: zhes pas mtshan nyid kun tshang ma rnyed na /
NK065(cu)001:4593: yon tan shas che ba la brten par gsungs shing /
NK065(cu)001:4594: 'on kyang med du mi rung ba'i yon tan ni /
NK065(cu)001:4595: dbang thob cing dam tshig la gnas pa /
NK065(cu)001:4596: gang 'chad pa'i rgyud dang dkyil 'khor gyi las la
NK065(cu)001:4597: ma rmongs pas slob ma rjes su 'dzin nus pa
NK065(cu)001:4598: zhig nges par dgos pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:4599: de yang slob mas bla ma bsten pa na /
NK065(cu)001:4600: thog mar brtag thabs gsum gyis brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:4601: bar du btsal thabs gsum gyis 'tshol pa /
NK065(cu)001:4602: tha mar bsten thabs gsum gyis bsten pa dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:4604: rgyang nas gzhan la dris te brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:4605: drung nas rang gis brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:4606: 'dod lha dang pra sen la brten nas brtag pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4608: de ltar brtags pas bzang por shes na /
NK065(cu)001:4611: nor zad 'phangs la mi blta bar btsal bar bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4613: de ltar btsal bas rnyed pa de nyid /
NK065(cu)001:4614: 'chi gsos kyi sman ltar 'bral med du bsten /
NK065(cu)001:4615: khog gi snying ltar gzu lum dang ras chod mi bya bar bsten /
NK065(cu)001:4616: yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar bsnyen bkur la tshad bzung mi bya bar bsnyen par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4617: mdor na bdag rkyen bla ma dam pa ma bsten par thar pa thob pa'i thabs med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:4618: bla ma ni sangs rgyas kun las lhag par bltas la bkur par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:4620: bskal pa 'bum gyi sangs rgyas pas //
NK065(cu)001:4621: slob dpon gnyan par shes pa bya //
NK065(cu)001:4622: zhes sogs mdo rgyud kun nas rgya cher gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:4624: spyir gang zag lnga'i dbye bas sngar bshad pa nyid yin mod /
NK065(cu)001:4625: 'on kyang bka' srol 'di nyid las 'byung ba ltar cung zad brjod na /
NK065(cu)001:4626: snod kyi skyon bzhi dang bral zhing /
NK065(cu)001:4627: yon tan lnga dang ldan pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4629: thos pa'i snod skyon kha sbubs lta bu dang /
NK065(cu)001:4630: bsam pa'i snod skyon zhabs brdol dang gzhogs ral lta bu dang /
NK065(cu)001:4631: sgom pa'i snod skyon dug can lta bu ste /
NK065(cu)001:4634: mi chags ma rungs byed pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:4637: ngang chu rgyun ltar ring ba /
NK065(cu)001:4638: tshul dge sbyong ltar zhib pa /
NK065(cu)001:4639: bsam pa gser ltar bzang ba /
NK065(cu)001:4640: blo ri rab ltar brtan pa /
NK065(cu)001:4641: lus dang longs spyod chos phyir gtong phod pa ste lnga'am /
NK065(cu)001:4646: nogs thub pa ni snod dang ldan pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4647: zhes pas don go ba'i shes rab dang /
NK065(cu)001:4648: gzhan don la spro ba'i snying rje dang /
NK065(cu)001:4649: bstan pa'i don 'dzin nus pa nogs thug pa ste gsum po bsnan nas /
NK065(cu)001:4650: yon tan brgyad du'ang dbyer yod do //
NK065(cu)001:4652: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la brtan //
NK065(cu)001:4653: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK065(cu)001:4655: de bas na rgyas pa las /
NK065(cu)001:4656: de bzhin gshegs pa'i spyod yul de //
NK065(cu)001:4657: skyes bu blo rtsal rab kyis rtogs //
NK065(cu)001:4658: zhes pas rgyud zab mo 'di nyid dbang rtul gyi yul ma yin gyi /
NK065(cu)001:4659: dbang po rnon po'i spyod yul yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:4660: shes rab dang ldan pa sogs chos gsum tshang ba
NK065(cu)001:4661: la 'grel par snod ldan zhes gsungs pa ni shin
NK065(cu)001:4663: dbang rnon de la'ang dbye na /
NK065(cu)001:4668: yangs la rgya che gting zab pa //
NK065(cu)001:4669: shes rab zab pas rtogs par 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:4673: thos bsam bsgom la rab sbyangs pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:4674: shes rab mig ldan rnams kyis bzung //
NK065(cu)001:4676: de yang bla mas slob ma la chos ston pa na /
NK065(cu)001:4677: snga rol du snod kyi skyon yon tan dang ldan mi ldan brtag thabs lngas legs par brtag ste /
NK065(cu)001:4679: rgyang drung pra sen mkha' 'gro yis //
NK065(cu)001:4680: gsang sngags ltas ston sbyor ba yis //
NK065(cu)001:4681: ci nas brtags te bzang ldan na //
NK065(cu)001:4682: mi ldog brtan byas ltas pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:4683: sish+ya gang yin lag tu gtad //
NK065(cu)001:4684: ces pas rigs bzang ngan dang rgyud 'jam rtsub dang /
NK065(cu)001:4685: dad pa dang gtong ba che chung sogs rgyang nas gzhan la dris te brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:4686: drung nas rang gis brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:4687: pra sen dang mo la sogs pas brtag pa /
NK065(cu)001:4688: ston du rung ma rung mkha' 'gro la gsol ba btab nas brtag pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4689: khyad par las la bkol zhing ngag gis 'thab pa
NK065(cu)001:4690: sogs spyo ba'i sgo nas brtags pas mi ldog cing
NK065(cu)001:4691: / brtan pa ni dge nyen nan chags kyis rigs
NK065(cu)001:4692: nges pa zhes bya ste bzung bar 'os pa la
NK065(cu)001:4693: / / de yang spyir rigs nges pa la /
NK065(cu)001:4696: dge nyen nan chags kyis rigs nges pa dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:4698: dbang rnon gsang sngags kyi rigs su nges pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4700: lta ba rtogs nas gzhan gyi bsgyur du mi btub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4702: bshad ma thag pa de nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:4703: gal te snod dang mi ldan par shes na re zhig btang snyoms su 'jog pa'am /
NK065(cu)001:4705: snod dang 'tshams pa'i drang don tshogs bshad tsam bshad du rung na bshad par bya ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:4712: 'byung po la gtor ma btang ba /
NK065(cu)001:4715: lam 'phrang gso ba sogs dge ba ji tsam 'grub
NK065(cu)001:4716: pa'i rim gros bsod rnams kyi dpung bskyed par byas
NK065(cu)001:4718: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK065(cu)001:4719: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK065(cu)001:4720: nyan pa la sogs brtsams pa rnams //
NK065(cu)001:4722: zhes gsungs pa ltar slob ma snod rung du bya ba'i phyir dbang bskur zhing /
NK065(cu)001:4723: des kyang sngon du slob dpon mnyes par byas te
NK065(cu)001:4724: dbang nod nas dam tshig dang sdom pa la gnas
NK065(cu)001:4726: de yang rgyud don dngos la thug pa nas bzung ste /
NK065(cu)001:4730: mchod gtor 'bul ba rnams byas la dpon slob gnyis kas sngon byung ji lta bar bsgom pa'am /
NK065(cu)001:4732: mdo 'don cho ga'i bya ba la //
NK065(cu)001:4733: rtag par rdo rje chos su bya //
NK065(cu)001:4734: zhes pa ltar 'chad pa pos bdag nyid gsung rdo
NK065(cu)001:4735: rje snang ba mtha' yas su bsgoms kyang rung ste
NK065(cu)001:4737: smra byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK065(cu)001:4738: zhes sogs 'chad dbang gi bsam rgyud du snang mtha' bsgom par gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:4739: de ltar na nyan pa pos kyang rin 'byung du bsgom dgos par mtshungs te /
NK065(cu)001:4740: nyan dbang gi bsam rgyud du de ltar 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:4741: de nas rdo rje slob dpon la phyag sngon du 'gro bas yon dang man+dala phul la /
NK065(cu)001:4742: pus btsugs thal mo sbyar te /
NK065(cu)001:4743: e ma'o sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK065(cu)001:4744: rtog pa kun gyi rgyal po ste //
NK065(cu)001:4745: cho ga rgyas par bstan pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:4746: dri med zab mo brtag dka' ba //
NK065(cu)001:4747: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK065(cu)001:4748: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:4749: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:4751: rang gsang thabs kyis chod pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:4752: 'gro ba kun la sman slad du //
NK065(cu)001:4753: bcom ldan bdag la bshad du gsol //
NK065(cu)001:4754: zhes lan gsum gyis gsol ba gdab par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:4755: bla ma lnga bcu pa las /
NK065(cu)001:4756: pus btsugs thal mo sbyar ba yis //
NK065(cu)001:4757: nyan sogs 'dod pas gsol gsum gdab //
NK065(cu)001:4759: de na dpon slob gnyis kas sgo gsum gyi skyon bcu gcig spangs te 'chad nyan bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4761: nyal ba dang rkang pa rkyong ba sogs lus kyi gnas ngan len dang /
NK065(cu)001:4765: zhe sdang ba'i brgal lan dang /
NK065(cu)001:4766: ha cang rtog ge la 'chol ba'i rtsod ngor thal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4769: ma smin pa'i skye bos thos pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4772: slob dpon gyis smra ba'i rgyan dang ldan pas snod
NK065(cu)001:4773: dang snod ma yin pa brtags la bshad pa gnyis
NK065(cu)001:4775: nyan pa pos kyang gus pa'i spyod lam gyis 'dug ste /
NK065(cu)001:4776: bsam sbyor phun sum tshogs pas legs par nyan la /
NK065(cu)001:4777: rjes su bka' drin dran pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4778: de'i dge ba'i rtsa ba rnams yongs su bsngo bar bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:4781: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK065(cu)001:4782: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK065(cu)001:4783: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK065(cu)001:4784: de nyid nga yin dbang yang rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:4786: de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK065(cu)001:4787: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:4788: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK065(cu)001:4789: zhes 'chad pa pos thob pa'i phan yon dang /
NK065(cu)001:4791: gang gis 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK065(cu)001:4792: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK065(cu)001:4793: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK065(cu)001:4794: nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:4795: zhes rgyud la mthong mos byas pa'i yon tan te /
NK065(cu)001:4796: gtso bor nyan pa pos thob pa'i phan yon no //
NK065(cu)001:4798: rgyal ba'i rig pa 'dzin pa de //
NK065(cu)001:4800: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:4801: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlob //
NK065(cu)001:4805: mos dang mthong dang bris pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:4807: rtogs dang goms pa'i spyor ba yis //
NK065(cu)001:4808: 'bras bu thob pa smos ci dgos //
NK065(cu)001:4810: he hu ka gal po las kyang /
NK065(cu)001:4811: sku dang gsung thugs rdo rje yi //
NK065(cu)001:4813: klog gam yang na sems kyang rung //
NK065(cu)001:4815: zhes pa rnams ni gnyis kas thob pa'i phan yon no //
NK065(cu)001:4816: gzhan yang 'chad nyan gyi phan yon mdo sde las
NK065(cu)001:4817: 'byung ba dag kyang bshad de spro ba skyed par
NK065(cu)001:4818: bya'o // man ngag des ji ltar bshad pa'i tshul bshad zin to //
NK065(cu)001:4819: dpal ldan rgyud rgyal snying po nyid //
NK065(cu)001:4821: rje btsun gter chen bla ma yi //
NK065(cu)001:4822: drin las ban chung chos dpal gyis //
NK065(cu)001:4823: legs par bshad las thob pa'i dges //
NK065(cu)001:4824: pad+mo'i gnyen dang sgron me ltar //
NK065(cu)001:4825: 'gro ba'i nang gi mun pa kun //
NK065(cu)001:4826: sel ba'i dpal du mdzes gyur cig /
NK065(cu)001:4827: ces rtsa rgyud snying po'i spyi don gsang bdag zhal lung las /
NK065(cu)001:4828: sa dmigs dang po sngon 'gro spyi'i rnam par gzhag
NK065(cu)001:4829: pa 'di yang sngags btsun d+ha rma sh+r+ais drug cu
NK065(cu)001:4830: skor bcu gnyis pa'i rab byung me yos kyi lo
NK065(cu)001:4831: la sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:4832: dge ba'i gshes gnyen dang rdo rje theg pa'i bstan
NK065(cu)001:4833: pa la gcig tu gus pa zem ston o rgyan
NK065(cu)001:4834: dpal 'byor ro // phyis lcags rta rang lo so
NK065(cu)001:4835: bdun pa las dmigs gnyis pa rgyud kyi spyi don
NK065(cu)001:4836: dngos nyid stan thog gcig tu rdzogs par brtsam pa'i
NK065(cu)001:4837: tshe dbri bsnan cung zad bgyis te dag par byas
NK065(cu)001:4838: dpal 'byor ro // pa'o // swa sti sid+d+ham /
NK065(cu)001:4839: 'khor 'das chos kun rang rig byang chub sems //
NK065(cu)001:4840: snang stong dbyer med lhag pa chos kyi skur //
NK065(cu)001:4841: ye nas rnam dag bde gshegs snying po ste //
NK065(cu)001:4842: gzhi rgyud sems kyi chos nyid la phyag 'tshal //
NK065(cu)001:4843: mtha' bral rigs lam mkha' la gtan tshigs rtas //
NK065(cu)001:4844: drangs pa'i thabs grol lam mchog tsha zer can //
NK065(cu)001:4845: shes thob byed pa'i snang bas gzhi ji bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:4846: gsal nus lam rgyud gsang ba'i snying por mos //
NK065(cu)001:4847: shes rab ral gri rnon pos ma rig pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:4848: sgo nga'i sbubs brtol gnas lugs mngon gyur la //
NK065(cu)001:4849: mthar thug 'bras rgyud bde bar gshegs pa zhes //
NK065(cu)001:4850: 'di na drin can bla mar bstan la 'dud //
NK065(cu)001:4851: sbyang gzhi sbyong byed sbyangs 'bras dri bral gyi //
NK065(cu)001:4852: gnas skabs gsum ste shes thob bya byed dang //
NK065(cu)001:4853: bdag nyid gcig par 'brel zhing rgyun chags don //
NK065(cu)001:4854: rmongs pas bde blag rtogs phyir de don dgrol //
NK065(cu)001:4855: gzhung lugs mang po'i thos rgya mi ldan zhing //
NK065(cu)001:4856: chos rab 'byed pa'i shes rab mthu chung yang //
NK065(cu)001:4857: bla ma'i drin gyis rnyed pa'i zab don gnad //
NK065(cu)001:4858: cung zad nges 'di brjod la skyon yod min //
NK065(cu)001:4859: de ltar sngon du 'gro ba spyi'i rnam par gzhag pas blo sbyangs nas /
NK065(cu)001:4860: dbang bskur ba thob cing dam tshig gis rgyud bsdams
NK065(cu)001:4861: pa'i skal ldan la zab mo'i rgyud bshad par bya
NK065(cu)001:4863: bye brag rgyud kyi don bshad pa la 'jug pa bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:4865: khungs la yid ches bskyed pa'i phyir sngon ji ltar byung ba'i lo rgyus dang /
NK065(cu)001:4866: chos la don gnyer gyi gus pas 'jug pa'i phyir rgyud kyi che ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4867: che ba de ldan gyi rgyud don dngos bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:4869: ston pas ji ltar gsung tshul /
NK065(cu)001:4870: de la ji ltar brgyud tshul lo //
NK065(cu)001:4872: nyi 'od seng ge'i bzhed pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4873: sgeg rdor gyi bzhed pa gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:4875: 'og min du longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa ston pa'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:4876: de dang dus mtshungs par mi'i yul du mchog gi
NK065(cu)001:4877: sprul pa'i rdo rje gdan du 'tshang rgya tshul ma
NK065(cu)001:4878: bstan pa'i gong rol du gsungs par bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:4880: chu bo nee rany+dza na'i 'gram du dka' thub mdzad
NK065(cu)001:4881: pa la rigs bzhi sangs rgyas kyis bskul nas zhus
NK065(cu)001:4882: pas / btags pa'i lus der bzhag nas /
NK065(cu)001:4883: ye shes kyi lus 'og min du gshegs nas /
NK065(cu)001:4884: don thams cad grub pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i bya ba rdzogs pa'i skad cig mar gnas pa las /
NK065(cu)001:4885: rang gi lus las 'od kyi rdzu 'phrul gyis nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad khyab par byas pas /
NK065(cu)001:4886: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyang gcig tu 'dus
NK065(cu)001:4887: nas phyogs bzhi'i rigs kyi sangs rgyas kyis mngon par
NK065(cu)001:4888: byang chub pa lngas byin gyis brlabsa pas mngon par
NK065(cu)001:4890: gal te de ltar ma yin du zin na /
NK065(cu)001:4891: slob dpon med pa'i ye shes ni mi 'thad pa nyid kyi phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:4892: mtshan yang rdo rje dbyings chen por gsol lo //
NK065(cu)001:4893: de nas shugs bzhin du ye shes kyi dbang gis babs nas /
NK065(cu)001:4894: ri rab ri'i rtse mo rdo rje dang nor bu brtsegs pa'i khang par byon nas /
NK065(cu)001:4895: de kho na nyid 'dus pa'i sde la sogs te
NK065(cu)001:4896: yo ga'i theg pa chen po rnams bka' stsal to
NK065(cu)001:4897: // de nas phyag na rdo rjes zhus pas /
NK065(cu)001:4898: rgya mtsho'i 'gram du byon nas rdo rje dbyings kyi
NK065(cu)001:4899: khang bzang chen por yang yo ga'i theg pa rnams
NK065(cu)001:4900: bka' stsal to // de nas o rgyan dang za
NK065(cu)001:4901: hor gyi yul du gshegs nas rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au
NK065(cu)001:4902: ti la sogs pa la gsang ba'i rgyud sde thams
NK065(cu)001:4904: de nas slar dka' thub mdzad pa'i sar gshegs nas btags pa'i lus la ye shes slar zhugs nas /
NK065(cu)001:4907: rdo rje gdan mnan nas sangs rgyas te /
NK065(cu)001:4909: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:4911: mthar mya ngan las 'das pas mdzad pa mthar dbyung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:4914: 'di ltar mi yul du bka' stsal pa lags na /
NK065(cu)001:4916: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa /
NK065(cu)001:4918: de mi yul du bka' stsal pa mi smos zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:4921: rnam pa gcig tu khungs gsang dgos pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4923: gang gi dus na 'og min lha'i rgyal po'i gnas
NK065(cu)001:4924: na longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skus gsang sngags rdo rje'i
NK065(cu)001:4925: theg pa ston pa de'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:4928: de'i dbang gis mi yul du'ang gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa 'chad par 'gyur ro //
NK065(cu)001:4929: zhes ta th+aa a ba lo ki ka ra las gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:4930: de nas mjug tu mya ngan las 'das nas lo
NK065(cu)001:4931: nyi shu rtsa brgyad na nga'i chos 'di dag phyung
NK065(cu)001:4932: la khungs lha yul nas babs par snyod la /
NK065(cu)001:4933: bka' yang dag pa'i don dang mi 'gal ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:4934: phyag na rdo rje'i mthus bstan to bar sgrogs shig
NK065(cu)001:4936: sdud pa po yin pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:4938: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK065(cu)001:4942: mchog gi sprul skus mi yul du lam thun mong ba bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4943: dus mtshungs par ston pas 'og min du gsungs par bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:4945: drug pa'i ston pa lhun gyis grub pa'i thabs dang /
NK065(cu)001:4946: smon lam gyis go phye nas /
NK065(cu)001:4947: le'u dang por rgyu snang bar mdzad /
NK065(cu)001:4949: gsum par thun mong bca' gzhi'i ston pa drug snang bar mdzad do //
NK065(cu)001:4950: dus mtshungs par tha dad pa'i rgyud rnams byung ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:4952: rgya bod kyi bla ma phal cher 'di dang mthun par 'og min du gsungs par bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:4960: gdul bya'i snang ba lam mtha' nyid du'o //
NK065(cu)001:4963: gtsang ma'i ris dag rnam spangs pa //
NK065(cu)001:4964: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK065(cu)001:4965: zhes 'og min chen por grags pa chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:4966: dag ma dag gi zhing chos phye ba'i gnas phyogs re ba gcig bsgrub tu med de /
NK065(cu)001:4968: chos dbyings 'og min gsang ba na //
NK065(cu)001:4969: lhan cig 'dus pa'i rin chen khang //
NK065(cu)001:4971: bla ma'i 'grel pa mun sel las /
NK065(cu)001:4972: 'og min chen po dbyings kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba'i gnas su /
NK065(cu)001:4975: mtha' dbus med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK065(cu)001:4976: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:4979: 'og min gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus med pa /
NK065(cu)001:4982: ston pa rigs drug pa kun tu bzang pos /
NK065(cu)001:4983: 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su med pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:4984: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor rnams la bstan pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:4985: rgyud kyi gleng gzhi sgra ji bzhin pa ltar bzhed pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:4986: de ltar bzhed lugs gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:4988: gong ltar bshad kyang mi 'gal bar mngon te /
NK065(cu)001:4989: mchog gi sprul sku thub pa'i dbang po yang ston
NK065(cu)001:4990: pa rigs drug pa las rgyud gzhan du ma gyur
NK065(cu)001:4992: chu snod ltar gdul bya'i blo snang ba la so sor gsungs pa'ang mi 'gal ba'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:4994: snga mas 'og min du longs skus bstan pa dang
NK065(cu)001:4995: dus mtshungs par sprul skus mi yul du gsungs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:4997: khungs lha yul nas byung bar bsnyad nas phyag rdor
NK065(cu)001:4998: gyis ston cig par ston pas bka' gnang ba'ang bshad
NK065(cu)001:4999: la / phyi mas de'i phyogs bzung nas longs sku'i
NK065(cu)001:5000: gleng gzhi dang sbyar te gsungs pas gnyis po 'gal
NK065(cu)001:5002: der ma zad rgyud gzhung gcig la gleng gzhi bshad tshul tha dad pa gzhan las kyang 'byung ste /
NK065(cu)001:5003: 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa'i bshad rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:5004: gleng gzhi rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK065(cu)001:5005: 'og min gnas dang ri rab rtser //
NK065(cu)001:5007: byang chub sems dang lha rnams dang //
NK065(cu)001:5008: mi rnams kyi ni don du gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:5009: ston pa yang ni rnam gsum ste //
NK065(cu)001:5010: sangs rgyas rdo rje 'chang chen dang //
NK065(cu)001:5011: sprul sku 'khor lo bsgyur ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:5012: sh+aakya thub pa nyid kyis gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:5013: dus ni gdul bya 'dul ba'i tshe //
NK065(cu)001:5016: de ltar lugs gnyis 'gal med du bsgrubs nas /
NK065(cu)001:5018: brgyud pa'i bka' srol phyi ma nyid yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:5019: re zhig 'dir yang spar khab kyi lugs ltar bzung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:5021: mi yul du sprul skus lam stegs kyi theg pa
NK065(cu)001:5022: tsam las ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud ma gsungs par
NK065(cu)001:5023: 'dod pa ni shin tu mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:5025: sprul sku'i bstan pa 'dul ba rnam pa bzhi las gsung gis 'dul ba'i skabs su /
NK065(cu)001:5026: bla na med pa'i theg pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5029: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK065(cu)001:5030: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK065(cu)001:5032: de'ang 'di'i lam stegs kyi rgyud sde 'og ma rnams la dgongs so zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:5035: thabs kyi rgyud du lam thun mong ba rnams 'dus pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5036: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po /
NK065(cu)001:5037: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas kyi phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:5041: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:5042: zhes mi yul du thub pas gsang sngags ma gsungs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5043: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK065(cu)001:5044: zhes sogs sngags phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:5046: bla ma snga rabs pa rtsags tsha /
NK065(cu)001:5049: gsang sngags kyi snod du ma gyur pa'i gdul bya
NK065(cu)001:5050: phal la ma bshad pas phyis 'byung bar lung bstan
NK065(cu)001:5052: snod ldan la bshad pas 'dir bla na med pa'i theg pa /
NK065(cu)001:5053: zhes gsungs pa dang mi 'gal lo gsungs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:5054: sngags kyi snod du ma gyur pa'i skal med la
NK065(cu)001:5055: phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa la don med cing
NK065(cu)001:5056: / skal ldan la phyis 'byung bar lung bstan na /
NK065(cu)001:5057: de ltar gsungs pa dang yang 'gal ba'i phyir ma nges so //
NK065(cu)001:5059: rgyu'i theg pa sde snod gsum ni dngos su zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' yin la /
NK065(cu)001:5060: 'bras bu'i theg pa rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod
NK065(cu)001:5061: rjes su gnang ba'i sgo nas gsungs pas gnyis ka
NK065(cu)001:5063: dang po la mdo'i gleng gzhi sogs kyis ma nges /
NK065(cu)001:5065: dpal ldan 'bras spungs su dus 'khor gyi rgyud gsungs pa sogs kyis ma nges so //
NK065(cu)001:5067: re zhig rdo rje'i theg pas 'dul ba'i dus la ma babs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5068: thub pa'i dbang pos gdul bya phal gyi snang ngor
NK065(cu)001:5069: yongs su grags par ma gsungs bas rigs can lnga
NK065(cu)001:5070: dang rgyal po zla bzang sogs la ma gsungs par
NK065(cu)001:5071: ma nges la / phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa'ang
NK065(cu)001:5072: 'jig rten du gsang sngags kyi sgra yongs su grags
NK065(cu)001:5073: par 'gyur pa la dgongs pa'i phyir skyon med do
NK065(cu)001:5074: ma nges la / // gnyis pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:5076: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK065(cu)001:5077: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK065(cu)001:5083: rgyal ba kun tu bzang pos rgyal tshab rigs lnga la brgyud /
NK065(cu)001:5084: rigs lngas rgyal sras sems dpa' sogs lhan cig pa'i 'khor la brgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:5086: mi ma yin la brgyud pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5087: mi dang mi ma yin pa gnyis la brgyud pa gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:5089: rgyal sras sems dpa'i 'khor rnams kyi nang nas rigs
NK065(cu)001:5090: gsum gyis gdul bya rang rang gi bsam pa dang
NK065(cu)001:5091: mthun par bstan cing dar bar mdzad de 'jam dpal
NK065(cu)001:5092: gyis lha'i gnas su lha grags ldan phyogs skyong la
NK065(cu)001:5093: bshad / des lha'i rig 'dzin rnams la brgyud cing dar bar bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:5094: spyan ras gzigs kyis klu'i gnas su /
NK065(cu)001:5095: klu rgyal mgrin pa nag po la bshad de rim par brgyud cing dar /
NK065(cu)001:5096: phyag na rdo rjes gnod sbyin gyi gnas su //
NK065(cu)001:5097: gnod sbyin kun tu bzang po la bshad de rim par brgyud cing dar ro //
NK065(cu)001:5099: thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'das pa na /
NK065(cu)001:5103: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK065(cu)001:5104: mi'i rig 'dzin li tsa b+ai dri med grags pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5105: dam pa'i rigs can lnga po rang rang gi mngon
NK065(cu)001:5106: par shes pas lang+ka'i yul gyi grong rdal gyi mtsho
NK065(cu)001:5107: gling ri ma la ya gnam lcags yod pa'i rtser
NK065(cu)001:5110: phyag na rdo rje mngon sum du byon nas //
NK065(cu)001:5111: rigs can lnga la bshad cing brgyud do //
NK065(cu)001:5113: mi yul du rgyud 'di thog mar babs tshul dang /
NK065(cu)001:5114: de las ji ltar brgyud tshul gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:5120: de la rtsod pa spang ba dang lnga /
NK065(cu)001:5123: gsang ba'i bdag pos mngon gshegs nas //
NK065(cu)001:5124: lha klu gnod sbyin srin po dang //
NK065(cu)001:5125: mi las skal ldan 'dus pa la //
NK065(cu)001:5126: dang pos ji ltar lung bstan dus //
NK065(cu)001:5127: rgyal bu rigs can ltas shar nas //
NK065(cu)001:5129: ri ma la ya'i rtser rigs can lnga la gsang bdag gis chos 'khor bskor ba'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:5130: de'i byin rlabs kyis rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas bdun shar zhing /
NK065(cu)001:5132: sngon thub pa'i dbang pos lung bstan pa bzhin du gsang sngags babs par bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:5133: de'ang lung ji ltar bstan snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:5134: 'gyur khyad tsam ma gtogs spyi mdo las gsungs pa dang tshig don mthun par /
NK065(cu)001:5135: sdom 'byung gi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK065(cu)001:5136: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK065(cu)001:5137: lo ni brgya dang bcu gnyis na //
NK065(cu)001:5138: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:5139: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK065(cu)001:5140: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK065(cu)001:5141: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK065(cu)001:5142: bsod nams chen po'i mthus snang ba'i //
NK065(cu)001:5143: gsang ba'i bdag pos snang bar 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:5146: gang du thub dbang gshegs nas lo nyer brgyad na babs par bshad pa mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:5147: 'dir lo brgyad dang bcu gnyis na babs par bshad pa'i phyir zer na /
NK065(cu)001:5149: lung 'dir bstan gyi lo bcu gnyis ni bcu tshan gnyis la dgongs pas don la nyi shu ste /
NK065(cu)001:5150: a ti zab don snying po'i lo rgyus las /
NK065(cu)001:5151: lo ni brgyad dang nyi shu'i tshe //
NK065(cu)001:5152: zhes gsungs pa dang mthun pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5153: brgyad dang nyi shu yang grangs kyi gnas gzhan 'god
NK065(cu)001:5154: pa'i rig pas don la nyi shu rtsa brgyad de
NK065(cu)001:5156: mya ngan las 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na /
NK065(cu)001:5158: a ti zab don snying por /
NK065(cu)001:5159: ston pa gshegs nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na rgyal po dzahl rmi ltas bdun byung ste /
NK065(cu)001:5162: rgya gar shar phyogs za hor gyi yul dang nye
NK065(cu)001:5163: ba lang+ka'i yul gyi ri ma la ya'i shar lho'i
NK065(cu)001:5164: ngos na a su ra'i brag phug bya ba yod
NK065(cu)001:5165: / der rgyal po dzahbasgruba pa mdzad cing bzhugs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5166: yang thog tu babs par bla ma gong ma rnams
NK065(cu)001:5167: / bzhed mod kyi / sher phyin tshul brgya lnga
NK065(cu)001:5168: bcu pa'i 'grel par za hor gyi yul nyid du
NK065(cu)001:5170: 'o na lang+ka'i yul de za hor gyi nye 'khor na yod pa gang gis shes zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:5171: de ni mdo'i 'grel pa sman pa lcags 'grol las /
NK065(cu)001:5172: za hor yul gyi nye 'khor na //
NK065(cu)001:5173: mthu stobs zhabs bcags ma la ya //
NK065(cu)001:5174: gnam lcags 'bar ba'i ri rtse na //
NK065(cu)001:5177: lang+ka za hor gyi nye 'khor na yod pa mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:5178: lang+ka'i yul ni rdo rje gdan gyi lho nub na yod la /
NK065(cu)001:5179: za hor shar na yod pa'i phyir zer /
NK065(cu)001:5180: lan du se ston chen po ni /
NK065(cu)001:5181: de gnyis kyi bar na 'gyang shin tu ring ba yod pa bden mod /
NK065(cu)001:5182: 'on kyang lang+ka dang za hor gnyis rgya mtsho'i do
NK065(cu)001:5183: la grong khyer zam ma chad par 'brel nas yod
NK065(cu)001:5184: pa la dgongs nas za hor gyi nye 'khor zhes
NK065(cu)001:5185: gsungs te / thugs sgrub rin chen 'bar ba las /
NK065(cu)001:5186: za hor yul zhes bya ba de //
NK065(cu)001:5187: rgyal mtsho'i gling gi ma h+aa do //
NK065(cu)001:5188: gnas pa 'dzam gling shar na gnas //
NK065(cu)001:5189: rgya mtsho'i gling la brgyud ma rung //
NK065(cu)001:5190: srin po lang+ka mgrin bcu'i yul //
NK065(cu)001:5192: srin po srin mo sha za rnams //
NK065(cu)001:5193: kun la dbang sgyur longs spyod che //
NK065(cu)001:5194: zhes 'byung ba'i phyir gsungs pa yang mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:5195: pha rol pa'i gegs ma sel ba'i steng /
NK065(cu)001:5196: de gnyis rgya mtsho'i do la grong khyer zam ma chad par 'brel ba'ang mi srid pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:5197: srid na'ang nye 'khor du mi rigs pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:5198: lung de'i don kyang de ltar ma yin par 'chad 'gyur las shes pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:5200: lang+ka'i yul yin na lho nub na yod dgos snyam pa'i dogs pa 'di /
NK065(cu)001:5201: rgol ba po khyod mthong rgya chung ba'am rnam dpyod rtsing ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:5202: 'dir bstan gyi lang+ka'i yul de rnga yab kyi lang+ka ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5204: 'di ni sngon bcom ldan 'das lang+ka'i bdag po sgra
NK065(cu)001:5205: sgrogs kyi bu mgrin bcus spyan drangs nas blo gros
NK065(cu)001:5207: lang+kara gshegs pa'i mdo gsungs pa'i gnas 'dzam gling gi shar lho mtshams na yod pa de yin cing /
NK065(cu)001:5208: yul de la sngon srin pos bzung pas lang+ka'i yul dang /
NK065(cu)001:5209: phyis ded dpon seng ges bzung bas /
NK065(cu)001:5210: ding sang seng+g+ha la'i gling zhes grags pa de yin te /
NK065(cu)001:5211: pan chen wa na rat+na'i zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:5212: sing+g+ha la'i gling de ni gsung rab las lang+ka'i gling du grags pa de yin te /
NK065(cu)001:5213: r+aa ma nas 'dzam bu'i gling dang lang+ka'i gling gi
NK065(cu)001:5214: bar du rdo'i zam pa btsugs pa rnams kyang rgya
NK065(cu)001:5215: mtsho'i nang na rdo'i phung po 'dug pa dngos su
NK065(cu)001:5216: snang zhing / skabs 'gar rdo'i phung po la gzigs thogs 'ong bas byol nas 'gro dgos pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5217: gling de na srin po lang+ka mgrin bcu bsad pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5218: khrag gis sbags pa yin zer ba'i rdo dmar po
NK065(cu)001:5219: snga dro tsam gyi sa'i cha khyab par yod pa
NK065(cu)001:5220: dang / gling de na su ma na k+au ta
NK065(cu)001:5221: zer ba'i ri bo sum gcig yan chad brag ri'i
NK065(cu)001:5222: ze bas bskor bas skye bo phal gyis bgrod mi
NK065(cu)001:5223: dang / nus pa der / pan chen 'khor bcas
NK065(cu)001:5224: kyis 'byon thub pa sogs kyi gtam rgyud gsung zhes
NK065(cu)001:5226: pan chen gyis gling der lo drug bzhugs par grags pas gtam khungs btsun par ma zad /
NK065(cu)001:5227: skyes bu de ni kun gyis rtsod med du bkur ba'i mkhas grub yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5229: lho nub rnga yab gling na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:5230: ri bo ma la ya sogs yod par bshad pas mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:5232: mtshan nyid de 'dra ba ci rigs gzhan na med pas ma khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:5233: 'dir bstan gyi a su ra dang ming gcig pa rgya bal mtshams na'ang yod la /
NK065(cu)001:5234: zhi byed kyi rgyud chu klung chen por gsungs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5235: gnas sid+g+ha la'i gling de'ang 'dir bstan dang don mi
NK065(cu)001:5236: gcig par rgyud de las gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:5237: 'di ltar 'thad pa'i rgyu mtshan gzhan yang yod de /
NK065(cu)001:5238: a nu'i rgyud rnams lang+ka'i yul du babs par kun la grags pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:5239: kun tu bzang po ye shes gsal bar ston pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5240: thabs kyi lam mchog 'dus pa'i rgyud kyi le'u lnga
NK065(cu)001:5241: par / ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud rnams ni rgyal po dzah'i khang steng du 'bab par 'gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:5242: a nu yo ga'i rgyud rnams ni sid+g+ha la'i nags tshal du 'byung bar 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:5244: des na gling der kha skad du su man k+au
NK065(cu)001:5245: ta zhes grags pa'i ri bo yod par gsungs pa'ang
NK065(cu)001:5246: / 'dir bshad pa'i drag shul can gyi ri'am /
NK065(cu)001:5247: ri bo ma la yar grags pa de yin nam snyam du sems te /
NK065(cu)001:5248: bgrod dka' ba sogs mtshan nyid cha 'dra ba yod par snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5250: ri ma la ya'i mtshan nyid kyang gang zhe na sman pa lcags 'grol las /
NK065(cu)001:5251: rtse na rtsal gyi rgyal po gnas //
NK065(cu)001:5252: ngos la brag dkar khyi tshugs pa //
NK065(cu)001:5253: seng ge gnam du mchongs 'dra brgyad //
NK065(cu)001:5254: rtsi sman rtsa brgyad tshang bar 'khrungs //
NK065(cu)001:5255: 'du ba'i nad kyis yongs mi tshugs //
NK065(cu)001:5256: spyi bor ka lan+ta ka ni //
NK065(cu)001:5257: mi gnyis gcig pur gnas pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:5258: mdzod ldan de yi tshangs bcas pa //
NK065(cu)001:5259: skal ldan rnams kyi bgrod par sla //
NK065(cu)001:5260: skal med rnams kyis yongs mi thar //
NK065(cu)001:5263: za hor gyi rgyal po u ta dz+ny+aa na'i sras rgyal po dzahla'o //
NK065(cu)001:5264: bzhi pa ni rgyal po nyid gsang sngags phyi rgyud
NK065(cu)001:5265: la sgrub pa mdzad cing bzhugs pa na rmi ltas
NK065(cu)001:5266: bdun shar te / de'ang mdo'i 'grel pa lung bstan ma las /
NK065(cu)001:5267: bdag nyid la ltas bdun shar ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:5269: sku gsung thugs rtags thim pa dang 1 //
NK065(cu)001:5270: rin chen glegs bam babs pa dang 2 //
NK065(cu)001:5271: chos kyi bgro ba byas pa dang 3 //
NK065(cu)001:5272: kun gyis dam par bsgrags pa dang 4 //
NK065(cu)001:5273: mchod pa chen po byas pa dang 5 //
NK065(cu)001:5274: rin chen char du babs pa6 //
NK065(cu)001:5275: sangs rgyas sa la lung bstan pa'o7 //
NK065(cu)001:5277: kha cig rmi lam gnyis pa dang gsum pa go barjesa nas 'chad de /
NK065(cu)001:5278: mdo 'grel ye shes snang ba rgyan gyi lugs su bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:5279: de nas rmi ltas dang mthun par dngos su rang
NK065(cu)001:5280: gi khang thog tu gsang sngags rgyud sde'i glegs bam
NK065(cu)001:5281: dang / phyag na rdo rje'i sku khru gang pa zhig babs te /
NK065(cu)001:5282: gsol ba btab pas rdor sems zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs nas /
NK065(cu)001:5283: de dang phyag rdor gyi sku la brten te zla
NK065(cu)001:5284: ba drug bsgrub pas rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal mjal
NK065(cu)001:5285: zhing byin gyis rlobs pa'i mthus glegs bam gyi don
NK065(cu)001:5287: zhes rje bla ma'i gter byon gyi a ti'i lo rgyus las gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:5288: snga rabs kyi bla ma phal cher /
NK065(cu)001:5289: rmi ltas bdun byung ba sad nas yang thog tu
NK065(cu)001:5290: byon pas phyag rdor gyi sku rnyed de la brten
NK065(cu)001:5291: te zla ba bdun bsgrub pas glegs bam rnams dngos
NK065(cu)001:5292: su babs pa la brtags na rtogs par 'dug kyang
NK065(cu)001:5293: / gdul bya rgyud la rang dgar 'jug pa dgag pa'i phyir ma rtogs pa ltar bstan nas /
NK065(cu)001:5294: glegs bam rnams shing rta la spyan drangs te u pa r+aa dza la bstan pas brda ma 'jal /
NK065(cu)001:5295: de nas dge slong ku ku r+aa dza la bstan pas /
NK065(cu)001:5296: des rdo rje sems dpa' zhal mthong gi le'u rtogs
NK065(cu)001:5297: te bsgrubs pas zhal mjal nas phyag rdor gyis ston
NK065(cu)001:5299: da dung bsgrubs pas phyag rdor byon nas /
NK065(cu)001:5300: spong len brtul zhugs spong ba'i dbang //
NK065(cu)001:5301: dge bar bskur nas sdig pa med //
NK065(cu)001:5302: ces don gyi bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad rdzogs pa'i dbang bskur /
NK065(cu)001:5303: tshig gi bstan pa li tsa b+ai dri med la zhus shig par lung bstan pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:5304: ku ku r+aa dzas gsang bdag gi bka' bzhin du bsgrubs te /
NK065(cu)001:5305: tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad du phye nas rgyal po dzahl bstan par bzhed cing /
NK065(cu)001:5306: tshul brgya lnga bcu pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5307: mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel par yang de ltar 'byung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:5308: lugs de gnyis ka la 'gal ba med de /
NK065(cu)001:5309: rgyal po nyid kyis rtogs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:5310: gzhan gyi gzu lum dang ras gcod dgag pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:5311: ku ku r+aa dza la bsten pa ltar mdzad pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5312: phyir ro // 'on kyang 'dir ni rgyal po rang gis rtogs pa'i phyogs legs te /
NK065(cu)001:5313: rgyal po nyid kyi mdzad pa'i lam rnam bkod las /
NK065(cu)001:5314: shar phyogs in+d+ra'i lung pa na //
NK065(cu)001:5315: rgya lung rdo rje brtsegs pa ru //
NK065(cu)001:5316: rigs can in+d+ra b+h+au ti ngas //
NK065(cu)001:5317: gsang ba'i bdag pos mngon bstan pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:5318: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i sgrub pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:5319: tshom bu lnga bcu stong dang bcas //
NK065(cu)001:5320: phyag na rdo rje mngon grub ste //
NK065(cu)001:5321: spong len brtul zhugs spyod pa'i dbang //
NK065(cu)001:5322: dge bar bskur nas sdig pa med //
NK065(cu)001:5323: de nas sa la reg par byas //
NK065(cu)001:5325: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim gyi lung snga ma'i 'phros las /
NK065(cu)001:5326: 'brel bas snang la mngon brtags pas //
NK065(cu)001:5327: thugs kyi sgrub pa mngon rtogs te //
NK065(cu)001:5328: de nyid sgo nas de nyid grub //
NK065(cu)001:5329: brtan pa'i dngos grub de nas 'thob //
NK065(cu)001:5330: don dam bcud kyis de nas rgyas //
NK065(cu)001:5332: smon pa'i lha dang de ru mjal //
NK065(cu)001:5333: zhes rang gis rtogs par bshad kyi /
NK065(cu)001:5334: gzhan la brten par ma bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:5335: de la tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad ni /
NK065(cu)001:5337: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi rgyud gsum gsum ste bco lnga /
NK065(cu)001:5338: spyi rgyud gsum ste bco brgyad do //
NK065(cu)001:5340: dpal phreng dam pa'i 'grel pa slob dpon ku ku r+aa dzas mdzad par /
NK065(cu)001:5341: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'i gzhi dang de' rtsa bar gyur pa'i rgyud sde lnga /
NK065(cu)001:5342: sgrub pa lag len du bstan pa rol pa'i rgyud lnga /
NK065(cu)001:5343: spyod pa'i yan lag tu 'gro ba'i rgyud lnga /
NK065(cu)001:5344: cho ga ma tshang ba kha skong bar byed pa rgyud phyi ma lta bu gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:5345: de thams cad kyi bsdus don lta bu'i rgyud chen po gcig dang bco brgyad do //
NK065(cu)001:5346: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdag cag gi rje bla ma'i dgongs pa'ang phyi mar gnas te /
NK065(cu)001:5347: shin tu legs pa nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:5350: glegs bam bltas nas bsgrubs pas 'grub na /
NK065(cu)001:5351: gsang sngags rang nyid len pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:5352: lus can dmyal ba 'ba' zhig rgyu //
NK065(cu)001:5354: bla ma med pas mi 'grub par bshad pa dang 'gal lo //
NK065(cu)001:5356: shar lho'i phyogs mtshams zhes zer ba de o d+y+aa
NK065(cu)001:5357: na yin zhes pa'ang 'jig rten gyi grags pa dang
NK065(cu)001:5358: mngon sum du 'gal lo zer ba /
NK065(cu)001:5360: skal med la de ltar 'gal yang /
NK065(cu)001:5361: skal ldan la nges pa med pa'i phyir mtha' gcig tu dgag pa mi rigs so //
NK065(cu)001:5362: rgyu mtshan dgyes rdor dang gdan bzhi sogs klu sgrub
NK065(cu)001:5363: kyis lkugs par bardzusa nas o d+y+aan nas brkus te
NK065(cu)001:5364: bros pa mkha' 'gro rnams kyis bdas kyang ma zin
NK065(cu)001:5365: te / skal ldan la byin cig ces rjes gnang
NK065(cu)001:5366: mdzad pa la brten nas slob dpon gyis dar bar
NK065(cu)001:5367: mdzad do zhes grags pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:5368: bi r+au pa la gsang sngags rang nyid len pa'i skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:5369: bdag med mas bstan pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:5370: de 'dod na phyag rdor gyis rgyal po dzahsogasa la bstan pa la'ang mtshungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:5371: gang du babs pa'i gnas sngar dpyad pa ltar yin
NK065(cu)001:5372: pas khyed kyi skyon 'di 'jug pa'i gnas med pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5374: shar lho mtshams kyi yul la o d+y+aan du 'dod
NK065(cu)001:5375: pa kho bo cag gi gzhung khungs ma gang du'ang
NK065(cu)001:5377: su zhig gis smras khyed cag la'ang cha med pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:5378: gsang sngags babs tshul 'di la thun mong du grags pa'i lung gi dpang po'ang yod de /
NK065(cu)001:5379: sher phyin tshul brgya lnga bcu pa'i 'gres pa las /
NK065(cu)001:5380: gsung rab 'di'i lo rgyus bshad na /
NK065(cu)001:5381: sngon sangs rgyas mi yul du lo brgyad cu bzhugs pa'i tshe na /
NK065(cu)001:5382: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga dang /
NK065(cu)001:5383: gu h+ya sa ma ya sogs pas 'dul zhing /
NK065(cu)001:5384: de nas theg pa de dag gi snod du gyur
NK065(cu)001:5385: pa 'dzam bu'i gling gi mi yul na med pas
NK065(cu)001:5386: rgyal chen rigs bzhi la sogs pa'i gnas na lha
NK065(cu)001:5387: rnams dang bskal pa bzang po'i byang chub sems dpa'
NK065(cu)001:5388: la sogs pa snod du gyur nas /
NK065(cu)001:5389: de'i tshe mdo sde de na bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:5390: slad kyis sangs rgyas mya ngan las 'das pa'i 'og
NK065(cu)001:5391: tu za hor gyi rgyal por 'khor dang bcas pa
NK065(cu)001:5393: chos la dad pa zhig 'dus pa theg pa de'i 'dul skal du gyur cing snod du gyur nas /
NK065(cu)001:5394: sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga la sogs pa mdo
NK065(cu)001:5395: sde chen po bco brgyad phyag na rdo rje'i byin
NK065(cu)001:5396: rlabs kyis za hor gyi yul du gshegs pa dang
NK065(cu)001:5397: / za hor gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+h+au tis mdo sde bltas pas brda ma 'phrod nas /
NK065(cu)001:5398: gang gis shes mngon shes kyis bltas pa na /
NK065(cu)001:5399: yul dbus su dge slong ku ku r+aa dza nyin re bzhin khyi stong la chos 'chad /
NK065(cu)001:5400: mtshan re bzhin khyi de dag la dam tshig gi
NK065(cu)001:5401: longs spyod mdzad pa zhig bzhugs pa de theg pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5403: bdag gi 'dul skal du 'gyur pa'ang 'dra nas /
NK065(cu)001:5404: rgyal pos pho nya btang ste slob dpon spyan drangs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5405: slob dpon gyis mngon shes kyis brtags pas bdag 'dul skal du'ang babs /
NK065(cu)001:5406: bdag kyang mdo sde'i snod du 'gyur bar shes mod kyi /
NK065(cu)001:5407: 'on kyang mdo sde de dag sngar ma bltas na /
NK065(cu)001:5408: rgya la rgyal po'i the tshom dag ma sel bar gyur na mi rung snyam nas /
NK065(cu)001:5409: mdo sde tshur blangs te bltas pa na /
NK065(cu)001:5410: mgo mjug gar yang blta ba'i cha ma mchis nas /
NK065(cu)001:5411: de nyid du lus brdabs te /
NK065(cu)001:5415: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' mngon par gshegs te /
NK065(cu)001:5417: bdag mdo sde zab mo 'di bltas pa tsam gyis shes par 'dod /
NK065(cu)001:5420: de nas sarba bud+d+ha sa ma yo ga la sogs
NK065(cu)001:5421: pa'i glegs bam rnams ma phye bar de dag gi
NK065(cu)001:5422: don yid la mngon sum gsal bar gyur to //
NK065(cu)001:5423: de nas slob dpon de za hor gyi yul du
NK065(cu)001:5424: gshegs nas rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa la chos
NK065(cu)001:5426: dpal rdo rje sems dpas lung bstan nas /
NK065(cu)001:5427: rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa rnams rdo rje dbyings
NK065(cu)001:5428: kyi dkyil 'khor lhar bkod nas bsgom du bcug pas
NK065(cu)001:5429: rim pa ltar rgyal po 'khor dang bcas pa dang
NK065(cu)001:5430: / de'i sras 'khor dang bcas pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5431: sras mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams /
NK065(cu)001:5432: sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin du grub bo //
NK065(cu)001:5433: de nas sras mo des rgyal bu la lung dang
NK065(cu)001:5434: man ngag bzhag pa las 'phel ba ni deng sang
NK065(cu)001:5437: mnyam sbyor gyi 'grel pa brgya byin sdong pos mdzad par yang /
NK065(cu)001:5438: sprul pa'i sku 'das phyi ma'i dus shig tshe //
NK065(cu)001:5439: rgyal ba'i bka' gsang 'dzam gling gnas su shar //
NK065(cu)001:5440: rgyal po'i khab tu spyan drangs mchod byas te //
NK065(cu)001:5441: dga' zhing gus bstod legs bltas brda ma 'jal //
NK065(cu)001:5442: thugs rje'i 'brel shugs gsang sngags 'dzin par grags //
NK065(cu)001:5443: dam par bzung ste glegs bam gzigs par zhus //
NK065(cu)001:5444: sgyu 'phrul thig le stong pa'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:5445: grub thob lhag pa'i lha yis lung bstan mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:5446: rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung lugs sna tshogs mtha' //
NK065(cu)001:5447: dam pa rnams kyi gdams pa ji bzhin pa //
NK065(cu)001:5448: mi 'gal legs par bsdus shing rab bkrol te //
NK065(cu)001:5449: 'grel dang bsdus don sgrub thabs mang du bstan //
NK065(cu)001:5451: gzhan yang lo ts+aa ba gzu dga' rdor gyis n+aa
NK065(cu)001:5452: len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na pusti'i char babs pa'i bkod
NK065(cu)001:5453: pa ri mor bris pa mthong ba sogs mkhas pa
NK065(cu)001:5454: la grags pa'i gtam nges pa can mang du yod
NK065(cu)001:5455: pas de thams cad mi bden no zhes smra dgos
NK065(cu)001:5456: na ha cang thal ba'i phyir bag yod par mdzod
NK065(cu)001:5458: rgyal po dzahs tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad po /
NK065(cu)001:5459: ku ku r+aa dza la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5462: des u pa r+aa dza la /
NK065(cu)001:5463: des sras mo go ma de w+ai la bstan te /
NK065(cu)001:5464: de rnams kyis bsgrubs pas rang rang gi tshom bu
NK065(cu)001:5465: dang bcas te rig pa 'dzin pa'i sar gshegs so
NK065(cu)001:5468: de nas rdo rje gdan steng gi //
NK065(cu)001:5469: 'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams su //
NK065(cu)001:5470: pho brang dam pa rin chen nang //
NK065(cu)001:5471: bkra shis dam pa'i khang bu ru //
NK065(cu)001:5472: ku ku r+aa dz+aan+d+ri b+h+au ti //
NK065(cu)001:5473: sim ha u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK065(cu)001:5474: sras mo go ma sa la sogs //
NK065(cu)001:5475: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK065(cu)001:5476: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon bsgrubs te //
NK065(cu)001:5477: rdo rje 'chang sar mngon du gshegs //
NK065(cu)001:5479: sras mos rgyal po ku ku r+aa dza /
NK065(cu)001:5480: slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje /
NK065(cu)001:5481: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba gsum la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5482: rgyal po ku ku r+aa dzas /
NK065(cu)001:5483: ro langs bde ba'i dngos grub dang /
NK065(cu)001:5484: drang srong b+ha shi ta gnyis la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5485: snga mas rdo rje bzhad pa la /
NK065(cu)001:5486: de dang phyi ma gnyis kas za hor gyi rgyal po pra hasti la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5487: de la slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:5488: slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam b+ha bas gsan /
NK065(cu)001:5489: yang slob dpon pad+mas ni rgyal po dzahnyida la'ang gsan
NK065(cu)001:5490: par a ti zab don snying po las gsungs so
NK065(cu)001:5492: sangs rgyas gsang ba gnyis kyis /
NK065(cu)001:5493: pan chen bi ma la mi tra la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5494: des bod du lo ts+aa ba rma rin chen mchog dang /
NK065(cu)001:5495: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra gnyis la bshad cing /
NK065(cu)001:5496: mnga' bdag ral pa can gyi dus su rmas bsgyur zhes rje g.yung bzhed kyang /
NK065(cu)001:5497: kun mkhyen chos rje'i dgongs pa ltar rma gnyags thun
NK065(cu)001:5498: mong gis mnga' bdag khri srong gi dus bsgyur gsung
NK065(cu)001:5500: spyir rtsa rgyud 'di la bod du lo pan bsdebs pa'i gzhi 'gyur gsum dang /
NK065(cu)001:5501: pan+di ta med pa'i rtsal 'gyur gnyis te 'gyur lnga byung bar grags pa las /
NK065(cu)001:5503: sangs rgyas gsang ba dang bee ro tsa na'i snga 'gyur /
NK065(cu)001:5504: pad+ma dang gnyags dz+ny+aa na'i bar 'gyur /
NK065(cu)001:5505: bi ma la dang rma gnyags thun mong gi phyi 'gyur gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:5506: 'di ni phyi ma ste 'phyong can yin la /
NK065(cu)001:5507: snga bar gnyis la 'phyong med par grags so //
NK065(cu)001:5509: thar lo nyi ma rgyal mtshan gyi 'gyur dang /
NK065(cu)001:5510: 'gos lo ts+aa ba gzhon nu'i zhabs kyi 'gyur bcos gnyis so //
NK065(cu)001:5512: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la rma gnyags gnyis las brgyud pa'i bka' srol gsum pa babs te /
NK065(cu)001:5513: de yang rma rin chen mchog gis //
NK065(cu)001:5514: gtsug ru rin chen gzhon nu dang /
NK065(cu)001:5515: gye re mchog skyong gnyis la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5516: de gnyis kas dar rje dpal gyi grags pa dang zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan gnyis la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5517: dar rje las yongs grags dbus lugs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5518: khams lugs pa zhes bka' srol gnyis su gyes /
NK065(cu)001:5519: zhang la gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis gsan /
NK065(cu)001:5520: 'di la sgyu 'phrul gdams ngag lugs sam nor bu lugs su grags te bka' sgrol gcig go //
NK065(cu)001:5522: slob dpon pad+ma dang bi ma la gnyis ka'i slob ma gnyags dz+ny+aa nas /
NK065(cu)001:5523: sog po dpal gyi ye shes la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5524: des gnubs la bshad de bka' srol gcig go //
NK065(cu)001:5525: yang rma gnyags thun mong gi slob ma khu byang chub 'od dang /
NK065(cu)001:5528: khyung pos dar rje la bshad /
