NK065(cu)001:5529: zhang gis mkhas pa gtsug gyer rnam gnyis dang khu'i
NK065(cu)001:5530: bshad bka' gtso bor bzung bar bka' phyogs skyong ma
NK065(cu)001:5531: dang / gnas las btags pa bka' mchims phu mar yang grags te /
NK065(cu)001:5532: gnubs la bshad pa ni bka' srol gcig go //
NK065(cu)001:5533: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes la /
NK065(cu)001:5535: sras kyi dam pa gcig dang lnga byung ba las /
NK065(cu)001:5540: sru legs pa'i sgron me rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:5541: sras kyi dam pa gcig ni gnubs yon tan rgya matsho'o //
NK065(cu)001:5542: des sras ye shes rgya mtsho la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5544: so ye shes dbang phyug gis nyang shes rab mchog la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5545: des nyang ye shes 'byung gnas la //
NK065(cu)001:5546: des lha rje zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5547: de la slob ma rtse mo bzhi /
NK065(cu)001:5549: sgom chen brgya rtsa brgyad sogs byung ba las /
NK065(cu)001:5554: lha rje zur chung ba shes rab grags pa rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:5559: dral ma sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:5560: yus po che mi gnyis sogs mang du byung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:5561: de la ka ba bzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:5562: rdzogs chen gyi ka ba skyo ston sh+aaka ye /
NK065(cu)001:5563: mdo'i ka ba yang khyed bla ma /
NK065(cu)001:5564: sgyu 'phrul gyi ka ba glan sh+aakya bzang po /
NK065(cu)001:5565: phrin sgrub kyi ka ba mda' tig chos sh+aaka go //
NK065(cu)001:5566: lha rje zur chung ba'i sras /
NK065(cu)001:5568: gsang bdag sgro phug pa chen po sh+aakya seng ge gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:5569: rje sgro phug pas yab kyi slob ma ka ba bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:5570: glan nya tshal pa sh+aakya byang chub rnams la gtugs te legs par gsan /
NK065(cu)001:5571: sgro phug pa la gdugs thogs kyi slob ma grwa sa 'dzin pa stong dang /
NK065(cu)001:5572: de'i nang nas kyang thugs zin gyi slob ma bzhi gsum bcu gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:5573: de la nag po bzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:5577: 'dar nag gtsug tor dbang phyug gam /
NK065(cu)001:5578: kha cig lce dpal seng zer /
NK065(cu)001:5584: phyi ma gnyis phri nas gnyan ston dang /
NK065(cu)001:5585: kha rag ston bsnan pa'ang mthong ngo //
NK065(cu)001:5591: des sngon du phyi ma gnyis phri nas shangs pa rtse ser ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:5592: bya ston rdo rje grags gnyis bgrangs so //
NK065(cu)001:5593: de yang la stod pa gtsang nag 'od 'bar gyis /
NK065(cu)001:5596: gtsang pa byis ston rnams la'ang nyan mod kyi /
NK065(cu)001:5597: gtso bor thugs thag gcod sa ni /
NK065(cu)001:5598: nya ri dri ngas pa nye'u ston chos seng ngo //
NK065(cu)001:5600: gcung gi mi ston mgon po la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5601: des so shes rab tshul khrims la /
NK065(cu)001:5604: des zur thams cad mkhyen pa byams pa seng ge la /
NK065(cu)001:5605: des sgrol ma pa 'bro ston bsam 'grub rdo rje la /
NK065(cu)001:5606: des sgrol chen sangs rgyas rin chen la /
NK065(cu)001:5607: des 'gos lo thams cad mkhyen pa gzhon nu dpal la /
NK065(cu)001:5608: des spyan snga rin po che ye shes dpal bzang po la /
NK065(cu)001:5609: des sgyur chos rgyal rin chen phun tshogs la /
NK065(cu)001:5610: des rang grol nyi zla sangs rgyas la /
NK065(cu)001:5611: de la 'khon tshe dbang nor rgyas kyis gsan pa
NK065(cu)001:5612: ni spar khab kyi bshad srol dang lung gi brgyud
NK065(cu)001:5613: pa ste / g.yung t+aika ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:5615: zur byams seng gnyis ka la /
NK065(cu)001:5616: g.yung ston rdo rje dpal gyis gsan /
NK065(cu)001:5617: des brag rgya bo pa ston pa mkha' 'gro la /
NK065(cu)001:5618: des rgya bo bla ma bkra shis la /
NK065(cu)001:5619: des rgya bo sri thar bsam 'grub la /
NK065(cu)001:5620: des slob dpon u legs pa la //
NK065(cu)001:5621: de la 'khor jo sras tshe dbang nor rgyas kyis gsan nas /
NK065(cu)001:5622: rang gi sras lung rtogs kyi mnga' bdag dpal 'byor lhun grub la bshad /
NK065(cu)001:5623: des zur chen bkra shis kun dga' la /
NK065(cu)001:5624: des smyos ston gsang bdag dpa' bo phrin las lhun grub dpal bzang po la /
NK065(cu)001:5625: des bka' drin mtshungs med gter chen chos kyi rgyal
NK065(cu)001:5626: po gter bdag gling pa 'jigs bral phyogs thams cad
NK065(cu)001:5627: las rnam par rgyal ba'i sde la /
NK065(cu)001:5628: des bdag gnyos kyi ban chung d+harma sh+r+ai la dgyes bzhin du stsal to //
NK065(cu)001:5629: gzhan yang sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang dang man ngag rgya gzhung phra mo'i dpe lung mang po dang /
NK065(cu)001:5630: lo ts+aa ba chen po d+harma b+ha dras mdzad pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5631: t+ai ka tshul bzhi yan lag bco lnga pa dang
NK065(cu)001:5632: / kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po'i t+aika phyogs bcu
NK065(cu)001:5633: mun sel rnams kyi bka' lung yang bdag la stsal
NK065(cu)001:5636: rgyud phran dang bcas pa rnams ni /
NK065(cu)001:5637: grogs rdo rje theg pa'i don gyi dge 'dun gnyis
NK065(cu)001:5638: brgya brgal ba dang thabs cig bar snga 'gyur bla
NK065(cu)001:5639: na med pa'i rgyud 'bum chen po stan thog gcig
NK065(cu)001:5640: tu stsal ba'i dus legs par nod cing /
NK065(cu)001:5642: brgyad cu pa ni gnas skabs gzhan du'ang lan du mar bka' drin du stsal te /
NK065(cu)001:5643: de dag gi brgyud pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5644: brgyud pa so so'i sku che ba'i lo rgyus la
NK065(cu)001:5645: sogs pa ni 'dir yi ge mang gi dogs nas
NK065(cu)001:5646: ma bkod pas gzhan las shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:5647: mdor na bdag cag gi dpal ldan bla ma dam
NK065(cu)001:5648: pa sa'i steng na 'gran pa'i zla thams cad dang
NK065(cu)001:5649: bral ba'i gtso bo gcig pu pa /
NK065(cu)001:5650: mtshan brjod par dka' ba rje btsun thams cad mkhyen
NK065(cu)001:5651: pa gter chen chos kyi rgyal po zhes lha dang
NK065(cu)001:5652: bcas pa'i 'jig rten du rnam par grags pa 'di
NK065(cu)001:5653: ni / spyir rgyal ba'i bstan pa yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5654: bye brag snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa bka' gter thams cad kyi ston pa po dang /
NK065(cu)001:5655: khyad par sgyu 'phrul snying po'i skor gyi dbang bka'
NK065(cu)001:5656: bshad bka' gdams ngag yan lag dang bcas pa nub
NK065(cu)001:5657: par nye ba na lha rje zur po che nyid
NK065(cu)001:5658: 'di'i nges pa gsal bar mdzad pa'i phyir slar yang
NK065(cu)001:5660: nges pa'i don du ni rje rin po che 'di
NK065(cu)001:5661: la thug pa rnams nye brgyud rmad du byung ba
NK065(cu)001:5662: yin no // gnyis pa che ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:5664: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di //
NK065(cu)001:5665: gzhan las 'phags pa'i che ba brgyad //
NK065(cu)001:5667: rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po yin pas nges par
NK065(cu)001:5668: che ba gzi ldan gsal ba'i nyi ma lta bu
NK065(cu)001:5669: / theg pa thams cad kyi yang rtse yin pas
NK065(cu)001:5670: che ba dbus kyi ri bo mchog rab lta bu
NK065(cu)001:5671: / / bstan pa thams cad kyi 'byung khungs yin pas che ba 'byung ba nam mkha' lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:5672: lung thams cad kyi spyi 'grel yin pas che ba
NK065(cu)001:5673: nam mkhas snang srid kyi go phye ba lta bu
NK065(cu)001:5674: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dgongs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:5675: zhe phugs yin pas che ba rgyal po'i bka' gsang
NK065(cu)001:5677: 'bras bu thams cad kyi thug sa yin pas che
NK065(cu)001:5678: ba yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin chen lta bu
NK065(cu)001:5679: / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gshegs shul
NK065(cu)001:5680: yin pas che ba stong lam gyi shul lta bu
NK065(cu)001:5681: / / ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi
NK065(cu)001:5682: lam yin pas che ba khri lam lta bu ste
NK065(cu)001:5683: / / brgyad do // de las dang po ni /
NK065(cu)001:5684: ji ltar nyi ma'i snang ba ni snang ba thams
NK065(cu)001:5685: cad kyi rgyal po yin pa bzhin du rgyud 'di
NK065(cu)001:5686: nyid kyang rgyud thams cad kyi rgyal po ste /
NK065(cu)001:5688: gsang ba'i snying po nges pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:5689: gsang sngags kun gyi rgyal po yin //
NK065(cu)001:5692: ji ltar lhun po'i rtser phyin na ri bran thams cad mig 'og tu tshud pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:5693: rgyud 'di'i don rtogs na theg pa thams cad kyi
NK065(cu)001:5694: don 'dir 'dus pa'i phyir de thams cad shes par
NK065(cu)001:5696: mnyam nyid don rtogs rang rig rgyal po ni //
NK065(cu)001:5697: rgya mtsho chen por chu klung kun 'bab ltar //
NK065(cu)001:5698: bla med don rtogs thabs chen 'di dag tu //
NK065(cu)001:5699: rnam thar theg pa bsam yas ma lus 'dus //
NK065(cu)001:5702: ji ltar nam mkha' las 'byung ba bzhi shar nas snod bcud chags pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:5703: rgyud 'di'i byin rlabs las bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad 'phros pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:5705: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK065(cu)001:5706: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:5707: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:5708: phyogs bcu kun tu rab grags pa //
NK065(cu)001:5709: gsang ba'i snying po las 'phros te //
NK065(cu)001:5712: ji ltar nam mkha' snang srid kyi go phye ba ltar /
NK065(cu)001:5713: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi don dang 'bras
NK065(cu)001:5714: bu thams cad 'dir 'dus shing 'dis ston pas na
NK065(cu)001:5715: lung thams cad kyi spyi 'grel te /
NK065(cu)001:5717: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK065(cu)001:5721: ji ltar rgyal po'i bka' gsang thob pa'i mi ni
NK065(cu)001:5722: rgyal po'i blo'i gtad pa yin pas 'bangs blon gzhan
NK065(cu)001:5723: la rag mi lus pa bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:5724: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs kyi gsang
NK065(cu)001:5725: ba dam pa'i mthar thug 'di las mi 'da' bas
NK065(cu)001:5726: 'di'i don rtogs na theg pa gzhan la rag lus
NK065(cu)001:5729: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:5730: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:5733: ji ltar yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin chen ni
NK065(cu)001:5734: 'dod rgu thams cad ster ba'i mchog mthar thug tu
NK065(cu)001:5736: bstan pa dang theg pa thams cad kyi mthar thug
NK065(cu)001:5737: gi 'bras bu ni rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po
NK065(cu)001:5740: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK065(cu)001:5741: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK065(cu)001:5744: ji ltar gang du 'gro ba'i lam po cher //
NK065(cu)001:5745: der slebs pa thams cad kyis phyin pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:5746: sngar 'das pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad lam 'di la brten nas sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5748: 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK065(cu)001:5749: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus kun //
NK065(cu)001:5750: brnyes nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK065(cu)001:5753: ji ltar gnas der slar 'gro 'gyur rnams kyang lam de la 'gro ba bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:5754: ma 'ongs pa na 'tshang rgya 'gyur rnams kyang lam
NK065(cu)001:5755: 'di kho na la bsten nas 'tshang rgya bar 'gyur
NK065(cu)001:5760: gsum pa che ba de ldan gyi rgyud don bshad pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:5761: de yang rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad kyang dgos 'brel yan lag bzhi ldan du gnas te /
NK065(cu)001:5763: brjod 'brel dgos dang yang dgos dang //
NK065(cu)001:5764: rgyu rkyen yan lag bzhi ru 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:5766: de'i don gyis dgos sogs mthong na nges par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5767: re zhig thog mar dgos 'brel brjod pa la /
NK065(cu)001:5768: dri bas mtshams sbyar ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:5769: lan gyis rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:5772: 'di la brjod par gyur pa gang //
NK065(cu)001:5773: 'di yi dgos pa'ang ci zhig yin //
NK065(cu)001:5775: brjod par byed pa gang la brjod //
NK065(cu)001:5779: stong nyid snying rjer sbyor ba ni //
NK065(cu)001:5780: brjod par bya ba 'dir bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:5781: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub ni //
NK065(cu)001:5782: dgos pa'i gtso bo'i rang bzhin phyir //
NK065(cu)001:5783: 'jig rten pa yi lam gyur pas //
NK065(cu)001:5784: sna tshogs rang bzhin mtha' dag go //
NK065(cu)001:5785: thabs dang thabs byung 'brel ba ste //
NK065(cu)001:5786: bla ma slob ma dag kyang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:5787: gang gis brjod bya 'chad byed pa //
NK065(cu)001:5788: de ni rjod byed du bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:5790: mtshon bya rang bzhin gyi rgyud gzhi lam 'bras gsum
NK065(cu)001:5791: gcig tu gyur pa'i zung 'jug rang bzhin gyi chos
NK065(cu)001:5794: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi yi rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:5796: de khong du chud par bya ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5797: mtshon byed yi ge'i rgyud rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu
NK065(cu)001:5798: 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa bshad kyi rgyud rnams ni rjod
NK065(cu)001:5801: sgro skur med par bstan pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:5802: mtshon byed sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste //
NK065(cu)001:5804: rjod byed la brten nas brjod bya'i don rnams shes pa ni dgos pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5806: mdzub mos ri bong can bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:5808: de ltar shes pa'i don nyams su blangs pas thun
NK065(cu)001:5809: mong gi dngos grub thob pa ni nying dgos phra
NK065(cu)001:5810: mo dang / slob ba dang mi slob pa'i zung
NK065(cu)001:5811: 'jug phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub thob
NK065(cu)001:5812: pa ni dgos pa'i yang dgos pa mchog ste /
NK065(cu)001:5814: dgos pa'i dgos pa 'bras bu nyid //
NK065(cu)001:5816: de'ang brjod bya rjod byed gnyis shes bya shes byed dang /
NK065(cu)001:5817: rjod byed dang dgos pa gnyis thabs dang thabs byung dang /
NK065(cu)001:5818: bla ma dang slob ma'i 'brel pa ni don rtags
NK065(cu)001:5819: kyi khyad par gyis ngo bo nyid dang snod bcud
NK065(cu)001:5820: du 'brel la / dgos pa dang nying dgos gnyis de las de byung dang /
NK065(cu)001:5821: nying dgos dang brjod bya gnyis ngo bo bdag nyid gcig par 'brel pa rnams ni 'brel pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5822: tsan+d+ra go mis rig pa grub pa'i sgron mar /
NK065(cu)001:5825: de lta bu'i don dang ldan pa'i rgyud 'di bshad pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK065(cu)001:5826: spyir theg pa chen po gsang sngags kyi sgor spyad
NK065(cu)001:5827: pa spyod pa'i skyes bu blo gros can rnams kyi
NK065(cu)001:5828: don du gnyer ba'i gtso bo ni gzhan don phun
NK065(cu)001:5830: gzhan don phun tshogs sangs rgyas kyi //
NK065(cu)001:5833: de'i rten ni rang don phun tshogs kyi byang chub ces grags pa 'bras rgyud yin la /
NK065(cu)001:5834: de mngon du byed pa'ang nyer len gyi rgyu dang /
NK065(cu)001:5835: lhan cig byed pa'i rkyen gnyis tshang ba la rag las pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5836: dang po'i dbang du byas te gazhi'am rgyu'i rgyud bzhag /
NK065(cu)001:5837: gnyis pa'i dbang du byas te thabs sam lam gyi rgyud bzhag go //
NK065(cu)001:5838: de'i phyir rgyud thams cad kyi brjod bya'i don rnams
NK065(cu)001:5839: ma lus pa gzhi lam 'bras gsum du 'du ba
NK065(cu)001:5840: nyid do // zhes rgyud gsum gyi ming gang la gdags bya'i yul ngos bzung nas /
NK065(cu)001:5842: tha snyad kyi dbang du byas te rnam par dbye ba /
NK065(cu)001:5843: don gyi dbang du byas te rnam par bsdu ba /
NK065(cu)001:5844: bsdus pa'i don gtan la dbab pa dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:5847: snang ba gsum mam bzhir dbye ba /
NK065(cu)001:5848: rnal 'byor gsum mam rigs gsum du dbye ba /
NK065(cu)001:5849: gzhi lam 'bras gsum du dbye ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:5852: rgyud ni rgyun chags la bshad de /
NK065(cu)001:5855: chos nyid rang bzhin gyi rnam par dag pa rgyu'i rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:5856: rang bzhin mngon du byed pa thabs kyi rgyud /
NK065(cu)001:5857: rang bzhin mngon du byas pa 'bras bu'i rgyud de /
NK065(cu)001:5858: shes thob kyi bya byed dang bdag nyid gcig par 'brel zhing /
NK065(cu)001:5859: gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi dgos pa ma tshang ba med pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:5861: 'brel dang ma tshang med pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:5862: phun sum tshogs pas rgyud ces bya //
NK065(cu)001:5865: thams cad du 'brel zhing thams cad tshang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5869: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya yi //
NK065(cu)001:5870: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo las //
NK065(cu)001:5871: rgyud kyi dbye ba rnam par bzhag /
NK065(cu)001:5872: gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo yang //
NK065(cu)001:5874: des na snang ba bzhi dag tu //
NK065(cu)001:5875: lung rigs kun las gsal bar bshad //
NK065(cu)001:5876: ces pas gzhi rang bzhin gyi snang ba /
NK065(cu)001:5878: 'bras bu bde gshegs kyi snang ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:5879: gzhi ni chos thams cad kyi 'byung gzhi /
NK065(cu)001:5882: rang bzhin dag ni bcos min dang //
NK065(cu)001:5883: gzhan la ltos pa med pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:5884: zhes pa ltar shes rab dang gtan tshigs kyis ma byas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5885: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:5886: gdul bya ni thun mong dang mchog gi sems lnga skyes sam skyer rung ba /
NK065(cu)001:5888: de gdul bya'i blo'i rim pas bye brag tu snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:5889: bral thob med pa'i yon tan nar son pas bde gshegs /
NK065(cu)001:5891: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:5892: de gsum ngo bo sems su gcig kyang so sor snang ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:5893: log rtog 'khrul ba'i snang bas bslad pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5894: yul yul can gnyis med pa gnyis su rtogs pas log rtog /
NK065(cu)001:5895: de ma yin la der bzung pas 'khrul ba /
NK065(cu)001:5896: las dang log rtog gi blor snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:5897: de ltar snang ba bzhi las /
NK065(cu)001:5898: phyi ma ni sbyang bya'i dri ma yin pas 'brel
NK065(cu)001:5899: ba dang dgos pa med pa'i phyir rgyud du bzhag
NK065(cu)001:5900: tu med pas rgyud kyi dbye ba ni gsum nyid
NK065(cu)001:5902: sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK065(cu)001:5903: tshad ma gsum gyi dngos po yis //
NK065(cu)001:5904: rnal 'byor gsum gyi phung po la //
NK065(cu)001:5905: rigs dang snang ba'i yan lag bzhag /
NK065(cu)001:5906: de nyid thur ma'i mchog tu nges //
NK065(cu)001:5907: zhes pas 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ma 'dres
NK065(cu)001:5908: la yongs su rdzogs pa ni bya ba gzhi'i rnal
NK065(cu)001:5911: de'i don la bcos slad med par ye nas gnas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:5913: phyi nang bye brag ji snyed pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:5914: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK065(cu)001:5915: ji bzhin ngang du ye gnas pa //
NK065(cu)001:5916: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK065(cu)001:5918: lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis med kyi 'jug pa byed pa rkyen gyi rnal 'byor te /
NK065(cu)001:5919: shes thob kyi rkyen du gyur pa'i byed rtsol gyi ngang du blo gnas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:5920: 'bras bur smin pa ni bya ba byas zin pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:5921: des rang gzhan gyi don gnyis med mngon du gyur
NK065(cu)001:5922: pa la dbang 'byor ba ni bya bral 'bras bu'i
NK065(cu)001:5923: rnal 'byor ro // 'o na 'dir bstan gyi rnal 'byor gsum dang /
NK065(cu)001:5925: bya ba gzhi dang byed pa rkyen //
NK065(cu)001:5927: ces gsungs pa gnyis dgongs pa gcig gam tha dad zer na /
NK065(cu)001:5929: lam rim so so'i go mthun brtsi tshul na gcig par mdzad kyang /
NK065(cu)001:5930: rnal 'byor phyi ma gnyis 'di dang bzhed tshul tha dad par mngon te /
NK065(cu)001:5933: theg pa de ni bya byed rkyen //
NK065(cu)001:5934: zhes kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum la byed pa rkyen gyi rnal 'byor du gsungs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:5935: gzhan du 'bras bu re rtsol med //
NK065(cu)001:5936: bsgrub bya nyid la lam gnas pa //
NK065(cu)001:5937: thabs chen theg 'di bya bral ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:5939: zhes phyi dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa gsum dang /
NK065(cu)001:5940: nang dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa gsum la bya bral 'bras bu'i rnal 'byor du gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5941: 'o na 'dir yang de dang mthun par bshad par bya ba yin nam snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:5945: mthar thug gi rnal 'byor bya ba med pa'i rgyud
NK065(cu)001:5946: du byung zin pas mi 'gyur ba 'bras bu'i rigs
NK065(cu)001:5947: so // zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:5948: yang 'dir rigs dang zhes pa'i zur gyis rigs gsum du'ang 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:5949: ngo bo gzhan du mi 'gyur zhing ma chad pa phyi mo'i rigs dang /
NK065(cu)001:5950: sems lnga bskyed pas chos nyid kyi rgyud du byung zhing /
NK065(cu)001:5951: de'i mi mthun phyogs su mi gtong ba rtsol ba'i rigs dang /
NK065(cu)001:5952: rgyud du byung zin pas lam rtsol gyi bya ba
NK065(cu)001:5953: med pa 'bras bu'i rigs dang gsum du bshad do
NK065(cu)001:5956: gzhi lam 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos //
NK065(cu)001:5958: gang rtogs bya gzhi'i rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:5959: gang gis rtogs shing bgrod pa lam gyi rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:5960: gang du mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i rgyud de gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du'ang bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:5961: de ltar na'ang dbye sgo bzhi'i nang gses bcu gnyis
NK065(cu)001:5962: su phye ba de rnams ngo bo ris su chad
NK065(cu)001:5963: pa zhig na / thugs thig las /
NK065(cu)001:5964: gcig la gsum gyi ngo bo yang //
NK065(cu)001:5966: yang ldog bcas kyi dbye ba'ang med par gcig pa
NK065(cu)001:5967: zhig na so sor phye ba dang 'gal lo zhe
NK065(cu)001:5968: na / ngo bo gcig la ldog pa tha dad pas skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:5970: de ltar ye shes rang gnas pa //
NK065(cu)001:5971: lam dang 'bras bu kun ngo bo //
NK065(cu)001:5972: zhes pas ngo bo rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems su gcig par gsungs pa gang zhig /
NK065(cu)001:5973: de'i mtshon tshul gyi ldog cha gzhi lam 'bras gsum du tha dad par snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5974: gnyis pa rnam par bsdu ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:5975: shes bya'i chos kun gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du 'du ste /
NK065(cu)001:5976: sngar dbye sgo bzhir phye ba de rnams ming gi
NK065(cu)001:5977: rnam grangs tsam las ngo bo tha dad du ma
NK065(cu)001:5978: grub pa'i phyir / dper na skyes bu gcig nyid
NK065(cu)001:5979: la ming gi rnam grangs du ma btags pa bzhin
NK065(cu)001:5980: grub pa'i phyir / no // gsum pa bsdus pa'i don gtan la dbab pa la /
NK065(cu)001:5981: gzhi lam 'bras gsum spyir gtan la dbab pas mdor bstan /
NK065(cu)001:5982: de so sor gtan la dbab pas rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:5992: nges byed kyi tshad ma bsam pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:5994: gang las 'byed pa'i gzhir med mi rung ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:5995: dbye gzhi med pa'i dbye sgo mi mtshungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:5996: shes bya tsam dbye gzhir 'thad ces mkhas pa phal cher zhal mthun par gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:5999: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i shes bya rnams //
NK065(cu)001:6000: 'bru mthun tshig don shes bya'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:6001: rnam gsum rgyud kyi don du bsdus //
NK065(cu)001:6004: lung rigs man ngag gsum dang 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6007: dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshigs sam /
NK065(cu)001:6008: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK065(cu)001:6009: rtogs par nus pa ma yin te //
NK065(cu)001:6014: de ming zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK065(cu)001:6015: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK065(cu)001:6018: shes bya tsam dbye gzhir byas nas gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi yang shes byar thal /
NK065(cu)001:6019: dbye gzhi'i khyab bya yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6021: de shes bya'i yul las 'das pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:6023: chos dbyings shes bya ma yin pas //
NK065(cu)001:6024: de ni rnam par shes mi nus //
NK065(cu)001:6027: don dam blo yi spyod yul min //
NK065(cu)001:6028: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zer na /
NK065(cu)001:6030: gnas lugs shes bya ma yin kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6031: gtan la 'bebs ldog shes bya'i yul yin pas skyon med zer kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6032: gtan la dbab bya kho na gnas lugs de yin pa'i phyir mi 'thad gsung /
NK065(cu)001:6034: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi shes byar thal ba la skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:6035: dgongs 'dus kyi lung de'i don ni /
NK065(cu)001:6036: rtog ge'i rigs pas mi rtogs pa la dgongs kyi /
NK065(cu)001:6037: kun khyab kyi gtan tshigs gsum gyis mi rtogs pa la dgongs pa ma yin bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:6038: man ngag kyang gnas lugs pa tha dad med pa la brjod kyi /
NK065(cu)001:6039: gtan la 'bebs tshul la brjod pa ma yin no //
NK065(cu)001:6040: 'on kyang shes bya la dngos po dang dngos med
NK065(cu)001:6041: gnyis su kha tshon chod dam ma chod zer na
NK065(cu)001:6042: / de tsam du gsang ba sgyu 'phrul pa'i lugs
NK065(cu)001:6043: kyi lam mtha' dag lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin
NK065(cu)001:6046: gnas lugs de dngos po dang dngos med kyi mthar thal zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6047: lam yang lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gang rung gis mtshon nus par thal lo //
NK065(cu)001:6050: 'o na shes bya kha tshon gcod pa'i tshad ma rgyun chad du thal /
NK065(cu)001:6051: shes bya la phung po gsum pa srid par 'gyur ro zer na /
NK065(cu)001:6052: lam mtha' dag lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis su 'dus par bshad pa dang 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:6053: lam gyi gtso bo gsum pa zhig kyang srid par 'gyur ro zhes mgo basgre'o //
NK065(cu)001:6054: des na lam mtha' dag lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis su 'dus kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6055: lam tsam spyi khyab tu gnas pa bzhin du shes
NK065(cu)001:6056: bya mtha' dag dngos po dang dngos med gnyis su
NK065(cu)001:6058: gnas lugs kyi gzhi de spyi khyab tu gnas pa ni gtan la dbab byar rigs shes gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:6060: kho bo ni gnas lugs kyi ngo bo shes bya shes byed pa las 'das kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6061: tha snyad tsam du gzhal byar byas pa mi 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:6062: dper na nam mkha' sems rtog gi yul las 'das kyang skyes bus 'jal ba bzhin dang /
NK065(cu)001:6063: yab sras mjal ba'i mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:6064: shes par bya ba'ang kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa gnyis su zad do //
NK065(cu)001:6067: shes bya'i nang nas dam par ni //
NK065(cu)001:6068: gyur phyir nges pa'i tshig yin no //
NK065(cu)001:6069: zhes don dam shes byar bshad pa'i skabs mang yang /
NK065(cu)001:6070: sngar gyi lung rnams dang mi 'gal ba'i gnad kyang de yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6071: mdor na gzhi lam 'bras gsum du phye ba yang
NK065(cu)001:6072: rmi lam gyi rgyu 'bras so sor snang ba ltar
NK065(cu)001:6073: / re zhig 'khrul snang kun brtags kyi dbang gis so sor snang ba tsam la bzhag mod /
NK065(cu)001:6074: chos kyi ngo bo nyid kyis phye ba ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6075: ngo bo rang rig pa'i byang chub kyi sems su gcig pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6076: 'on kyang tha snyad kyi blo ngo bor dbye gzhi
NK065(cu)001:6077: shes bya tsam du byas pas gnas lugs shes byar
NK065(cu)001:6078: thal ba la skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:6079: 'dir dbye gzhi nyid gnas lugs yin pas de shes
NK065(cu)001:6080: par bya ba'i rgyud don gyi rtsa ba yin pa'i
NK065(cu)001:6082: phyi nang bye brag ji snyed pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:6083: chos rnams thams cad byang chub sems //
NK065(cu)001:6084: ji bzhin ngang du ye gnas pa //
NK065(cu)001:6085: shes par bya ba'i rgyud don yin //
NK065(cu)001:6087: don dam blo'i spyod yul min kyang bden gnyis 'byed pa'i rnam gzhag gi tshe /
NK065(cu)001:6089: shes bya tsam gyi snang ba la //
NK065(cu)001:6090: bden pa gnyis kyi zhing yang grub //
NK065(cu)001:6091: ces dbye gzhi shes byar gsungs pa ltar 'dir yang mtshungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6093: dbye gzhi shes bya tsam las /
NK065(cu)001:6094: dbye ba'i chos gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du nges te /
NK065(cu)001:6095: de las mang mi dgos shing /
NK065(cu)001:6096: nyung na mi 'du ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6098: gzhi de rang la yod pa la brten nas /
NK065(cu)001:6099: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la brod pa bskyed
NK065(cu)001:6100: pas lam gyi dka' tshegs bzod par byas nas 'jug
NK065(cu)001:6102: yungs kar la mar nag lhun grub tu yod pas /
NK065(cu)001:6103: mar nag 'dod pa rnams btag 'tshag gi rtsol ba la mi blta bar 'jug pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6105: de ltar dbye sgo gzhi lam 'bras gsum kho nar nges shing 'dus pa de tshad mas shes sam /
NK065(cu)001:6106: tshad ma ma yin pa zhig gis shes zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6108: gzhan du na sgro 'dogs kyi blor zad pa'i phyir yid brtan mi rung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:6109: 'o na rtog ge'i rigs pas shes par 'gyur rum snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:6111: rtogs bya gnas lugs kyi don de ni tha snyad pa'i shes ngo las 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6113: dape'am tshad ma'am gtan tshigs sam //
NK065(cu)001:6114: rjes su dpag pa'i shes rab kyis //
NK065(cu)001:6115: rtogs pas nus pa ma yin te //
NK065(cu)001:6119: so so rang rig mtshan med spyod yul ni //
NK065(cu)001:6120: brjod du med cing tha snyad yongs chad pas //
NK065(cu)001:6121: rtsod dang bral ba don dam chos yin te //
NK065(cu)001:6122: de ni rtog ge'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6125: byis pa de dag rtog ge ba //
NK065(cu)001:6126: ro dang 'dra bas de dag brtags //
NK065(cu)001:6130: bye brag bsdus pas kun khyab gsum //
NK065(cu)001:6131: zhes pas shin tu lkog gyur gyi don chad lhag med par 'jal nus pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:6132: rgyal ba'i bka' dri ma med pa'i lung tshad ma dang /
NK065(cu)001:6133: mkhas pas mdzad pa'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK065(cu)001:6134: de gnyis dang rjes su mthun par skyes pa'i rigs pa tshad ma gsum las gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6135: kun khyab kyi tshad ma gsum gyis shes te /
NK065(cu)001:6136: bshad rgyud rdo rje me long las /
NK065(cu)001:6137: lung dang rigs pa man ngag gi //
NK065(cu)001:6138: tshad ma dag gis gang gzhal pas //
NK065(cu)001:6139: shes bya khong du chud par 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:6142: thugs kyi sgron ma gsang ba'i 'grel pa 'di //
NK065(cu)001:6143: lung dang man ngag gi rig pas gtan la dbab //
NK065(cu)001:6145: slob dpon dpal dbyangs kyis lta ba yang dag sgron mar /
NK065(cu)001:6146: rnam par mi rtog don dam rang bzhin gyi //
NK065(cu)001:6147: rig pa'i tshul chen sems kyi dmigs pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:6148: lung dang man ngag rigs pas thag bcad de //
NK065(cu)001:6149: chos kyi rang bzhin yang dag yid ches bya //
NK065(cu)001:6151: des na lung ni 'di nyid las /
NK065(cu)001:6152: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK065(cu)001:6153: thos bsam sgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK065(cu)001:6154: rang byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK065(cu)001:6157: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i shes bya rnams //
NK065(cu)001:6158: 'bru mthun tshig don shes bya'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:6159: rnam gsum rgyud kyi don du bsdus //
NK065(cu)001:6162: dbye gzhi las dbye sgo gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du nges te /
NK065(cu)001:6163: de dag ma tshogs par don gnyis rdzogs pa'i byang chub kyi 'bras bu mi 'byung ba gang zhig /
NK065(cu)001:6164: der shes bya'i chos kun 'dus pa med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6166: de gsum kha yar ba las 'bras bu 'byung mi srid pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6168: sa bon yod kyang zhing sa dang skyes bu'i rtsol ba med pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6169: de gnyis yod kyang sa bon med na ston thog mi 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6171: der ma 'dus pa'i chos gzhan ma dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6172: kha cig 'khrul pa'i snang ba ma 'dus so zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6173: de ni brtags gzhi yin pa'i gzhir 'du ba'i phyir skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:6174: gzhi la ngo bo'i gzhi dang brtags gzhi gnyis su nges pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:6176: ngo bo'i gzhi dang brtags pa'i gzhi //
NK065(cu)001:6186: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK065(cu)001:6188: ngo bo thams cad sems nyid de //
NK065(cu)001:6189: gser gyi dpe bzhin gnyis su med //
NK065(cu)001:6192: bcos bslad med par rang rtsal 'gag med du cir yang snang ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:6194: rang rig pa'i lugs kyi cir yang snang ba /
NK065(cu)001:6197: snod bcud snang zhen gyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad de /
NK065(cu)001:6199: ngo bo snod bcud 'jig rten gyi //
NK065(cu)001:6200: snang dang zhen pa'i chos rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:6202: gnyis pa lam gyi ngo bo ni //
NK065(cu)001:6203: skyed byed shes rab gsum gyis bskyed bya thun mong
NK065(cu)001:6204: dang mchog gi sems bzhi'am lnga skyes sam skye ba
NK065(cu)001:6206: ngo bo shes rab rnam gsum gyis //
NK065(cu)001:6207: sems lnga skyes bar bstan pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:6210: lnga sems ldan pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK065(cu)001:6211: skye ba'i gzhi dag skye nges pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6213: gsum pa 'bras bu'i ngo bo ni /
NK065(cu)001:6214: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'am nyi shu rtsa lnga ste /
NK065(cu)001:6216: sku dang gsung dang thugs nyid dang //
NK065(cu)001:6217: yon tan phrin las rmad byung ba //
NK065(cu)001:6218: lnga'am lnga nyid ngo bor gnas //
NK065(cu)001:6224: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi 'byung khungs sam gzhir gyur pas na gzhi ste /
NK065(cu)001:6226: tha snyad gnyis kyi chos rnams kun //
NK065(cu)001:6227: ma lus 'byung phyir gzhi zhes bya //
NK065(cu)001:6230: gang gis gang du bgrod byar gyur bas na lam ste /
NK065(cu)001:6232: bgrod dang de chos ldan pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:6235: smin pa'am mthar phyin pa'i phyir 'bras bu ste /
NK065(cu)001:6237: grub pa mthar phyin 'bras bur brjod //
NK065(cu)001:6239: zhar la de gsum rgyud du mtshon bya'i sgra bshad ni /
NK065(cu)001:6241: rgyud ni rgyun chags zhes bya ste //
NK065(cu)001:6243: zhes pas gzhi lam gnyis shes bya shes byed /
NK065(cu)001:6244: lam 'bras gnyis thob bya 'thob byed gzhi 'bras gnyis bdag nyid gcig par 'brel bas /
NK065(cu)001:6245: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu'i tshul du 'brel zhing rgyun chags pas na rgyud de /
NK065(cu)001:6247: rang bzhin 'bras bu rnam gnyis kyis //
NK065(cu)001:6248: shes thob btags pa'i nges tshig gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:6262: lam de shes shing gsal bar bya dgos sam mi dgos /
NK065(cu)001:6267: sngon por rtogs pa gsum yang sgyu 'phrul gyi gzhi lam 'bras gsum du 'gyur ro gsung /
NK065(cu)001:6272: de ltar na lam yang gzhir thal /
NK065(cu)001:6273: gang gis bgrod byar gyur pa'i gnas sam rten lam yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6274: lam gyi mtshan nyid kyis kyang lta ba la ma khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:6275: de shes byed yin gyi 'jug byed ma yin pa'i phyir grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:6280: 'jug cing bgrod pa byed pas na lam /
NK065(cu)001:6281: yon tan gyis smin pa mthar thug pa 'bras bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:6283: gzhi lam gnyis la skyon snga ma ltar 'bab cing /
NK065(cu)001:6284: 'bras bu la 'chad 'gyur gyi skyon gnas pas mi rigs so //
NK065(cu)001:6285: yang bdag nyid chen po 'ga' zhig /
NK065(cu)001:6286: ye nas gnas pa brtag bya dang bcas pa ni gzhi /
NK065(cu)001:6287: bgrod par byed pa rtogs byed dang bcas pa ni lam /
NK065(cu)001:6288: mthar thug pa'i don mngon du byas pas rtsol ba las grol ba ni 'bras bu'o //
NK065(cu)001:6291: de ltar na lam 'bras gnyis ye nas gnas pa'i brtag bya yin nam min /
NK065(cu)001:6293: gzhi lam 'bras gsum ka mtshan nyid gcig gis mtshon nus par 'gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:6294: gal te ma yin na ni /
NK065(cu)001:6295: de ltar ye shes rang gnas pa //
NK065(cu)001:6296: lam dang 'bras bu kun ngo bo //
NK065(cu)001:6299: lam gyur gyi 'bras bu la ma khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:6300: da dung mthong zin bsgom pa'i rtsol ba las ma
NK065(cu)001:6301: grol bas mthar thug gi don mngon du ma byas
NK065(cu)001:6302: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:6303: chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa ni
NK065(cu)001:6304: gzhi shes 'jug gi byed rtsol dang bcas pa ni
NK065(cu)001:6305: lam / chos nyid mngon gyur bskyed du byar med par son pa ni 'bras bu ste /
NK065(cu)001:6306: mtshan nyid dang pos ngo bo dang brtag gzhi gnyis ka la khyab cing lam 'bras bcad /
NK065(cu)001:6307: bar pas lta ba dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis ka la khyab cing gzhi 'bras bcad /
NK065(cu)001:6308: tha mas gnas skabs dang mthar thug gnyis ka la
NK065(cu)001:6309: khyab cing gzhi lam bcad pas skyon las grol ba'i
NK065(cu)001:6310: phyir / mkhas pas basngagasa par 'os pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:6311: gnyis pa la so so'i gtan la dbab pas rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK065(cu)001:6317: bye brag rgyu rgyud du ji ltar 'gyur pa'i 'thad pa bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6320: dang po rnam pa gnyis yin te //
NK065(cu)001:6321: ngo bo'i gzhi dang brtags pa'i gzhi //
NK065(cu)001:6323: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:6326: rang gi mtshan nyid ngos bzung ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:6331: skabs 'phros kyi gzhal bya dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:6333: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems shes bya dngos
NK065(cu)001:6334: po'i gshis mtha' dang bral bar gnas tsam zhig ste
NK065(cu)001:6336: mtshan nyid mtha' rnams kun bral ba //
NK065(cu)001:6337: cir yang gzung du med pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6340: kun khyab kyi gtan tshigs gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:6344: thams cad rang rig byang chub sems //
NK065(cu)001:6345: de ni lung gi tshad mar bshad //
NK065(cu)001:6349: chos thams cad sems la gnas /
NK065(cu)001:6351: rnal 'byor mig gi bsam gtan gyi rgya cher 'grel las /
NK065(cu)001:6352: chos thams cad rang rig pa'i ye shes rang gi
NK065(cu)001:6353: mtshan nyid rig par gsal bas cis kyang ma bsgribs
NK065(cu)001:6354: pa / gnyis su med pa la mtshan nyid 'di 'drar brjod du med pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6357: 'khor 'das lam gsum gyi bsdus pa'i chos rnams chos can /
NK065(cu)001:6358: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6360: sems las ma gtogs pa'i chos gzhan med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6361: rin chen gser gling du phyin pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6362: de la kha cig na re /
NK065(cu)001:6363: yul rdzas su snang ba 'di dag shes pa las gzhan du grub pa'i phyir mi 'thad do zer /
NK065(cu)001:6365: yul shes la bdag gcig gi 'brel pa med de /
NK065(cu)001:6366: bdag nyid mi gcig pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6367: ka ba dang bum pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6368: de las de byung gi 'brel pa'ang med de /
NK065(cu)001:6369: bstan med thogs med kyi rig tsam de las bem po'i rdzas skye mi srid pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6370: nam mkha' dang pad+ma bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6372: shes pa las yul rnams snang ba mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:6373: yul shes la 'brel ba gtan med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6376: mngon sum gyi tshad mas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6377: de bas na sems las gzhan pa'i chos gzhan ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:6378: 'di ltar yul sogs snang ba na nyams su myong ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6379: rmi lam gyi snang ba bzhin dang /
NK065(cu)001:6380: sems kyis ji ltar dbang bsgyur ba ltar rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6381: zad par goms pa'i snang ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6382: de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK065(cu)001:6383: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:6384: dngos po sna tshogs par snang ste //
NK065(cu)001:6386: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos rnams kun //
NK065(cu)001:6387: rdos pa can gyi chos min te //
NK065(cu)001:6388: rtog med rang rig 'od gsal ba'i //
NK065(cu)001:6392: sems las ma gtogs chos med phyir //
NK065(cu)001:6393: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK065(cu)001:6395: slob dpon dpal dbyangs kyi mtha'i mun sel sgron ma las /
NK065(cu)001:6396: chos rnams sems kyi 'phrul pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:6397: sems las ma gtogs chos rnams med //
NK065(cu)001:6399: de ltar thun mong gi lung las kyang gsungs te /
NK065(cu)001:6401: ji ltar phyis bas brtags pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:6402: phyi rol dngos po yod min par //
NK065(cu)001:6403: bag chags kyis ni spags pa'i sems //
NK065(cu)001:6404: don gyi dngos por rab tu skyes //
NK065(cu)001:6406: mdo sde sa bcu par yang /
NK065(cu)001:6408: khams gsum pa 'di dag sems tsam mo //
NK065(cu)001:6410: rigs pa drug cu pa las /
NK065(cu)001:6411: 'byung ba che la sogs bshad pa //
NK065(cu)001:6412: rnam par shes su yang dag 'du //
NK065(cu)001:6414: de dag thun mong gi gtan tshigs kyis chos thams cad rang snang du sgrub pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6415: de nyid thun min gyi gtan tshigs kyis mtha' bral
NK065(cu)001:6416: du bsgrub pa ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ro
NK065(cu)001:6418: de ltar na so skye'i snang ba sor bzhag 'di
NK065(cu)001:6419: gnas lugs ngo bo nyid kyi gzhir 'dod na ni
NK065(cu)001:6420: / shes bya ma nor ba yul du byed pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6421: so skye'i shes pa 'di yang dag pa'i tshad mar 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6423: gal te ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi ma yin na
NK065(cu)001:6424: 'khrul snang 'di chos nyid kyi khyab bya ma yin
NK065(cu)001:6425: par 'gyur te / ngo bo tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6426: ka ba dang bum pa bzhin no zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6429: snang ngo nas chos nyid rang snang yin pas chos nyid yin gyi /
NK065(cu)001:6430: zhen ngo la phyogs su zhes pas ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6431: ltos sa tha dad la ltos pa'o gsung /
NK065(cu)001:6433: rtogs pa'i dus na gzhir ma 'gyur ba med la /
NK065(cu)001:6434: ma rtogs pa'i 'khrul ngo 'di ma yin no gsungs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6435: de gnyis ka legs par mi sems te /
NK065(cu)001:6437: snang zhen gnyis blo rdzas ngo bo gcig na //
NK065(cu)001:6438: rdzas gcig la snang mi snang gi cha gnyis 'gal bas /
NK065(cu)001:6439: zhen ngo yang chos nyid rang snang du 'gyur zhing /
NK065(cu)001:6440: tha dad na zhen 'khrul spangs tshe snang 'khrul mi spong bar thal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:6442: rtogs pa de rkyen la rag lus na rang bzhin gyi snang ba ma yin par 'gyur zhing /
NK065(cu)001:6443: rag ma lus na rtogs ma rtogs kyi dus kyi
NK065(cu)001:6444: ldog chas gzhi yin min du 'dod pa'i dam bca'
NK065(cu)001:6445: nyams so // 'o na gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6446: rang bzhin chos nyid du yongs rdzogs /
NK065(cu)001:6448: ngo bo la dbyer med ces bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:6450: zhe sdang ma 'dres mnar sems pa //
NK065(cu)001:6451: yongs su rdzogs par stong bdag med //
NK065(cu)001:6452: de nyid ma 'dres yongs rdzogs nas //
NK065(cu)001:6453: ma bcos de bzhin nyid kho na //
NK065(cu)001:6455: 'o na ma 'dres pas chos nyid min pa bzhin du //
NK065(cu)001:6456: yongs rdzogs kyi ngos nas kyang ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6457: de nyid ngo bo dbyer med yin pas so //
NK065(cu)001:6460: til 'bru dang snum gnyis rdzas dbyer med na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:6462: snum gong bur mi snang ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6465: ka dag lhun grub kyi dbye ba bshad pas gzhi 'ching grol med par bstan /
NK065(cu)001:6466: grub mtha' bden pa gsum gyis rang gzhung mtha' bral du bsgrubs /
NK065(cu)001:6467: gzhi nges byed kyi tshad ma bsam pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6469: ka dag lhun grub kyi go ba bstan /
NK065(cu)001:6472: rang gzhung bzhag ste la bzla ba dang bzhi /
NK065(cu)001:6474: gzhi gdod ma nas dag pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6475: ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6476: nor bu rin po che mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyis gtums pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6477: zhes gzhi dang dri ma tha dad du 'dod pa'i ka dag pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6478: gzhi ye nas lhun grub yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6479: ma rig pa gzhan byung ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6480: ye nas gser lcags dbyer med du med na gser
NK065(cu)001:6481: 'gyur gyi rtsis lcags gser du bsgyur du mi btub
NK065(cu)001:6482: pa bzhin no // zhes gzhi dang dri ma dbyer med du 'dod pa'i lhun grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6484: de gnyis re re la'ang dbye ba gsum gsum du yod na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:6486: lhun grub chen po gnyis yongs gcod bsgrub bya yin pas 'og tu 'chad la /
NK065(cu)001:6487: 'dir skyon can gyi 'dod gzhung gi dbang du byas nas re re la'ang gnyis gnyis su dbye ste /
NK065(cu)001:6488: de yang ka dag la gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:6489: dbyings ka dag pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:6490: gzhi chos dbyings rnam dag yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6491: ma rig pa'i gzhi mi rung ste /
NK065(cu)001:6492: nor bu rin chen la mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi sel med pa bzhin no zer /
NK065(cu)001:6493: ye shes ka dag pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:6494: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes la ma rig pa
NK065(cu)001:6495: glo bur gyi dri ma lam lngas spangs pa yin
NK065(cu)001:6496: te / rin po che'i dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i gegs
NK065(cu)001:6497: mi gtsang ba'i 'dam de bkrus shing phyis nas dag
NK065(cu)001:6498: pa las dgos 'dod 'byung ba bzhin no zer /
NK065(cu)001:6500: chos nyid lhun grub pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:6501: gzhi ma rig pa dang ye shes dbyer med yin
NK065(cu)001:6502: pa'i gnad kyis chos nyid gcig gi rang bzhin las
NK065(cu)001:6504: chos can so so yang phan tshun gcig la gcig lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6505: ye nas gser lcags dbyer med du med na 'gyur
NK065(cu)001:6506: rtsis gser du bsgrur du mi btub pa rdza shing
NK065(cu)001:6507: la sogs pa bzhin no zer /
NK065(cu)001:6508: chos can lhun grub pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:6509: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes thob kyang ma rig pa gtan nas ma spangs te /
NK065(cu)001:6510: 'khor 'das gnyis de las de mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6511: lcags gser du gyur pa'i tshe lcags la gser gyi
NK065(cu)001:6512: mtshan ma mi snang yang lcags der gyur pa las
NK065(cu)001:6513: logs su ma spangs pa bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:6516: dbyings ka dag pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:6517: gzhi de ma rig pa'i rgyud rgyur yang mi rung ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6518: 'khrul pa skye mi srid par thal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:6519: gal te ma rig pa glo bur gyi dri ma yin no zer na /
NK065(cu)001:6520: rgyu bkag pas 'bras bu khegs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6521: glo bur gyi dri ma 'byung ba mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:6522: rgyu bde gshegs snying po dri bral yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6523: ye shes ka dag pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:6524: sku dang ye shes thob pa'i tshe 'khor ba spangs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6525: lha dang rtog pa tha dad du 'gyur pas /
NK065(cu)001:6526: rdo rje phung po yan lag ni //
NK065(cu)001:6527: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK065(cu)001:6529: ka dag pa spyi'i skyon du /
NK065(cu)001:6530: gzhi dang dri ma tha dad pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6532: ma rig ye shes tha dad min //
NK065(cu)001:6533: ma rtog rtogs pa'i lam 'dir gcig /
NK065(cu)001:6536: 'khrul snang dag phyogs su bsgyur du mi btub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6537: chos nyid mthong yung 'khrul snang mi spong ba sogs char ltar 'bab cing /
NK065(cu)001:6539: 'khrul gzhi med na skyon du 'gyur ba'i lung rigs rnams kyis kyang gnod do //
NK065(cu)001:6540: yang chos nyid lhun grub pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:6541: gzhi dang 'khrul pa dbyer med yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6542: 'khrul pa spang du mi rung bar thal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:6543: chos can lhun grub pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:6544: ma rig pa'i rang bzhin las ma 'das pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6545: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob kyang dgos med du thal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:6547: gzhi dang dri ma dbyer med du 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6549: thams cad dag ces bya ba yang //
NK065(cu)001:6550: dngos po bsal dag ma yin te //
NK065(cu)001:6551: snang spyod nyid na rnam par dag /
NK065(cu)001:6552: ces pa'i lung dang 'gal zhing ma rig pa'i 'khrul snang mthong bas chos nyid mthong ba sogs dang /
NK065(cu)001:6553: 'khrul gzhi yod na skyon du 'gyur ba'i gnod byed
NK065(cu)001:6554: 'og tu 'chad pa rnams kyang 'chad par 'gyur zhing
NK065(cu)001:6556: ka dag lhun grub gnyis gcig gi grub mthas gcig la gnod pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6557: grub mtha' bzhi po de thams cad skyon can 'ba' zhig pa'o zhes bla ma rnams gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:6558: bzhi pa ka dag chen po'am ka dag skyon med dang /
NK065(cu)001:6559: lhun grub chen po'am lhun grub skyon med gnyis ni /
NK065(cu)001:6560: gzhi 'bras lam rig pa mi ldan pa'i cha nas ka dag dang /
NK065(cu)001:6561: gzhi 'bras kyis ma rig pa ma spangs pa'i cha nas lhun grub ces btags kyi /
NK065(cu)001:6562: don la gzhi 'bras gnyis la ma rig pa ma spangs la mi ldan pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6563: dper na snum la til gyi rdzas ma spangs la /
NK065(cu)001:6564: til gong mi ldan pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6566: 'khor 'das so sor snang ba yang kun brtags 'khrul ngo tsam du zad kyi /
NK065(cu)001:6567: chos kyi ngo bo nas yang dag par gzhal na /
NK065(cu)001:6568: ye nas bcing grol med pa /
NK065(cu)001:6569: dpe rgyal bu dmangs su 'khyams pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:6570: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du la bzlas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6572: bcing med rnam par grol med pas //
NK065(cu)001:6573: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK065(cu)001:6576: spros pa thams cad nyer zhi ba //
NK065(cu)001:6577: rang bzhin gyis ni grol bar brjod //
NK065(cu)001:6578: 'ching ba med phyir de grol lo //
NK065(cu)001:6581: btsal nas grub pa'i 'bras bu bstan pa min //
NK065(cu)001:6582: ma btsal ye nas lhun gyis grub pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:6586: de yang rnam gsum gnas tshul bzhag /
NK065(cu)001:6590: bden pa dbyer med dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:6598: lhag pa kun rdzob kyi ngo bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:6600: tha snyad kyi ngo bor snang la ma 'gags tsam mo //
NK065(cu)001:6602: chu zla ltar bden dngos kyi stong pa'i snang ba ris su ma chad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6604: lung rigs man ngag gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:6607: kun rdzob sgyu mar mnyam pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:6608: 'dus byas dngos po sna tshogs ni //
NK065(cu)001:6609: sgyu ma'i tshul du thams cad snang //
NK065(cu)001:6610: 'phrul snang bya ba kun byed kyang //
NK065(cu)001:6611: rtog pa kun gyi tshad mar snang //
NK065(cu)001:6612: 'di dag thams cad gzugs brnyan te //
NK065(cu)001:6613: bya byed med cing dngos po med //
NK065(cu)001:6614: chu zla'i tshul du thams cad gnas //
NK065(cu)001:6615: thams cad snang la rang bzhin med //
NK065(cu)001:6617: kun rdzob chu zla ltar yin pas //
NK065(cu)001:6622: chu zla sgyu ma sprul pa bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:6624: rig pa la snang tsam 'gags med du sgrub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6625: bden pas stongs pa'i snang ba ris med du sgrub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6627: snang ba chos can 'gag pa med pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6628: gshis la yang dag ye shes kyi snang ba zhig yod par gtan tshigs bzhis grub pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6630: snang ba ma grub na 'khrul snang 'byung mi rigs pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6631: snang ba med na don dam shes byed kyang med pa'i skyon du 'grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6632: snang tsam pa 'di sus kyang dgag mi nus pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6633: rang rig pa thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6636: da ltar gyi 'khrul snang 'di chos can /
NK065(cu)001:6638: de la gzhi gshis la snang ba med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6639: gang du snang ba khegs pa la 'khrul snang khegs pas khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:6640: dngos po'i sbrul khegs na thag khra la sbrul 'dzin gyi 'khrul shes khegs pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6643: khyod med na don dam stong pa rang du shes
NK065(cu)001:6644: byed med de stong pa phyogs gcig par song ba'i
NK065(cu)001:6646: snang ba ma yin pa zhig gis shes zer na /
NK065(cu)001:6648: 'khrul na don dam stong par mi bden pa 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6649: shes byed 'khrul pas shes pa'i yul yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6650: mig shes 'khrul mthong gi dung gi rang bzhin ser po min pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6651: ma 'khrul na shes bya don dam shes pa'i shes
NK065(cu)001:6652: bya de kho na la snang ba zer ba yin
NK065(cu)001:6653: te / ka ba zhes pa gdung 'degs nus pa la zer ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6656: thams cad mkhyen pa'i phyag gis kyang mi khegs te /
NK065(cu)001:6658: rigs drug gi sdug bsngal ma khegs par 'dug pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6659: khegs te ma bkag go zer na /
NK065(cu)001:6660: rgyal ba thabs mkhas la thugs rje dang mi ldan par thal lo //
NK065(cu)001:6663: thams cad du rtsal ma 'gags par rang snang ba yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6664: gzhan dun bem stong dang khyad par med par thal ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6666: stong pa'i rang 'od 'gag pa med par 'khor 'das kyi chos su shar ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6667: dper na mtsho nyid rlabs dang /
NK065(cu)001:6668: nyi ma nyi 'od kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6669: gnyis pa snang ba bden stong ris med du sgrub pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:6670: mthun snang gi chos can gcig pa sgrub na /
NK065(cu)001:6671: rang cag mi rnams la snang gyur thun mong du dmigs pa'i chu 'di chos can /
NK065(cu)001:6672: rig pa sgyu ma'i snang ba yin te /
NK065(cu)001:6673: snang ba'i ngo bo ris su ma nges pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:6674: yi dwags rnams la rnag tu snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6675: de ltar yang ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim las /
NK065(cu)001:6676: dmyal ba rang sems me sogs snang //
NK065(cu)001:6677: yi dwags sdig sems mi gtsang yul //
NK065(cu)001:6678: byol song gyen mthur ngam grog ste //
NK065(cu)001:6679: mi la mthong yul 'di nyid snang //
NK065(cu)001:6680: de bzhin lha mi'i go mtshon sogs //
NK065(cu)001:6681: lha la dge sems rin chen snang //
NK065(cu)001:6685: nga la chur snang ba bzhin du khyod la mi snang bar 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6686: ma nges pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6687: khyod dang nga gnyis las mthun gcig tu tshogs pas mthun par snang ba mi 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:6688: dper na nad kyis btab pa'i mig ser can gnyis
NK065(cu)001:6689: kyis dung dkar po ser por mthun par mthong ba
NK065(cu)001:6690: de / dung ser por yod nas mthong lugs mthun pa ma yin /
NK065(cu)001:6691: nad rigs mthun pas mthong lugs gcig pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6693: shes ngo thun mong pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6694: dus gsum thun mong pa la mthun pa mi 'gal yang /
NK065(cu)001:6695: shes ngo khyad par ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:6696: dus gsum snga phyi mthun par mi 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6697: yi dwags gnyis kyi chu rnag tu mthun par mthong na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:6698: mi dang yi dwags gnyis mthong lugs so so ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6699: shes ngo khyad par ba la snang ba'i ngo bo ris su ma nges pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6700: dus thun mong pa dus gsum gdong tshugs su snang ba nges na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:6701: dus gsum snga phyi ma nges te /
NK065(cu)001:6704: phyis kyi gyo dum rnams snang ba'i ngo bo ma nges pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6705: rgyu mtshan de dag gis rig pa sgyu ma'i snang ba yin par grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:6707: ji ltar sgyu ma mkhan gyis sprul pa'i gzugs //
NK065(cu)001:6708: rta dang glang po shing rta sna tshogs byas //
NK065(cu)001:6709: de la ji bzhin snang ba gang yang med //
NK065(cu)001:6710: chos rnams thams cad de bzhin shes par bya //
NK065(cu)001:6713: sam prit+ta sat+ya zhes pa'i sgra las /
NK065(cu)001:6715: pri nya 'gegs pa dang sgrib pa la'o //
NK065(cu)001:6717: nyon mongs pa can ma yin pa'i ma rig pa'i
NK065(cu)001:6718: rtogs pas bskyed pa'i kun brtags bden 'dzin gyi snang
NK065(cu)001:6719: brnyan ni kun rdzob yin la /
NK065(cu)001:6720: des bden par bzung bas na kun rdzob bden pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6722: rnam pa rtog pa'i snang brnyan yang //
NK065(cu)001:6723: rnam pa kun tu kun rdzob 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:6726: gti mug yang dag sgrib phyir kun rdzob ste //
NK065(cu)001:6727: des gang bcos ma bden bar snang de la //
NK065(cu)001:6728: kun rdzob bden zhes thub pa des gsungs te //
NK065(cu)001:6732: tha snyad kyi ngor mi bslu ba yang dag kun rdzob dang /
NK065(cu)001:6733: bslu ba log pa'i kun rdzob ba bden pa gnyis su 'byed de /
NK065(cu)001:6735: snang du 'dra yang don byed dag /
NK065(cu)001:6736: nus pa'i phyir dang mi nus phyir //
NK065(cu)001:6737: yang dag yang dag ma yin pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:6738: kun rdzob kyi ni dbye ba byas //
NK065(cu)001:6741: dbu ma pas yang dag kun rdzob tu 'dod pa'i phung sogs kyi chos su rtog pa rnams la /
NK065(cu)001:6742: ma dag pa las snang log pa'i kun rdzob zhes bzhag /
NK065(cu)001:6743: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob ni phung po lnga de bzhin gshegs pa lnga dang /
NK065(cu)001:6744: yul 'byung ba lnga rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK065(cu)001:6745: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar rang bzhin gyis
NK065(cu)001:6746: dag pas ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK065(cu)001:6750: mtshon bya don gyi bstan pa ye shes lnga rang la gnas pa'i tshul dang /
NK065(cu)001:6754: 'bras bu rang la gnas tshul rnams rgya cher gsungs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6755: 'dir kha rag ston snying gi zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:6757: ji ltar phyi rol de bzhin dang //
NK065(cu)001:6758: de bzhin gsang bar shes par bya //
NK065(cu)001:6760: phyi nang gsang gsum du dbye gsung //
NK065(cu)001:6761: de yang kun rdzob phyi ltar /
NK065(cu)001:6762: rtog tshogs lha'i rang bzhin du gnas te /
NK065(cu)001:6763: rdo rje phung po yan lag ni //
NK065(cu)001:6764: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK065(cu)001:6767: steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi rang la ye nas ji ltar gnas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:6769: dkyil 'khor bzhi dang srog shing gsum //
NK065(cu)001:6770: gnas na k+aa li sgra dbyangs ldan //
NK065(cu)001:6772: de'i nang nas kyang chos kyi 'khor lo la gleng gzhi ji ltar gnas tshul kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6775: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK065(cu)001:6776: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK065(cu)001:6777: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK065(cu)001:6778: ma nu rnam shes yid sogs bzhi //
NK065(cu)001:6779: ye shes myong bas sdud par bshad //
NK065(cu)001:6780: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK065(cu)001:6781: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK065(cu)001:6782: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK065(cu)001:6783: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK065(cu)001:6786: 'og sgo thabs shes la gleng gzhi gnas tshul kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6788: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:6789: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK065(cu)001:6790: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK065(cu)001:6791: wam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6792: ma da ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK065(cu)001:6793: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK065(cu)001:6794: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:6795: pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:6796: y+aa na theg chen 'di nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:6797: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK065(cu)001:6798: n+aa ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:6801: sgyu ma mig yor sprul pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:6802: smig rgyu 'ja' tshon chu zla bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:6803: zhes pa'i dpes sgyu ma'i dngos po drug tu dbye ste /
NK065(cu)001:6804: de la log rtog sgyu ma ni /
NK065(cu)001:6805: sgyu ma'i rta glang ltar de ma yin la der 'dzin gyi zhen pa'i log rtog dang /
NK065(cu)001:6806: rten 'brel sgyu ma ni rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed pa'i
NK065(cu)001:6807: chos des dbang po bslad pa'i mig yor gyi gzugs
NK065(cu)001:6808: ltar snang la ma grub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6809: dngos po sgyu ma ni snang la tshim pa med pa /
NK065(cu)001:6810: smig rgyu'i dpes bum pa la bum par snang ba lta bu'i snang cha dang /
NK065(cu)001:6812: snang la rtog pa med pa chu zla'i dpes bden
NK065(cu)001:6813: dngos kyis stongs pa'i snang ba lha skur gsal ba'i
NK065(cu)001:6814: cha dang / ye shes sgyu ma ni med bzhin
NK065(cu)001:6815: du rnam par bkra ba 'ja' tshon gyi dpes rig
NK065(cu)001:6816: pa phyi nang med par gsal ba'i cha dang /
NK065(cu)001:6817: thabs sgyu ma ni gcig tu ma nges pa sprul
NK065(cu)001:6818: pa'i dpes de dang der snang gi snang ba 'gag
NK065(cu)001:6819: med du 'char ba'i cha nas bzhag pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6820: de ltar sgyu ma'i dngos po drug po tha dad
NK065(cu)001:6821: med par rig pa la gsal ba ni lhag pa
NK065(cu)001:6822: kun rdzob bo // bzhi pa la /
NK065(cu)001:6825: rang bzhin gyis spags lugs gsum /
NK065(cu)001:6827: rgyu'i theg pa'i kun rdzob rgyu rkyen gyis bskyed la /
NK065(cu)001:6828: 'dir rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed pas 'phags te /
NK065(cu)001:6830: rgyu rkyen rang lus med pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:6833: rgyu'i kun rdzob skye 'jig can yin la /
NK065(cu)001:6836: sgyu ma rdo rje btsan po mchog /
NK065(cu)001:6839: rgyu'i kun rdzob bzang ngan can yin la /
NK065(cu)001:6840: 'dir kun rdzob tu'ang chos rnams la mi gnyis pa'i bsam spyod dang ldan pas 'phags te /
NK065(cu)001:6842: thabs kyi theg pa chen po ni //
NK065(cu)001:6843: rnam par byang dang sdug bsngal dag /
NK065(cu)001:6844: kun rdzob tu'ang dbyer med de //
NK065(cu)001:6845: lta ba mtho dman de tsam mo //
NK065(cu)001:6847: kun rdzob tu ni mnyam rdzogs so //
NK065(cu)001:6849: de ltar na kun rdzob dang bden pa dbyer med la khyad par med par 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6850: snang yang bden pas stongs pa tsam du ngo bo gcig kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6851: gtan la 'bebs tshul gyi ldog pa tha dad pas skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:6852: 'khyags pa dngos su mthong bas chu lkog gyur du shugs las rtogs pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:6853: snang ba kun rdzob kyi bden par gtan la phab
NK065(cu)001:6854: pas rang bzhin med par shugs las rtogs pa yin
NK065(cu)001:6855: gsungs / zhar la skabs 'phros kyi rtsod spong ni /
NK065(cu)001:6857: kun rdzob spyi mtshan gyis lhag pa'i kun rdzob spyi
NK065(cu)001:6858: mtshan gyis lhag pa'i kun rdzob la khyab bam ma
NK065(cu)001:6859: khyab / khyab na lhag pa'i kun rdzob kyang 'khrul snang log shes su 'gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:6860: ma khyab na spyi mtshan khegs pas rang mtshan kyang khegs par 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6861: shing tsam khegs pas sha ba sogs khegs pa bzhin zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6862: spyi la ma ltos pa'i bye brag mi srid pa'i phyir khyab pa khas blang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:6864: lhag pa'i kun rdzob 'khrul snang log shes su mi 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6865: khyab byed kun rdzob spyi mtshan bden pa'i spros pas stongs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6866: dper na mi la chu dang yi dwags la rnag tu snang ba'i mthong tshul tha dad kyang /
NK065(cu)001:6867: gzhi gsher bas gnyis ka la khyab pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6868: yang lhag pa kun rdzob 'di ltar snang ba lha'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod pa de /
NK065(cu)001:6869: ye nas med pa'i sgro btags zhig gam /
NK065(cu)001:6870: ngo bo nyid kyis yongs su grub pa zhig yin /
NK065(cu)001:6873: gal te sgro btags zhig na /
NK065(cu)001:6874: sgro btags dngos med rdzun pa yin pas don byed nus pa mtha' dag gis stongs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6875: lam lha'i rnal 'byor bsgom pa don med du 'gyur bas na mi rigs so //
NK065(cu)001:6876: de ltar na'ang chos can mtshan mar snang ba 'di
NK065(cu)001:6877: dag ye nas dag pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du grub
NK065(cu)001:6878: zin na / gser sa le sbram ltar rgyu rkyen gzhan la ma ltos pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6879: lhar skyed byed kyi shes pa tsam la'ang ma ltos par thal zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6881: ji ltar nor bu rin po che rnyed pa ngo
NK065(cu)001:6882: ma shes te nor bur phal pa'i khrod du bzhag
NK065(cu)001:6883: pa na / de'i yon tan mi mthong mod /
NK065(cu)001:6884: de nor bu'i rigs shes pas ngo sprad de byi dor byas pa na /
NK065(cu)001:6885: gdod de las rin po che'i yon tan khyad par can 'byung ba ltar /
NK065(cu)001:6886: ye nas lhar dag kyang snang ba 'di'i bden zhen gyis dag par ma shes pas /
NK065(cu)001:6887: de'i phyir lam bskyed rim kyang bden zhen 'gog byed tsam yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:6888: de la ltos nas yongs grub kyi dam bca' nyams par mi 'gyur ro //
NK065(cu)001:6889: des na 'dir yongs grub tu lung rigs man ngag gsum kas 'grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:6892: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK065(cu)001:6893: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:6896: ye nas lhun mnyam dkyil 'khor la //
NK065(cu)001:6897: yin par shes nas bsgom pa las //
NK065(cu)001:6901: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK065(cu)001:6902: rang bzhin yongs kyis dag pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:6903: ting 'dzin de bzhin gshegs pa lngar //
NK065(cu)001:6904: ye nas ma bcos yongs kyis gnas //
NK065(cu)001:6906: nam snying gi zhi khro gal phreng las /
NK065(cu)001:6907: rdo rje phung po yan lag rnams //
NK065(cu)001:6908: ye nas lha yi dkyil 'khor la //
NK065(cu)001:6909: ting 'dzin sngags rkyen bsgom pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:6910: rang bzhin mngon du gyur bya'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:6911: phyag rgya chen po tshang bar bskyed //
NK065(cu)001:6914: ye nas dkyil 'khor yin pa'i bdag nyid la //
NK065(cu)001:6915: yin par shes pa'i tshul gyis gsal 'debs las //
NK065(cu)001:6916: ma grub pa la yang grub byed pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:6919: phung sogs rang bzhin gyis lha'i dkyil 'khor du grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:6920: rang bzhin mthar phyin gyi gzugs sku mngon du byar rung ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6921: dngul rdo la dngul rang bzhin gyis gnas pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6922: des rang bzhin 'dus byas su yang mi 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:6923: lam gyis med pa zhig yod par sgrub pa lta bu ma yin gyi /
NK065(cu)001:6924: rang gnas mngon du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6925: 'khrul zhen sbyong ba tsam du zad do //
NK065(cu)001:6926: dper na dung ser mthong gi mig nad sbyong byed kyi sman la ltos te /
NK065(cu)001:6927: dung gi dkar po med pa yod par sgrub pa lta bu ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:6934: don dam tsam gyi ngo bo dang /
NK065(cu)001:6935: lhag pa don dam gyi ngo bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:6937: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin skye med spros pa'i mtshan ma dang bral ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:6939: rig pa spros bral la snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6942: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK065(cu)001:6943: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK065(cu)001:6944: mtshan med ma yin rigs brgyud min //
NK065(cu)001:6945: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:6946: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK065(cu)001:6947: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK065(cu)001:6948: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK065(cu)001:6952: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pa //
NK065(cu)001:6953: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK065(cu)001:6956: spros bral du sgrub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:6957: 'di nyid snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub par sgrub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:6960: skye med sgrub byed kyi gtan tshigs bzhi gsungs te /
NK065(cu)001:6962: yang dag par rang bzhin med de /
NK065(cu)001:6963: gtan tshigs bzhis skye med du grub pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6965: rgyu rkyen las ma skyes pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6966: dus glo bur du ma byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6967: byed pa pos ma byas pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:6968: skyes pa'i dngos po 'di 'dra ba ma grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:6971: dngos po thams cad rgyu rkyen las skyes pa'i phyir zer na /
NK065(cu)001:6972: 'o na dngos po de bdag gam /
NK065(cu)001:6974: rgyu med pa gzhi gang las skye /
NK065(cu)001:6975: dang po bdag las skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6978: gal te grub pa las skye snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:6981: 'jim pa la grub zin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6982: rtags ma grub na skyed byed kyi rgyu grub dus su bskyed bya 'bras bu grub pa nyams la /
NK065(cu)001:6983: gal te grub zin nas kyang skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6984: thug med du skye bar thal te /
NK065(cu)001:6985: bum pa las kyang bum pa skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK065(cu)001:6986: yang ma grub pa las skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6987: rgyu ma grub pa'i skyed byed du mi 'thad cing /
NK065(cu)001:6988: 'bras bu ma grub pas bskyed byar yang mi 'thad do //
NK065(cu)001:6989: gnyis pa gzhan las skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6990: gzhan rtag mi rtag gang las skye /
NK065(cu)001:6991: rtag pa las skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:6992: rtag pa skyed byed kyi rgyur mi 'thad de /
NK065(cu)001:6993: rgyu mi 'gyur bas 'bras bu bskyed pa mi srid pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:6994: bskyed na rtag pa nyams te /
NK065(cu)001:6996: dngos rnams gzhan du 'gyur ba la /
NK065(cu)001:6997: mkhas rnams mi rtag brjod par mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:6999: gal te mi rtag pa las skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7001: 'das pa rgyu 'bras spyad zin pas skye mi 'thad /
NK065(cu)001:7002: ma 'ongs pa ma skyes pas skyed byed du mi 'thad /
NK065(cu)001:7003: da ltar pa las skye na /
NK065(cu)001:7004: 'bras bu rang dang dus mnyam pa las skye'am /
NK065(cu)001:7006: dus mnyam pa bskyed bya skyed byed du mi 'thad /
NK065(cu)001:7008: 'phrad pa med pas skye bar mi rigs so //
NK065(cu)001:7009: gsum pa gnyis ka las skye'o zhe na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:7011: rgyu 'bras gnyis bdag gcig pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:7012: rdzas gzhan gnyis phan tshun gcig yin na gcig yin pa 'gal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:7013: bdag gzhan so so las skye ba khegs pas gnyis ka las skye ba khegs te /
NK065(cu)001:7014: bye ma re re la mar bskyed pa'i nus pa
NK065(cu)001:7015: med par bye ma tshogs pa'i phung po la'ang nus
NK065(cu)001:7016: pa de med pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:7017: bzhi pa rgyu med pa las skye'o zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7018: yul 'di gang du yang de ltar skyes pa tshad mas ma mthong ba'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:7019: gzhan du na nam mkha' las kyang pad+ma skye bar thal ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:7020: des na mu bzhi las skye ba khegs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7022: skye ba bden par grub pa med de /
NK065(cu)001:7024: bdag las ma yin gzhan las min //
NK065(cu)001:7025: gnyis las ma yin rgyu med min //
NK065(cu)001:7026: dngos po gang dang gang na yang //
NK065(cu)001:7027: skye ba nam yang yod ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:7029: yang gnyis pa ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:7030: dus glo bur du byung ngo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7031: glo bur ba de rgyu rkyen zhig yod nas byung ngam /
NK065(cu)001:7033: gal te yod nas byung snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:7034: rgyu rkyen bdag gzhan gang las byung brtag pa sngar dang 'dra /
NK065(cu)001:7035: rgyu rkyen med par skye mi srid de /
NK065(cu)001:7036: skyed byed kyi rgyu bdag ma grub par gzhan skyed byed kyi nus pa stongs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7037: gang du 'bras bu dmigs pa la rgyu sngon song gis khyab pas glo bur ba nyams so //
NK065(cu)001:7038: de ltar yang rnam nges las /
NK065(cu)001:7039: rgyu med rkyen la mi ltos phyir //
NK065(cu)001:7040: rtag tu yod pa'ang med par thal //
NK065(cu)001:7042: yang gsum pa ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:7043: byed pa po gzhan gyis byas so zer na /
NK065(cu)001:7044: byed pa po de rtag pa zhig gam /
NK065(cu)001:7045: mi rtag pa zhig gis byas /
NK065(cu)001:7046: gal te rtag pa zhig gis byas zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7048: don byed nus pas stongs te /
NK065(cu)001:7050: gang don byed mi nus pa la byed pa po min pas khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:7052: ri bong gi rwa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:7053: gal te mi rtag pa zhig gis byas zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7054: de ni skad cig ma 'gyur ba dang bcas pa
NK065(cu)001:7055: yin pas 'das ma 'ongs gnyis dngos med yin pa'i
NK065(cu)001:7057: da ltar ba la bskyed bya rang dang dus mnyam par byed na phan 'dogs byed med la /
NK065(cu)001:7058: dus mi mnyam pas byed na bya byed 'phrad pa med pas byed por mi 'thad do //
NK065(cu)001:7061: byed pa pos kyang ma byas /
NK065(cu)001:7062: dus glo bur du'ang ma byung mod /
NK065(cu)001:7063: 'on kyang dngos po 'di dag skyes nas 'dug pa sus kyang mi khegs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7064: bzhi pa ma grub bo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7066: yang dag par rang bzhin med de /
NK065(cu)001:7067: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7068: de ltar yang dbu ma snang ba las /
NK065(cu)001:7069: bdag dang gzhan gyi dngos 'di dag /
NK065(cu)001:7070: yang dag par ni gcig pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:7071: du ma'i rang bzhin bral ba'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:7072: rang bzhin med de gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:7074: gtan tshigs ma grub zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7075: 'o na bum pa nyid gcig tu yod dam //
NK065(cu)001:7078: cha shas dang bcas par yod dam /
NK065(cu)001:7080: gal te cha shas dang bcas par yod na /
NK065(cu)001:7082: skar ma'i tshogs ltar du mar thal lo //
NK065(cu)001:7083: cha bral du 'dod na mi 'grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:7084: phyogs cha drug dang bcas pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7087: drug gis cig char sbyar ba na //
NK065(cu)001:7088: phra rab rdul cha drug tu 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:7089: drug po dag kyang go gcig na //
NK065(cu)001:7090: gong bu'ang rdul phran dag tu 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:7092: yang du mar yod na du ma de gcig la ltos sam mi ltos /
NK065(cu)001:7093: ma ltos na khyab byed gcig ma grub pas khyab bya du ma'ang mi 'grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:7097: ltos pas grub pa'i phyir mer 'dzin la me gcig tu snang ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:7098: des na gang gcig dang du ma'i spros pa dang bral ba la /
NK065(cu)001:7099: rang bzhin med pas khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:7101: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i rigs pas spros
NK065(cu)001:7102: bral de nyid snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu
NK065(cu)001:7103: lhun grub tu sgrub pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:7104: gong gi spros bral de chos can /
NK065(cu)001:7105: snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:7106: snang tsam nyid nas brtags na yang dag tu ma grub cing /
NK065(cu)001:7107: snang tshod tsam zhig ma 'gags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7109: 'o na snang stong la 'brel yod dam med /
NK065(cu)001:7110: yod na grub pa nyid de /
NK065(cu)001:7111: 'brel pa'i mtshan nyid med na mi 'byung ba'i rgyu 'bras yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7112: gal te 'brel med do zer na /
NK065(cu)001:7113: 'o na gzhi'i dus na chos dang chos nyid ma yin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:7114: lam gyi dus na tshogs gnyis bsten pa'i rgyud tha dad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:7115: 'bras bu'i dus na sku gnyis ngo bo phan tshun gcig gis gcig spangs par thal te /
NK065(cu)001:7116: snang stong la 'brel med pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:7119: med pa nyid na sna tshogs snang //
NK065(cu)001:7120: thams cad shes rab dbyings las byung //
NK065(cu)001:7122: gang du 'brel med la rdzas phan tshun spangs pas khyab ste /
NK065(cu)001:7123: ka ba dang bum pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:7125: pa ra m+aar+tha sat+ya zhes pa'i sgra las /
NK065(cu)001:7126: pa ra ma ni dam pa /
NK065(cu)001:7129: dam pa ni bsgom byung gi mnyam gzhag ye shes dang /
NK065(cu)001:7130: de'i rjes mthun rig shes rjes dpag /
NK065(cu)001:7132: de'i spyod yul du gyur pa'i stong nyid dang /
NK065(cu)001:7133: rjes mthun med dgag gi mtshan nyid can gyi stong nyid /
NK065(cu)001:7134: de la rig pa gzhan gyis mi gnod pas na bden pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:7135: yang na dbu ma tshig gsal las /
NK065(cu)001:7137: dam pa'ang de yin pas na don dam pa zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:7138: de nyid bden pa yin pas na don dam pa'i bden pa zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:7142: bden pa gsum gzhi mthun pa'i bsdu bar bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:7145: spros pa phyogs re chod pa rnam grangs pa'i don dam dang /
NK065(cu)001:7146: spros pa mtha' dag chod pa rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam gnyis su 'byed /
NK065(cu)001:7149: don mchog lnga 'bras ye shes dbyings //
NK065(cu)001:7150: bdun dang gsum phyir don dam pa //
NK065(cu)001:7152: ye nas rig pa sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin
NK065(cu)001:7153: las dbyings dang ye shes kyi ngo bor lhun gyis
NK065(cu)001:7154: grub pa ste / de nyid las /
NK065(cu)001:7155: thabs kyi lta spyod chen po ni //
NK065(cu)001:7156: bla med theg pa las 'phags pa //
NK065(cu)001:7157: don dam du ni dkor bdun la //
NK065(cu)001:7159: de bdun yang rigs bsdus na gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:7163: dang po ni chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin spros pa dang bral ba'i gnas lugs te dbyings so //
NK065(cu)001:7165: don rtogs pas shes bya la sgrib g.yogs kyis dben pa ste ye shes so //
NK065(cu)001:7167: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga'o //
NK065(cu)001:7168: de dag kyang rang bzhin dang 'bras bu mngon du byas ma byas dang /
NK065(cu)001:7169: 'bras bu dang ye shes spyi bye brag dang /
NK065(cu)001:7170: rang bzhin dang ye shes gnyis gzhi 'bras kyi cha las phye bar zad do //
NK065(cu)001:7171: zhes snga rabs pa rnams gsung yang /
NK065(cu)001:7172: gzhi 'bras gnyis dmigs 'dres pa'i skyon du 'gyur ram snyam ste /
NK065(cu)001:7174: dbyings spros bral de nyid rang gsal sgrib g.yogs dang bral ba'i cha nas ye shes don dam dang /
NK065(cu)001:7175: de nyid la 'bras chos lnga po ye nas lhun
NK065(cu)001:7176: grub tu bzhugs pa ni 'bras bu don dam mo
NK065(cu)001:7178: de ltar na mthar thug gi 'bras bu dang khyad par yod dam med ce na /
NK065(cu)001:7179: de las gzhan pa'i thob bya med //
NK065(cu)001:7180: ces pas ngo bo la khyad par med kyang /
NK065(cu)001:7181: rnam pa lam gyis mngon gsal du byas ma byas la khyad par yod pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:7185: rang bzhin gyis spags lugs gsum /
NK065(cu)001:7187: rgyu'i theg pa'i don dam stong nyid spros bral du 'dod la /
NK065(cu)001:7188: 'dir stong mtha' las grol te snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub pas 'phags te /
NK065(cu)001:7190: dpag bsam shing dang rin chen ltar //
NK065(cu)001:7191: de kun ngo bo nyid rgyur gnas //
NK065(cu)001:7194: rgyu'i don dam stong pa'i mthar lhung la /
NK065(cu)001:7195: 'dir ni snang chos ma spangs la mi ldan pa'i phyir 'phags te /
NK065(cu)001:7197: gang yang ma spangs mi ldan pas //
NK065(cu)001:7198: ma bral phyir na bral zhes bya //
NK065(cu)001:7201: rgyu'i don dam skye med sgra ji bzhin par song
NK065(cu)001:7202: bas byin rlabs rig pa rang snang du mi 'char
NK065(cu)001:7203: la / 'dir ni byin rlabs rig pa rang snang
NK065(cu)001:7204: lha dang gzhal yas khang sogs su 'char bas 'phags
NK065(cu)001:7206: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK065(cu)001:7207: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK065(cu)001:7209: zhar byung skabs 'phros kyi rtsod spong ni /
NK065(cu)001:7210: khyed cag spros bral la snang ba ngo bo nyid rgyur grub par 'dod pa de /
NK065(cu)001:7211: skyed byed dam rnam 'jog gi rgyu gang yin /
NK065(cu)001:7213: skyed byed kyi rgyur grub pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7214: don dam dngos por thal bas spros bral nyams la /
NK065(cu)001:7216: don dam gyis rnam par bzhag pa'i 'bras bu yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7217: kun rdzob de nyid don las mi bslu ba'i 'jug yul du thal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7219: rdzas ma spang la ldog pa mi gnas pa ngo bo nyid kyi rgyu ste /
NK065(cu)001:7220: shel me ldan bzhin no gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:7221: 'o na kun rdzob ma spangs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7222: don dam la spros pa ma khegs par thal zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:7223: de tsam du shel grang mo la me ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur grub bam ma grub /
NK065(cu)001:7225: nyi ma la skyon med pa dang bar snang la
NK065(cu)001:7226: sgrib g.yogs med pa'i rkyen dang sprod pa don med
NK065(cu)001:7227: du thal / rgyu med rkyen la mi ltos phyir //
NK065(cu)001:7230: me rdzas ma spangs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7231: shel grang mo la sreg byed mngon gyur gyi don byed ma khegs par thal zhes mgo basgre'o //
NK065(cu)001:7232: gsum pa bden pa dbyer med la'ang /
NK065(cu)001:7238: mtha' gang du'ang ma reg pa'i sems nyid ye nas
NK065(cu)001:7239: dkor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur lhun gyis grub
NK065(cu)001:7240: pa'i don dam bden pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:7241: de nyid kyi rtsal snod bcud sku dang ye shes
NK065(cu)001:7242: kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang ba kun rdzob kyi
NK065(cu)001:7243: bden pa gnyis / mtshon byed kyi tshig la snga phyi byung yang /
NK065(cu)001:7244: mtshon bya'i don ngo bo mnyam pa nyid du gnas
NK065(cu)001:7245: pas bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod yul dang bral
NK065(cu)001:7246: ba'o // de sgrub pa la gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:7249: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK065(cu)001:7250: 'phrul dag'i tshul de tha dad min //
NK065(cu)001:7253: don dam kun rdzob dbyer med de //
NK065(cu)001:7255: 'dus byas snang ba rdo rje nyid //
NK065(cu)001:7259: rgyal 'gros ma mdzad ma bcos par //
NK065(cu)001:7260: rang bzhin ngang gis dbyer med pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:7264: ma yin pa dpe la brten nas dgag pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:7265: yin pa dpe la brten nas bsgrub pa gnyis yin gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:7267: skud pa dkar nag sgril ba bzhin snang stong re mos med pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:7268: bum pa dang snam bu bzhin tha dad pa med pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:7269: dngos po glang rwa dang dngos med ri bong gi
NK065(cu)001:7270: rwa ltar snang stong tha dad pa med pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:7273: gser dang gser gyi ser po dang /
NK065(cu)001:7274: g.yu dang g.yu'i sngon po dang /
NK065(cu)001:7276: bar snang dang 'ja' tshon gyi dpe bzhis dbyer med du bsgrub gsung /
NK065(cu)001:7277: rgyal ba g.yung sogs gong ma phal cher /
NK065(cu)001:7278: dbyer med du sgrub byed kyi rigs pa bzhir bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:7279: bden pa gnyis po de rang bzhin bzang ngan med pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:7280: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:7281: 'dug sa tha mi dad pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:7282: dus snga phyi med pa'i phyir dbyer med du grub gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:7283: 'dir mthun snang gi chos can gcig gi steng du bsgrub na /
NK065(cu)001:7285: bden pa dbyer med yin te /
NK065(cu)001:7286: snang stong gang gi yang phyogs su ma chad pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7287: gtan tshigs ma grub ce na /
NK065(cu)001:7288: 'o na bum pa snang phyogs su chad dam /
NK065(cu)001:7291: snang ba 'di yang dag par bden pas stong ngam mi stong /
NK065(cu)001:7292: stong na snang phyogs su chad pa nyams la /
NK065(cu)001:7293: mi stong na snang ba rtag dngos su thal /
NK065(cu)001:7296: byas pa thams cad mi rtag phyir //
NK065(cu)001:7297: zhes pa ltar 'dus byas 'jig pas gsal te /
NK065(cu)001:7298: bum pa dngos po gzhan gyis bcom pa na rang
NK065(cu)001:7299: gi gnas skabs btang ste mi rtag par 'gyur pa'i
NK065(cu)001:7302: dper na rdo rje dngos po las //
NK065(cu)001:7303: btags sam phye mar byas nas ni //
NK065(cu)001:7304: rlung gi ngo la bskyod byas na //
NK065(cu)001:7305: de la rang bzhin gang yang med //
NK065(cu)001:7309: bum par snang rung ma grub par thal /
NK065(cu)001:7312: gal te snang stong gang gi phyogs su ma chad
NK065(cu)001:7313: na'ang bden pa dbyer med yin na ci sto zhe
NK065(cu)001:7314: na / gang du snang phyogs dang stong phyogs gar
NK065(cu)001:7315: yang ma chad na dbyer med yin pas khyab ste
NK065(cu)001:7316: na / / sgyu ma'i rta glang bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:7317: de'i phyir snang ba ma spangs snang ba'i mtha' las grol /
NK065(cu)001:7318: stong pa ma spangs stong pa'i mthar mi 'dzin /
NK065(cu)001:7319: gnyis ka ma spangs gnyis su 'dzin pa'i mtha' las grol /
NK065(cu)001:7320: mdor na dbyer med ces brjod pa nyid kyang snang
NK065(cu)001:7321: stong tha dad du zhen pa dgag pa'i phyir smos
NK065(cu)001:7322: par zad kyi / yang dag par na /
NK065(cu)001:7323: dbyer med du 'dzin pa dang yang bral ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:7324: blo'i spyod yul dang bral ba zhes bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:7326: a ni stong dang mi stong gi //
NK065(cu)001:7327: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:7330: de ming zhen pa dgrol phyir las //
NK065(cu)001:7331: tha snyad gnyis par bsam brjod 'das //
NK065(cu)001:7338: snang stong gang gi'ang ris su ma chad pas dbye ba byar med pa'i don te /
NK065(cu)001:7339: phan tshun bsdebs pa lta bu ma yin par /
NK065(cu)001:7340: chos gnyis po gcig gis gcig mi gtong ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi dbyer med do //
NK065(cu)001:7342: gcig la gnyis med pa'i dbyer med /
NK065(cu)001:7343: mtha' gnyis bkag pa'i dbyer med /
NK065(cu)001:7346: sems tsam pa'i don dam bden pa gzung 'dzin gnyis med kyi shes pa rang rig rang gsal /
NK065(cu)001:7348: dbu ma pa'i rnam grangs ma yin pa'i don dam bden pa /
