NK065(cu)001:9283: sgyu 'phrul snying po lung gi spyi //
NK065(cu)001:9284: lag gi rtsa bzhin dbu zhabs rtogs //
NK065(cu)001:9285: skal pa can gyi ched phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9286: zhes pas mtshan gyi rnam grangs gsum ste /
NK065(cu)001:9287: rgyud dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i mtshan thun mong du bstan pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9288: che ba las btags pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9289: don rang gi ngo bo las btags pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9291: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:9293: chos rnams ma lus gnyis med pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:9294: rang rig byang chub sems nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:9295: tha dad med pa'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK065(cu)001:9296: rdo rje zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:9298: rdo rje ni dbyer mi phyed pa'i rang bzhin can /
NK065(cu)001:9300: sat+wa'i sgra spyir don drug la 'jug kyang /
NK065(cu)001:9303: rtogs pa gsum la 'jug ces rong zom chen po gsungs pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:9304: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems bden pa dbyer med de nyid /
NK065(cu)001:9305: rdo rje ltar brtan pas na /
NK065(cu)001:9307: des 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad rdo rje ltar dbyer med pas bsdus pas sam /
NK065(cu)001:9308: dbyer mi phyed pa'i don rtogs pas kyang rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK065(cu)001:9309: gang rtogs pa'i ye shes de yang rdo rje ltar gnyis su med par gyur pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9310: dang po gnyis kyis gzhi 'bras dbyer med pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK065(cu)001:9311: phyi ma gnyis kyis 'bras bu'i spyi dang bye brag gi phyogs bzung ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:9313: spyir rgyal ba rnams kyis 'gro ba 'dul ba'i thabs
NK065(cu)001:9314: kyi rnam 'phrul sgyu ma ltar cir yang ma nges
NK065(cu)001:9315: par snang ba'i sgo nas thugs rje'i dpyang thag gis
NK065(cu)001:9316: mi gtong bar 'dzin cing 'brel ba'i don dam /
NK065(cu)001:9317: thabs kyi 'phrul pa ji snyed pa'ang mtshan ma med
NK065(cu)001:9318: pa'i shes rab kyis ma zin pa med pas kyang
NK065(cu)001:9322: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i don //
NK065(cu)001:9323: sgyu 'phrul zhes ni bzhir bshad do //
NK065(cu)001:9324: zhes pas phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid
NK065(cu)001:9325: dang bzhir brgyud pa'i bka' srol gyis 'chad pa las
NK065(cu)001:9327: 'byung ba lnga sgyu ma ltar snang la ma nges pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9328: de'i rgyus cir yang 'phrul pa ni phung po lnga'o //
NK065(cu)001:9329: de gnyis 'brel pa can gyi phyir d+r+wa ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:9330: don des sgyu ma mtshon pa lha yum /
NK065(cu)001:9332: d+r+wa ba mtshon pa zung du 'brel ba'am /
NK065(cu)001:9335: yum la d+r+wa bar bshad de /
NK065(cu)001:9337: phung lnga sgyu ma lta bu la rang rig rtog
NK065(cu)001:9338: pa'i thabs kyis ye shes lngar mtshon nas rigs lngar
NK065(cu)001:9339: snang ba la 'phrul zhes bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:9341: lnga phung sgyu ma'i ye shes la //
NK065(cu)001:9342: rang rig thabs kyis rigs lngar 'phrul //
NK065(cu)001:9346: 'phrul pa lha gnyis dbyer med du 'brel ba la'ang bshad du rung mod /
NK065(cu)001:9347: 'dir ni yum gyi mkha' dang d+r+wa ba chos mthun pa'i phyir yum la d+r+wa bar bshad de /
NK065(cu)001:9348: rdo rje g.yung drung 'khyil ba'i mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:9349: d+r+wa ba cir yang 'gyur ba ste //
NK065(cu)001:9350: mdo mdud 'brel cing zang thal ba //
NK065(cu)001:9351: gang nas bltas kyang gsang bar snang //
NK065(cu)001:9352: cir yang sdud cing shong ba bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:9353: de ni yum gyi mkha' dbyings kyang //
NK065(cu)001:9354: mdo mdud 'brel cing zang thal bas //
NK065(cu)001:9355: gang nas zhugs kyang gsal bar snang //
NK065(cu)001:9356: thams cad sdud cing shong ba'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:9357: yum la d+r+wa ba zhes su brjod //
NK065(cu)001:9359: gnyis pa nang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:9360: sgyu ma ni rten 'khor lo bzhi'i rtsa /
NK065(cu)001:9361: 'phrul pa ni brten pa dang thig le /
NK065(cu)001:9362: de gnyis sgom pa'i thabs kyis 'brel pa ni d+r+aa ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:9364: gnas bzhi gar thabs sgyu ma las //
NK065(cu)001:9365: nam mkha'i ye shes cir yang gsal //
NK065(cu)001:9366: cir snang bdag nyid rig par 'brel //
NK065(cu)001:9367: d+r+wa ba'i don du nga yis bshad //
NK065(cu)001:9369: gsum pa gsang ba sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:9370: sgyu ma ni yab kyi rdo rje /
NK065(cu)001:9371: 'phrul ba ni yum gyi mkha' pad+ma /
NK065(cu)001:9372: de gnyis bde bas 'brel ba ni d+r+wa ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:9374: thabs dang shes rab sgyu ma las //
NK065(cu)001:9375: rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul chen por shar //
NK065(cu)001:9376: thabs dang thabs su 'brel pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:9377: thams cad kun gyi gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9379: bzhi pa de kho na nyid sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:9380: snang yang ma grub pa'i phyir sgyu ma ni don dam /
NK065(cu)001:9381: de las 'khor 'das sna tshogs su shar ba ni
NK065(cu)001:9382: med bzhin du snang ba'i phyir 'phrul pa ste kun
NK065(cu)001:9383: rdzob / de gnyis dbyer med pas na d+r+wa ba'am /
NK065(cu)001:9384: yang na rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems lhag
NK065(cu)001:9385: pa bden pa dbyer med des 'khor 'das kun la
NK065(cu)001:9386: khyab cing 'brel bas na d+r+wa ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:9388: stong zhing dben pa'i sems nyid 'dis //
NK065(cu)001:9389: rigs dang kha dog dbyibs med de //
NK065(cu)001:9390: cir yang med las cir yang snang //
NK065(cu)001:9392: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs kyang //
NK065(cu)001:9393: sems kyi sgyu 'phrul chen po yin //
NK065(cu)001:9395: de ltar na gzhi 'bras la rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar grags pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:9396: shes thob kyi bya byed dang 'brel ba'i lam dang /
NK065(cu)001:9397: de ston pa'i gzhung tshogs yi ge'i rgyud la'ang de skad du btags te /
NK065(cu)001:9399: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rdo rje sems //
NK065(cu)001:9402: 'phags pa rtog pa'i rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK065(cu)001:9404: 'o na 'phags pa rtog pa' rgyal po zhes pa'i don gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:9406: 'phags pa theg pa gzhan las rgyud 'di che ba brgyad kyis khyad par du byas pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9408: thun mong dang mchog gi dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs
NK065(cu)001:9409: kyi rgyud thams cad la de skad du grags shing
NK065(cu)001:9410: / 'di ni de dag gi nang nas kyang mchog tu gyur pa'i phyir rgyal po'o //
NK065(cu)001:9412: mtshon bya yang dag pa'i don blo la nges par
NK065(cu)001:9413: byed pa'i phyir yang dag pa'i rtog pa la bzhed
NK065(cu)001:9414: do // gnyis pa che ba las btags pa ni lung gi spyi ste /
NK065(cu)001:9416: ma brjod grags pa'i bstan pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:9417: sgro skur med dang zhal nas gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:9418: dri ma med pa'i lung nyid de //
NK065(cu)001:9419: las dang ye shes spyi nyid kyi //
NK065(cu)001:9420: rdzogs pas rdzogs phyir lung nyid de //
NK065(cu)001:9421: bstan pa spyi yi bdag nyid ni //
NK065(cu)001:9422: thams cad kun gyi bdag nyid pas //
NK065(cu)001:9423: gcig dang du mar mi gnas kyang //
NK065(cu)001:9424: so so bstan pa rgya mtsho'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:9426: don kun 'di la yongs rdzogs pas //
NK065(cu)001:9427: lung gi spyi zhes bshad pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:9429: rgya ma las kyi lung mtshan nyid sde gsum //
NK065(cu)001:9430: ye shes lha'i lung phyi rgyud sde gsum /
NK065(cu)001:9431: bya bral rdzogs pa'i lung nang rgyud sde gsum mo //
NK065(cu)001:9432: de ltar theg pa kun gyi don dang 'bras bu thams cad 'dir 'du zhing /
NK065(cu)001:9437: rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi /
NK065(cu)001:9439: gsum pa don rang gi ngo bo las btags pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:9440: glegs bam gyi klad du bkod pa'i mtshan te /
NK065(cu)001:9443: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9444: zhes pa las skad gnyis ma smos so //
NK065(cu)001:9446: dpal gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid rnam par nges pa'i rgyud chen po zhes bya ba /
NK065(cu)001:9447: zhes bsgyur cing skad gnyis ka smos te /
NK065(cu)001:9449: sh+r+ai gu h+ya gar+b+ha ta t+wa bi nish+tsa ya ma h+aa tan+t+ra n+aa ma /
NK065(cu)001:9450: zhes snang ba ltar bkod do //
NK065(cu)001:9451: des na 'dir snar ston gyi bka' tshoms dang /
NK065(cu)001:9452: rtsags tsha dang nyang glan gyi t+ai ka sogs su /
NK065(cu)001:9453: de kho na nyid kyis nges pa zhes pa'i skad dod /
NK065(cu)001:9455: zhes klad du bkod pa ni rgya dpe'i mtshan gyi
NK065(cu)001:9456: skad ma yin pas ma dag la klong t+aika tu
NK065(cu)001:9458: gu h+ya gar+b+ha ta t+wa bi nish+tsa ya /
NK065(cu)001:9459: zhes smos pa nyid rgya dpe dang mthun pas dag par mngon no //
NK065(cu)001:9462: klad du smos pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9467: bum pa zhes pa'i ming las /
NK065(cu)001:9468: lto ldir zhabs zhum chu skyor gyi don byed nus pa'i dngos po go ba ltar /
NK065(cu)001:9471: dbang po rab kyis gzhung gi don go ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:9472: 'bring gis don gyi rnam grangs khong du chud pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9473: tha mas kyang sman gyi kha byang ltar glegs bam btsal bde ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK065(cu)001:9478: nges pa bzhis rim pa bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:9482: nges pa'i don du ston pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9484: 'di yi rang bzhin che ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:9485: mtshan nyid dang ni don bstan phyir //
NK065(cu)001:9486: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud chen las //
NK065(cu)001:9487: mdor bsdus gtan la phab pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:9488: rang bzhin gsal ba zhes bya ste //
NK065(cu)001:9489: che ba zhes pa'i snying po'i don //
NK065(cu)001:9490: de kho na nyid mtshan nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:9491: nges pas nges don mdor bstan pa //
NK065(cu)001:9492: de ltar rnam pa bzhi po ru //
NK065(cu)001:9493: mdor bsdus spyi yi don du bshad //
NK065(cu)001:9495: de las go tshul kyang rtogs dka' ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:9497: mtshan nyid gzhan rnam par bcad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9498: drang don ma yin nges don the tshom dang bral bar go zhing /
NK065(cu)001:9499: ston tshul dang rjes su mthun par rgyud kyi rang
NK065(cu)001:9500: bzhin dang che ba sogs kyang rtogs par 'gyur ro
NK065(cu)001:9502: bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag las /
NK065(cu)001:9503: phyi ltar shes rab grol lam dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK065(cu)001:9504: nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te bshad pa /
NK065(cu)001:9505: gsang ba ltar 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad pa gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:9509: rang bzhin gab dang sbas pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:9510: bstan ming zhes pa'i rang bzhin ni //
NK065(cu)001:9511: mnyam pa nyid dang dgongs pa'i don //
NK065(cu)001:9512: mdzad spyod gsang ba'i theg pa 'di //
NK065(cu)001:9513: rnam bzhi gsang ba zhes bya'i mtshan //
NK065(cu)001:9516: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs pas /
NK065(cu)001:9517: sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chel nas /
NK065(cu)001:9518: zhes pas gab sbas gnyis su 'dus par /
NK065(cu)001:9519: lo ts+aa ba chen po rong zom dang /
NK065(cu)001:9520: kun mkhyen chen po bzhed na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:9521: 'dir slob dpon sgeg pa'i rjes su 'brangs te bshad na gsum ste rang bzhin gyi dang /
NK065(cu)001:9525: sems nyid bden pa dbyer med lhag pa chos kyi
NK065(cu)001:9526: skur ye nas rang chas su gnas kyang blo'i spyod
NK065(cu)001:9527: yul dang bral bas ma rtogs pa ni rang bzhin
NK065(cu)001:9529: nam mkha' nyid mig gis mthong byar ma gyur pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:9531: e ma ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK065(cu)001:9532: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK065(cu)001:9533: ngo bo nyid kyi rab tu gsang //
NK065(cu)001:9534: gzhan du min las shin tu gsang //
NK065(cu)001:9536: lhan skyes kyi ma rig pas don dam ma rtogs pa ni ye nas gsang ba /
NK065(cu)001:9537: de bzhin kun brtags kyis kun rdzob ma rtogs pa ni rang bzhin gsang ba /
NK065(cu)001:9538: snang stong so sor bzung bas dbyer med ma rtogs pa ni ngo bo nyid kyis gsang ba /
NK065(cu)001:9539: yul yul can du bzung bas spyod yul dang bral
NK065(cu)001:9540: bar ma rtogs pa ni shin tu gsang ba ste
NK065(cu)001:9541: / gsang tshul bzhis chod pa'i tshul du gsang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:9543: gdul bya 'khrul pa'i blo can gyis rtogs dka' ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:9544: ras chod can gyis rtogs su mi rung bas gab pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9545: mig ser can la dung gi kha dog bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:9546: de yang rang bzhin gyi rgyud du gab pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:9547: mtshon bya'i rgyud rang la rang chas su gnas kyang rtog pas bsgrubs pa'i phyir gab ste /
NK065(cu)001:9548: de dag gis 'byin na lung tshad ma'i bdag po sangs rgyas kyis so //
NK065(cu)001:9549: dkyus yi ge la gab pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:9550: ras chod can mgo rmongs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9553: man ngag gab pa'i tshul du ste /
NK065(cu)001:9554: de ni man ngag tshad ma'i bdag po rdo rje slob dpon gyis 'byin par mdzad de /
NK065(cu)001:9556: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK065(cu)001:9557: ston pa rdo rje thugs la gnas //
NK065(cu)001:9560: sngags kyi man ngag med pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:9561: sgra ji bzhin par spyod pa rnams la sbas te /
NK065(cu)001:9562: de dag gi yul ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9563: gcan gzan chen po'i sgyu rtsal spre'usa mi bzod pa'am /
NK065(cu)001:9564: seng zho snod ngan du blug par bya ba ma yin pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:9566: gsang sngags kyi mdzad spyod sbyor sgrol la sogs pa
NK065(cu)001:9567: lta spyod 'brel bas spyad par gsungs pa de dag
NK065(cu)001:9570: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK065(cu)001:9571: sems can don phyir rab tu gsang //
NK065(cu)001:9572: gsang thub dngos grub mi yal bas //
NK065(cu)001:9573: gsang phyir brda dag sna tshogs gsungs //
NK065(cu)001:9575: de yang lta spyod mgo ma 'brel ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:9577: kha cig lta ba mnyam gnas kyang //
NK065(cu)001:9578: spyod pa dag dang yongs mi mthun //
NK065(cu)001:9579: kha cig spyod pa rdzogs byed kyang //
NK065(cu)001:9580: mnyam pa'i don la yongs mi gnas //
NK065(cu)001:9581: kha cig lta spyod gnyis ka med //
NK065(cu)001:9583: ma rtogs par tshig tsam la brten nas spyad na ltung ba yang /
NK065(cu)001:9585: ma rtogs pa yis spyad gyur na //
NK065(cu)001:9586: yi dwags srin po'i gnas su skye //
NK065(cu)001:9591: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po'o //
NK065(cu)001:9593: theg pa thams cad kyi 'phro gazhi'am 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pa ni rgyud 'di yin te /
NK065(cu)001:9595: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK065(cu)001:9596: zhes sogs rkang pa lnga gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9598: theg pa'i sgo gang nas bsgrubs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:9599: mthar rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di'i don mngon du byed dgos pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9601: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:9602: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK065(cu)001:9604: theg pa bzhi yi nges 'byung la //
NK065(cu)001:9605: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK065(cu)001:9608: gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas gtan la phab kyang /
NK065(cu)001:9609: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i don rtog tshogs
NK065(cu)001:9610: thams cad sku dang ye shes bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK065(cu)001:9611: su sangs rgyas pas 'khor ba ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:9613: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:9614: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK065(cu)001:9615: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK065(cu)001:9616: rang blos bsam pas 'khrul ba yin //
NK065(cu)001:9621: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:9623: rtog tshogs thams cad rang rig las mi gzhan pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9624: snang stong gnyis med rang byung gi ye shes la /
NK065(cu)001:9625: sgom byed kyi blos ma bcos par bzhag pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9627: ma bcos lhun mnyam ji bzhin ngang bzhag dang //
NK065(cu)001:9629: de las 'bras bu 'byung bas rgyu'i de kho na nyid ces kyang bsnyad do //
NK065(cu)001:9631: de nyid goms pa las 'bras bu sku dang ye
NK065(cu)001:9632: shes kyi phyag rgya mang por rang snang ba ste
NK065(cu)001:9633: / ma bcos par bzhag pa las byung ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:9634: de la 'bras bu'i de kho na nyid du'ang tha
NK065(cu)001:9637: rgyu 'bras lhun gyis grub pa'i ngang du gnas //
NK065(cu)001:9640: 'bras bu de'ang sgrib byed kyi zhen pa dag pa'i
NK065(cu)001:9641: tshe rang la yod pa'i don snang ba las gzhan
NK065(cu)001:9642: nas byung ba ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9643: de la rgyu 'bras kyi dbye ba tsam yang ma
NK065(cu)001:9644: grub pas rgyu 'bras gnyis su med pa'i de kho
NK065(cu)001:9648: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul rmad kyi chos //
NK065(cu)001:9649: gzhan nas yod 'ong ma yin te //
NK065(cu)001:9652: ji snyed brjod pa'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK065(cu)001:9653: yang dag don gyi snying po ni //
NK065(cu)001:9654: gzhan nas btsal kyang mi rnyed do //
NK065(cu)001:9655: rang rig sgrib med dag pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:9662: gzhi'i rgyud rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po de /
NK065(cu)001:9663: chos nyid sgro skur dang bral bar bden pas na nges pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9665: sgro dang skur pa bzhi ba yi //
NK065(cu)001:9666: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK065(cu)001:9667: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK065(cu)001:9670: theg pa 'di'i lugs kyis ye nas gnas pa'i 'bras bu nyid /
NK065(cu)001:9671: shes thob kyi byed pas 'bras bu lam du byed pa'i phyir nges pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9672: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:9673: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:9676: rgyud 'di rang gi ngo bos brjod bya rgyal ba'i
NK065(cu)001:9677: dgongs pa nges don mngon du phyung nas ston pa'i
NK065(cu)001:9679: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus las //
NK065(cu)001:9680: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK065(cu)001:9682: gnyis pa mtshan nang ltar bshad pa la /
NK065(cu)001:9683: snying ga'i 'khor lo dang sbyar te bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9684: mtshan bzhi dang 'khor lo bzhi sbyar te bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9686: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab rgyad kyi dbus na dwangs ma chen po lnga dang /
NK065(cu)001:9687: de'i dkyil na ye shes snying po'i thig le ye
NK065(cu)001:9688: nas gnas kyang rang gsang thabs kyis chod nas ma
NK065(cu)001:9690: thig le de nyid la shes bya dang bsgrub bya'i don gyi bcud 'dus pas na snying po'o //
NK065(cu)001:9691: thabs kyi man ngag dang ldan pa'i sgo nas nyams su blangs bas /
NK065(cu)001:9692: rang gi sems nyid bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK065(cu)001:9693: ye shes su rang gsal ba ni de kho na
NK065(cu)001:9694: nyid do // snying po'i thig le de gzhi lam
NK065(cu)001:9695: 'bras gsum gyi dngos gzhir nges pa'i phyir nges pa'o
NK065(cu)001:9697: lte ba'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab drug cu rtsa bzhi'i
NK065(cu)001:9698: dbus na dbyings phyug lnga'i thig le a'i rnam par
NK065(cu)001:9699: gnas pa ni gsang ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:9700: yum gyi mkha' gsang gi sna rtse'i thig le dang 'brel te gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9701: snying gi 'khor lo'i dwangs ma lnga'i dbus na ye
NK065(cu)001:9702: shes snying po'i thig le bzhugs pa ni snying po
NK065(cu)001:9703: ste / chos thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i snying po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9704: mgrin pa'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab bcu drug gi dbus
NK065(cu)001:9705: na mkha' 'gro ma rngams pa'i thig le am gi
NK065(cu)001:9706: dbyibs su gnas pa ni de kho na nyid de
NK065(cu)001:9707: / thig le 'od du 'bar tsam na bde ba
NK065(cu)001:9708: skye bas de kho na nyid las mi g.yo ba'i
NK065(cu)001:9709: / phyir ro // spyi bo'i 'khor lo rtsa 'dab
NK065(cu)001:9710: so gnyis kyi dbus na kun tu bzang po'i thig
NK065(cu)001:9711: le ham gyi rnam par gnas pa ni nges pa
NK065(cu)001:9712: / phyir ro // ste / de las skyes pa'i
NK065(cu)001:9713: bde chen mi rtog pa'i ye shes de ni rgyal
NK065(cu)001:9714: ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i dngos gzhir nges pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:9715: / phyir ro // ste / ro // gsum pa
NK065(cu)001:9716: mtshan gsang ba ltar bshad pa ni lus can rnams
NK065(cu)001:9717: kyi rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis la sogs
NK065(cu)001:9718: pa'i nang na thig le bde ba'i ye shes kyi
NK065(cu)001:9719: ro dang bcas pa rang chas su yod kyang ngo
NK065(cu)001:9720: ma shes pa ni gsang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:9721: thig le de la rgyu 'bras thams cad kyi bcud 'dus pa'i phyir snying po'o //
NK065(cu)001:9722: byed pa sdom pa rlung dang bcas pa'i thabs kyis
NK065(cu)001:9723: nyams su blangs pas bde chen lhan cig skyes pa'i
NK065(cu)001:9724: ye shes dngos su rgyud la skyes pa ni de
NK065(cu)001:9726: thig le de nyid gzhi lam 'bras gsum ka'i dngos gzhir nges pa'i phyir nges pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9729: phyi bshad ltar mtshan gyi don bzhi po re rer
NK065(cu)001:9730: chos gsum gsum du phye ste 'chad pa'i bka' srol
NK065(cu)001:9731: yod kyang yi ges 'jigs te ma spros pas spro
NK065(cu)001:9732: na t+ai ka las shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:9733: de ltar mtshan gyi bshad tshul gsum po de ni bla ma brgyud pa'i man ngag yin la /
NK065(cu)001:9735: rang gi shes rab kyi 'phrul gyis 'di ltar yang bshad du rung ste /
NK065(cu)001:9736: chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas su gyur ba'i gnas
NK065(cu)001:9737: lugs de bzhin nyid nam mkha'i dbyings ltar khyab cing
NK065(cu)001:9738: rtog pa'i bdag nyid can du bzhugs pa'i dpal kun
NK065(cu)001:9740: de nyid shin tu rtogs dka' bas na gsang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:9741: de rtogs par byed pa'i thabs kyi lam dang /
NK065(cu)001:9742: de'i rjod byed zab cing rgya che ba rnams ni
NK065(cu)001:9743: bstan pa thams cad kyi 'phro gazhi'am bcud 'dus pa
NK065(cu)001:9744: dang dam pa'i mchog tu gyur pa'i phyir snying po'o
NK065(cu)001:9745: // gzhi mi 'gyur ba dang lam gyis de rtogs
NK065(cu)001:9746: pa la mi bslu bas don la phyin ci ma
NK065(cu)001:9747: log pa'i phyir de kho na nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:9748: de yang ston pas gdul bya rnams kha drang ba'i ched du gsungs pa lta bu ma yin gyi /
NK065(cu)001:9749: 'dir rang gi dgongs pa mthar thug tu nges pa
NK065(cu)001:9750: gang yin pa de bstan pa'i phyir rnam par nges
NK065(cu)001:9753: rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK065(cu)001:9754: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don med //
NK065(cu)001:9757: gsang ba ni snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo dang /
NK065(cu)001:9758: snying po ni de'i dkyil gyi srog mi shigs pa'i thig le'am /
NK065(cu)001:9760: gsang ba ni yum gyi gsang ba'i pad+ma /
NK065(cu)001:9761: snying po ni de'i dbus na byang chub kyi sems
NK065(cu)001:9762: zla ba ltar dag cing gsal ba'i tshul du gnas
NK065(cu)001:9763: pa ste / gnyis ka'i nang tshan gyi chos gnyis
NK065(cu)001:9764: po phyin ci ma log par 'dir nges par bstan
NK065(cu)001:9765: pa'i phyir de kho na nyid nges pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9768: gsang ba'i snying po zhes gsungs gang //
NK065(cu)001:9769: de nyid rnam nges ji lta bu //
NK065(cu)001:9770: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis dris pa'i lan du bstan pas /
NK065(cu)001:9771: gsang ba chos 'byung la bshad de //
NK065(cu)001:9772: snying po'ang de yi thabs can no //
NK065(cu)001:9773: gnyis po phyin ci ma log phyir //
NK065(cu)001:9774: de nyid do 'dir rnam nges so //
NK065(cu)001:9777: 'khor 'das dbyer med pa ni gzhi gsang ba'i snying po /
NK065(cu)001:9778: de 'ching grol med par rtogs pa'i thabs bskyed rdzogs zung du 'jug pa lam de kho na nyid /
NK065(cu)001:9779: des rtogs pa mthar thug mngon du gyur pa ni 'bras bu 'ching grol med par nges pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9780: zhes kyang bshad du rung ste /
NK065(cu)001:9781: rdo rje'i tshig yin pa'i phyir spros pas chog go //
NK065(cu)001:9783: mtshan rgyud don yin min gyi /
NK065(cu)001:9784: mtshan du rgyud don 'dus ma 'dus kyi /
NK065(cu)001:9785: man ngag kho na'i mtshan nas smos pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9786: rgya skad mi smos par bod skad smos pa'i brgal lan no //
NK065(cu)001:9787: dang po la brgal ba dang lan gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:9790: mtshan rgyud don yid nam min /
NK065(cu)001:9791: yin na gleng gzhi gleng bslang dgos med du thal /
NK065(cu)001:9792: dam bca' de 'thad pa gang zhig /
NK065(cu)001:9793: gleng gzhi gleng bslang gi gong du rgyud don byung ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9795: rgyud 'di'i ched du bya ba'i gdul bya dbang po
NK065(cu)001:9796: yang rab des mtshan mthong ba'am thos pas rgyud don
NK065(cu)001:9806: sngon byung 'og min du gleng gzhi tshogs /
NK065(cu)001:9807: gleng bslangs nas rgyud don gsungs pas /
NK065(cu)001:9808: gleng gzhi gleng bslang mi dgos pa'i skyon med la /
NK065(cu)001:9809: mi yul du gsang bdag gis tshig dang yi ger 'dod pa'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:9810: blo rab 'bring tha gsum la dgongs nas mtshan klad du smos pas /
NK065(cu)001:9812: gleng gzhi gleng bslang dgos med du mi 'gyur gsung /
NK065(cu)001:9813: de la rje 'khon ston na re /
NK065(cu)001:9814: 'o na ston pas 'og min du rgyud 'di rjod byed kyi tshig tu ma gsungs par thal /
NK065(cu)001:9818: zhes gsung ba mi 'thad par thal /
NK065(cu)001:9821: dgongs pa brda'i bshad pa nyid gsang bdag gis tshig tu bsdud pa'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:9822: rang nyid ston pa dang dgongs pa mnyam par khas blangs nas /
NK065(cu)001:9823: 'di skad ces sogs bsdus par bzhed pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:9825: da ni sdud pa pos bcom ldan 'das kyi lung
NK065(cu)001:9826: dang mthun pa ltar rgyud kyi gleng gzhi mdzad pa
NK065(cu)001:9827: bla ma'i man ngag gi bshad par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:9829: ces sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9833: mtshan du rgyud don 'dus sam ma 'dus /
NK065(cu)001:9834: 'dus na mtshan dang rgyud kyi dngos po bcu po brang sprad la sbyor rigs par thal /
NK065(cu)001:9836: dbang rab kyis mtshan la brten nas rgyud don mi rtogs par thal lo //
NK065(cu)001:9839: rgyud kyi dngos po bcu dang mtshan don so sor sbyor du med kyang /
NK065(cu)001:9840: mtshan don gzhi lam 'bras gsum du gnas pas /
NK065(cu)001:9841: der rgyud don ma 'dus pa'i skyon med do gsung /
NK065(cu)001:9843: mtshan mthong bas rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don rtogs par gsungs pa de /
NK065(cu)001:9844: don mthong ba la brten nas mtshan du btags pa'i
NK065(cu)001:9845: phyir sngon byung gi 'khor gyi rtags tshul lo zhes
NK065(cu)001:9846: nyang t+aika pa bzhed pa nyid legs sam snyam ste
NK065(cu)001:9847: / de yang gsang bdag gis rang gis rgyud don
NK065(cu)001:9848: thugs su chud nas 'khor la 'chad pa'i tshe don
NK065(cu)001:9849: la brten nas mtshan du btags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9850: des na sngon byung gi ngor mtshan du tshig don ma lus pa 'dus pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:9851: skad cig tsam la rtogs pa mi 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:9853: sgrib pa mtha' spang gdul bya la //
NK065(cu)001:9854: skad cig tsam gyis snang bar mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:9856: rjes 'jug tu mtshan la brten nas don go ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:9857: der gzhi lam 'bras gsum gyi brda 'phrad pa tsam du go ba yin te /
NK065(cu)001:9858: ming gis don mtshon par nus pa tsam gyi ming yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9859: dper na bum pa zhes brjod pas /
NK065(cu)001:9860: lto ldir zhabs zhum chu skyor nus pa'i dngos po tsam go yang /
NK065(cu)001:9861: gser bum sogs khyad chos rnams go bas ma khyab pa bzhin snyam mo //
NK065(cu)001:9864: rgyud kyi mtshan rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK065(cu)001:9865: lung gi mtshan lung gi spyi /
NK065(cu)001:9866: man ngag gi mtshan gsang ba snying po zhes grags pa las /
NK065(cu)001:9867: glegs bam gyi klad du man ngag gi mtshan kho na smos pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:9869: ma h+aa yo ga la'ang nang gses kyi rgyud lung man ngag gsum du phye ba las /
NK065(cu)001:9870: 'di ni ma h+aa'i a ti yin pa'i phyir man ngag gi mtshan nas smos so //
NK065(cu)001:9875: rmongs pa kha cig na re /
NK065(cu)001:9876: rgyud 'di rgya gar nas bsgyur ba ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:9877: klad du rgya skad ma smos pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:9883: rgya skad gtan med na bod skad du sgyur ba mi rigs pas /
NK065(cu)001:9884: bod skad du zhes pas rgya skad yod par shugs kyis brda' 'jal bar bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:9885: zhes gsungs pa ni ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:9886: bod kyi skad la rgya nag la sogs pa'i skad
NK065(cu)001:9887: kyang sbyar du rung ba'i phyir rgya gar mar mi
NK065(cu)001:9888: 'grub cing / bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos rnams
NK065(cu)001:9889: la'ang rgya skad shugs la sbyar du rung ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:9890: rgya gar mar thal bar 'gyur ro //
NK065(cu)001:9892: 'dir rgya skad med pas bod mar 'gyur ba'i khyab pa med de /
NK065(cu)001:9893: bod du brtsams pa'i bstan bcos du mar yang rgya skad klad du bkod pa yod mod /
NK065(cu)001:9894: des rgya gar mar mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:9895: gzhan yang klad du rgya gar gyi skad gcig po ma smos pas bod mar 'gyur zer na ni /
NK065(cu)001:9896: rgya nag nas bsgyur ba'i chos kyang bod mar thal zhing /
NK065(cu)001:9897: skad gnyis ma smos pa'i phyir zer na rgya gar
NK065(cu)001:9898: gyi dpe rnams kyang bod mar thal bar bzlog tu
NK065(cu)001:9900: ci'i phyir bod skad kho na klad du smos she na /
NK065(cu)001:9901: snga 'gyur gyi rgya dper rgya gar skad du zhes yod par mngon te /
NK065(cu)001:9902: 'grel pa nyi seng mar bkral ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:9903: de ltar smos pa la dgos pa ci yod snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:9904: gsang sngags kyi rgyud rnams rgya gar gyi skad rigs
NK065(cu)001:9905: bzhi kho nar ma nges pa dus 'khor 'grel chen
NK065(cu)001:9906: sogs las rgya cher bshad pa ltar yod pas /
NK065(cu)001:9907: de'i phyir 'di ni rgya gar gyi skad rigs bzhi
NK065(cu)001:9908: las samskri ta'i skad du bstan to zhes nges par
NK065(cu)001:9909: bzung ba ni / 'grel pa nyi seng ma las /
NK065(cu)001:9910: rgya gar zhes pa snod dang bcud rnam pa gnyis te /
NK065(cu)001:9911: rdo rje gdan drung la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9912: skad ces pa ni rigs bzhi'i skad la sogs pa las /
NK065(cu)001:9913: 'dir samskri ta'i skad la shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:9915: lo ts+aa bas kyang de dang bstun te bod skad du zhes klad du smos par mngon no //
NK065(cu)001:9917: tshig nyung bar bya ba'i phyir rgya skad ma smos la /
NK065(cu)001:9918: don myur du ngos zin par bya ba'i phyir bod
NK065(cu)001:9919: skad du zhes bod skad rkyang pa smos so gsung
NK065(cu)001:9920: ba ni gsungs pa tsam du zad do //
NK065(cu)001:9921: mdor na rgyud 'di ni yongs su grags pa'i rgya
NK065(cu)001:9922: gar gyi pan chen rnams kyis mang du bkral zhing
NK065(cu)001:9923: / gsang 'dus kyi 'grel pa bi shwa mi tras
NK065(cu)001:9924: mdzad pa yang rgyud 'di'i lung mang du drangs pa
NK065(cu)001:9925: / dang / dus phyis kyang rgya dpe rnyed pa
NK065(cu)001:9926: las thar lo dang 'gos lo sogs lo ts+aa ba
NK065(cu)001:9927: chen po 'gas 'gyur mdzad pa'i phyir bod mar 'gyur
NK065(cu)001:9929: gnyis pa mtshan de ldan gyi rgyud don la /
NK065(cu)001:9930: ston pa la dbang mi za ba'i phyir klad don phyag dang /
NK065(cu)001:9931: bka'i don bde blag tu rtogs par bya ba'i phyir gzhung don gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9937: byed pa'i mu bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK065(cu)001:9938: phyag gang gis na sdud pa pos /
NK065(cu)001:9939: gang la na rgyud kyi ston pa la /
NK065(cu)001:9940: dus gang gi tshe na sdud pa pos 'og min du dang por shes pa'i rgyud la bsdus te /
NK065(cu)001:9941: de nas mi yul du tshig tu sdud pa'i tshe na'o //
NK065(cu)001:9945: tha ma mos gus kyi phyag gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:9946: 'di ni sdud pa po'i phyag yin pa'i phyir dang po'o //
NK065(cu)001:9949: mnyam nyid dbyings su bdud bzhi ngang gis bcom //
NK065(cu)001:9950: phyag rgya'i rang bzhin tshogs gnyis rdzogs par ldan //
NK065(cu)001:9951: yod med mtha' 'das bdag gzhan yongs kyi dpal //
NK065(cu)001:9952: thams cad rang bzhin rtogs dang thugs rje bzang //
NK065(cu)001:9953: kun bzang lha yi lha khyod dbyer med la //
NK065(cu)001:9954: rtogs dang gus pas rab tu phyag 'tshal lo //
NK065(cu)001:9956: de yang chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su bdud bzhi ngang gis dag pas bcom pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9958: rgyu nyon mongs pas mtshan ma rang sar grol bas /
NK065(cu)001:9959: 'bras bu nyer len gyi phung po mi len zhing /
NK065(cu)001:9960: de ma blangs na skye shi dang /
NK065(cu)001:9961: lha'i bu'i bdud kyis bar du gcod pas mi tshugs pa'i phyir bdud bzhi bcom pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9963: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK065(cu)001:9964: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK065(cu)001:9965: bdag nyid lha yi dkyil 'khor te //
NK065(cu)001:9966: skye shi med pa'i g.yung drung gnas //
NK065(cu)001:9969: b+ha ga b+aan gyi sgra las b+ha ga ni bcom pa la 'jug par ma zad /
NK065(cu)001:9970: rnam pa gcig tu skal ba'am legs pa rnam pa
NK065(cu)001:9971: drug la 'jug par yang rgyud gzhan las bshad pa
NK065(cu)001:9972: la / 'dir ni chos sku'i phyag rgya ye shes
NK065(cu)001:9973: kyi tshogs dang gzugs sku'i phyag rgya bsod nams kyi
NK065(cu)001:9974: tshogs rdzogs pas sku lnga la sogs pa'i yon tan
NK065(cu)001:9975: rang rig pa'i ye shes la rang bzhin gyis ldan
NK065(cu)001:9978: 'jig rten pa'i b+ha ga b+aan las khyad par 'das zhes bla thabs su bsnan te /
NK065(cu)001:9980: b+ha ga'i sgra srid pa dang 'jigs par 'gro ba la 'jug pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:9981: de las 'das pas na b+ha ga b+aan no //
NK065(cu)001:9982: 'dir ni chos sku skye ba med pas yod pa'i mtha' dang /
NK065(cu)001:9983: gzugs sku 'gag pa med pas med pa'i mtha' ste spros pa'i mtshan ma kun las 'das pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:9984: de ltar yang phal po che las /
NK065(cu)001:9985: spros pa kun las rab 'das pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:9986: bcom ldan 'das ni mkha' rab zhi //
NK065(cu)001:9989: gzhi chos dbyings shin tu dri med de rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal dang /
NK065(cu)001:9990: de mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:9991: chos sku rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang /
NK065(cu)001:9992: gzugs sku thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal gnyis so //
NK065(cu)001:9993: de'ang rdo rje las rim las /
NK065(cu)001:9994: rang bzhin mngon byas ma lus re ba skong //
NK065(cu)001:9996: kun tu bzang po ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK065(cu)001:9997: cad 'ching grol med pa'i rang bzhin mngon du rtogs
NK065(cu)001:9998: pas spyod yul dag pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10000: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK065(cu)001:10001: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:10003: spyir gnas lugs ye sangs rgyas pa ni rang bzhin kun tu bzang po /
NK065(cu)001:10004: de nyid rtogs pa'i yon tan mngon du gyur pa ni rtogs pa kun tu bzang po /
NK065(cu)001:10005: de las gzugs kyi sku mngon du snang ba ni thugs rje kun tu bzang po'o //
NK065(cu)001:10006: de dag kun kyang 'gro ba la phyogs dus kun
NK065(cu)001:10007: tu gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi phan bde ster
NK065(cu)001:10010: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad du //
NK065(cu)001:10011: mngon mtho nges legs rab bstan pa //
NK065(cu)001:10012: kun tu bzang por brjod pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:10014: yul de la sdud pa po gsang bdag gis rang
NK065(cu)001:10015: dang ston pa'i thugs gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10016: sgo nas phyag btsal ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:10018: de yang thun mong pa dag lus ngag yid gsum
NK065(cu)001:10019: gyis so sor bltas nas phyag 'tshal ba ni shin
NK065(cu)001:10020: tu 'gal te / tshi chad par 'gyur ro //
NK065(cu)001:10021: rmad du byung ba'i theg pa 'dir kun tu bzang
NK065(cu)001:10022: po dang rig pa gnyis med du mjal ba phyag
NK065(cu)001:10023: tu gsungs te / dpe mar gyi nang du mar blugs pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:10027: 'di lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur phyag yin gyi sdud pa po'i phyag ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10028: sdud pa po'i tshig ni 'di skad bshad pa'i dus na /
NK065(cu)001:10029: zhes pa man chad yin pa'i phyir zer /
NK065(cu)001:10030: de ltar na sdud pa pos bka' bsdu byed pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10031: thog mar rang gi ston pa la bstod phyag byas
NK065(cu)001:10036: so thar gyi mdo'i bka' bsdu ba'i tshe ston pa
NK065(cu)001:10037: la bstod phyag byas nas bka' bsdus pa'i phyir te
NK065(cu)001:10039: 'gro ba'i gtso la spyi bos phyag btsal nas //
NK065(cu)001:10040: thams cad mkhyen pa'i bslab gzhi dkon mchog snod //
NK065(cu)001:10041: 'phags pa'i tshogs kyi dbus su dbye bar bya //
NK065(cu)001:10042: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir byas pa la /
NK065(cu)001:10044: 'o na rgyud 'di'i klad du smos pa'i phyag 'di sdud pa po'i phyag yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10045: lo ts+aa ba'i 'gyur phyag med par thal lo zer na /
NK065(cu)001:10047: lo ts+aa bas rgyal po'i bkas bcad dang bstun pa'am
NK065(cu)001:10048: rang gi 'dod lha la phyag byed pa gang ltar
NK065(cu)001:10049: na'ang / ston pa kun tu bzang po la phyag
NK065(cu)001:10050: 'tshal bar rigs par mthong nas 'gyur phyag zur du
NK065(cu)001:10052: dus 'khor gyi rgyud kyi klad du'ang yi ge pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10053: phyag gis go bcad de 'gyur phyag ma bkod pa
NK065(cu)001:10055: rgyud gzhung spyi'i lugs kyi klad kyi bstod phyag yi
NK065(cu)001:10056: ge pa'i phyag tu bzhed pa ni ma yin te
NK065(cu)001:10057: / phal cher bar 'gyur phyag tu snang ba'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:10060: sdud pa pos tshig gnyer ba de'i tshe rang gi ston pa la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10061: zhes sdud pa po'i phyag tu bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10062: gnyis pa gzhung don gtan la dbab pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:10064: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK065(cu)001:10065: mthun par gsang bsgrag gzhan du min //
NK065(cu)001:10066: zhes pas rgyud 'di nyid kyi ched du bya ba'i
NK065(cu)001:10067: gdul bya dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum la ltos
NK065(cu)001:10068: nas 'chad tshul gsum du gsungs te /
NK065(cu)001:10070: rab la mtshan bstan 'bring la dbye //
NK065(cu)001:10076: gnyis pa dbang po 'bring la don rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:10077: gsum pa dbang brtul la 'bru re gnyer re'i sgo nas 'chad pa gnyis kyi /
NK065(cu)001:10079: me long bcu'i bshad thabs dang sbyar te rgyud kyi
NK065(cu)001:10080: mtshan dang d+ai ka sogs las shes par bya zhing
NK065(cu)001:10081: / 'dir bar ma'i dbang du byas te bshad na /
NK065(cu)001:10083: lung gi spyi ru grags pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:10084: rnam par dbye ba lnga ru 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:10088: rgyud gzhung gzhi blang yongs su shes //
NK065(cu)001:10091: dgos 'brel sngar bshad grub pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:10094: rgyu dang rkyen dang gzhung nyid dang //
NK065(cu)001:10095: 'gro ba'i don du snang ba'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:10096: gleng gzhi dang ni gleng bslang ste //
NK065(cu)001:10097: don dang yongs su bzung ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:10098: rnam pa bzhir ni bsdus pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:10103: gdams shing bstan pa gtad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10111: gleng gzhi tshogs pas rgyud don 'byung ba'i rgyu byed pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:10112: gleng gzhi lo rgyus la brten nas ma 'ongs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10113: gdul bya rnams yid ches shing 'jug par 'gyur ba'i
NK065(cu)001:10115: phun sum tshogs pa lnga'am drug ldan te /
NK065(cu)001:10117: ngo bo tshogs pa drug nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:10120: gang gleng na bstan pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10121: de'i rgyu'am gzhi ni phun sum tshogs pa lnga yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:10122: yang rnam pa gcig tu na /
NK065(cu)001:10123: n+aa da'i sgra las nges pa sbyin pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10124: bka' ma yin par rtog pa'i the tshom can gyi
NK065(cu)001:10125: blo la yid ches kyi nges pa sbyin par byed
NK065(cu)001:10129: thun mong gleng gzhi rnam gnyis dang //
NK065(cu)001:10130: thun mong min pa rnam pa gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:10132: thun mong ma yin pa'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:10135: nang ltar thabs lam steng sgo dang sbyar te dang /
NK065(cu)001:10136: gsang ba ltar 'og sgo dang sbyar te bshad pa gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:10138: snying ga chos kyi 'khor lo rtsa 'dab brgyad las /
NK065(cu)001:10139: rtsa ba'i 'dab ma bzhi e gru gsum sogs las bzhi'i dbyibs dang /
NK065(cu)001:10140: kha dog 'od bzhi'i rnam par gnas pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:10141: ye shes snying po'i thig le bzhugs pa'i gnas yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10142: gnas phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10145: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs su gnas //
NK065(cu)001:10148: srog mi shigs pa'i thig le dwangs ma lnga 'dus
NK065(cu)001:10149: kyi ngo bo yi ge wam gyi dbyibs can ni
NK065(cu)001:10150: / dper na mar me gsal byed gzhan la ltos
NK065(cu)001:10151: mi dgos pa ltar de nyid rang la bde ba
NK065(cu)001:10152: gsal bar ston pa'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir ston
NK065(cu)001:10153: pa phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10154: mi shigs thig le wam dbyibs can //
NK065(cu)001:10155: rang la bde ba gsal byed dag /
NK065(cu)001:10161: sgo lnga'i rnam shes bzhi gnas la /
NK065(cu)001:10162: de dag gis brjod bral rnam par mi rtog pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10163: ye shes gsal bar nyams su myong ba ni bshad
NK065(cu)001:10165: bye brag tshogs bdun kun gyi rjes su 'jug pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10166: yid kyi rnam shes ni sdud pa por bzhed pas
NK065(cu)001:10168: ma nu rnam shes yid sogs bzhi //
NK065(cu)001:10169: ye shes myong bas sdud par bshad //
NK065(cu)001:10171: steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams
NK065(cu)001:10172: su blangs pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK065(cu)001:10173: nyams su myong ba'i phyir bstan pa phun sum tshogs
NK065(cu)001:10174: pa ste / ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK065(cu)001:10175: pa ra m+aar+tha don zab mo //
NK065(cu)001:10177: de'i tshe dus snga phyir 'dzin pa'i rtog pa dang
NK065(cu)001:10178: bral ba ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus yin
NK065(cu)001:10179: pa'i phyir dus phun sum tshogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10180: bde ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK065(cu)001:10181: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor gnas //
NK065(cu)001:10184: yum gyi b+ha ga phyi khyams e gru gsum la
NK065(cu)001:10185: sogs te las bzhi'i dbyibs su gnas pa ni gsang
NK065(cu)001:10186: ba'i sku'i bzhugs gnas kyi phyir gnas te /
NK065(cu)001:10188: 'di zhes nye bar mtshon pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:10189: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK065(cu)001:10191: yab kyi rdo rje'i dbang bskur thig le thabs kyis
NK065(cu)001:10192: bzung ba'i tshe rtsa sa ya phrag bcu gsum gyi
NK065(cu)001:10193: bcud 'dus pa'i kun rdzob ye shes kyi thig le
NK065(cu)001:10195: yab yum gnyis ka'i rgyud la bde ba gsal bar
NK065(cu)001:10196: byed pa'i bdag nyid du bzhugs pa'i phyir ston pa
NK065(cu)001:10197: ste / skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK065(cu)001:10198: wam dbyibs thigs ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10200: bde ba sdom par byed pa'i las kyis yid la
NK065(cu)001:10201: sogs pa gsal ba'i rnam shes ni bde ba'i ye
NK065(cu)001:10202: shes nyams su myong ba'i phyir 'khor te /
NK065(cu)001:10203: ma da ma nu sdom byed yid //
NK065(cu)001:10204: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK065(cu)001:10205: gsal bar go bas bshad par 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:10207: de'i tshe bde ba sdom par byed pa'i yid ni
NK065(cu)001:10208: nyams su myong ba'i chos rnams bde bar bsdus nas
NK065(cu)001:10209: ston pa'i phyir sdud pa por yang rung la /
NK065(cu)001:10210: myang bya sems lnga rdzogs pa'i dga' ba bcu drug
NK065(cu)001:10211: gi mtha'i skad cig ma rang bzhin lhan cig skyes
NK065(cu)001:10212: pa'i ye shes nyams su myong ba ni rang bzhin
NK065(cu)001:10213: gsang ba'i snying po'i don yin pa'i phyir bstan pa
NK065(cu)001:10214: ste / pa sgra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:10215: y+aa na theg chen 'di yin no //
NK065(cu)001:10217: de'i tshe snga phyi'i 'dzin rtog bral ba'i phyir bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus te /
NK065(cu)001:10218: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab dus //
NK065(cu)001:10219: na ma de ming zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:10224: zhes pa thun min gyi gleng gzhi dbang btsan par byas te /
NK065(cu)001:10225: 'di skad bshad pa'i dus na zhes 'gyur gyi rgyud
NK065(cu)001:10226: gzhung thams cad kyi legs par sbyar ba'i skad la
NK065(cu)001:10227: / e wam ma ya bya ba las /
NK065(cu)001:10228: bshad dang thos sogs rnam dbye gzhi mi mthun pa med ces /
NK065(cu)001:10232: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK065(cu)001:10233: zhes pa'i rgya dpe rnams su /
NK065(cu)001:10234: e wam ma yu sh+ru ta me ka sman sa ma ye /
NK065(cu)001:10236: yang rje rong zom gyi zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:10237: rgyud 'di la yi ge ma ya gnyis med pas /
NK065(cu)001:10238: 'di nyid nas ni bsdus pa'i gzhi med do gsungs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10239: ma ya'i yi ge gnyis yod par drangs ma thag pa'i bshad rgyud kyi lung rnams kyis ston cing /
NK065(cu)001:10241: 'di skad bdag gis bshad pa'i dus na zhes 'byung ste /
NK065(cu)001:10242: ma ya nyid a smad la t+aa byin pa'i rnam 'gyur du mdzad de bsgyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10243: des na thar los ni sgra 'gyur gtso bor mdzad la /
NK065(cu)001:10244: sngon gyi lo chen rnams kyis bshad rgyud kyi yi ge bsdus bshad ltar /
NK065(cu)001:10245: don 'gyur gtso bor mdzad par mngon no //
NK065(cu)001:10248: yi ge bzhi yis shes par 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:10249: zhes pa ltar e wam ma ya bzhis ston pa'i dbang du bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:10254: de bzhin sogs la 'jug pa las /
NK065(cu)001:10256: e ni i dam la bdun pa'i tra sbyar ba'i rnam 'gyur du byas te 'di dang /
NK065(cu)001:10257: wam ni wa tsa'i bying don las skad /
NK065(cu)001:10259: kun mkhyen chen po'i t+ai kar /
NK065(cu)001:10263: 'byung ba sogs la 'jug pa las 'dir 'byung ba
NK065(cu)001:10264: gzung ste bshad pa'i dus na zhes bsgyur bar gsungs
NK065(cu)001:10265: so // de ltar 'di sogs kyis mtshon pa'i e ni yum lnga'i mkha' ste gnas /
NK065(cu)001:10266: wam ni wam badz+ra zhes rdo rje kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin te ston pa /
NK065(cu)001:10267: ma ni ma da na sdom pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10268: ma nus sgras yid sogs rnam shes te 'khor dang sdud pa po /
NK065(cu)001:10269: ya ni ya na'i sgras theg pa ste bstan pa /
NK065(cu)001:10270: de'ang pa sgras pa ra m+aar+tha zhes don dam ste /
NK065(cu)001:10271: 'od gsal lam lhan skyes kyi ye shes zab mo'i don no //
NK065(cu)001:10272: ya ni rnam pa gcig tu sa ma ya'i ming
NK065(cu)001:10273: mtha' bsdus pa la byas te dus la'ang 'jug go
NK065(cu)001:10274: // de dag dang bstun te sngon gyi mkhan po chos kyi spyan ldan rnams kyis /
NK065(cu)001:10275: 'di zhes pa gnas sogs bod skad la'ang so sor
NK065(cu)001:10276: sbyar te bsgyur bshad kyis gtan la 'bebs par mdzad
NK065(cu)001:10277: pa yin mod / 'on kyang rgya skad ji lta bar bod skad la sbyar du med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10278: 'dir skad gnyis ka dang sbyar nas bshad na legs pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:10283: zhes pa'i lung gi yi ge gnyis spyod dgos sam
NK065(cu)001:10284: snyam du rtog pa ni rgya skad bod skad du
NK065(cu)001:10285: 'khrul pa'i bshad par mngon te legs par mi sems
NK065(cu)001:10286: so // 'dir skabs 'phros kyi brgal lan ni /
NK065(cu)001:10288: mdo rgyud gzhan thams cad du /
NK065(cu)001:10289: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK065(cu)001:10291: 'dir de ltar ma smos pa'i phyir gleng gzhi log pas bka' yang dag pa ma yin no //
NK065(cu)001:10294: lha rje glan sh+aaka bzang na re /
NK065(cu)001:10295: bshad thos gnyis tshig mi mthun kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10296: ston pas 'khor la bshad pa dang 'khor gyis ston pa las thos pa don mthun gsungs na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10297: thos pa la bshad pas ma khyab pa'i phyir legs par mi sems so //
NK065(cu)001:10298: lha rje mda' tig na re /
NK065(cu)001:10299: thos pa la ma rtogs log rtogs the tshom gsum gyi skyon srid pa las /
NK065(cu)001:10300: 'dir bshad ces pa ston 'khor dgongs pa gnyis su
NK065(cu)001:10301: med pa nyid la nyid bshad pa'i phyir sngar gyi
NK065(cu)001:10302: skyon gsum rnam par bcad pa'o gsung yang /
NK065(cu)001:10304: bshad tsam la skyon gsum dang 'bral bas ma ma khyab cing /
NK065(cu)001:10305: dgongs pa gnyis su med pa nyid la nyid thos pa'ang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10306: yang khyed bla ma dang rje sgro phug pa'i bzhed kyi /
NK065(cu)001:10307: sku gnyis kyi bstan pa'i khyad par yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10308: longs sku tshig tu mi gsung bas rna bas thos su med pa'i phyir bshad ces dang /
NK065(cu)001:10309: sprul sku tshig tu gsungs pa'i phyir thos bya bar 'ong ba yin gsungs na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10310: longs skus gsungs pa'i rgyud du bshad ces 'ong bas
NK065(cu)001:10311: khyab na longs skus bstan pa'i rgyud kun tu de
NK065(cu)001:10312: ltar 'byung rigs pa las ma byung ba'i phyir snyam
NK065(cu)001:10313: du dogs so // rje dri ngas pa na re /
NK065(cu)001:10314: ston pa'i dgongs pa brda'i bshad pa sdud pa pos ma phri ma bsnan par bshad par bzhed pa'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10315: snga ma dang zhe 'dod gcig mod /
NK065(cu)001:10316: 'on kyang 'di la 'gal ba ma mthong ngo //
NK065(cu)001:10318: gsang bdag gis bsdu ba byed pa na rang nyid ston pa nyid du khas blangs te /
NK065(cu)001:10319: sngar ngas 'og min du bshad pa nyid yang 'dir bshad par bya zhes dang /
NK065(cu)001:10320: dus na zhes pa'ang dus res 'ga' ba ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10321: rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor gsungs pa'i don gyis
NK065(cu)001:10322: rgyud gzhan dang thun mong ma yin pa'i phyogs bzung
NK065(cu)001:10324: nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel bar bshad ces
NK065(cu)001:10325: pas ni 'khor dang ston pa gnyis su med par
NK065(cu)001:10329: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi ste /
NK065(cu)001:10330: rgyud gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir zhes gsungs pa'i phyir byas pa la /
NK065(cu)001:10332: 'o na bde 'dus kyi zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud kyi klad du'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10335: rgyud der ston 'khor rgyud gcig tu gsungs pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:10336: nga ni che ba'i rgyal po ste /
NK065(cu)001:10337: 'chad dang nyan pa'ang nga nyid yin //
NK065(cu)001:10338: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zer na /
NK065(cu)001:10340: ston 'khor khyad med par mtshungs pa bden kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10341: rgyud 'di ni khyad par med par mtshon pa'i ngos nas smos la /
NK065(cu)001:10342: bde 'dus sogs thun mong ma yin pa'i rgyud gzhan
NK065(cu)001:10343: du khyad par yod par mtshon pa'i ngos nas smos
NK065(cu)001:10345: gdul bya mos pa tha dad pa la grags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10346: kho bos khyabs mtha' ma bcas so //
NK065(cu)001:10348: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NK065(cu)001:10349: zhes ma smos pas bka' yang dag pa ma yin par 'gyur na /
NK065(cu)001:10351: 'jam dpal mtshan brjod sogs kyang der thal /
NK065(cu)001:10352: de ltar ma smos pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:10353: de nas gsang ba bshad par bya //
NK065(cu)001:10355: de nas dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK065(cu)001:10358: mngon rtogs rgyan gyi 'grel pa las /
NK065(cu)001:10359: 'di ni rnam par gzhag pa gzhan kho na yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:10360: theg pa gzhan gyi lugs la brten nas nam du'ang sun 'byin brjod par mi bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:10361: zhes pa ltar shes par byas te bag yod par spyod cig /
NK065(cu)001:10362: gnyis pa thun mong gi gleng gzhi la /
NK065(cu)001:10363: rgyud khyad par gyi gleng gzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:10364: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:10367: zhar byung gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gazhi'o //
NK065(cu)001:10368: dang po ni rgyud 'di'i le'u dang pos ston te /
NK065(cu)001:10373: 'di skad bshad pa'i sogs la phun sum tshogs pa
NK065(cu)001:10374: drug sngar ltar ngos bzung nas rgyas bshad dang sbyar
NK065(cu)001:10375: ro // 'dir thun mong gi gleng gzhir brjod pa ni snga ma thun min pa ltos nas te /
NK065(cu)001:10376: gzhan du na 'di yang thun min nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:10377: gal te thun mong yin na /
NK065(cu)001:10380: 'khor gang dang lhan cig tu bzhugs pa'i dus de'i tshe chos 'di lta bu zhig thos shes /
NK065(cu)001:10382: chos theg pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10383: dus res 'ga' ba zhig ston dgos pa las 'dir de ltar mi ston te /
NK065(cu)001:10386: de'i don rgyas bshad las shes par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10387: de bas na thun mong khyad par gyi gleng gzhir bsnyad do zhes bla ma rnams gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:10389: thun khyad 'gal bar mi 'gyur ram snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:10392: glan t+aika pa sogs snga rabs ba dag /
NK065(cu)001:10393: gnas 'og min tsam du ming thun mong du gyur kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10394: 'dir dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min gyis khyad par du spags /
NK065(cu)001:10395: ston pa longs sku tsam du mthun kyang rgyal ba drug pas spags /
NK065(cu)001:10396: 'khor byang sems tsam du mthun kyang 'bras bu'i sems dpas spags /
NK065(cu)001:10397: bstan pa grol lam tsam du mthun kyang grol lam khyad par can lam gsang ba'i snying pos spags /
NK065(cu)001:10398: des na thun mong khyad par gyi gleng gazhi'o gsung /
NK065(cu)001:10401: ston pa la sogs par dbye bas //
NK065(cu)001:10402: phun sum tshogs pa lngar brjod do //
NK065(cu)001:10405: ston gnas 'khor dang sdud pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:10406: bstan pa dus kyis shes par bya //
NK065(cu)001:10407: zhes pas phun sum tshogs pa lnga'am drug las /
NK065(cu)001:10412: bcom ldan 'das drug pa spyi'i gzugs can kun tu bzang po ste /
NK065(cu)001:10414: ston pa'i rang bzhin brgyad dang ldan //
NK065(cu)001:10415: bdag nyid byed pa kun tu bzang //
NK065(cu)001:10424: ston pa'i dgongs pa rang byung gi ye shes de
NK065(cu)001:10425: nyid chos can 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK065(cu)001:10426: cad dang chos nyid tha mi dad par gnas pa
NK065(cu)001:10429: bi ma las rang bzhin bzhir bshad de /
NK065(cu)001:10431: byang chub mchog gi ngo bo dang //
NK065(cu)001:10432: chos rnams rol par longs spyod dang //
NK065(cu)001:10433: phyogs dus bde gshegs bdag po dang //
NK065(cu)001:10434: chos so cog dang dbyer med pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10437: rgyal ba drug pa'i yon tan mtha' yas pa'ang mdor bdun du 'du ste /
NK065(cu)001:10438: zhes pa rang bzhin bdun dang /
NK065(cu)001:10441: rdzogs pa so sor phye bas brgyad du bshad kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10443: dang po 'das pa'i chos dang dbyer mi phyed par bstan pa la /
NK065(cu)001:10444: mtshan gyi rnam grangs lnga so sor bstan pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10445: spyir bsdus te mi phyed par bstan pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10447: ston pa'i che ba'i yon tan gyi ldog cha nas smos na mtshan lnga ste /
NK065(cu)001:10448: de bzhin nyid du nar son pa'i rang bzhin ni de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK065(cu)001:10450: spyir ta th+aa ga ta'i sgra las ta th+aa ni de bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:10455: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams ji ltar byang chub kyi
NK065(cu)001:10456: spyod pa'i sgo nas gshegs pa de ltar lam mthun
NK065(cu)001:10457: pas gshegs shing byon pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10458: de bzhin nyid ji lta bar mkhyen cing gsung ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:10459: 'dod yon gyi snang ba ji ltar snang ba de ni thabs kyis spyad pas gshegs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10460: sems can rnams skye ba rnam pa bzhi'i tshul gyis
NK065(cu)001:10461: skye ba las de dag gi bsam pa dang mthun
NK065(cu)001:10462: par mngal nas skye ba de bzhin du gshegs pa
NK065(cu)001:10465: gang phyir de bzhin nyid du gshegs //
NK065(cu)001:10466: de bzhin gshegs par mngon par brjod //
NK065(cu)001:10468: chos nyid de bzhin nyid kyi don sgrib byed kyi zhen pa dang bral bas nar son zhing /
NK065(cu)001:10469: de'i ngo bo mngon du gyur pa'i gshegs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10471: de bzhin nyid du gshegs pa yang //
NK065(cu)001:10472: sna tshogs zhen las grol bar bshad //
NK065(cu)001:10475: zhes pa ni yon tan ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK065(cu)001:10476: rang byung gi ye shes la spang bya ma grub
NK065(cu)001:10477: pas ma nor mi 'gyur mi bslu ba'i phyir yang
NK065(cu)001:10478: dag pa dang / des na thams cad 'bras bu
NK065(cu)001:10479: sku dang ye shes su rang snang bas spang thob
NK065(cu)001:10480: lhag ma ma lus pa'i phyir rdzogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10481: 'dis lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin las khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10482: sangs rgyas zhes pa ni sgrib bral gyi ye shes mtha' dbus med par brdal ba'i rang bzhin te /
NK065(cu)001:10484: gnyid sad pa ltar sangs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10485: pad+ma kha bye ba ltar rgyas pa'i don gnyis la 'jug par /
NK065(cu)001:10487: ma rig gnyid las sangs phyir dang //
NK065(cu)001:10488: shes bya la yang blo rgyas phyir //
NK065(cu)001:10490: 'dir ni mi mthun pa dang gnyen po dbyer med kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10491: don ji bzhin pa mngon du byas pa'i stobs kyis
NK065(cu)001:10492: spang thob med pa'i yon tan mthar thug pa ste
NK065(cu)001:10494: ma rig pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK065(cu)001:10495: nyon mongs sdug bsngal byang chub mchog /
NK065(cu)001:10497: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa ni sgrib pa'i cha shas
NK065(cu)001:10498: phra mo tsam yang mi gnas pas bdud bzhi bcom
NK065(cu)001:10499: zhing che ba'i yon tan gyi 'bras bu la mnga'
NK065(cu)001:10500: mdzad kyang rang gi ngo bo bstan du med pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10501: rang bzhin te / rdo rje las rim las /
NK065(cu)001:10502: bdud bzhi la sogs rig pa'i gdeng gis bcom //
NK065(cu)001:10503: sku lnga la sogs yon tan brjod las 'das //
NK065(cu)001:10504: rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes bstan du med //
NK065(cu)001:10506: longs spyod chen po zhes pa ni mnyam pa nyid
NK065(cu)001:10507: kyi don mngon du mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral
NK065(cu)001:10509: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad la spyad bya spyod
NK065(cu)001:10510: byed du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa dang bral ba'i sgo
NK065(cu)001:10511: nas longs spyod par gzhan las ches mchog tu gyur
NK065(cu)001:10512: pa'i phyir ro // de ltar yang 'chi med mdzod las /
NK065(cu)001:10513: chen po mchog dang tshad med dang //
NK065(cu)001:10514: mkhas mtshon spros pa'i las 'di nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10515: shin tu rmad byung byed pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:10516: chen po zhes ni bshad pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:10520: rdo rje'i bdag nyid ces pa'i bar gyis de bzhin
NK065(cu)001:10521: gshegs pa kun gyi bdag gcig dang du ma las
NK065(cu)001:10523: sngar smos pa'i mtshan lnga dang ldan pa'i phyogs dus
NK065(cu)001:10524: bde gshegs kun gyi yon tan thams cad bsdu na
NK065(cu)001:10526: de'i zlas drangs pa'i yon tan phrin las gnyis te lnga'o //
NK065(cu)001:10527: de'ang rten byed pa'i ngos nas sku lnga /
NK065(cu)001:10531: gzhan don mdzad pa'i phrin las lnga ste /
NK065(cu)001:10532: de dag gcig dang du ma dang bral zhing /
NK065(cu)001:10533: rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK065(cu)001:10534: mtshan nyid skye 'jig dang bral ba /
NK065(cu)001:10535: ngo bo 'dus ma byas pa'i phyir rdo rje'i bdag nyid de /
NK065(cu)001:10537: 'bras bu lnga ni rigs lnga ste //
NK065(cu)001:10538: zhes pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lnga po ni rigs lngar bzhed la /
NK065(cu)001:10539: de'i phyir sngar gyi 'bras bu nyer lnga po'ang kun
NK065(cu)001:10540: tu bzang po'i dgongs pa rang byung gi ye shes
NK065(cu)001:10541: su 'dus shing / rigs lnga yang drug par 'dus pas na du ma dang bral ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10542: kun bzang la sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi gzugs can zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:10543: drug pa'i yon tan gyi khyad par las 'bras bu
NK065(cu)001:10544: nyer lnga dang rigs lngar ma 'gags par snang bas
NK065(cu)001:10545: gcig dang du ma dang bral ba'i phyir rigs thams
NK065(cu)001:10546: cad kyi bdag po zhes btags so //
NK065(cu)001:10547: gnyis pa 'khor ba'i chos dang dbyer mi phyed pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK065(cu)001:10548: ma lus nas rang bzhin te zhes pa'i bar te /
NK065(cu)001:10549: khams gsum dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos dang rgyal ba drug pa gnyis ka'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10550: kun rdzob tu rig pa sgyu ma yin pa'i phyir so so ma yin /
NK065(cu)001:10551: don dam par sems nyid du ma skyes pa'i phyir tha mi dad /
NK065(cu)001:10552: bden pa gnyis kyi tha snyad las 'das pa'i phyir dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK065(cu)001:10553: gal te kun rdzob tu so so dang /
NK065(cu)001:10554: don dam du tha dad na /
NK065(cu)001:10557: so so rang bzhin nges shes na //
NK065(cu)001:10558: yang dag lam gyis bcos su med //
NK065(cu)001:10560: ye nas ngo bo yod min na //
NK065(cu)001:10561: nyon mongs spangs shing byang bsgrub med //
NK065(cu)001:10562: ces pas gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10563: de ltar rang bzhin bdun po kun tu bzang po'i
NK065(cu)001:10564: rang bzhin yin pa ltar rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yang
NK065(cu)001:10565: de bdun dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10566: rigs lnga la rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i 'khor zhes grags so //
NK065(cu)001:10571: rang bzhin de nyid gdul bya la sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma sna tshogs par snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:10573: ston pa'i ngo bo yang yin la 'chad pa'i skyes
NK065(cu)001:10574: bu'i mtshan nyid kyang yin pas thun mong du ston
NK065(cu)001:10575: zhes spar khab mkhan po gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:10576: de'ang tshoms bsdus na bzhi ste /
NK065(cu)001:10577: sku gsum gyi bdag nyid yin pa'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:10578: thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:10579: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i dang /
NK065(cu)001:10580: rnam thar gsum chub pa'i don rtags so //
NK065(cu)001:10583: sku mdun dang rgyab med pa thams cad du zhal thal le bar gsal zhing /
NK065(cu)001:10585: ston pa dang rigs lnga ni ye shes kyi sku yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10586: bde gshegs rang snang la sku mdun dang rgyab ma grub cing /
NK065(cu)001:10587: gdul bya'i snang ba la ris med par thams cad
NK065(cu)001:10588: du zhal thal le bar gsal bar gzugs sku'i yon
NK065(cu)001:10591: kun tu bzang po'i zhal ni phyogs bcur gsal //
NK065(cu)001:10592: kun gzigs kun bzang sku la mdun rgyab med //
NK065(cu)001:10593: phyogs bcu gang bar spyan gyis rnam par gzigs //
NK065(cu)001:10596: mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pa /
NK065(cu)001:10601: mtshan mchog sum cu rtsa gnyis ni //
NK065(cu)001:10602: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldan //
NK065(cu)001:10606: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni //
NK065(cu)001:10607: sen mo zangs kyi mdog ltar 'dug /
NK065(cu)001:10609: khyad par gyi mtshan dpe la phyi nang gsang gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:10611: me long lta bu sogs ye shes bzhi po re
NK065(cu)001:10612: re la'ang bzhi bzhir phye ba'i ye shes bcu drug
NK065(cu)001:10613: gi rtsal sems dpa' bcu drug dang /
NK065(cu)001:10614: de'i yul chos kyi dbyings bcu drug gi rtsal sems
NK065(cu)001:10615: ma bcu drug ste sum cu rtsa gnyis ni mtshan
NK065(cu)001:10616: bzang po'o // sems dpa' bcu drug por ye shes
NK065(cu)001:10617: lnga'i rtags rigs lngas dbu brgyan pa'i lha brgyad cu
NK065(cu)001:10620: mtshan gyi me tog la dpe byad kyi 'bras bus spras pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10621: sras kyi tshogs kyis kun nas brgyan pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10623: 'dir yum bcu drug la dbu rgyan ma bshad de /
NK065(cu)001:10624: chos kyi dbyings mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10625: de dag kyang rgyan du cis 'gyur zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:10626: 'khor dang 'khor gyi rgyan phun sum tshogs pas gtso
NK065(cu)001:10627: bo'i rang bzhin yang bkod pas mdzes shing phun sum
NK065(cu)001:10631: spyi bo'i so gnyis kyis mtshan bzang po dang mgrin pa'i bcu drug /
NK065(cu)001:10633: lte ba'i drug cu rtsa bzhi las stong pa'i rtsa bzhi phri bas drug cu ste /
NK065(cu)001:10634: de ltar brgyad cu ni dpe byad do //
NK065(cu)001:10636: sgra dbyangs gsung gi gnas bzhi yi //
NK065(cu)001:10637: dbye bas gsum gsum ngos gnyis dang //
NK065(cu)001:10638: bzhi bcu gnyis su gyur pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:10641: ston pa yab yum gnyis rol pa'i dus kyi dga' ba la brtsi ste /
NK065(cu)001:10642: yab kyi dga' ba bcu drug dang yum gyi dga'
NK065(cu)001:10643: ba bcu drug ste so gnyis ni mtshan bzang po'o
NK065(cu)001:10644: // yab kyi dga' ba re re la'ang ye shes
NK065(cu)001:10645: lnga lnga'i ro dang ldan pa'i phyir brgyad cu ni
NK065(cu)001:10646: // dpe byad de / rgya mtsho las /
NK065(cu)001:10647: +aa li k+aa li'i bde ba nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10648: phan tshun ma 'dres gcig par shes //
NK065(cu)001:10649: bcu drug ros gnyis mtshan dang ldan //
NK065(cu)001:10650: phyogs gcig ye shes lnga ldan pa //
NK065(cu)001:10651: brgyad cu'o bzod sogs rgyu las 'phags //
NK065(cu)001:10653: ci'i phyir nang dang gsang ba'i mtshan dpe rtsa khams
NK065(cu)001:10654: kyi rang bzhin du 'dug pas rgyan du ji ltar
NK065(cu)001:10655: 'gyur snyam na / longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la
NK065(cu)001:10656: rtsa khams rnam par dag pa bde ba chen po'i
NK065(cu)001:10657: rang bzhin du ro mnyam pa ni rgyan gyi nang
NK065(cu)001:10658: nas mchog go ces g.yung t+aika ba gsung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:10659: de ltar na phyag zhabs 'khor lo la sogs pa
NK065(cu)001:10660: ni sprul sku sogs la'ang yod pa'i phyir thun mong
NK065(cu)001:10661: dang / phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi mtshan dpe
NK065(cu)001:10662: ni ston pa dang 'chad pa'i skyes bu kho na'i
NK065(cu)001:10663: 'phags chos yin pa'i phyir khyad par ro //
NK065(cu)001:10665: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba /
NK065(cu)001:10666: zhes pa sprul pa thams cad kyi 'byung gnas te /
NK065(cu)001:10667: rnam par 'phrul pa bsam gyis mi khyab cing tshad med pa ni mdzad pa'i snang tshul lo //
NK065(cu)001:10668: de ltar yang sdong po bkod pa las /
NK065(cu)001:10669: spu yi rtse mo gcig la yang //
NK065(cu)001:10670: zhing rnams bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK065(cu)001:10671: sna tshogs dbyibs kyang tha dad de //
NK065(cu)001:10672: de dag 'dres par gyur pa med //
NK065(cu)001:10674: gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:10676: nam mkhas ji tsam khyab pa de tsam du de bzhin gshegs pa'i skus khyab bo //
NK065(cu)001:10677: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:10679: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis sogs te /
NK065(cu)001:10680: thabs snying rje chen po dang /
NK065(cu)001:10681: shes rab stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi brdar
NK065(cu)001:10682: zhabs gnyis yab yum gnyis ka skyil krung du mtshungs
NK065(cu)001:10685: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mtshungs par skyil
NK065(cu)001:10686: krung du bcings nas snyoms par 'jug cing bzhugs pa
NK065(cu)001:10687: / zhes pas bzhengs pa lta bu ma yin gyi gnyis ka skyil krung du bstan no //
NK065(cu)001:10688: skyil krung la bla ma rnams rigs drug pa rdo rje'i skyil krung dang /
NK065(cu)001:10690: 'chad pa'i skyes bu'i rigs lnga yab rnams mnyam pa'am rdzogs pa'i skyil krung dang /
NK065(cu)001:10691: yum brtul zhugs kyi skyil krung gis g.yon phyogs nas 'khyud pa'o gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:10693: ye shes drug gi sogs te /
NK065(cu)001:10694: ye shes lnga rang byung gi ye shes dang drug ldan pa'i rtags su phyag drug dang /
NK065(cu)001:10695: des 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags su phyag mtshan drug 'dzin pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:10696: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i mtshan mar gyur pa'i rdo rje sogs lnga dang /
NK065(cu)001:10697: chos kyi dbyings kyi phyag rgya dril bu ste /
NK065(cu)001:10698: sgyu 'phrul rol pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:10699: ye shes drug gi bdag nyid kyi //
NK065(cu)001:10700: phyag rgya rin chen 'bar ba'i mtshan //
NK065(cu)001:10701: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK065(cu)001:10705: sku gsung thugs zhes sogs te sku stong pa nyid dang /
NK065(cu)001:10706: gsung mtshan ma med pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10707: thugs smon pa med pa gsum ni blo'i spyod yul
NK065(cu)001:10708: las 'das pa'i phyir bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste
NK065(cu)001:10709: / de gsum gyi mtshan ma'ang rim bzhin dbu dkar dmar mthing gsum gyi kha dog tu bstan no //
NK065(cu)001:10710: de dag gis ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rgyas par bstan pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10713: bdag po kun bzang 'khor rnams la //
NK065(cu)001:10715: mi bskyod rgyal po mdun na gnas //
NK065(cu)001:10717: rgyud kyi ston pa rigs drug pa kun bzang dang /
NK065(cu)001:10720: 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga ste //
NK065(cu)001:10721: zhes pas rigs lnga char yin kyang //
NK065(cu)001:10722: thugs kyi sgyu 'phrul gyi skabs 'dir mi bskyod pa mdun na bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:10723: gnyis pa 'chad pa'i skyes bu ni /
NK065(cu)001:10726: mtshungs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:10727: lngas kyang bstan pa gsung mi 'gal //
NK065(cu)001:10729: dang po rigs lnga yab lnga ni /
NK065(cu)001:10730: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK065(cu)001:10738: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK065(cu)001:10739: 'du byed rnam par shes pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10740: phung po lnga zhes rab tu brjod //
NK065(cu)001:10743: yul rnam par rig pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi tshogs brgyad de /
NK065(cu)001:10749: gzugs su rung ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi chos bco lnga ste /
NK065(cu)001:10753: gzugs ni dbang po lnga dang don //
NK065(cu)001:10754: lnga dang rnam rig byed min nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10756: tshor ba nii nyams su myong ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi /
NK065(cu)001:10762: yul la mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi /
NK065(cu)001:10765: tshad med pa ste gsum mo //
NK065(cu)001:10767: mngon par 'du byed pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi sems pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10768: de'ang sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig ste /
NK065(cu)001:10774: gzhan 'gyur bzhi rnams su yod pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10776: tshor 'du sems reg yid byed de //
NK065(cu)001:10777: kun tu 'gro ba rnam pa lnga //
NK065(cu)001:10779: 'dun mos dran ting shes rab ste //
NK065(cu)001:10780: yul nges skye ba rnam pa lnga //
NK065(cu)001:10782: dad dang ngo tsha shes khrel yod //
NK065(cu)001:10783: ma chags zhe sdang gti mug med //
NK065(cu)001:10784: brtson 'grus bag yod shin tu sbyangs //
NK065(cu)001:10785: btang snyoms rnam par mi 'tshe ba //
NK065(cu)001:10786: bcu gcig po ni dge ba yin //
NK065(cu)001:10788: 'dod chags khong khro nga rgyal dang //
NK065(cu)001:10789: ma rig the tshom lta ba ste //
NK065(cu)001:10790: rtsa ba'i nyon mongs rnam pa drug /
NK065(cu)001:10793: g.yo rgyags med ngo tsha khrel gnyis rnam par 'tshe //
NK065(cu)001:10794: dmu rgod ma dad le lo dang //
NK065(cu)001:10795: bag med brjed ngas shes bzhin min //
NK065(cu)001:10796: rnam g.yeng nyi shu nye nyon mongs //
NK065(cu)001:10800: de ltar sems byung lnga bcu rtsa gcig las /
NK065(cu)001:10802: 'du shes gnyis phri ba'i lhag ma bzhi bcu rtsa dgu ni 'du byed do //
NK065(cu)001:10804: kun 'gro lnga las tshor 'du gnyis phung por logs su bzhag ce na /
NK065(cu)001:10806: rtsod pa'i rtsa bar gyur pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:10807: 'khor ba'i rgyu phyir rim rgyu'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:10808: sems byung rnam las tshor ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:10809: 'du byed logs shig phung por bzhag /
NK065(cu)001:10811: des na phung po lnga la yan lag brgyad cu ste /
NK065(cu)001:10813: de dag rang gi yan lag brgyad cu dang bcas pa nyid /
NK065(cu)001:10814: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK065(cu)001:10818: phung po'i go rim dang por gzugs phung smos na /
NK065(cu)001:10819: 'dir rnam shes dang por smos pa gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:10821: 'di las phyi rol du gyur pa'i thun mong gi
NK065(cu)001:10822: theg pa las khyad par du 'phags par ston pa
NK065(cu)001:10824: phyi rol ba dag gzung ba'i don rags pa dag la gtso bor 'dod pa yin la /
NK065(cu)001:10825: 'dir ni 'dzin pa'i gzhi rtsa ba'i rnam pa shes pa gtso bor 'dod pa yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:10827: theg pa chen po sangs rgyas kyi bkar bzhed pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:10829: gnyis pa lha dang sbyor tshul la /
NK065(cu)001:10833: 'di'i skabs kyi rnam shes ni tshogs brgyad ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10835: gal te tshogs brgyad du 'dod na /
NK065(cu)001:10836: mi bskyod pa'i rgyud la kun gzhi yod pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10837: dgra bcom pa ma yin par thal ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:10839: sgrib gnyis spangs pa'i gang zag ma yin par thal ba'i skyon yod do gsungs na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10840: thun mong gi gzhung dang bstun par zad kyi /
NK065(cu)001:10841: 'dir ni shin tu mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:10842: dmyal ba'i thub pa chos can khyod kyi rgyud la zhe sdang med par thal /
NK065(cu)001:10843: khyod zhe sdang bzod par spangs pa'i gang zag yin pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:10844: khyod sangs rgyas 'phags pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10845: zhes rtog pa thams cad la mgo mtshungs pa'i phyir mi 'thad do //
NK065(cu)001:10847: thams cad ma lus chos so cog /
NK065(cu)001:10848: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:10851: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po ni /
NK065(cu)001:10852: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' kun gzhi rnam par dag pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10853: de yang yongs su ma dag pa'i dus na ni /
NK065(cu)001:10854: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba yin la /
NK065(cu)001:10855: yongs su dag pa'i dus na ni /
NK065(cu)001:10856: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:10858: de'i phyir theg pa 'di'i lugs kyi kun gzhi nyid
NK065(cu)001:10859: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su ye nas dag
NK065(cu)001:10860: pas spang gnyen du mi 'dod de /
NK065(cu)001:10863: rdo rje phung po yan lag ni /
NK065(cu)001:10864: zhes pa'i yan lag 'dren pa'i tshe brgyad cur bgrangs pa dang yang nang 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:10865: kun gzhi dang nyon yid phri bas /
NK065(cu)001:10866: rtog pa don brgyad las ma byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10868: rtog tshogs phung po lnga'i rang bzhin ye ji bzhin pa'i rigs lnga yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:10869: khyad par du rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas lnga'i 'bras
NK065(cu)001:10870: bu mngon du byas te mthar phyin par gyur pa'am
NK065(cu)001:10871: / de lta bu'i rtog pa thugs rang rig pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10872: ye shes kyis rang dbang bsgyur zhing zag med kyi
NK065(cu)001:10873: chos la mnga' brnyes pas bde ba chen por longs
NK065(cu)001:10874: spyod pas na rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:10876: gzhung 'dir lha'i mtshan nas mi smos par rtog pa'i mtshan nas smos pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:10877: rgyal po dang 'og tu chen po zhes sogs kyis rtog pa'i mtshan nas smos pa ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:10878: mya ngan las 'das pa zhes pas sangs rgyas la
NK065(cu)001:10879: mya ngan gyi ming gis brjod pa ma yin pa
NK065(cu)001:10880: bzhin no gsungs / don du 'di yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10881: ma dag pa 'khor ba'i gnas skabs su'ang /
NK065(cu)001:10882: rtog pa rnams rang bzhin gyis dag pas sku dang
NK065(cu)001:10883: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs par gsang sngags
NK065(cu)001:10884: kyi rgyud rnams su gsungs par ma zad /
NK065(cu)001:10885: nges don gyi mdo sde zab mo rnams las kyang 'byung ste /
NK065(cu)001:10888: gzugs dang tshor ba 'du shes dang //
NK065(cu)001:10889: rnam par shes dang sems dpa' ni //
NK065(cu)001:10890: grangs med de bzhin gshegs pa rnams //
NK065(cu)001:10891: de dag thub pa chen por 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:10893: byams pa seng ge'i sgra'i mdo las kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10894: gal te de bzhin gshegs pa mchod par 'dod pa des bdag nyid mchod par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:10896: dri ma med par bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:10897: 'jig tshogs la blta ba ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:10898: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:10899: des na 'dir rtog pa'i mtshan nas smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:10901: kun gzhi la sogs pa'i rtog pa lnga smos pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:10902: rang bzhin dang thun mong ma yin pa'i phyir smos pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:10903: de dag kar dag par thugs su chud pa la
NK065(cu)001:10904: rdo rje 'dzin pa la sogs par rang snang ba'i
NK065(cu)001:10905: phyir ro // zhes pas rang bzhin shes bya'i gshis la /
NK065(cu)001:10906: rtog pa dang lha gnyis snang na snang mnyam /
NK065(cu)001:10908: bzang ngan med par mnyam pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:10909: thun min gyi theg pa 'dir lam pas lha rtog
NK065(cu)001:10910: dbyer med du ngos zin par bya ba'i phyir dang
NK065(cu)001:10911: / 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i dus na rtog pa
NK065(cu)001:10912: nyid ma spangs ma bsgyur bar lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK065(cu)001:10913: rang snang ba'i phyir smos pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10914: rtog tshogs lhar snang ba'i 'thad pa gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:10916: phyi rol gyi don yod pa'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10917: shes bya nang gi dbang du byas pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:10919: rtog pa'i rang bzhin lhar snang ba yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10920: ye nas yin pa nyid lam rkyen dang 'phrad na lhar snang rung ma 'gags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10921: dper na dngul chus bsdus pa'i gser phye nyid dngul
NK065(cu)001:10922: gyi gong bu lta bur snang yang me'i rkyen dang
NK065(cu)001:10924: ma 'phrad na mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:10926: sgyu 'phrul rtog pa'i d+r+wa ba rnam par bsal ba'i rgyud phyi ma'i phyi ma las /
NK065(cu)001:10928: bcom ldan 'das rnal 'byor pa 'di dag rgyu ci lta bu zhig las bsgrub par bgyi ba lags /
NK065(cu)001:10935: 'o na rgyu las kyang 'bras bu snang ba bskyed par 'gyur pa lags /
NK065(cu)001:10940: rgyu las 'bras bu'i shes rab snang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:10942: phung po lnga la sogs pa gang dag pa sgyu mar phyag rgya bzhi bcur snang ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:10943: don dam par na don dam rtse gcig par snang ba'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:10947: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:10948: de nyid ni de yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10949: bsgrub par bya ba dang yang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10952: dper na rkyen gyi 'brel ba dang ma 'phrad pa'i 'bras bu skye ba'i rgyu yod kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10953: mngon du 'byin pa'i nus pa med bzhin du /
NK065(cu)001:10954: byang chub kyi rgyu yod kyang /
NK065(cu)001:10955: rkyen ting nge 'dzin la ma 'brel ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:10956: 'bras bu 'byin pa'i nus pa med pas na /
NK065(cu)001:10960: snang la ma nges pa'i phyir rtog pa'i rang bzhin lha yin te /
NK065(cu)001:10963: dag pa'i zhing gi 'gro ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:10964: grub pa'i gang zag rnams kyis mthong tshul tha dad pa bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:10965: de'ang dpal nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:10966: 'gro ba 'di kun sangs rgyas lnga bdag nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10967: gar mkhan dang ni ri mo bzang ltar snang //
NK065(cu)001:10969: lha dang rtog pa'i chos mthun ni /
NK065(cu)001:10970: rnam shes thugs kyi bdag nyid yin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:10971: gzugs dang sku mthun pa gnyis ni dngos su mthun par zad do //
NK065(cu)001:10972: tshor ba ni yul la longs spyod du blta ba'i gzhi yin pa'i phyir yon tan dang /
NK065(cu)001:10973: 'du shes ni mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i bdag nyid phyi
NK065(cu)001:10974: nang gi chos rnams la tha snyad du 'dogs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10975: las kyis brda' sprod pa'i phyir gsung dang /
NK065(cu)001:10976: 'du byed ni bya ba byed pas las kyi bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:10977: de dag kyang ye shes grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:10978: gzugs ni rnam par snang mdzad nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10979: tshor ba rin chen 'byung ldan la //
NK065(cu)001:10980: 'du shes snang ba mtha' yas te //
NK065(cu)001:10981: 'du byed don yod grub pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:10982: rnam par shes pa mi bskyod pa //
NK065(cu)001:10985: tshul khrims la sogs phung po lnga //
NK065(cu)001:10986: zag med rnams ni gzhan yin no //
NK065(cu)001:10987: zhes nyer len gyi phung po lnga gnas gyur pa'i
NK065(cu)001:10988: zag med kyi phung po lnga dang chos mthun brtsi
NK065(cu)001:10989: ba ni / rnam shes gnas gyur rnam par grol
NK065(cu)001:10990: ba'i ye shes gzigs pa'i phung po ni thugs kyi
NK065(cu)001:10992: de bzhin du gzugs gnas gyur tshul khrims kyi phung po ni dri ma med pa'i sku dang /
NK065(cu)001:10993: tshor ba gnas gyur ting nge 'dzin yon tan gyi gzhir gyur pa'i phyir yon tan dang /
NK065(cu)001:10994: 'du shes gnas gyur shes rab ni lung rtogs kyi chos kyi gzhi'i phyir gsung dang /
NK065(cu)001:10995: 'du byed gnas gyur rnam par grol ba'i phung po
NK065(cu)001:10996: ni mdzad pa la yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid
NK065(cu)001:10997: dang gzhir gyur pa'i phyir phrin las te /
NK065(cu)001:10999: sgrol t+aika tu 'di dang go rim mi gcig par sbyar na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:11001: gzugs kyi phung po gnas gyur tshul khrims sku //
NK065(cu)001:11002: tshor ba gnas gyur ting 'dzin 'bum phrag brnyes //
NK065(cu)001:11003: 'du shes gnas gyur shes rab phung po ste //
NK065(cu)001:11004: 'du byed gnas gyur rnam par grol ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:11005: sems gyur ye shes de ni rnam grol mthong //
NK065(cu)001:11006: zhes dkon mchog 'grel du gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11007: yang nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK065(cu)001:11008: phung po lnga chos mthun brtsis te rigs lnga dang sbyar ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:11010: gzugs ni gti mug tu bstan pa //
NK065(cu)001:11011: blun pas bcings pa'i ngo bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:11012: tshor ba 'dod pas myos bstan pa //
NK065(cu)001:11013: nga rgyal gyi ni ngo bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:11015: dngos po la ni chags pa'i mtshan //
NK065(cu)001:11016: 'du byed rtag tu phrag dog ste //
NK065(cu)001:11017: rtse gcig bdag nyid gtod pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11018: rnam shes zhe sdang zhes bstan te //
NK065(cu)001:11019: rgyud dang 'bras bur rab tu grags //
NK065(cu)001:11020: zhes pa sngar bzhin rigs lnga dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11022: gal te rnam shes lhar dag pa'i tshe mig gi
NK065(cu)001:11023: rnam shes kyang mi bskyod par dag gam ma dag
NK065(cu)001:11025: dag ma dag 'gal ba'i chos can yin pa'i phyir spyi bye brag bdag mi gcig par 'gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:11027: dag pa gzhan du brjod du med par 'gyur zhing /
NK065(cu)001:11029: 'og tu byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:11030: zhes pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11032: ltos sa tha dad la ltos nas /
NK065(cu)001:11033: rnam shes kyi phung po spyi bye brag gnyis gtso 'khor du dag pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11034: tha mal gyi rnam shes ril po gcig tu zhen
NK065(cu)001:11035: pa'i gnyen por bye brag sa snying sogs su dag
NK065(cu)001:11036: tshul dang / slar tha dad du zhen pa'i gnyen
NK065(cu)001:11037: por spyir mi bskyod par dag tshul smos pa ste
NK065(cu)001:11039: tha dad min las tha dad pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:11040: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK065(cu)001:11041: dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye shes lo //
NK065(cu)001:11042: 'jigs med kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK065(cu)001:11044: de bzhin du gzugs phung spyi rnam snang du dag
NK065(cu)001:11045: pa'i tshe rgyu'i gzugs bzhi yum du dag gam ma
NK065(cu)001:11046: dag gi rtsod spong sogs rigs 'gre sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11047: gsum pa rigs kyi dbye ba la /
NK065(cu)001:11052: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po zhes pa ni lha'i dus na mi bskyod pa ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:11053: rnam shes dag pa thugs kyi bdag nyid rnam snang yin pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:11054: dbus su rigs bdag mtshon byed kyi gdan 'khor lo dang seng ge /
NK065(cu)001:11056: chos dbyings ye shes rnams byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:11057: khro bo'i skabs su'ang bud+d+ha he ru ka'i sku mdog
NK065(cu)001:11058: dang sngags thog mar smos pa'i phyir ro zhe na
