NK065(cu)001:11059: / de ni rgyud gzhung so so'i dgongs pa tha
NK065(cu)001:11060: dad pa mang du snang ba ltar gdul bya la
NK065(cu)001:11061: shes rab kyi blo nor ster ba'i skyes bu snang
NK065(cu)001:11062: ba'i phyir gces spras su bya ba tsam yin gyi
NK065(cu)001:11063: / / skabs 'dir blang bar bya ba ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:11064: thun mong ma yin pa'i lung rigs man ngag gsum dang 'gal ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11065: de yang lung dang gal te /
NK065(cu)001:11067: gzugs la rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK065(cu)001:11069: rnam shes rdo rje sems dpa' ste //
NK065(cu)001:11073: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' dag /
NK065(cu)001:11075: shar gyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK065(cu)001:11076: bde gshegs rnam par snang mdzad dag /
NK065(cu)001:11080: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK065(cu)001:11081: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pa //
NK065(cu)001:11082: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK065(cu)001:11085: kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems rdo rje mi bskyod
NK065(cu)001:11086: pa la ni rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po zhes
NK065(cu)001:11090: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po chos can /
NK065(cu)001:11092: khyod mi bskyod pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11094: rnam shes dag pa thugs yin la /
NK065(cu)001:11095: de rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod par nges pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:11096: glang po che rab 'bog gi rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:11097: don dam par sems can gyi rnam par shes pa
NK065(cu)001:11098: gnas su dag pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs kyi
NK065(cu)001:11100: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mi bskyod pa /
NK065(cu)001:11102: de ltar rnam shes dag pa mi bskyod par grub mod /
NK065(cu)001:11103: 'on kyang sngar gyi skyon rnams kyis gnod par mi 'gyur ram snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:11105: gdan gyi 'khor lo ni rigs bdag mtshon byed kyi mtshan ma ma yin gyi /
NK065(cu)001:11106: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i phyag rgya ste /
NK065(cu)001:11108: gzhi yang tshad med 'khor lo ste //
NK065(cu)001:11109: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin yin //
NK065(cu)001:11111: seng khri yang thugs gtso bor ston pa'i phyir rdo rje'i rigs dang sbyar ba tsam du zad de /
NK065(cu)001:11112: slob dpon pad+mas mdzad pa'i yang dag gi las rim shel phreng las /
NK065(cu)001:11113: seng ge glang rta rma bya khyung //
NK065(cu)001:11114: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK065(cu)001:11115: gtso dang 'khor du rim par bsam //
NK065(cu)001:11116: zhes gtso bo rdo rje'i rigs mi bskyod pa'i gdan du seng ge byung ba'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:11117: yum dbyings phyug ma ni rnam shes kyi yul nam mkha'i khams dang sbyor ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:11119: mi bskyod mthing ga dkar dmar zhal //
NK065(cu)001:11120: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK065(cu)001:11121: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK065(cu)001:11122: dbyings phyug g.yas brten g.yon dril sogs //
NK065(cu)001:11125: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK065(cu)001:11126: ces pas kyang bstan pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11129: zhe sdang rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin rnam par
NK065(cu)001:11130: shes pa'i phung po yongs su dag pa thugs rdo
NK065(cu)001:11131: rje chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi bdag nyid
NK065(cu)001:11133: zhes pas 'dir zhe sdang dag pa chos dbyings ye
NK065(cu)001:11134: shes su bzhed pa'i lugs yin pa'i phyir skyon med
NK065(cu)001:11135: de / ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:11136: gti mug me long ye shes blta //
NK065(cu)001:11137: nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid du dran //
NK065(cu)001:11138: so sor rtog pa 'dod chags yin //
NK065(cu)001:11139: bya ba grub pa phrag dog che //
NK065(cu)001:11140: zhe sdang chos dbyings rnam par dag /
NK065(cu)001:11143: bud+d+ha he ru ka gtso bor ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:11144: pan grub kyi man ngag rnams su rgyud 'khrugs pa
NK065(cu)001:11145: bsdebs nas gtso bor badz+ra he ru kar bzhed pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11146: phyir / de ltar yang rgya cher 'grel las /
NK065(cu)001:11147: zhi ba'i dus su mi bskyod pa dang por smos shing gtsor byas la /
NK065(cu)001:11148: khro bo'i dus su ni gzugs kyi phung po rnam
NK065(cu)001:11149: par dag pa bud+d+ha he ru ka dang por byung
NK065(cu)001:11150: zhing gtso bor smos pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11151: de ni rgyud dkrugs pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:11152: dbyings phyug ma gtso bo la 'khril ba'i gnas skabs na de nyid mngon par 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:11153: 'di ni rdo rje khrag 'thung nyid la ci nas kyang don gyis shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:11155: 'dir yang rnam par shes pa'i rang bzhin zhe sdang
NK065(cu)001:11156: rnam par dag pa'i ngo bo mi bskyod pa rdo
NK065(cu)001:11157: rje khrag 'thung du mngon par 'du mdzad pa de
NK065(cu)001:11161: 'bar ba chen po'i khrag 'thung sku smug nag /
NK065(cu)001:11163: ma h+aa dz+wa lan+tam ru d+hi ra p+aa n+aa ma n+ai la krish+n+aa k+aa yam /
NK065(cu)001:11164: zhes mthing nag gi skad dod yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:11165: der rdo rje khrag 'thung gi sngags kyang thog mar byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11168: sku ni ma bco sa de bzhin nyid //
NK065(cu)001:11169: thugs ni mi 'gyur rdo rje'i rigs //
NK065(cu)001:11170: yon tan kun 'byung rin chen rigs //
NK065(cu)001:11171: gsung ni chags med pad+ma'i rigs //
NK065(cu)001:11172: don grub spyod pa las kyi rigs //
NK065(cu)001:11175: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo mi bskyod pa thugs rdo rje rigs dang chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK065(cu)001:11176: de bzhin du rnam snang sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs me long lta bu /
NK065(cu)001:11177: rin 'byung yon tan rin po che'i rigs mnyam nyid /
NK065(cu)001:11178: snang mtha' gsung pad+ma'i rigs sor rtog /
NK065(cu)001:11179: don grub phrin las las kyi rigs bya grub ye shes so //
NK065(cu)001:11180: de dag kun kyang zhes sogs kyis rigs kyi mtshan mar gyur pa'i kha dog rnams bstan te /
NK065(cu)001:11181: chos nyid 'gyur ba med pa dang 1 /
NK065(cu)001:11182: nyes skyon gyis ma gos pa dang 2 /
NK065(cu)001:11183: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa dang 3 /
NK065(cu)001:11184: gdul bya'i don la chags pa dang 4 /
NK065(cu)001:11185: las sna tshogs lhun gyis 5grub pa'i rtags su /
NK065(cu)001:11187: chos dbyings ye shes dang rdo rje'i rigs mthing ga1 /
NK065(cu)001:11188: me long lta bu dang bde gshegs rigs dkar po2 /
NK065(cu)001:11189: mnyam nyid dang rin chen rigs ser po3 /
NK065(cu)001:11190: sor rtog dang pad rigs dmar po 4 /
NK065(cu)001:11191: bya grub dang las rigs ljang gu ste5 /
NK065(cu)001:11193: ma mthong rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK065(cu)001:11194: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11195: dkar dang dmar dang ser ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:11196: ljang gu la sogs nag por bstan //
NK065(cu)001:11197: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:11198: gnyis pa rigs kyi yum lnga'i mtshan la /
NK065(cu)001:11203: de la btsun mo'i sgra ni /
NK065(cu)001:11204: skyed par byed pa'i rgyu dang /
NK065(cu)001:11205: spyad bya'i yul du gyur pa gnyis la 'jug ste /
NK065(cu)001:11206: rtog pa'i dus su 'byung ba lngas phung po lnga bskyed cing /
NK065(cu)001:11207: lha'i skabs su rigs kyi yab lngas spyad par bya ba'i yul yin pa'i phyir ram /
NK065(cu)001:11209: yum gyi ngo bo dbyings dang /
NK065(cu)001:11210: yab kyi ngo bo ye shes te /
NK065(cu)001:11211: dbyings kyis ye shes bskyed pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11212: dbyings ye shes kyi yul du gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11213: dam pa'i sgra ni rang bzhin rtog pa las khyad par du byas pa'i 'phags chos so //
NK065(cu)001:11216: dbyings kyi sgra ni mi zad pa la bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:11218: don la sras kyi 'byung khungs dang bde ba'i ye shes bskyed pa'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir ram /
NK065(cu)001:11219: yum rnams dbyings kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir yang de skad du grags so //
NK065(cu)001:11220: bye brag ni rtog pa'i mtshan te /
NK065(cu)001:11221: de la snang ba zhes pa ni nam mkhas go
NK065(cu)001:11222: ma phye na dngos po thams cad snang mi nus
NK065(cu)001:11224: chos kyi khams rnam shes kyi yul yin pa'i phyir thugs rdo rje'i rigs kyi yum dbyings phyug ma'o //
NK065(cu)001:11225: sra ba ni sra brtan mkhrang ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi sa'i khams te /
NK065(cu)001:11226: brtan zhing rten du gyur pa'i phyir sku'i rigs kyi yum sangs rgyas spyan ma'o //
NK065(cu)001:11227: mnyen pa ni gsher sdud brlan pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi chu'i khams te /
NK065(cu)001:11228: rgyud brlan cing yon tan sdud pa rin po che rigs kyi yum m+aa ma k+ai'o //
NK065(cu)001:11229: dro ba ni tsha zhing sreg pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi me'i khams te /
NK065(cu)001:11230: mtshan 'dzin gyi spu ris gsal ba dang shes rab
NK065(cu)001:11231: kyi mes dag par byed pa'i bdag nyid pad+ma rigs
NK065(cu)001:11233: bskyod pa ni yang zhing g.yo ba'i mtshan nyid can gyi rlung gi khams te /
NK065(cu)001:11234: bskyod 'degs kyi bya ba byed pa ltar thogs pa
NK065(cu)001:11235: med pa'i las can las rigs kyi yum sgrol ma'o
NK065(cu)001:11238: sa chu spyan dang m+aa ma k+ai //
NK065(cu)001:11239: me rlung gos dkar sgron ma ste //
NK065(cu)001:11240: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK065(cu)001:11242: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa rnams de lta bu'i
NK065(cu)001:11243: btsun mo'i tshogs dang thabs shes gnyis su med pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11244: tshul gyis kun tu khyab par bzhugs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11246: nam mkha'i dbyings ni mtha' klas par //
NK065(cu)001:11247: ston pa'i mdzad spyod rol mo yis //
NK065(cu)001:11248: til gyi gang bu bzhin du khyab //
NK065(cu)001:11249: ston pa'i khyad par yin par grags //
NK065(cu)001:11251: gnyis pa gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:11252: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang ste /
NK065(cu)001:11254: gnas kyi rang bzhin de bzhin nyid //
NK065(cu)001:11255: ngo bo 'og min gzhal yas khang //
NK065(cu)001:11262: dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min dang lnga /
NK065(cu)001:11265: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rten yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:11266: rnam rtog dang mtshan ma gang gi'ang 'og tu ma gyur pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:11268: gzung 'dzin bral ba'i ye shes ni //
NK065(cu)001:11269: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK065(cu)001:11272: de rtogs pa rang rig pa'i ye shes ni gnyis 'dzin gyi 'og tu ma gyur pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:11273: yang na longs sku'i zhing dang cha mthun par lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11275: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ji lta bar //
NK065(cu)001:11278: de la btags pa'i 'og min zhes kyang zer ro //
NK065(cu)001:11281: ston pa gsang ba'i sku'i gnas dang mtshan ma'i rtog
NK065(cu)001:11282: pa rang rgyud pa'i 'og tu ma gyur pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:11283: / de ltar yang rgyas pa las /
NK065(cu)001:11284: nub phyogs 'og min gnas mchog tu //
NK065(cu)001:11285: ma chags pad+ma'i gdan bting nas //
NK065(cu)001:11286: dus gsum rgyal ba bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK065(cu)001:11289: rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:11291: smos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa yum lnga'i mkha' klong gi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11292: 'dir gzhal yas spyi'i khyad par sogs kyang bshad du rung zhing /
NK065(cu)001:11293: bcom ldan 'das zhes pa'i mtshan las kyang grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:11294: b+ha ga w+aan gyi sgra las /
NK065(cu)001:11295: b+ha ga ni yum gyi mkha' dbyings //
NK065(cu)001:11296: ldan pa ni de dang gnyis su med par bzhugs pa'i don no //
NK065(cu)001:11298: gzugs khams gnas rigs bcu bdun gyi ya tha gtsang rigs kyi lha'i gnas dang po de'o //
NK065(cu)001:11299: de la der grags pas na grags pa'i 'og min zhes bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:11300: gzugs can gyi gnas gzhan gyi 'og tu ma gyur pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11302: yod min med min gyi skye mched la grangs pa'i 'og min zhes btags te /
NK065(cu)001:11303: srid pa'i rtse mor gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11305: 'dir 'chad pa'i gnas longs sku'i bzhugs gnas 'og min chen po ste /
NK065(cu)001:11307: gtsang ba'i rigs dang rab spangs pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:11308: 'og min chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK065(cu)001:11309: rigs bdag phyag rgya lhun grub sku //
NK065(cu)001:11310: gcig dang du ma rnams spangs pa //
NK065(cu)001:11311: sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs te //
NK065(cu)001:11312: 'dod nas theg chen mdzod nyid phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11313: sgrib pa mtha' spangs gdul bya la //
NK065(cu)001:11314: skad cig gcig gis snang bar mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:11321: don dbyings dang ye shes dbyer mi phyed pa'i rtags
NK065(cu)001:11322: gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang
NK065(cu)001:11325: a ka nish+tha'i sgra las 'og ma ma yin pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11326: don gdul bya'i blo las 'das shing /
NK065(cu)001:11327: rtags de 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min las nyis 'gyur gyis spags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11330: nyis 'gyur shin tu spags pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:11332: 'dir 'phros don nyis 'gyur 'phags tshul gyi dogs pa bcad pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:11334: 'di nas 'jig rten gnas kyi 'og min la bar thag ji tsam yod pa'i nyis 'gyur /
NK065(cu)001:11335: de nas 'og min chen po'i bar du yod zer
NK065(cu)001:11336: ba sogs pha rol du 'phags par 'dod pa ni
NK065(cu)001:11337: mi rigs te / ma dag pa'i 'jig rten spangs
NK065(cu)001:11338: pa'i pha rol na dag pa'i zhing bsgrub tu med
NK065(cu)001:11339: pa'i phyir des na dmus long gis ma mthong bas
NK065(cu)001:11340: nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor med par mi 'gyur ba ltar
NK065(cu)001:11341: mi rigs te / / ma dag pa'i 'gro ba
NK065(cu)001:11342: la ma dag pa'i zhing du snang ba tsam gyis
NK065(cu)001:11343: mi rigs te / / / de nyid dag pa'i zhing ma yin par bsgrub tu med de /
NK065(cu)001:11345: yang dag shes pa'i rang rig blo med na //
NK065(cu)001:11346: bde gshegs zhing yang ngan song gnas su mthong //
NK065(cu)001:11347: theg mchog mnyam pa'i don nyid rtogs pa na //
NK065(cu)001:11348: ngan song gnas kyang 'og min dga' ldan gnas //
NK065(cu)001:11350: don la sems can gyis gar khyab tu rgyal ba'i
NK065(cu)001:11351: sku dang phrin las kyis khyab pa'i phyir sangs rgyas
NK065(cu)001:11352: kyi zhing la phyogs dang ris su chad pa med
NK065(cu)001:11353: do // de'i phyir dag ma dag gi snang bas phye ba nyid du shes par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:11354: dri ma med par grags pa'i mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:11355: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor gyi dkyil 'khor rnams la
NK065(cu)001:11356: sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di'i rang bzhin bstan par mdzad
NK065(cu)001:11357: pas / thams cad kyis shar phyogs kyi sangs rgyas
NK065(cu)001:11358: rin po che'i rgyan bkod pa'i zhing khams bzhin yongs
NK065(cu)001:11359: su dag par mthong bar gyur pa de'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:11360: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NK065(cu)001:11361: nga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing 'di ni rtag tu 'di 'dra ste /
NK065(cu)001:11362: khyed rnams kyis mi mthong ngo //
NK065(cu)001:11364: de bas na spags lugs la nyis 'gyur zhes brjod pa'ang /
NK065(cu)001:11365: gtsang ma'i 'og min ni rgyu'i byang sems dang po'i bden pa mthong ba'i gnas yin la /
NK065(cu)001:11366: 'og min chen po ni nges don du 'tshang rgya ba'i gnas yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:11367: slob lam dang po nas bden pa mthong ba la
NK065(cu)001:11368: yun ji tsam thogs pa'i nyis 'gyur mi slob pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11369: sa'i bar du dgos pas na de skad ces bya'o
NK065(cu)001:11370: zhes gsungs pa nyid legs par mngon no //
NK065(cu)001:11372: gnas de'i rang bzhin gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11373: de'i rang bzhin ni chos kyi dbyings nyid yin pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11374: phyir mtha' dbus la sogs pa'i spros pa thams cad
NK065(cu)001:11377: mtha' dbus med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK065(cu)001:11378: de ni gnas kyi bla mar 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:11380: de nyid kyi ngang las yon tan gyi khyad par rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11381: gnas kyi ngo bo'i chos rnams dbye bar bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:11387: bcu gcig dag gis dbye bar bya //
NK065(cu)001:11389: dang po la spyi'i 'og gzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:11390: ye shes lnga mtshon pa'i phyir rgya khyon tshad med pa'i 'khor lo ste /
NK065(cu)001:11391: bshad rgyud rol pa chen po las /
NK065(cu)001:11392: 'khor lo chen po'i sa gzhi la //
NK065(cu)001:11393: khang pa gru bzhi rnam par brjid //
NK065(cu)001:11395: nang gi 'og gzhi ni sgo dang khyams sogs nas
NK065(cu)001:11396: lte ba'i bar rdo rje 'greng bu res spags pa
NK065(cu)001:11397: ste / theg pa 'og ma nas 'dir 'phags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11400: ye shes nyid dbyibs dang kha dog tu rang snang bas re ba skong ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11402: phyogs kun tu yongs su ma chad pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11403: chos dbyings mtha' klas par khyab par rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11406: de bzhin gshegs pa'i che ba'i yon tan thams cad
NK065(cu)001:11407: kyis 'dir khyab pa dang mnyam pa dang rgyas pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11408: phyir / de yang rgya cher 'grel las /
NK065(cu)001:11409: mnyam pa'i phyir dang khyab pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11410: rgyas pa'i phyir ni gru bzhir gyur //
NK065(cu)001:11413: gru chad las phyir 'phyar ba'i dbyibs mkhar gyi 'bur thabs lta bu dang /
NK065(cu)001:11414: kha dog rigs bzhi'i mdog can gyi rin po che'i glo 'bur gyis mdzes pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11415: ye shes re re'ang lhag pa'i ye shes bzhi bzhi dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11417: tshad dpag tu med pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11418: dbyibs bum pa zlum po'i rnam pa 'khyil ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:11419: rim pa bzhin chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la
NK065(cu)001:11420: mthar thug pa med cing spros pa dang bral ba'i
NK065(cu)001:11421: phyir / bdun pa rgyan la bdun las /
NK065(cu)001:11423: gzhal yas khang gi lte bar ye shes lnga mtshon
NK065(cu)001:11424: pa'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa'i mtha' chos nyid mtshon
NK065(cu)001:11425: pa'i rdo rje'i ra ba bzlum pos bskor ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:11427: gnyis su med pa'i ye shes kyi rtsal snang ma 'gags pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11428: pany+tsa re kha'i rtsig pa'i steng du /
NK065(cu)001:11429: rin po che'i pha gu dang /
NK065(cu)001:11433: mda' yab la sogs pa'i rgyan dang /
NK065(cu)001:11434: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ma spangs rnam dag rgyan du rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11435: 'dod yon gyi lha mos phyogs kun tu 'khrigs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11437: ye shes rtsig steng seng mgos gtams //
NK065(cu)001:11438: mi 'jigs kha nas mu tig har //
NK065(cu)001:11439: pha gu mdzes pa'i bad dang ldan //
NK065(cu)001:11440: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed mgul 'khor ldan //
NK065(cu)001:11441: gzugs sogs lha mo 'khrigs pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:11442: sna tshogs mchod byed rol mo yis //
NK065(cu)001:11443: bar snang khams kun sprin phung bzhin //
NK065(cu)001:11446: bum pa zlum po'i steng du bre mtshon pa'i phyur bu'i rtser /
NK065(cu)001:11447: pad+ma la gnas pa'i 'khor lo rim pa bcu gsum
NK065(cu)001:11448: gyi steng na rat+na'i gdugs kyis mdzes shing tog dang
NK065(cu)001:11449: ldan pa ste / rdo rje me long las /
NK065(cu)001:11450: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor byas shing //
NK065(cu)001:11451: nyon mongs tshad pa'i gdung ba sel //
NK065(cu)001:11452: thugs rje gdugs kyi 'khor lo bstan //
NK065(cu)001:11453: ma lus gcig tu 'dus pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:11456: rta babs kyi rtser yang gdugs kyi rtsa bar 'khor lo dwags kyis bskyod pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11457: gzhan yang phyogs kun tu rnga yab dang ba dan la sogs pas mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11458: sgo dang rta babs kyi rgyan ni /
NK065(cu)001:11460: gzhal yas de yi sgo bzhi na //
NK065(cu)001:11461: glang seng gnyis kyis mdzes par brgyan //
NK065(cu)001:11462: rta babs rnams kyi 'khor lo la //
NK065(cu)001:11463: gser gyi dril bu 'bar ba dag /
NK065(cu)001:11464: dkon mchog gsum gyi sgra yang sgrogs //
NK065(cu)001:11468: sgo bzhi g.yas g.yon ljon shing dang //
NK065(cu)001:11469: dpag bsam shing zung tsong tsong sbrel //
NK065(cu)001:11470: dril bu g.yer kha theg chen sgrog /
NK065(cu)001:11471: bkra shis bya snyan sgra sgrogs ldan //
NK065(cu)001:11472: yid bzhin rin chen brgyad bskor ba //
NK065(cu)001:11473: rin chen phung po bzhi gnyis ldan //
NK065(cu)001:11475: ngo bo nyid kyi rgyan ni /
NK065(cu)001:11476: bden bzhi mtshon pa'i gru chad dang /
NK065(cu)001:11477: bden pa dbyer med mtshon pa'i bar khyams la sogs pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11478: gru chad bzhis brgyan sogs gsungs pa ltar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11480: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK065(cu)001:11482: 'di la bdag po nyid rgyan du bzhag pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11483: de'i sprul pa'i 'phro 'du la rgyan du bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11484: bdag po la yod pa'i yo byad rgyan du bshad pa gsum las /
NK065(cu)001:11485: rog t+aika pa dang po 'thad gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:11486: mang mkhar ba phyi ma ltar bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:11487: khyim bdag gi longs spyod kyis khang pa mdzes pa bzhin no gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:11488: gong ma phal cher spar khab kyi rjes su 'brangs te bar ma ltar bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:11490: rnam thar bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo nas byang
NK065(cu)001:11491: chub chen por lhun gyis 'jug pa'i phyir sgo bzhi
NK065(cu)001:11494: de phyir ye shes sgo bzhir shar //
NK065(cu)001:11496: de'ang thang sgo lta bu ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:11497: sgo khyud kyi zlas drangs pa'i 'gram logs dang /
NK065(cu)001:11498: ya phubs rdo rje'i d+r+wa mig can no //
NK065(cu)001:11501: lam brgyad rim par bgrod pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:11502: 'bras bu'i yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK065(cu)001:11503: rta babs rgyu 'bras bcu drug bstan //
NK065(cu)001:11506: mtshon sgo rnam thar bzhi'i sgo nas mtshon bya mi gnas pa'i ye shes la 'jug pa de yang /
NK065(cu)001:11507: thun mong rnam thar gyi theg pa brgyad la sbyangs par rtogs pa'i rtags su /
NK065(cu)001:11508: sgo phubs kyi phyi nang gnyis su them skas bzhi
NK065(cu)001:11509: bzhi ste brgyad ni babs zhon gyi rta babs te
NK065(cu)001:11511: der 'gro lam stegs brgyad dang ldan //
NK065(cu)001:11512: rta babs brgyad du gyur pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:11515: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub dang //
NK065(cu)001:11516: bya ba'i rgyud dang gnyis ka'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:11517: rnal 'byor bskyed dang rdzogs pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:11518: rnam thar brgyad phyir rta babs brgyad //
NK065(cu)001:11521: theg pa brgyad kyi grub mtha'i yon tan brgyad rdzogs pa'i rtags su /
NK065(cu)001:11522: sgo logs kyi phyi zur bzhi nas ka bas btegs
NK065(cu)001:11523: pa'i sgo khang gi steng du rgyan gyi rta babs
NK065(cu)001:11524: brgyad de / sgyu 'phrul bye brag bstan pa las /
NK065(cu)001:11525: de yi grub pa'i mtha' rdzogs pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:11526: yon tan brgyad phyir rta rkang dang //
NK065(cu)001:11527: chu skyes sgro mdang za ra tshags //
NK065(cu)001:11529: khyung mgo mdzes pas rim par 'khrigs //
NK065(cu)001:11531: de la sgo khang dang sgo'i bsil khang gi mun pa sel byed glang rgyab logs pas spras pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11533: rang byung ye shes la phyi gzungs ba'i yul dang /
NK065(cu)001:11534: nang 'dzin ba'i sems gnyis su med pas shes bya'i
NK065(cu)001:11535: dkyil 'khor du kun kyang rang byung ye shes su
NK065(cu)001:11536: gsal ba las gzhan ma dmigs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11537: chos kyi dbyings rdo rje kun tu bzang mo'i b+ha
NK065(cu)001:11538: ga nyid du 'dus pas na nang zhes bya ste
NK065(cu)001:11540: gnas mchog mtshan nyid brjod pa ni //
NK065(cu)001:11541: gzhal yas phyi nang chos dbyings nang //
NK065(cu)001:11542: b+ha ga nyid du bsdus pas na //
NK065(cu)001:11543: kun tu nang zhes brjod pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:11545: de ltar na chos kyi dbyings de'i ngang las /
NK065(cu)001:11546: ye shes kyi 'phrul bar rang snang ba'i gzhal yas khang rgyan dang bcas pa thams cad kyang /
NK065(cu)001:11547: shel gyi sbu gur rin po che sna tshogs bcug
NK065(cu)001:11548: pa ltar mi bsgrib par gsal ba'i rang bzhin can
NK065(cu)001:11549: no // bcu gcig pa gdan la /
NK065(cu)001:11551: sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i yon tan gyi che bas nyes tshogs bcom pa'i gdan no //
NK065(cu)001:11553: sngar gyi 'og gzhi'i rgyan de nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:11555: rang byung gi ye shes rtogs pa'i rig pa la
NK065(cu)001:11556: 'bras bu'i chos mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs lhun gyis
NK065(cu)001:11557: grub pas / yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK065(cu)001:11558: su bstan cing nges par byas pa'i rtags su seng
NK065(cu)001:11559: ge la sogs pa sems can lnga'i gdan byung ba
NK065(cu)001:11560: ni yon tan rtags kyi gdan khri ste /
NK065(cu)001:11561: dbang bskur rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:11562: thugs ni mi 'jigs bzhi yis bdud bzhi 'joms //
NK065(cu)001:11563: de grub rtags su seng ge'i khri la bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:11564: sku ni stobs bcus mi dge bcu rnams 'dul //
NK065(cu)001:11565: de grub rtags su glang chen khri la bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:11566: yon tan rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis chags med sgrol //
NK065(cu)001:11567: de grub rtag su rta mchog khri la bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:11568: gsung gi dbang bcu mthar phyin rgyal po'i gsung //
NK065(cu)001:11569: de grub rtags su rma bya'i khri la bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:11570: las ni phrin las bzhi yis thogs med sgrol //
NK065(cu)001:11571: de grub rtags su shang shang khri la bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:11573: de la mi 'jigs pa bzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:11575: mngon sangs rgyas dang zag pa zad //
NK065(cu)001:11576: bar mi chod dang nges par 'byung //
NK065(cu)001:11579: gnas dang gnas min yang dag mkhyen //
NK065(cu)001:11580: dus gsum las 'bras rnam smin mkhyen //
NK065(cu)001:11581: khams rnams sna tshogs mkhyen pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:11582: pha rol mos pa mkhyen pa'i stobs //
NK065(cu)001:11583: dbang po mchog dang mchog min mkhyen //
NK065(cu)001:11584: kun tu 'gro lam mkhyen pa'i stobs //
NK065(cu)001:11585: bsam gtan thar dang nyon mongs mkhyen //
NK065(cu)001:11586: sngon gyi gnas mkhyen stobs dang ni //
NK065(cu)001:11588: zag pa zad med sems grol mkhyen //
NK065(cu)001:11589: de bcu stobs su gyur pas na //
NK065(cu)001:11590: 'bras bu mngon shes drug yin no //
NK065(cu)001:11593: dpyod pa'i ting 'dzin spong ba yi //
NK065(cu)001:11594: 'du shes rnams te rkang pa bzhis //
NK065(cu)001:11595: ye shes bzhi grub 'bras bu ste //
NK065(cu)001:11596: chos dbyings ye shes kun la khyab //
NK065(cu)001:11598: yo byad skye ba tshe la dbang //
NK065(cu)001:11599: ye shes chos dang sems dang las //
NK065(cu)001:11600: rdzu 'phrul smon lam chos rnams kyis //
NK065(cu)001:11601: khams gsum kun gyi dbang phyug rgyal //
NK065(cu)001:11603: zhi rgyas dbang drag las rnams kyis //
NK065(cu)001:11604: thogs med las rnams lhun gyis grub //
NK065(cu)001:11605: ci la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK065(cu)001:11607: 'o na sems can gyi gdan de dag thugs rig pa rang snang du 'dod pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:11609: byang chub sems dpa' smon lam dbang //
NK065(cu)001:11610: thos pa'i rgya mtsho bsag pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11611: lus ni seng ge'i gdan du phul //
NK065(cu)001:11614: seng ge la sogs pa smon lam gyi dbang gis byang chub sems dpa' gcig kyang brgyad brgyad do //
NK065(cu)001:11615: zhes smon lam gus pa'i gdan du gsungs pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11616: rgyud tha dad pa la ltos nas 'gal yang /
NK065(cu)001:11617: 'dir ye shes rang snang dang smon lam gus pa
NK065(cu)001:11618: gnyis rgyud tha dad du ma grub pas mi 'gal
NK065(cu)001:11619: te / dper na dge bshes kyi chibs de rang gi bsod nams kyis grub pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11620: gzhan gyis dad pas phul ba gnyis rta gcig gi steng du mtshungs pa bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:11621: rgyal ba la mi 'jigs pa bzhi sogs lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su snang ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:11622: byang sems smon lam gyi dbang gis rang dbang can
NK065(cu)001:11623: du seng ge la sogs par sprul te gus pas
NK065(cu)001:11624: lus gdan du phul nas rna bas chos nyan pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11626: gzhan yang gsang ba'i theg pa 'di ni /
NK065(cu)001:11627: 'og ma la nyam mi nga zhing mi 'jigs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11628: 'og mar mi tshud pa'i don 'dir shong zhing chud pa'i stobs dang /
NK065(cu)001:11629: gdul bya rnams smin grol gyi sar myur du bkri ba'i rdzu 'khrul dang /
NK065(cu)001:11630: las nyon ma spangs par dbang du byed pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11631: chags thogs med pa'i phrin las kyis gdul bya 'dul ba'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:11632: rim bzhin seng ge la sogs pa dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11633: de'ang theg pa brgyad la bgrod nas 'bras bu'i yon
NK065(cu)001:11634: tan thugs su chud pa'i rtags su seng ge la
NK065(cu)001:11635: sogs pa re re'ang brgyad brgyad mjug ma nang du
NK065(cu)001:11636: bsnol nas rin po che'i khri rkang 'degs pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:11637: / sa'i khyad par bgrod pa'i gdan zhes grags so //
NK065(cu)001:11639: rgyal ba'i thugs rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal zhing thabs shes dbyer med pa'i brdar nyi zla'i gdan dang /
NK065(cu)001:11640: pad+ma ni 'dam las skyes kyang nyes skyon gyis ma
NK065(cu)001:11641: gos pa ltar mtha'i skyon gyis gos pa med pa
NK065(cu)001:11642: pad+ma'i gdan dang / yid bzhin gyi re ba skong ba'i rtags su rin po che'i gdan dang /
NK065(cu)001:11643: de ka bas bteg pa'i mdzod mig bdun ldan ni dkor bdun lhun gyis grub pa'i barda'o //
NK065(cu)001:11645: skyes bu lnga la lnga brtseg ste //
NK065(cu)001:11646: sems dpa' la ni sum brtseg go //
NK065(cu)001:11647: nyi rkyang khro la pad rkyang thub //
NK065(cu)001:11648: kun bzang yab yum bzhi brtseg go //
NK065(cu)001:11649: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsungs te 'od rim
NK065(cu)001:11650: dang 'grel ba mun sel gyi bzhed par mngon no
NK065(cu)001:11652: kun bzang yab yum dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i tshe sum brtseg dang chos 'chad pa'i tshe lnga brtseg /
NK065(cu)001:11653: sgo ba la pad nyi brtseg ma ste gzhan 'dra'o //
NK065(cu)001:11654: gdan brtsegs kyi zla ba steng du 'ong ba gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11656: gtso bo ni shes rab la spyod pa'i phyir dang
NK065(cu)001:11657: nang gi chu skyes kyi lte ba'i nyi ma la
NK065(cu)001:11658: zla ba brten pa'i phyir ri bong steng na gnas
NK065(cu)001:11659: so // zhes pa ni gsang ba ltar bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11660: gzhan du grol lam ltar na gtso bor thabs snang
NK065(cu)001:11661: ba 'gags pa med pa mtshon pa'i phyir zla ba
NK065(cu)001:11662: steng dang / nang ltar na lte ba'i a thung gi steng du spyi bo'i ham yig gam /
NK065(cu)001:11663: snying ga'i srog mi shigs pa'i thig le gnas pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11664: de dag gis gnas rgyas par bstan te /
NK065(cu)001:11666: dga' bde yang dag rdzogs pa'i gnas //
NK065(cu)001:11667: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:11668: ma lus 'dus pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK065(cu)001:11669: bdag po rgyan dang bcas pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:11671: nyis 'gyur shin tu spags pa na //
NK065(cu)001:11672: ngo bo mtha' gsum las 'das pa //
NK065(cu)001:11673: ma spangs rgyan rdzogs gzhal yas khang //
NK065(cu)001:11674: yon tan lnga yi bdag po ste //
NK065(cu)001:11675: gru bzhi spyi bo 'khyil snang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:11677: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la /
NK065(cu)001:11679: zhar la de dag gi tshad bshad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11680: dang po la'ang lhan cig pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11683: lhan cig 'khor dang go phye ba //
NK065(cu)001:11686: rang bzhin gnyis su med pa'i //
NK065(cu)001:11687: rig pa khyad par can gyi /
NK065(cu)001:11688: dad pas gtam nyan pa'i 'khor ro //
NK065(cu)001:11691: nyid las mi gzhan rigs lnga dang //
NK065(cu)001:11692: zhes pas 'chad pa'i skyes bu lnga ste bshad grub bo //
NK065(cu)001:11694: ston pa'i thugs rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi khyad
NK065(cu)001:11695: par las rang snang ba'i phyir rig pa khyad par
NK065(cu)001:11698: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK065(cu)001:11699: rang snang rgyal ba sems sogs dang //
NK065(cu)001:11706: bye brag gi mtshan gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:11708: mig shes la sogs pa'i rtog tshogs rnams ye nas chos nyid byang chub kyi sems yin pa las /
NK065(cu)001:11709: yin pa ltar mngon du gyur pa'i 'bras bu ni byang chub chen po'o //
NK065(cu)001:11710: de ltar rgyu 'bras ltar snang yang don dam par
NK065(cu)001:11711: lha rtog dbyer mi phyed pas na rdo rje ste
NK065(cu)001:11713: 'khor gyi bkod pa ji snyed pa //
NK065(cu)001:11714: khams dang skye mched yin par grags //
NK065(cu)001:11715: rnam shes yul dang dbang po dang //
NK065(cu)001:11716: dus dang phyin ci ma log rnams //
NK065(cu)001:11717: byang chub chen po'i rang bzhin du //
NK065(cu)001:11718: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor yin //
NK065(cu)001:11720: yum gyi mtshan btsun mo ni sngar ltar las /
NK065(cu)001:11721: khyad par yul bzhis rnam shes bzhi bskyed pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11722: dus bzhis go phye nas dbang po bzhi bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11725: mthong ba la sogs par smos pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:11726: mig rna ba sna lce'i rnam shes bzhi ste /
NK065(cu)001:11727: mig dbang la brten nas mig shes kyis yul gzugs mthong ba la sogs pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11732: spyan ras gzigs dbang phyug rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:11733: de rnams la thugs kyi sems dpar grags te /
NK065(cu)001:11735: ka ni spyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK065(cu)001:11738: rnam shes bzhi po ni rig pa kho na'i phyir thugs te //
NK065(cu)001:11740: mthong bar bya ba sogs ni /
NK065(cu)001:11741: yul gzugs sgra dri ro bzhi ste /
NK065(cu)001:11742: mig shes sogs kyis mthong bya la sogs pa'i yul yin pa'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11747: n+airti ma rnams dang rim par sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11748: de rnams la sku'i sems mar grags te /
NK065(cu)001:11749: yul bzhis rnam par shes pa'i rten byed pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11751: tsa ni spyan gyi sku yi mchog /
NK065(cu)001:11754: rnam shes bzhi yis dmigs pa'i yul //
NK065(cu)001:11755: mthong bar bya ba la sogs pa //
NK065(cu)001:11756: dmigs par bya phyir sku yi mchog /
NK065(cu)001:11759: rtog pa'i go rim kho na ltar sbyar na yul yul can ma 'khrul na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:11760: lha yab yum sbyor ba'i rna ba'i yul ro dang /
NK065(cu)001:11761: lce'i yul sgrar byung bas sbyar tshul nor te /
NK065(cu)001:11763: spyan ras gzigs kyi yum g+airti ma dang /
NK065(cu)001:11764: phyag rdor gyi yum n+airti mar byung bas so //
NK065(cu)001:11766: yul yul can gyi dbang du byas na /
NK065(cu)001:11768: 'dir rigs kyi dbang du byas pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11770: nyi 'od seng ge'i rgya cher 'grel las /
NK065(cu)001:11771: rgyud 'dir ni rigs kho na gtso bor byas te /
NK065(cu)001:11772: mnyam par bya ba sgra'i lha mo rna ba'i yul yin kyang /
NK065(cu)001:11773: rigs kyi dus su gsung gi rigs yin pas /
NK065(cu)001:11774: 'jig rten dbang phyug gi yum du shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:11775: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11777: rnam shes bzhis yul bzhi mthong ba'i bdag rkyen dbang po bzhis byed pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11778: mthong byed la sogs par smos so de'ang /
NK065(cu)001:11779: mig rna ba sna lce'i dbang po bzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:11785: de dag la gsung gi sems dpa' zhes kyang grags te /
NK065(cu)001:11786: dbang pos yul dang shes pa gnyis phyi nang gi brda' sbyor byed pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11787: ba ni spyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK065(cu)001:11789: yum ni dus bzhi'i lha mo ste /
NK065(cu)001:11793: ma byon pa ste 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus rnams rim pa bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:11799: 'das pa dang ni dpyid kyi dus te d+h+au pe ma /
NK065(cu)001:11800: da ltar ba ni dbyar gyi dus te push+pe ma //
NK065(cu)001:11801: ma 'ongs pa ni ston gyi dus te +aa lo ke //
NK065(cu)001:11802: ma nges pa ni dgun gyi dus te gan+d+he'o //
NK065(cu)001:11804: 'di'i skabs su kha cig na re /
NK065(cu)001:11805: 'dir dus bzhi smos pas dus log ste /
NK065(cu)001:11806: sde snod gzhan du dus gsum ma bshad pa'i phyir zer ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:11807: rang gi rang bzhin gsal bar sgrog pa'i smre sngags te /
NK065(cu)001:11809: chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhi dang ldan la sogs pa'i dus bzhi bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11810: dkon mchog brtsegs pa las kyang /
NK065(cu)001:11812: sems dang chos kyi de bzhin nyid ni gang nas kyang ma 'ongs /
NK065(cu)001:11814: gar yang mi gnas pas na ma nges pa ste bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus so //
NK065(cu)001:11815: zhes dus gsum dang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus te bzhir gsungs pa sogs kyang /
NK065(cu)001:11816: dus log par thal ba bzlog tu med do //
NK065(cu)001:11818: khyed cag dus gsum kho nar 'dod pa de tshod du /
NK065(cu)001:11820: dus gsum du nges par 'dod pa'ang mi rigs par thal /
NK065(cu)001:11821: dus nyid na gnyis kho nar nges pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:11823: da ltar ma yin pa gnyis su nges pa'i phyir byas na cis 'gog /
NK065(cu)001:11825: da ltar ma yin pa las 'das pa dang ma
NK065(cu)001:11826: 'ongs pa gnyis su phye bas gsum mo zhe na
NK065(cu)001:11827: / de 'dra dus bzhi la'ang mtshungs te /
NK065(cu)001:11828: da ltar ma yin pa las /
NK065(cu)001:11829: 'das ma 'ongs ma nges pa gsum du phye ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11830: des na lha rtog sbyar ba'i dbang du 'dir dus bzhir grangs dang go rim nges pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11832: dus ring ba dper byas na /
NK065(cu)001:11833: bskal pa gcig la chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhir grangs nges /
NK065(cu)001:11834: dus thung ba dper byas na /
NK065(cu)001:11835: lo gcig la dbyar dgun ston dpyid bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:11836: nyin zhag re la thun chen bzhi la sogs par grangs nges pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11838: da lta bskal pa gnas pa'i dus la dper mtshon na /
NK065(cu)001:11839: gnas pa'i dus 'di ni rgyu spyad cing 'bras bu ma spyad pa'i phyir da ltar ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:11840: chags pa ni rgyu 'bras gnyis ka spyad zin pa'i phyir 'das pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11841: 'jig pa ni rgyu 'bras tshogs la ma sdud pa'i phyir ma 'ongs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11842: stongs pa ni rgyu 'bras yod la ma tshogs pa'i
NK065(cu)001:11843: phyir 'das ma 'ongs gang du'ang ma nges pa'i dus
NK065(cu)001:11844: so // de ltar yang rngam glog las /
NK065(cu)001:11845: rgyu 'bras nges pa ma tshogs pa //
NK065(cu)001:11846: 'byung bar ma nges dus zhes grags //
NK065(cu)001:11849: bskal pa sngar stongs pa ni 'das pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11850: phyis stongs par 'gyur ba ni ma 'ongs pa'i phyir dus gsum du nges so zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11851: stongs pa'i dus de nyid gzhir byas pa la 'das
NK065(cu)001:11852: ma 'ongs gang rung gcig tu kha tshon ma chod
NK065(cu)001:11853: pas ma nges pa'i dus su ci'i phyir mi 'gyur
NK065(cu)001:11854: / rgyu mtshan de'i phyir dus bzhir grangs dang go rim nges pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:11856: ma nges pa'i dus ni mnyam pa nyid kyi dus te /
NK065(cu)001:11858: la ni stong pa bdag pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11860: ngo bo nyid 'di 'dra bstan du med pa /
NK065(cu)001:11861: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir zer mi rigs te /
NK065(cu)001:11862: 'grel pa'i dgongs pa ni dus gsum gang rung gi
NK065(cu)001:11863: ngo bo 'di 'drar bstan par byas med pa'i don
NK065(cu)001:11864: te / gzhan du na mnyam pa nyid rtog pa
NK065(cu)001:11865: ma yin pa'i phyir rtog tshogs ma tshang ba'i skyon
NK065(cu)001:11866: te / gnas so // de lta na'ang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i dus ma 'dus so zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:11868: de ni don dam 'dus ma byas kyi dus yin
NK065(cu)001:11869: pa'i phyir rtog pa bshad pa'i skabs 'dir ma smos
NK065(cu)001:11870: te / rtog pa ni kun rdzob 'dus byas kyi dus bzhir dmigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11871: gnyis pa la'ang spyi bye brag gnyis kyi /
NK065(cu)001:11874: zhes pa la phyi nang gnyis las /
NK065(cu)001:11875: phyi lus kyi chos bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK065(cu)001:11876: rtog pa'i rang bzhin mngon du gyur pa'i khro bo
NK065(cu)001:11877: bzhi'i sku gsung thugs kyi mdzad pas bdud dang log
NK065(cu)001:11879: nang gsang ba'i khams bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK065(cu)001:11880: 'og sgo gsang ba'i khams gsum 'dus pa'i bde ba'i
NK065(cu)001:11881: rtog pa lha'am bde bar 'dzin pa'i zhen pa gnyis
NK065(cu)001:11884: nga ni thugs kyang 'jig par byed //
NK065(cu)001:11886: oo ni thams cad zhig pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:11888: de'i phyir 'joms pa la thogs pa med pas na rdo rje dang /
NK065(cu)001:11889: des 'joms pa'i phrin las gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa'i phyir chen po'o //
NK065(cu)001:11890: de lta bu 'joms byed kyi gnyen po de'ang /
NK065(cu)001:11891: dper na dkar po 'joms pa de dkar po min pa gcig gis bskyed pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:11892: rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi ma yin pa'i chos nyid
NK065(cu)001:11893: yum gyi ngo bo des bskyed pa'i phyir btsun mo
NK065(cu)001:11896: phyin ci log gi rtog pa bzhi ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:11897: des lus kyi rtog pa bzhi dngos su mi bskyed kyang brgyud nas bskyed ces gsung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:11899: phyi ltar lus kyi 'dus te reg pa'i tshor ba bskyed pa la /
NK065(cu)001:11902: de gnyis 'phrad pa'i rig shes sam /
NK065(cu)001:11904: gsang ba'i yul dbang rnam shes gsum 'dus kyi reg pa bskyed pa la /
NK065(cu)001:11905: reg byed gsang dbang thabs kyi rdo rje /
NK065(cu)001:11906: reg bya gsang yum shes rab kyi pad+ma /
NK065(cu)001:11907: gsang ba'i reg shes dga' ba nyams su myong ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:11908: phyi nang gi rtog pa gnyis ka rim pa bzhin /
NK065(cu)001:11909: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:11912: gshin rje gshed rnams dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11913: rtag par ma yin pa sogs yum bzhi'i rtog pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:11914: phung po mi rtag par 'dzin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11915: sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin ngar 'dzin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:11917: stong par 'dzin pa bzhi go rim ji lta bar khro mo lcags kyu la sogs dang sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:11919: rtag par 'dzin pa'i rtog pa nyid rang ga mar snang ba ltar ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:11920: de ma spangs par khro mo lcags kyu ma'i rang bzhin du dag pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11922: rtag chad bdag mtshan du 'dzin pa'i phyin ci log
NK065(cu)001:11923: gi rtog pa bzhir slob dpon kha cig bzhed pa'ang
NK065(cu)001:11926: rtag sogs mtshan ma las bskyed phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11927: btsun mo zhes su bstan pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:11929: glang po che rab 'bog las kyang //
NK065(cu)001:11930: don dam par sems can rtag par blta ba gnas su dag pa badz+ra ang+ku sha ste /
NK065(cu)001:11931: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:11934: dad pas nyan pa'i lha chen rnams //
NK065(cu)001:11935: zhes pas phyi'i khor yug la bzhugs pa'i 'jig rten gyi lha chen po rnams te /
NK065(cu)001:11937: thams cad la ni dbang bsgyur phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11938: 'jig rten lha chen rnams kyis bskor //
NK065(cu)001:11940: 'khor ba'i chos rnams kyang bdag nyid du rang snang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11941: phyi rol du ma h+aa de ba la sogs pa'i lha chen po rnams kyis bskor ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:11942: rang rang gi mchod yon dang rgyan dang ldan par 'khod pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11944: gnyis pa go phye ba'i 'khor ni /
NK065(cu)001:11945: thun mong 'gro ba 'dul ba'i sprul sku thub pa drug dang /
NK065(cu)001:11946: rjes 'jug chos kyi mig dang ldan pa'i gang zag skal pa can rnams te /
NK065(cu)001:11951: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:11952: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK065(cu)001:11955: rang rig ye shes rgyud don phyir //
NK065(cu)001:11956: rang snang rig pa mngon byas pas //
NK065(cu)001:11957: rig 'dzin mchog de lhun grub pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11958: ting 'dzin nus pa'i mthu med kyang //
NK065(cu)001:11959: sa sbyangs sems dpas bskyed du med //
NK065(cu)001:11960: bde gshegs nyid dang spyod yul gcig /
NK065(cu)001:11961: rig pa'i skyes bur lung thob pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:11965: 'khor gyi tshad ni khyab dang mang //
NK065(cu)001:11966: brjod 'das nam mkha'i mtha' klas gang //
NK065(cu)001:11970: kun tu khyab cing mtha' klas par khyab pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:11971: chos kyi dbyings mtha' yas par khyab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK065(cu)001:11972: dper na til gyi gang bu bzhin du gang nas khyab par bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:11975: grangs brjod kyis mi lang ba'i phyir mang ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:11976: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:11978: de'ang de bzhin gshegs pa dang byang chub sems dpa'
NK065(cu)001:11979: ma lus pa thams cad dpal kun tu bzang po'i
NK065(cu)001:11981: 'gro ba'i phung khams skye mched ji snyed pa thams cad kyang lha'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:11982: rang bzhin gnyis su med par bzhugs te /
NK065(cu)001:11984: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK065(cu)001:11985: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK065(cu)001:11986: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK065(cu)001:11988: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK065(cu)001:11989: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK065(cu)001:11990: thams cad bdag nyid rtag par bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:11993: mtshungs pa bzhi'i sgo nas gnyis su med par bzhugs par bzhed de /
NK065(cu)001:11996: thun mong ma yin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12003: rgyud mas sbyangs rang rgyud pa yin nam /
NK065(cu)001:12004: thugs rang snang sprul pa ba yin /
NK065(cu)001:12006: gang zag gcig gis sbyangs sam tha dad pas sbyangs /
NK065(cu)001:12008: gang zag gcig gi rtog pa la lha gtso 'khor bzang ngan du 'ong ba mi rigs la /
NK065(cu)001:12010: 'dir gang zag gcig gi rtog tshogs las ma smos pa'i phyir mi 'thad do //
NK065(cu)001:12012: gdul bya rang rgyud pa med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12013: 'dul byed sprul pa tshogs pa don med du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12014: lan du bla ma rgya gab gong pa sogs snga rabs pa kha cig na re /
NK065(cu)001:12015: rigs lnga yan chad sprul pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12016: sems dpa' man chad rang rgyud par 'thad de /
NK065(cu)001:12017: rigs lnga'i skabs su spar khab las /
NK065(cu)001:12018: mtshan thun mong pa gnyis ni sngar thal te /
NK065(cu)001:12020: sems dpa' sems ma'i skabs su /
NK065(cu)001:12021: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK065(cu)001:12022: zhes bag la nyal phra ba'i sgrib pa yod par bshad pa'i phyir gsungs na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:12024: rgyud 'di'i mthar thug gi 'bras bu sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yin nam min /
NK065(cu)001:12027: don bsdus gsung rab bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:12028: de bas lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK065(cu)001:12029: de ni rnam dag lam min te //
NK065(cu)001:12030: rang blo bsam pa 'khrul pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:12033: sems dpa' man chad rang rgyud bar 'dod pa'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK065(cu)001:12035: le'u dang por dngos su smos pa'i 'khor 'di rnams thugs rang snang sprul pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:12039: 'khor khyad par du gyur pa la ngam pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12040: rang rig pa nyid gsum gyi khyad par du snang ba la ngam pa gsum mo //
NK065(cu)001:12042: skabs don sngar drangs pa'i gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:12043: zhes pa'i 'grel pa'i lung gis gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12044: de lta na'ang 'dul byed tshogs pa don med du mi 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:12045: go phye ba'i 'khor gyis gsang sngags kyi nges pa
NK065(cu)001:12046: rnyed par bya ba'i phyir ston 'khor du bstan nas
NK065(cu)001:12047: rgyud gsung ba'ang mi 'gal ba'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:12049: rje sgro phug pa khu dbon dang nya ri dri ngas pa'i zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:12050: dkyus gcig la 'khor cha gnyis bzung ba mi 'thad kyang /
NK065(cu)001:12051: spyir cha gnyis yod par nges pas /
NK065(cu)001:12052: 'dir rtog tshogs sbyar ba'i 'khor 'di rnams thugs rang snang sprul pa yin te /
NK065(cu)001:12054: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK065(cu)001:12055: rang snang rgyal ba sems sogs dang //
NK065(cu)001:12057: de dang cha 'dra ba'i rgyud mas sbyangs kyi mthar lam pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12058: theg pa 'og ma'i rgyal ba brjod kyis mi lang ba yod te /
NK065(cu)001:12060: dang po'i sangs rgyas sa rgyal ba //
NK065(cu)001:12061: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK065(cu)001:12062: brjod kyis mi lang tshad med dang //
NK065(cu)001:12063: rnam gnyis tshul du bzhugs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12066: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi'i skabs 'dir byung
NK065(cu)001:12067: ba'i 'khor thams cad yin tshul nas thugs rang snang
NK065(cu)001:12069: snang tshul gyi dbang du sa mtha'i byang chub sems dpa'i tshul du snang ba mi 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:12071: gdul bya las mthar thug pa ni drug pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing du 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:12072: de dag sa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas chen po ste /
NK065(cu)001:12073: lta ba'i sgrib pa 'joms pa'i phyir las kyi rdo rje'o //
NK065(cu)001:12074: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:12076: dngos su smos pa dang cha 'dra'i mas sbyangs kyi
NK065(cu)001:12077: 'khor yod par gnyis ka bzhed pa'i phyir gdul bya
NK065(cu)001:12078: med pa'i skyon 'jug pa'i gnas med do //
NK065(cu)001:12080: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs sam mi bzhugs /
NK065(cu)001:12081: gal te mi bzhugs na rjes 'jug lam pas bsgom pa blos brtags su 'gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:12082: bzhugs na kun tu bzang mo dang thub drug mi 'dug pas gsal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12085: thabs dang shes rab zhes pa'i skabs su kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK065(cu)001:12086: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par kun tu snang ba
NK065(cu)001:12087: zhes pa'i skabs su thub drug yod par shugs kyis
NK065(cu)001:12088: bstan cing / bshad rgyud snying po bkod pa'i gleng gzhir /
NK065(cu)001:12089: dpal kun tu bzang po rang snang ba'i sku dkar
NK065(cu)001:12090: dmar mthing ga'i zhal gsum du snang ba rdo rje
NK065(cu)001:12091: dang / 'khor lo dang rin po che g.yas na 'dzin pa /
NK065(cu)001:12092: pad+ma dang dril bu dang ral gri g.yon na 'dzin pa /
NK065(cu)001:12093: rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis kun tu bzang mo dang 'du 'bral med pa /
NK065(cu)001:12095: gzhan yang thub pa chen po gser thub 'dzin dang /
NK065(cu)001:12096: zhes sogs gnyis ka dngos su smos pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12097: 'o na thub drug 'og min du bzhugs pa ltar na /
NK065(cu)001:12098: gdul bya dang 'dul byed gnas tha dad par 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:12099: thub drug gi gdul bya rigs drug gi sems can yin pa'i phyir zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12101: rigs drug gi gnas dang chos kyi dbyings kyi pho
NK065(cu)001:12102: brang gnyis de nyid dang gzhan du brjod du med
NK065(cu)001:12103: pa ste / dag ma dag gi snang bas phye ba tsam du zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12105: bde mchog gi sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor lo'i dpa'
NK065(cu)001:12106: bo dang dpa' mo rnams yul nyer bzhi na bzhugs
NK065(cu)001:12107: par rtsa rgyud du gsung mod /
NK065(cu)001:12108: des na 'og min gyi gnas su bde mchog lha
NK065(cu)001:12109: drug cu rtsa gnyis ma tshang ngam snyam du rtog
NK065(cu)001:12110: pa dang 'dra ste bzhad gad kyi gnas so //
NK065(cu)001:12111: bzhi pa bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:12112: lam gsang ba'i snying po ste /
NK065(cu)001:12113: mtshon bya rang bzhin gzhi yi rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:12114: ces sogs gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12116: mdor bstan gyi rjes su rgyas bshad 'jug gam mi 'jug /
NK065(cu)001:12117: gnyis pa ltar na mdor bstan don med du thal zhing /
NK065(cu)001:12119: bstan bshad kyi don gnyis nang 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:12120: rgyud 'dir mdor bstan la lnga byung la /
NK065(cu)001:12121: rgyas bshad la ston 'khor gnas gsum las ma byung ba'i phyir zer na /
NK065(cu)001:12124: dogs pa de'i skyon med de /
NK065(cu)001:12125: bstan pa ni ston pa'i thugs la rdzogs shing /
NK065(cu)001:12126: dus ni ston 'khor gnas gsum nam 'dzom pa'i dus te /
NK065(cu)001:12127: ye shes rdzogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK065(cu)001:12128: gnas dang ston pa 'khor tshogs na //
NK065(cu)001:12129: dus dang bstan pa shugs las 'byung //
NK065(cu)001:12131: lha rje zur chung ba'i zhal nas /
NK065(cu)001:12132: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces sogs kyis bstan pa bstan te /
NK065(cu)001:12133: gleng bslang gi gang du byung ba ni rgyud 'khrugs pa'o gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:12134: rje sgro phug pa khu dbon sogs phal cher /
NK065(cu)001:12135: spar khab kyi rjes su 'brangs te gtso bor gleng gzhi bsdus pa'i don du bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:12137: bstan par 'dod pa'i phyogs la gleng ma bslang bar
NK065(cu)001:12138: byung ba'i skyon dang gleng gzhir 'dod pa'i phyogs la
NK065(cu)001:12139: rdo rje la phyung ngo zhes pas gnod do zhe
NK065(cu)001:12140: na / kho bo ni gnyis ka ltar bshad kyang mi 'gal bar sems te /
NK065(cu)001:12142: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus pa'i spyi gzugs
NK065(cu)001:12143: rigs lnga dbyer mi phyed pa'i ston pa nyid kyi
NK065(cu)001:12144: thugs la rgyud don ji ltar shar ba'i don gsang
NK065(cu)001:12145: bdag gis bsdu ba byed pa'i tshe bsdus pas gleng
NK065(cu)001:12146: ma bslang bar byung ba'i skyon med cing /
NK065(cu)001:12147: de nyid gdul bya dbang rab la ltos nas rgyud
NK065(cu)001:12148: don mdor bstan du bshad pa yin pas bstan pa
NK065(cu)001:12151: da ni chos phun sum tshogs pa bstan pa bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:12152: de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang /
NK065(cu)001:12155: rgyud 'di nyid kyi mdo don du //
NK065(cu)001:12157: sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK065(cu)001:12158: rdo rje las ni nges par phyung //
NK065(cu)001:12159: zhes rgyud don mdor bstan du bzhed pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12161: gdul bya dbang 'bring man chad la rgyud don 'og
NK065(cu)001:12162: tu ston pa'i phyir 'di nyid gleng gzhi bsdus pa
NK065(cu)001:12164: 'di nas mar gleng gzhi bsdus pa ston te //
NK065(cu)001:12166: de lta na'ang rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:12167: zhes pas gnod dam snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:12170: dbang rdzogs pa rigs drug pa nyid du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12171: zhes dbang rdzogs nas ston sdud khyad par med cing /
NK065(cu)001:12172: dgongs pa'i rgyud gcig dang tha dad las grol ba'i
NK065(cu)001:12173: phyir sdud pa pos bshad pa la rdo rje las
NK065(cu)001:12174: phyung go zhes ston pa dang skyes bu'i thugs las
NK065(cu)001:12175: phyung bar bstan pa mi 'gal lo //
NK065(cu)001:12177: 'dis dbang rab la rgyud don mdor bstan du ji ltar 'gro zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12178: 'grel chung las dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis dang /
NK065(cu)001:12179: bla ma rnams dkyil 'khor bdun dang theg pa rim
NK065(cu)001:12180: dgur bsdu bar mdzad pas kyang rgyud don du 'gyur
NK065(cu)001:12181: te / dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis sam bdun ni rgyud don dngos dang /
NK065(cu)001:12182: theg pa'ang rgyud don dang ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12184: rgyud kyi brjod bya thams cad rgyud gsum du 'du ba las /
NK065(cu)001:12185: de 'dir bsdus pas na bstan par 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:12186: de bzhin nyid kyi ces pas gzhi rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:12188: rkang pa gnyis pas lam rgyud dang /
NK065(cu)001:12189: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor thugs rje'i ngang //
NK065(cu)001:12191: rkang pa gsum pa man chad kyis 'bras rgyud de /
NK065(cu)001:12192: rgyud gsum mdor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12193: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi brjod bya gzhi lam 'bras gsum dang /
NK065(cu)001:12194: de ston pa thams cad 'di las 'phros pas shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:12195: lnga pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:12197: dus kyi ngo bo mnyam gnas kyang //
NK065(cu)001:12198: skal pa can la dkon pa'i dus //
NK065(cu)001:12201: gdul bya la snang ba'i dus gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:12203: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dus te /
NK065(cu)001:12204: kun rdzob bden ngor dus snga phyi tha dad pa ltar snang yang /
NK065(cu)001:12205: don dam bden pa'i cha nas der ma dmigs la /
NK065(cu)001:12206: dbyer med kyi ngos nas de nyid dang gzhan du
NK065(cu)001:12207: brjod du med pas na mnyam pa nyid kyi dus
NK065(cu)001:12208: zhes bya ste / rgyas pa las /
NK065(cu)001:12210: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK065(cu)001:12211: dus bzhi snga phyi med pa yi //
NK065(cu)001:12212: mnyam pa nyid du lhan ner sbyor //
NK065(cu)001:12215: dus bzhi mnyam pa chos kyi dbyings nyid du //
NK065(cu)001:12216: stug po bkod pa'i rgyan la thim par bzhugs //
NK065(cu)001:12219: rgyud kyi rgyu phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshang bas
NK065(cu)001:12220: gdul bya'i ngo la rgyud don byung ba de yin
NK065(cu)001:12221: te / skal ba can la dkon pa'i dus //
NK065(cu)001:12223: drug pa sdud pa po ni /
NK065(cu)001:12224: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK065(cu)001:12225: kyi gsang ba'i mdzod 'dzin pa'i rgyal sras lag na
NK065(cu)001:12226: rdo rje ste / rgya mtsho las /
NK065(cu)001:12227: 'khor gyi nang nas skal mchog ldan //
NK065(cu)001:12228: 'dul ba'i dus babs gsang ba'i bdag /
NK065(cu)001:12229: lag na rdo rjes bsdu ba mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:12232: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje yis //
NK065(cu)001:12233: thun mong ma yin nges pa'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:12234: dris lan mi mngon don gyis bsdus //
NK065(cu)001:12235: byin rlabs mi yul grags pa yin //
NK065(cu)001:12238: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK065(cu)001:12241: rdo rje gsang ba zhes pa ni dbang bskur ba'i mtshan yin te /
NK065(cu)001:12242: gsang ba'i bdag po phyag na rdo rje la grags pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12244: de ltar sdud pa po smos pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:12245: sdud pa po med na gtam lkugs pa ltar phyis mi 'byung ba'i skyon dang /
NK065(cu)001:12248: ston pa gang gis bstan cing /
NK065(cu)001:12250: de nas su zhig gis spel zhes pa'i sgro skur spang ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12254: gnyis pa gdul bya dgos ched kyi gleng gzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:12255: rgyud 'di'i le'u bco lnga pa khro bo sngon byung gi le'usa ston te /
NK065(cu)001:12256: de la spyir khro bo la /
NK065(cu)001:12259: phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:12261: bdag med rtogs pa'i shes rab ste /
NK065(cu)001:12262: des dngos po dang mtshan 'dzin gyi rnam rtog 'joms pa 'i phyir ngang gis khro ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:12264: yang dag shes rab chen po ni /
NK065(cu)001:12265: mtshan ma 'joms phyir khro bo mchog /
NK065(cu)001:12268: rang rig rtogs pa'i ye shes te /
NK065(cu)001:12269: des chos thams cad la dbang bsgyur zhing 'khor ba'i sa bon drungs nas 'joms pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12272: rang rig ye shes rgyal po yis //
NK065(cu)001:12273: phyogs bcur khams rnams dbang bsdus nas //
NK065(cu)001:12274: kun kyang mi dmigs dbyings su thim //
NK065(cu)001:12275: thams cad khro bo'i tshogs su gyur //
NK065(cu)001:12278: gdul bya nam yang mi 'dor ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12279: 'dul ba'i dus las mi 'da' ba ni phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK065(cu)001:12280: de la'ang 'gro ba skyob pa na 'bad rtsol med
NK065(cu)001:12281: pa'i thugs rjes mi mthun phyogs 'joms pa'i phyir ngang
NK065(cu)001:12282: ngam shugs kyis khro ba ni thugs rje ste /
NK065(cu)001:12284: 'dzin pa mi rtog thugs rje zhen chags khro //
NK065(cu)001:12286: rgyu des gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12287: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku dang cha lugs su snang ba'i khro bor bcos pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12288: ji ltar 'tshams par ston pa'i mdzad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12291: shin tu gdug cing gtum pa la //
NK065(cu)001:12292: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK065(cu)001:12293: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK065(cu)001:12294: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:12297: 'dir ni phyag rgya chen po'i khro bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:12298: de yang de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi mngag gzhug
NK065(cu)001:12299: gi pho nyar khros pa lta bu zhig ston pa
NK065(cu)001:12301: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyis khro ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du mdzad de /
NK065(cu)001:12304: sngar ltar phun sum tshogs pa drug las /
NK065(cu)001:12306: rigs thams cad kyi bdag po sangs rgyas thams cad
NK065(cu)001:12307: kyi spyi'i gzugs can drug pa kun tu bzang po
NK065(cu)001:12309: ru dra'i ngo na dpal chen po che mchog badz+ra he ru kar snang ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:12310: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo /
NK065(cu)001:12313: bzod par dka' ba'i dur khrod chen po ste /
NK065(cu)001:12314: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil na /
NK065(cu)001:12315: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng /
NK065(cu)001:12316: 'bar ba chen po'i klong gi 'khor lo'i dkyil na /
NK065(cu)001:12319: gdul bar bya ba gdug pa can gyi 'khor dang /
NK065(cu)001:12322: ru dra 'khor dang bcas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12323: der gol ba'i rgyu ci snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:12324: spyir ma rig pa gnyis kyis sems can thams cad srid par 'khyams la /
NK065(cu)001:12325: bye brag tu ru dra ni /
NK065(cu)001:12326: sngon bskal pa kun bkod kyi dus su thar pa nag por skyes pa'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:12328: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK065(cu)001:12329: dngos po bzhi la gnas spyad kyang //
NK065(cu)001:12330: nam mkha' la ni sprin bzhin te //
NK065(cu)001:12332: zhes gsungs pa sgra ji bzhin par spyad pas gol
NK065(cu)001:12333: ba'i rnam smin gyis dmyal ba tsha grang gi gnas
NK065(cu)001:12334: su bskal pa chen po stong phrag bcu gnyis dang
NK065(cu)001:12335: / de nas bskal chen drug tu yi dwags su
NK065(cu)001:12336: skye ba brgyud de rnam smin gyi 'bras bu myong
NK065(cu)001:12338: sngon gyi rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bus mtshams sbyar nas /
NK065(cu)001:12339: yul lang+ka bu rir yi dwags kyis 'gro bas bsdus
NK065(cu)001:12340: pa'i srin po bya'i gshog pa can du skyes te
NK065(cu)001:12341: / gzugs khams kyi 'phags pa'i gnas lnga ma gtogs
NK065(cu)001:12342: pa 'dod gzugs kyi khams thams cad dbang du bsdus
NK065(cu)001:12343: / te / 'gro ba'i tshogs la gnod par byed pa'i las kyi ru drar gyur pa de nyid /
NK065(cu)001:12344: thub dka' rdo rje snying por gyur pa dang sngon
NK065(cu)001:12345: dpon slob tu 'brel ba'i stobs kyis gdul byar gyur
NK065(cu)001:12347: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12349: thugs rjes 'dul bar gyur te zhes pa'i bar ro //
NK065(cu)001:12351: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen por gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:12352: zhes sogs kyis rigs bzhi'i 'khor dang /
NK065(cu)001:12354: zhes sogs kyis gsang ba'i bu mo brgyad dang /
NK065(cu)001:12355: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK065(cu)001:12356: zhes sogs kyis gus pa'i bu mo brgyad dang /
NK065(cu)001:12357: rdo rje sring 'gro ma'i tshogs dang sogs kyis dur khrod pa'i sgo srung bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:12358: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK065(cu)001:12359: zhes sogs kyis dbang mo nyer brgyad rnams so //
NK065(cu)001:12361: gdul dka' drag po'i gdul bya nyid phrin las drag shul gyi sgo nas 'dul ba'i don mdzad pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12362: de yang ji ltar btul ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:12364: ji ltar 'dul ba'i dbang ni drug 'gyur te //
NK065(cu)001:12365: che mchog nyid dang khro bo 'chol ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:12366: rdo rje zhe sdang rdo rje srin po dang //
NK065(cu)001:12367: rdo rje khro bo 'jigs byed khro bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:12369: 'dir slob dpon sgeg pa'i bzhed pa ltar don bcu bzhis 'chad do //
NK065(cu)001:12371: zhi ba rigs drug pa nyid khro bo che mchog
NK065(cu)001:12372: tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK065(cu)001:12373: pa ni ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul 1lo //
NK065(cu)001:12374: de nas de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas gsang ba'i
NK065(cu)001:12375: yum sprul te sbyor ba mdzad pas dkyil 'khor thams
NK065(cu)001:12376: cad bskyed pa'i rgyu byang chub kyi sems spro ba
NK065(cu)001:12377: ni che mchog longs spyod chen po'i dkyil 'khor 2ro
NK065(cu)001:12378: // de'i tshe h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra zhes
NK065(cu)001:12379: sogs brjod pa ni gnyen po'i khro tshogs kun snang
NK065(cu)001:12380: ba'i rkyen de kun brjod pa'i cho 'phrul 3lo //
NK065(cu)001:12381: rgyu sems sprin dang rkyen sngags las khro bo 'chol
NK065(cu)001:12382: pa grangs med par 'thon pa ni sprul pa rdzu
NK065(cu)001:12385: phyir 'jig rten gyi khams g.yos pa sogs ltas chen po bco lnga dang /
NK065(cu)001:12386: nang du lam pa'i sems la tshogs sbyor gyi ting
NK065(cu)001:12387: nge 'dzin lngar g.yo thob goms pa'i nyams gsum bogs
NK065(cu)001:12388: 'thon pa ni byin rlabs kyi cho 'phrul 5lo //
NK065(cu)001:12389: phyi snod g.yo ba sogs dang nang khro bo'i sprin tshogs mi bzad pa'i chos kun tu snang bas /
NK065(cu)001:12390: de'i tshe gdug pa can thams cad brgyal bar byas pa ni chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul 6lo //
NK065(cu)001:12391: de nas sprul pa'i khro tshogs de dag rigs lnga'i
NK065(cu)001:12392: khrag 'thung yab yum dang bcas pas bsdus nas rang
NK065(cu)001:12393: rang gi rigs dang mthun pa'i phyogs su dregs pa
NK065(cu)001:12394: can de rnams gdan du byas te bzhugs pa ni
NK065(cu)001:12395: gong gi sprul pa las khyad par du gyur pa'i
NK065(cu)001:12396: phyir sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor 7ro //
NK065(cu)001:12397: de nas dregs pa de rnams khros te gtum tshig tu smra ba na /
NK065(cu)001:12398: de'i gnyen por rdo rje srin po dbu dgu phyag
NK065(cu)001:12399: bco brgyad zhabs brgyad du snang bar mdzad nas de
NK065(cu)001:12400: dag gi phung po bsgral te zhal du gsol ba
NK065(cu)001:12401: ni phrin las rmad du 8byung ba'i ngo bo'o //
NK065(cu)001:12402: de ltar pho rnams bsgral nas de dag gi chung
NK065(cu)001:12403: ma dbang phyug ma bran g.yog gi tshogs dang bcas
NK065(cu)001:12404: pa dbang du bsdus pa ni 'khor sdud pa'i cho
NK065(cu)001:12405: 'phrul 9lo // che mchog nyid dbang mo'i ngo la
NK065(cu)001:12406: rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed chen po lnga ga yongs su
NK065(cu)001:12407: rdzogs par snang ba ni yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil
NK065(cu)001:12408: 'phrul 9lo // 'khor 10ro // rigs lnga'i gtso bo la ma mo brgyad dang /
NK065(cu)001:12409: rigs bzhi la lnga lnga 'khril te rol pa ni 'khor bsdus pa'i cho 'phrul gyi 11bya ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:12410: gnyis su med bar rol pa'i sems sprin las 'khor
NK065(cu)001:12411: gyi dkyil 'khor khro mo nyi shu ngo mtshar dang
NK065(cu)001:12412: bcas pas re re yang nyer brgyad du 'thon cing
NK065(cu)001:12413: / so so yang rang rang gi rigs gcig tu
NK065(cu)001:12414: bsdus te dkyil 'khor la 'god pa'i mdzad pa rdzogs
NK065(cu)001:12415: nas dbang mo rnams rang gnas su bkye ba ni
NK065(cu)001:12417: de nas dregs pa can rnams 'og sgo nas bton te mi gtsang ba'i 'dam du chud pa na /
NK065(cu)001:12418: slar yang snams nas khro bo rme brtsegs sam dam
NK065(cu)001:12419: rdzas bdud rtsi rlon sbyor phyung nas 'dam kun 'thungs
NK065(cu)001:12420: te dbang bskur bas bsam yas lhun grub kyi ting
NK065(cu)001:12422: sku 'bar ba chen po mi bzad par mthong ngo //
NK065(cu)001:12423: de'i tshe 'dul thabs bsam yas tha dad pas 'jig
NK065(cu)001:12424: rten gyi dregs pa can thams cad dus gcig tu
NK065(cu)001:12425: btul te / de dag shin tu 'dar zhing bred pas mna' bor nas lus gdan du phul zhing /
NK065(cu)001:12426: mgrin gcig tu 'khor phul ba rnams ni phrin las
NK065(cu)001:12427: kyi 'bras bu dregs pa can gnas su 13bstab pa'o
NK065(cu)001:12428: // de nas ma mo rnams slar 'khor du 'dus
NK065(cu)001:12429: te dngos grub nos pa na lag tu rdo rje
NK065(cu)001:12431: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi khyams su bkod pa ni phrin las kyi 'bras bu 'khor dam la 14btags pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12432: de dag ni de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa /
NK065(cu)001:12433: zhes pa man chad kyis ston no //
NK065(cu)001:12436: 'dir bstan gyi ru dra de tha mal pa'am sprul pa yin /
NK065(cu)001:12437: dang po ltar yi dwags srin po chen po zer bas 'dod khams pa yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12438: de gzugs khams dbang du bsdud pa mi 'thad de /
NK065(cu)001:12439: der bgrod pa bsam gtan gyi ting nge 'dzin thob dgos pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:12440: dpal chen po dang spyod yul gcig tu ma spyad
NK065(cu)001:12441: pa'i phyir zhal mthong ba'i dngos kyi gdul byar gyur
NK065(cu)001:12444: ngan song gi sdug bsngal myong bar bshad pa sogs rigs pa ma yin no zer na /
NK065(cu)001:12446: 'dod pa'i rten la 'phags sa thob pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12447: sngon gyi las rmad du byung ba'i mthu ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12448: 'dod pa yin yang gzugs dbang du sdud pa mi 'gal zhing /
NK065(cu)001:12450: skye bo ma rig gis ldongs pas //
NK065(cu)001:12451: srid rtse'i bar du song nas kyang //
NK065(cu)001:12452: zhes 'dod pa'i so skyes bsam gtan gyi ting 'dzin thob par gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12453: de ma thob par yang ma nges pa'i phyir dang /
NK065(cu)001:12454: dpal chen po mthong ba la spyod yul gcig tu spyod dgos na /
NK065(cu)001:12455: sh+aaka thub mthong ba'i sems can thams cad kyi thub
NK065(cu)001:12456: pa dang spyod yul gcig tu spyod dgos pa sogs
NK065(cu)001:12459: tha mal ba'i gzugs dang sdug bsngal myong ba ltar
NK065(cu)001:12460: bstan pas sdug bsngal rang mtshan pa myong ba dang
NK065(cu)001:12461: tha mal pa yin par ma nges te /
NK065(cu)001:12462: sems can gyi don du de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul
NK065(cu)001:12463: pa tha mal pa'i gzugs su snang ba rnams dang
NK065(cu)001:12464: / sems can rnams skyo ba bskyed pa'i phyir dmyal
NK065(cu)001:12465: ba'i 'jig rten sprul nas bstan pa sogs kyang der
NK065(cu)001:12468: kho bo ni gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pa'i
NK065(cu)001:12469: rjes su 'brangs nas sprul pa bar khas blangs te
NK065(cu)001:12471: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis tshul du bstan par rig par bya ste /
NK065(cu)001:12472: de la dgos pa dang dgongs pa ci yod ce na /
NK065(cu)001:12473: rang rgyud pa'i gol sa dgag pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12474: che ba'i mthu'i tshad bstan pa'i dgos pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12475: nang du bdud bzhi btul ba'i rtags phyi rol du bstan par 'grel to //
NK065(cu)001:12477: ji skad bshad pa'i mthu 'di dag rang rgyud la yod pa ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:12478: sprul pa yin par som nyi mi bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:12480: de ltar na'ang bdag tu rmongs pa'i zhes sogs kyis gnod do zhe na mi gnod de /
NK065(cu)001:12481: phyis 'jig rten du cha lugs dang mthu cha 'dra
NK065(cu)001:12482: ba'i ru dra rang mtshan pa 'byung ba rnams rgyu
NK065(cu)001:12483: de lta bus bskyed par bstan te /
NK065(cu)001:12485: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ltar //
NK065(cu)001:12488: de'i phyir gnyen po mchog rnams la nyes pas mi
NK065(cu)001:12489: gos par bstan pa'i ched du rgyal ba'i sor phreng
NK065(cu)001:12490: can du sprul nas btul bzhin thabs kyi che ba
NK065(cu)001:12491: dbyung ba dang / sngags lam pa'i gol sa dgag
NK065(cu)001:12492: pa'i phyir thabs la mkhas pa cho 'phrul du gdon
NK065(cu)001:12493: dbyung ba dang / mi za'o // yang /
NK065(cu)001:12494: he ru ka rnams dbang mo dang rol pa las sras sprul pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK065(cu)001:12496: he ru ka re re la dbang mo brgyad dang lnga lngas 'khril ba'i tshe /
NK065(cu)001:12498: yang na zhi ba'i lhag chog tu /
NK065(cu)001:12499: mdun rgyab zur gnyis dbu gsum po //
NK065(cu)001:12500: bdun la gtso mo bdun gyis 'khril //
NK065(cu)001:12501: zhes pa ltar dus gcig tu rol grang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12502: 'khril tshul gnyis ka ltar ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:12504: ma mo re re yang de bzhin gshegs pa re
NK065(cu)001:12505: re dang sbyor bar ma mo rnams kyis mthong ba
NK065(cu)001:12506: ni / zhes ma mo'i snang ba la de bzhin
NK065(cu)001:12507: gshegs pa re re yang brgyad dang lngar snang nas
NK065(cu)001:12508: sbyor bar gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12509: yang 'dir dbang mo dang rol pa las sras nyi shu bskyed pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12510: sgrub thabs las rigs kyi yum lnga dang rol pa las bskyed pa nang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12511: 'dir ni gzhan gyi che ba dbyung ba'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12513: mo rnams sbyor nas 'dul ba'i ched du bstan par zad kyi /
NK065(cu)001:12514: nyams len gyi dus su las kyi srin mo la
NK065(cu)001:12515: mos pa mi skye bas rigs kyi yum lnga dang
NK065(cu)001:12516: rol pa las bskyed pa'i phyir skyon med do //
NK065(cu)001:12518: ma rung ba'i gdul bya la drag po'i phrin las su snang ba'i dus te /
NK065(cu)001:12519: 'dul ba'i thabs sna tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab par so sor snang bas dus gcig tu btul lo //
NK065(cu)001:12521: drug pa sdud pa po ni /
NK065(cu)001:12522: gong ma ltar gsang bdag nyid do //
NK065(cu)001:12523: gnyis pa bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK065(cu)001:12524: rgyud 'di'i le'u gsum pa'i stod kyis ston te /
NK065(cu)001:12528: zhar byung rtsod pa spang ba dang gsum /
NK065(cu)001:12530: 'di'i don ma rtogs pa rnams lam stegs kyi theg
NK065(cu)001:12531: pa la bkri ba'i ched du ston pa'i thugs rig
NK065(cu)001:12532: pa ye shes kyi byin rlabs las thub pa drug
NK065(cu)001:12533: 'phros pa ni / de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NK065(cu)001:12534: thams cad las thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis rlabs
NK065(cu)001:12535: zhes bya ba'i rig pa skyes bu thub pa drug
NK065(cu)001:12536: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo
NK065(cu)001:12539: 'dir rig pa'i skyes bu'i don ni /
NK065(cu)001:12540: gsang 'dus kyi rgyud phyi ma las /
NK065(cu)001:12541: rang gi lus ngag yid rdo rje //
NK065(cu)001:12542: mi phyed pa yi ngo bo ste //
NK065(cu)001:12543: rig dang bcas par ldan pas na //
NK065(cu)001:12544: rig pa'i skyes bu zhes su bshad //
NK065(cu)001:12545: ces spar khab tu drangs pa ltar ro //
NK065(cu)001:12549: grags pa'i thun mong ngo bo ni //
NK065(cu)001:12550: thub drug ston pa stong gsum gnas //
NK065(cu)001:12551: khyad par sh+aakya thub pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:12552: rgyal srid btsun mo'i 'khor spangs nas //
NK065(cu)001:12553: rab tu byung rdzogs mdzad pa yis //
NK065(cu)001:12554: rgyu yi 'khor lo bstan par sgrogs //
NK065(cu)001:12556: shin tu dkon pa'i dus su'o //
NK065(cu)001:12557: zhes phun sum tshogs pa lnga las /
NK065(cu)001:12560: phyogs rnams kun na zhing rnams rgya mtsho snang //
NK065(cu)001:12561: la la zlum po la la zur gsum ste //
NK065(cu)001:12562: de dag la la phyogs na gru bzhir gnas //
NK065(cu)001:12563: nor bur pad+ma 'khor lo yan lag brgyad //
NK065(cu)001:12564: kun kyang las rnams rgya mtshos rnam par bris //
NK065(cu)001:12565: zhes 'gro ba'i las dbang gis zhing khams kyi bkod pa mtha' yas kyang /
NK065(cu)001:12567: gling bzhi dang ni nyi zla dang //
NK065(cu)001:12568: ri rab dang ni 'dod lhar bcas //
NK065(cu)001:12569: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten stong la ni //
NK065(cu)001:12570: stong ni spyi phud yin par 'dod //
NK065(cu)001:12571: de stong la ni stong gnyis pa //
NK065(cu)001:12572: bar ma'i 'jig rten khams yin no //
NK065(cu)001:12573: de stong la ni stong gsum ste //
NK065(cu)001:12575: zhes pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po ni sprul sku thub pa gcig gi zhing ste /
NK065(cu)001:12576: stong gsum gyi stong chen po rer /
NK065(cu)001:12579: s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med pa'i /
NK065(cu)001:12580: zhes pa don med du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12582: de ni chos sku dang longs sku'i zhing yin la /
NK065(cu)001:12583: de sprul sku'i zhing gi gzhir mtshon pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12584: zhes bla ma gong ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:12585: sku gsum gyi zhing khams kyi khyad par de gang zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12586: don la sku gsum dbyer med yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12587: spyi'i dbang du zhing khams la che chung med na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:12588: bye brag gi dbang du byas na /
NK065(cu)001:12590: chos dbyings brdal khyab chen po'i zhing yin pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12591: dngos po'i chos kyis tshad gzung du med do //
NK065(cu)001:12595: stong gsum gyi 'jig rten stong la stong rgyu bkod dang po /
NK065(cu)001:12596: de stong la stong rgyu bkod bar ma /
NK065(cu)001:12597: de stong la stong mtshams sbyor yongs su 'das pa zhes bya ba longs sku'i zhing gi tshad do //
NK065(cu)001:12598: s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu /
NK065(cu)001:12599: zhes pas bstan par bzhed do //
NK065(cu)001:12601: de yang mi spong mod kyi 'on kyang phal chen las /
NK065(cu)001:12602: las kyi bye brag bsam mi khyab //
NK065(cu)001:12604: gshin rje'i 'jig rten s+n+rel gzhi ste //
NK065(cu)001:12605: byol song lha mi gyen du 'gro //
NK065(cu)001:12607: yang na mgo gyen bstan du 'gro ba mtho ris /
NK065(cu)001:12608: s+n+rel gzhi ste 'phred bstan gyis 'gro ba dud 'gro /
NK065(cu)001:12609: mthur bstan gyis 'gro ba dmyal ba dang yi dwags te /
NK065(cu)001:12610: de ltar stong gsum gyi 'jig rten gcig la'ang /
NK065(cu)001:12611: s+n+rel gzhi dang yan man gsum du sbyar te 'gro ris lngas bsdus pa'i snod bcud dam /
NK065(cu)001:12614: stong gsum gcig la'ang chags tshul drug /
NK065(cu)001:12615: sprul sku gcig gi zhing du grags //
NK065(cu)001:12617: las mi mthun pa'i dbang gis s+n+rel gzhi'i 'jig rten ljid 'bebs lugs bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:12618: yan man ste s+n+rel ma dang spyi'u tshugs kyi 'jig
NK065(cu)001:12619: rten gyi khams 'chags tshul mi 'dra ba drug gis
NK065(cu)001:12620: bsdus pa'i 'jig rten re re la'ang phyogs mtshams steng
NK065(cu)001:12621: 'og gi dbye bas phyogs bcur rgya dang grangs las
NK065(cu)001:12622: 'das pas mtha' yas mu med pa'i stong gsum gyi
NK065(cu)001:12623: stong chen por sprul sku re res 'dul ba'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:12624: / 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu med /
NK065(cu)001:12625: ces pa nyid sprul sku'i zhing du bshad na bade'am snyam ste /
NK065(cu)001:12626: phal chen gyi le'u bcu bzhi par /
NK065(cu)001:12627: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK065(cu)001:12628: 'di snang bar grags nas 'dzam gling bye ba phrag
NK065(cu)001:12629: brgya bstan to // zhes pa nas /
NK065(cu)001:12630: de ltar phyogs bcu shin tu rgyas par byas nas
NK065(cu)001:12631: chos kyi dbyings ma lus pa thams cad snang bar
NK065(cu)001:12632: byas so // 'jig rten gyi khams re re yang 'dzam gling bye ba phrag brgya bstan nas /
NK065(cu)001:12634: ji ltar bcom ldana'adasa sangs rgyas kyi gdan la bzhugs shing /
NK065(cu)001:12635: byang chub sems dpa' sangs rgyas kyi zhing bcu'i rdul
NK065(cu)001:12636: shin tu phra ba snyed dang thabs gcig tu snang
NK065(cu)001:12638: 'jig rten gyi khams re re'i gling bzhi ba bye ba phrag brgya kun na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:12639: de bzhin gshegs pa bye ba phrag brgya dag sangs rgyas kyi gdan la bzhugs pa snang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:12642: dper na bar snang zla ba gcig shar ba //
NK065(cu)001:12643: 'dzam gling chu rnams kun tu chu zla snang //
NK065(cu)001:12644: chu gcig nang gi nam mkha'i zla ba yang //
NK065(cu)001:12645: 'gro ba so so rang gi mdun du snang //
NK065(cu)001:12646: de ni sprul sku gcig la gling rnams snang //
NK065(cu)001:12647: gling rnams gcig la 'gro ba drug tu snang //
NK065(cu)001:12648: tha dad de kun sprul sku gcig tu grags //
NK065(cu)001:12649: de 'dra'i stong gsum mtha' yas mu med na //
NK065(cu)001:12650: de 'dra'i sprul sku re res 'gro don mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:12653: thub pa chen po bcom ldan 'das re res /
NK065(cu)001:12655: stong gsum gyi stong chen po re rer thub pa re res don mdzad pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12656: sher phyin gyi ljags kyi dbang po bkram pa'i le'u las /
NK065(cu)001:12657: bcom ldan 'das kyis stong gsum gyi stong chen po ljags kyi dbang pos khebs par mdzad pas /
NK065(cu)001:12658: de na gnas pa'i sems can 'dul ba'i snod du
NK065(cu)001:12659: gyur pa rnams ni bla na med pa'i byang chub
NK065(cu)001:12660: tu lung bstan par gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:12661: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams rab 'byams thams cad ni 'od kyis khyab pa mdzad do //
NK065(cu)001:12663: de 'dra'i thub pa re re'ang gdul bya'i rigs drug gi dbang gis drug tu snang bar 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:12665: lha yi gnas na brgya byin mgon //
NK065(cu)001:12666: lha ma yin la thags bzang ris //
NK065(cu)001:12668: yi dwags gnas na kha 'bar te //
NK065(cu)001:12669: byol sol seng ge nyid du smra //
NK065(cu)001:12670: dmyal ba la ni gshin rje'i mgon //
NK065(cu)001:12672: de dag so sos kyang 'gro ba'i ngor gang 'dul
NK065(cu)001:12673: gyi bkod pa tshad med pa ston bar mdzad kyang
NK065(cu)001:12675: gang 'dul ba'i tshe sku'i bkod pa bsgyur ba bzo'i sprul pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12676: gang 'dul gyi gzugs su skye ba zhes pa'i tshul ston pa skye ba sprul sku dang /
NK065(cu)001:12677: byang chub chen po mchog gi sprul sku dang gsum mo //
NK065(cu)001:12679: 'gro ba las dag pa'i sems snang la snang ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:12680: dper na bee d+aur+ya'i sa gzhi la brgya byin gyi gzugs brnyan snang ba bzhin no //
NK065(cu)001:12681: de yang rgyud bla ma las /
NK065(cu)001:12682: ji ltar beed+aura sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK065(cu)001:12683: lha dbang lus kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK065(cu)001:12684: de bzhin 'gro sems sa gzhi gtsang ma la //
NK065(cu)001:12685: thub pa'i dbang po'i sku yi gzugs brnyan 'char //
NK065(cu)001:12689: zhes pas lha min stod ris lha dang smad ris dud 'gror bsdus pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12690: don la 'gro ba rigs drug dang /
NK065(cu)001:12691: bye brag 'khor rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12693: 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis gdul bya'i bsam pa dang mthun par chos ston pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12695: sku gzhan las 'phags pas bstan pa'i phyir bsod nams chen pos 'dul ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:12696: gsung rig pa dang ldan pa'i theg pa sna tshogs
NK065(cu)001:12697: kyi chos ston pa'i phyir rig pas 'dul ba dang
NK065(cu)001:12698: / thugs mngon shes chen po ni don thams cad
NK065(cu)001:12699: mngon sum du gyur pas 'dul ba'i phyir mngon sum
NK065(cu)001:12701: phrin las bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'dul ba ni
NK065(cu)001:12702: rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs ston pa'i phyir rdzu 'phrul gyis
NK065(cu)001:12705: zhes sogs mdzad pa brgyad dngos su gsungs shing /
NK065(cu)001:12706: bla ma gong ma rnams mdo sde dang mthun par kha bskang ste mdzad pa bcu gnyis su bzhed /
NK065(cu)001:12707: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po ni /
NK065(cu)001:12709: 'dir cho 'phrul bstan par gsungs pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK065(cu)001:12710: de la mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi dbang du byas na /
NK065(cu)001:12712: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK065(cu)001:12713: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK065(cu)001:12714: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK065(cu)001:12715: sprul pa'i rang bzhan sna tshogs kyis //
NK065(cu)001:12716: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:12717: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK065(cu)001:12718: lhums su 'jug dang bltams pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:12719: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:12720: btsun mo'i 'khor dgyes rol pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12721: nges 'byung dka' ba spyod pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:12722: byang chub snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:12723: bdud sde 'joms dang rdzogs par ni //
NK065(cu)001:12724: byang chub chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK065(cu)001:12725: mya ngan 'das par gshegs mdzad rnams //
