NK065(cu)001:12726: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK065(cu)001:12727: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK065(cu)001:12728: zhes sogs sku'i cho 'phrul chen pos 'gro ba 'dul ba'i mdzad pa thams cad de /
NK065(cu)001:12729: mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs par ston pa'i thub pas /
NK065(cu)001:12730: zhes pa'i sogs khongs kyi bsdus so //
NK065(cu)001:12733: 'dul ba'i dbang gis lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12734: zhes sogs kyis theg pa'i rkang grangs dang /
NK065(cu)001:12735: ma rig pa'i zhes sogs kyis gang gi gnyen por dgongs te gsung tshul dang /
NK065(cu)001:12738: gnyen po de dag kyang dbang po'i bye brag gis lngar bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12742: mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang /
NK065(cu)001:12744: de yang dus bzhi la ma thogs ma chags pa'i
NK065(cu)001:12745: ye shes kyis mnyam pa nyid du rang gsal 'dzin
NK065(cu)001:12746: pa med par mkhyen pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12748: mkhyen pa'i skad cig gcig nyid kyis //
NK065(cu)001:12749: shes bya'i dkyil 'khor kun khyab par //
NK065(cu)001:12750: zhes pa ltar gnas lugs dus las 'das kyang /
NK065(cu)001:12751: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i blo dus ltar 'khrul pa
NK065(cu)001:12752: thams cad ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su sa ler gzigs
NK065(cu)001:12753: pa ni / sngon dang phyi mtha' mkhyen pa'i mngon shes so //
NK065(cu)001:12754: de bzhin du nyid las mi gzhan pa'am yul med
NK065(cu)001:12755: rang gsal gyi tshul gyis gzhan sems mkhyen pa'i mngon
NK065(cu)001:12756: shes dang / gzigs pa lha'i mig gi mngon shes dang /
NK065(cu)001:12757: gsan pa lha'i rna ba'i mngon shes dang /
NK065(cu)001:12758: gang gis 'dul ba de la der ston pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes dang /
NK065(cu)001:12759: de lta bu'i tshul ji ltar spyod kyang gzung 'dzin
NK065(cu)001:12760: mi mnga' bas zag med kyi mngon shes dang drug
NK065(cu)001:12761: gi rim pa thams cad thugs kyi rjes su 'gro
NK065(cu)001:12762: zhing mkhyen nas don mdzad pa'i phyir mngon shes so
NK065(cu)001:12766: sprul pa'i skus 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12767: ris drug gis bsdus pa'i 'gro ba gang dang gang gis 'dul ba de dang mthun par /
NK065(cu)001:12768: zhi khro la sogs pa'i sku dang /
NK065(cu)001:12769: de las byung ba'i gsung dang /
NK065(cu)001:12770: de dag slong ba po'i thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12771: sku gcig la'ang zhal mang po dang phra men la
NK065(cu)001:12772: sogs pa'i zhal gzugs mi mthun pa'ang sna tshogs ston
NK065(cu)001:12776: res 'ga' gdon chen gegs mdzad de //
NK065(cu)001:12777: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK065(cu)001:12778: ri dang skye bo thams cad do //
NK065(cu)001:12780: mdor na sku sogs mang por ston pas grangs bsam gyis mi khyab par ma zad /
NK065(cu)001:12781: nam mkhas ji tsam khyab pa de srid du skus
NK065(cu)001:12782: khyab pa sogs tshad bsam gyis mi khyab pa'ang sbyar
NK065(cu)001:12783: du rung ngo // lnga pa dus ni /
NK065(cu)001:12784: sgron ma bkod pa'i dus te /
NK065(cu)001:12785: shin tu dkon pa'i dus na'o //
NK065(cu)001:12791: sha za dge sbyong gi tshul 'dzin pa dpal 'dzin na re /
NK065(cu)001:12792: khyod kyi thub pa'i dbye ba la //
NK065(cu)001:12793: 'gro drug thub pa drug yin lo //
NK065(cu)001:12794: 'o na thub pa gzhan lnga yis //
NK065(cu)001:12795: mdzad pa bcu gnyis gang du bstan //
NK065(cu)001:12796: chos kyi 'khor lo gang du bskor //
NK065(cu)001:12797: bstan pa gang yin de 'dzin su //
NK065(cu)001:12798: gal te de dag med na ni //
NK065(cu)001:12799: thub pa yin pa'i sgrub byed gang //
NK065(cu)001:12802: de skad du smra ba dag shin tu rigs pa ma yin te /
NK065(cu)001:12804: 'byon 'gyur gyi rgyal ba byams pa mgon po chos can /
NK065(cu)001:12805: khyod thub pa ma yin par thal /
NK065(cu)001:12806: thub pa yin na da ltar gyi ston pa 'di
NK065(cu)001:12807: kho na ltar mdzad pa bcu gnyis ston dgos pa
NK065(cu)001:12808: gang zhig / khyod kyis dka' ba spyod pa'i mdzad pa mi ston pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12810: gnyis pa mdo'i lung gis grub /
NK065(cu)001:12812: dag pa'i zhing na nges 'byung dang rol rtsed mi ston pa'i rgyal ba mtha' yas pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12813: zhing khams la lar bdud kyang med pas /
NK065(cu)001:12815: de dag kyang thub pa ma yin par thal lo //
NK065(cu)001:12816: de'i phyir 'gro 'dul sprul sku grangs med na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:12817: rigs bsdus na drug tu bzhag pa ni 'thad pa dang bcas pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12818: 'phags pa de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yul la 'jug pa'i mdo las /
NK065(cu)001:12820: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gser gyi kha dog tu mthong bas 'dul bar bya ba yin na /
NK065(cu)001:12821: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku yang gser gyi kha dog tu snang ngo //
NK065(cu)001:12826: mu tig dmar po'i kha dog gis 'dul bar bya ba yin na /
NK065(cu)001:12827: de dag gi kha dog tu bzhugs so //
NK065(cu)001:12828: de bzhin du 'jig rten skyong ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:12836: gshin rje'i 'jig rten pas 'dul bar bya ba yin na /
NK065(cu)001:12837: de dag gi gzugs su bzhugs nas chos ston to //
NK065(cu)001:12841: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa ni tshad med de /
NK065(cu)001:12842: 'gro ba gang dang gang gis 'dul ba de dang
NK065(cu)001:12843: de'i gzugs dang kha dog dang ming gis don mdzad
NK065(cu)001:12845: dbang bsgyur gyi gnas su lha'i bdag po dbang bsgyur
NK065(cu)001:12846: du sprul nas dge bcu'i las kyi lam yang dag
NK065(cu)001:12848: zhes pa nas yi dwags dang dmyal ba'i gzugs kyis
NK065(cu)001:12849: 'dul ba rnams la'ang de'i gzugs su sprul zhing don
NK065(cu)001:12850: mdzad do // zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12851: rgyal ba thub pa nyid dmyal ba'i 'gro ba pas
NK065(cu)001:12852: dge sdig lung ston gyi chos rgyal gshin rjer mthong
NK065(cu)001:12853: ba sogs 'gro ba'i las mthun du bstan par zad
NK065(cu)001:12855: la la lhums zhugs la la bltams //
NK065(cu)001:12856: la la tshul bsrung rab tu byung //
NK065(cu)001:12857: la la bsnyen rdzogs dka' thub byed //
NK065(cu)001:12858: la la dam nod 'gro ba sgrol //
NK065(cu)001:12859: la la bcu drug chos la 'dzud //
NK065(cu)001:12860: la la me 'bar chu yang brub //
NK065(cu)001:12862: de lta na'ang thub pa drug ka rab byung sprul
NK065(cu)001:12863: skur byed par snang ba'i phyir las mthun du bstan
NK065(cu)001:12864: par mi rigs so zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:12867: dag pa rnams la mtshan dpe dod pa'i sku //
NK065(cu)001:12868: ma lus 'dul phyir ston pa'i thub pa drug /
NK065(cu)001:12869: ces pa ltar 'gro ba gzhan lnga yang mi'i gdul
NK065(cu)001:12870: bya ltar sh+aakya thub pa'i skus 'dul ba yod pa'i
NK065(cu)001:12871: phyir te / de bzhin gshegs pa'i cho 'phrul chen
NK065(cu)001:12872: pos dmyal ba'i me zhi bar byas nas byams pa
NK065(cu)001:12873: chen po'i ting nge 'dzin la rab tu 'dzud pa
NK065(cu)001:12874: phyir te / dang / yi dwags la de bzhin
NK065(cu)001:12875: gshegs pa'i 'od zer gyis bza' ba'i dbang thob par
NK065(cu)001:12876: byas nas sbyin pa rnam bzhis 'dul ba sogs bshad
NK065(cu)001:12877: phyir te / dang / pa'i phyir / de ltar
NK065(cu)001:12878: sprul pa mchog gis 'dul ba'i ngos nas rang byung
NK065(cu)001:12880: de dag gis mi thul ba la so so'i las mthun du ston pa'i phyir 'gal ba med do //
NK065(cu)001:12882: lha'i thub pa sogs la bstan pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:12883: de 'dzin gyi gang zag med par yang bsgrub mi nus te /
NK065(cu)001:12884: ma mthong ba'i phyir med pas ma khyab cing /
NK065(cu)001:12885: der ma zad lha'i bdag po dbang bsgyur du sprul
NK065(cu)001:12886: nas dge bcu'i las lam len du 'jug par sngar
NK065(cu)001:12887: gyi lung gis grub pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12888: de 'dzin pa'i lha yod par nges te /
NK065(cu)001:12889: dper na brgya byin gyis bstan pa'i sgra mdo 'dzin pa'i lha yod pa bzhin dang /
NK065(cu)001:12890: de dag gi gzugs su bzhugs nas chos ston to //
NK065(cu)001:12891: zhes pa'i lung gis kyang gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12892: gzhan du thub pa yin na /
NK065(cu)001:12893: des bstan pa'i chos dang de 'dzin gyi gang zag
NK065(cu)001:12894: yod dgos par 'dod pa'ang blo gros shin tu rtsing
NK065(cu)001:12895: ba ste / rang rgyal la'ang thub pa'i sgras bshad pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:12897: de 'dzin gyi slob ma yod dgos na ha cang thal lo //
NK065(cu)001:12898: des na bdag cag gi lugs 'di la 'gro 'dul
NK065(cu)001:12899: gyi sprul sku drug la thub pa'i sgrar bshad pa
NK065(cu)001:12900: ni shin tu 'thad pa dang bcas nas smra ste
NK065(cu)001:12902: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab
NK065(cu)001:12903: pas 'khor ba'i dpung gtan bcom pa'i phyir thub pa
NK065(cu)001:12904: zhes bya'o // zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:12905: gnyis pa rkyen gleng bslang ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:12913: rgyud don gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams bar myur du 'byung ba'i dgos pa yod de /
NK065(cu)001:12915: brjod bya rang bzhin gsang ba'i rgyud //
NK065(cu)001:12916: de ji bzhin du rjod byed dag /
NK065(cu)001:12917: ston pas rgyud don lam dang tshig /
NK065(cu)001:12919: gleng gzhi'i rjes su nges par 'gro //
NK065(cu)001:12922: ston 'khor gyi dri lan gcig gi rkyen du gcig gyur pas bstan pa 'byung ma rag pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12924: ston pas gnang dang 'khor gyis zhus //
NK065(cu)001:12925: skabs las gleng bslang don dang 'khor //
NK065(cu)001:12926: gnang dri'i rkyen du gang gyur pa //
NK065(cu)001:12927: de des gsung la ma rag pa //
NK065(cu)001:12930: gleng bar bya ba bstan pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:12931: de gleng bar bskul ba ni /
NK065(cu)001:12932: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen du gyur ba'i phyir bslang zhes bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:12935: de bzhin gleng bslang rnam pa gnyis //
NK065(cu)001:12937: thun mong lhan cig pa'i ched du ston pas mdun bsus te gleng bslang ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:12938: thun mong gi phye ba'i ched du 'khor gyis gus pas dris te gleng bslang ba gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:12940: 'khor dang gzhan gyi don phyir du //
NK065(cu)001:12941: rgyu tshogs thugs rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK065(cu)001:12947: ston pa yab yum gyis lhan cig pa'i 'khor ba
NK065(cu)001:12948: zab dbang gsum bskur bas zhes pa dag nas rang
NK065(cu)001:12949: bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don rtogs te rang don
NK065(cu)001:12950: du sangs rgyas pa ni thun min gyi gleng bslang
NK065(cu)001:12951: yin te / don dam nges pa'i tshig gis rang
NK065(cu)001:12952: bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don dngos su ston pa'i
NK065(cu)001:12953: yin te / phyir / de skad du'ang khog gzhung las /
NK065(cu)001:12954: thun mong ma yin ston pa nyid //
NK065(cu)001:12955: yab yum chags bskul rol pa dang //
NK065(cu)001:12956: dgyes bstar 'khor la dbang bskur bas //
NK065(cu)001:12957: rgyud don 'byung phyir bslang zhes bya //
NK065(cu)001:12961: dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du bstan pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:12963: ma rtogs pa'i dus na yid kyi rtog pa ni 'khor ba'i byed pa po dang /
NK065(cu)001:12964: rtogs pa'i dus na 'das pa'i byed pa po rang
NK065(cu)001:12965: rig pa'i ye shes gnyis rang bzhin dbyer mi phyed
NK065(cu)001:12966: pa'i phyir rdo rje yid de kun tu bzang po'o
NK065(cu)001:12968: dbang po lnga'i yul du ma gyur pa'i yul 'dus
NK065(cu)001:12969: byas dang 'dus ma byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi
NK065(cu)001:12971: des yid skyed par byed cing /
NK065(cu)001:12972: yid kyi yul du gyur pa'i phyir btsun mo ste kun tu bzang mo'o //
NK065(cu)001:12974: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje yid /
NK065(cu)001:12976: de nas btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mos /
NK065(cu)001:12978: de ltar ston pa yab yum gnyis snyoms par zhugs
NK065(cu)001:12979: pa las byung ba'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems
NK065(cu)001:12981: yab yum gyis nyams su bstar ba'i don ched du brjod pa gnyis kyis rkyen byas te /
NK065(cu)001:12982: de'i 'bras bu rtogs pa brjod pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:12983: yab kyis thabs kyi cha bzung nas /
NK065(cu)001:12984: 'khor 'das thams cad phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gcig gi
NK065(cu)001:12985: rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pa la ngam pa'i tshul
NK065(cu)001:12987: rdo rje phung po yan lag ni //
NK065(cu)001:12988: zhes sogs gleng bar mdzad pas /
NK065(cu)001:12989: 'khor rnams kyis lhag pa kun rdzob kyi bden pa mthong ste /
NK065(cu)001:12990: phung khams skye mched thams cad lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du rtogs shing /
NK065(cu)001:12991: yum gyis shes rab kyi cha bzung ste /
NK065(cu)001:12993: phyogs bcu stong khams ye nas dben //
NK065(cu)001:12994: zhes sogs dbyings kyi don gleng bar mdzad pas /
NK065(cu)001:12995: 'khor rnams kyis lhag pa don dam gyi bden pa mthong ste /
NK065(cu)001:12996: 'di ltar phyogs bcu stong khams dang /
NK065(cu)001:13000: tha snyad bzhis bsdus pa thams cad ye nas chos kyi skur mngon sangs rgyas pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:13001: 'bras bu gzhan nas btsal du med par rtogs pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:13002: de'i tshe sngon byung lhan cig pa'i 'khor la /
NK065(cu)001:13005: rgyud bshad pa gsum ka chig rdzogs yin la /
NK065(cu)001:13007: snga phyi rim pa ji lta bar sgrib pa rags
NK065(cu)001:13008: 'bring dag cing kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden
NK065(cu)001:13009: pa bshad du rung ba'i snod ldan du byas pa'o
NK065(cu)001:13010: // gal te gzhung gi tshig 'brel ltar /
NK065(cu)001:13011: yab yum gnyis snyoms par zhugs pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:13013: 'khor gyis bden pa mthong ba rnams dus snga phyi yin nam snyam na /
NK065(cu)001:13015: spar khab las thig le gnyis su med pa ste dgongs pa'ang bsdu'o //
NK065(cu)001:13016: yab yum gnyis kyi las dang /
NK065(cu)001:13018: tshig 'di dag yi ge snga phyir yod kyang /
NK065(cu)001:13020: zhes pas tshig la snga phyi byung kyang dus snga phyi med do //
NK065(cu)001:13021: de'i phyir sngon du zhugs pa gnyis bshad nas /
NK065(cu)001:13022: nyams su bstar ba gnyis phyi la bshad pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:13023: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to zhes pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:13024: gsang dbang gi nges tshig ste /
NK065(cu)001:13025: nyi zla gnyis bsres kyi thig les 'khor la gsang
NK065(cu)001:13026: dbang bskur bas don dam pa'i bden pa rtog med
NK065(cu)001:13028: ston pa'i dgongs pa dbyer med kyi ye shes chen
NK065(cu)001:13029: po da dung ma myong ba'i phyir gsang dbang zhes
NK065(cu)001:13031: ston pa yab yum gyis gsang dbang bskur pa mi 'thad de /
NK065(cu)001:13032: khyad par gyi byed chos dbang rdzas med pa'i phyir te /
NK065(cu)001:13033: ston pa yab yum rdos bcas sha khrag gi lus su med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:13034: de la brten pa'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems med de /
NK065(cu)001:13035: gyang med na de la brten pa'i ri mo med pa bzhin no zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:13036: rdos pa'i de dang de med pa bden kyang /
NK065(cu)001:13037: gdul bya'i snang ba la nyi zla gnyis 'dres kyi byang sems 'ong ba mi 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:13039: gnas rten rtsa dang thig le las //
NK065(cu)001:13040: rang rig ye shes gzugs su 'chags //
NK065(cu)001:13042: rgyal ba'i thugs rang rig pa nyid gdul bya'i ngo
NK065(cu)001:13043: la ye shes sgyu ma'i rang bzhin gyi gnas pa
NK065(cu)001:13044: rtsa dang brten pa thig ler snang nas don mdzad
NK065(cu)001:13045: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:13046: de ltar gsang dbang bskur nas /
NK065(cu)001:13048: dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang gnyis kyi las thun mong du ston par bzhed pas /
NK065(cu)001:13049: de nas gnyis su med pa'i bdag nyid chen pos /
NK065(cu)001:13052: rtags yab yum gyi nyi zla gnyis su med pa'i ngang nas /
NK065(cu)001:13053: bdag rmad byung rgyal po las /
NK065(cu)001:13054: dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK065(cu)001:13055: ye nas sangs rgyas yin pa la //
NK065(cu)001:13056: yin par shes pa'i bdag nyid du //
NK065(cu)001:13057: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK065(cu)001:13058: zhes pa ltar 'khor gyi sems lnga bskyed pa'i phyir 'di gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:13059: de'ang sems bskyed pa'am dbang bskur ba dngos la bla
NK065(cu)001:13060: ma rnams kyi dgongs pa tha dad pa rnams bsdu
NK065(cu)001:13064: mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed do //
NK065(cu)001:13066: e ngo rmad gsum rim par gzhi rnam shes ye nas ye shes yin pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:13067: de nyams su len pa'i thabs dang /
NK065(cu)001:13068: des mthar phyin pa'i 'bras bul ngam pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:13069: de dag ni rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:13070: thugs kyi brnag bya gzhi 'ching grol med par yon
NK065(cu)001:13071: tan lhun gyis grub pa 'di phal gyi yul ma
NK065(cu)001:13073: de yang don dam par skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong med pa las /
NK065(cu)001:13074: kun rdzob tu skye sogs lngar snang zhing /
NK065(cu)001:13075: skyes par snang tsam nyid nas skye ba la sogs pa med pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:13078: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su dang /
NK065(cu)001:13079: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi me long lta bu dang /
NK065(cu)001:13082: sgo lnga bya grub ye shes su sems bskyed par sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:13087: e ma sogs bden pa gsum la rim par ngam pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:13088: sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa de rtogs dka' ba'i phyir gsung ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:13089: de'ang sems lnga dang sbyar ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:13090: ye shes lnga dang sbyar ba gnyis /
NK065(cu)001:13092: skye ba med sogs bden pa dbyer med du la bzla ba lnga po g.yo /
NK065(cu)001:13097: grol lam gyi sems lnga rim cig char du skye ba gnyis la sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:13098: 'dir gnas pa'i rjes su smon pa ni dkyus kyi go rim ste /
NK065(cu)001:13099: skye rim gyi dbang du g.yo ba'i rjes su smon pa 'byung ngo //
NK065(cu)001:13102: thams cad skyes pa kun rdzob /
NK065(cu)001:13103: skyes ma skyes gnyis su med par rtogs pa chos
NK065(cu)001:13104: kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su bskyed pa sogs go
NK065(cu)001:13106: rngam glog gi le'u bzhi par gsungs so //
NK065(cu)001:13107: gnyis pa thabs lam 'og sgo ltar bshad pa ni /
NK065(cu)001:13109: 'dod chags chen po'i spyod pas mi 'ching ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:13110: des myur du 'bras bu la sbyor ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:13111: thabs de gzhan las 'phags pa bka' rmad du byung
NK065(cu)001:13112: ba 'di'i khyad chos yin pa la ngam pa dang
NK065(cu)001:13113: / rgyal ba'i dgongs pa thabs kyi lam 'di khe nyen dang bcas pa'i phyir gsang ba'o //
NK065(cu)001:13115: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes la nyi
NK065(cu)001:13116: zla byang chub kyi sems skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro
NK065(cu)001:13118: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su
NK065(cu)001:13119: blang ba'i dus su thams cad skye 'gag gnas dmigs
NK065(cu)001:13120: ltar snang ba bzhi rim pa ltar /
NK065(cu)001:13125: dbang gnyis kyi sngon 'gro thun mong ba sems bzhi dang /
NK065(cu)001:13126: 'gro dang 'ong zhes pas dngos gzhi thun mong ba ste /
NK065(cu)001:13127: nyi zla byang chub kyi sems rdo rje dang pad+ma'i
NK065(cu)001:13128: rtser dga' bzhi lugs 'byung du 'gro ba'i dus der
NK065(cu)001:13129: / thig le gnyis 'phrad nas thabs kyis bzung ste
NK065(cu)001:13130: ma shor bas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang thob
NK065(cu)001:13131: / cing / don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes skyes pa'o //
NK065(cu)001:13132: slar thabs kyis ldog ste yar gyen du 'ong bas
NK065(cu)001:13133: ma sa brtan gyi dga' bzhi rdzogs nas thig le
NK065(cu)001:13134: rang gnas su sleb tsam na rtog tshogs sku dang
NK065(cu)001:13135: ye shes su sangs rgyas pa ni bde ba chen
NK065(cu)001:13137: de'i tshe kun rdzob dang dbyer med kyi ye shes
NK065(cu)001:13138: skyes pa ni mthar phyin pa'am 'gro 'ong byang chub
NK065(cu)001:13139: kyi sems te / dbang phyi ma gnyis skabs 'di nyid du bskur bar shes par bya'o //
NK065(cu)001:13140: de ltar dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK065(cu)001:13141: la skye 'gag gnas dmigs 'gro 'ong du snang ba
NK065(cu)001:13142: bdo ba'i dus nyid na rang bzhin lhan skyes kyi
NK065(cu)001:13143: ye shes skyes pa la sogs pa lnga dbyer med
NK065(cu)001:13144: du la bazla'o // 'dir kha cig na re /
NK065(cu)001:13145: zab mo'i dbang gsum po 'di gleng bslang yin nam rgyud don yin /
NK065(cu)001:13147: lhan cig pas dbang thob pa'i tshe rgyud go ba mi 'gyur te /
NK065(cu)001:13148: rgyud don mthar phyin pa'i phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:13151: sems lngas gling bslang ba'i las kyi /
NK065(cu)001:13152: zhes pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK065(cu)001:13153: ltos sa gnyis la ltos nas rkyen dang bstan pa gnyis ka yin pa mi 'gal te /
NK065(cu)001:13156: dbang bskur ba'i sgo nas brjod bya don gyi rgyud 'khor la snang bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:13157: rgyud don rtogs pa'i ldog cha nas bstan pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:13158: gsang dbang bskur bas snod rung du byas nas /
NK065(cu)001:13159: dbang phyi ma gnyis kyis smin pa grol ba'i skal pa can du byas te /
NK065(cu)001:13160: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don rtogs pa'i rkyen du gyur pa'i phyir gleng bslang du'ang 'gyur la /
NK065(cu)001:13161: yang na gsang dbang rkyen dang /
NK065(cu)001:13162: dbang phyi ma gnyis rgyud don du 'gyur ba'i phyir nyes pa dang po med do //
NK065(cu)001:13164: rgyud kyi rkyen gnyis las thun mong ma yin pa'i
NK065(cu)001:13165: gleng bslang ba gsang ba'i dbang ston pa'i phyir ro
NK065(cu)001:13167: pa ra m+aar+tha ni don dam pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK065(cu)001:13168: sems lnga'i tha ma skad cig ma bcu drug pa'i
NK065(cu)001:13169: byang chub sems mthas ma reg pa ni ma h+aa
NK065(cu)001:13170: y+aa na ni theg pa chen po ste rgyud 'adi'o
NK065(cu)001:13173: ston pa yab yum gyis gleng bslang ba ni dbang bskur zhing rgyud bshad pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:13175: go phye ba la ltos te /
NK065(cu)001:13176: dbang bskur bas ston 'khor khyad med du gyur nas /
NK065(cu)001:13177: gzhan don du rgyud zhu ba'i spobs pa skyes te
NK065(cu)001:13178: bstan pa 'byung ba'i rkyen du gyur pas na dbang
NK065(cu)001:13179: gsum ka gleng bslang du 'gyur ba'i phyir nyes pa
NK065(cu)001:13182: 'khor gyis rtogs nas gleng bslang ba ni go phye ba rnams kyi ched do //
NK065(cu)001:13186: rgyud go ba gsum ngo bo gcig pa'i phyir /
NK065(cu)001:13187: sngon byung lhan cig pa la rgyud tshar gcig rdzogs pa yin no //
NK065(cu)001:13188: de ltar lhan cig pa la dbang bskur bas shes bya'i sgrib pa cha phra mo dag /
NK065(cu)001:13189: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'i don khong du chud
NK065(cu)001:13190: de gnyis med kyi ye shes shar nas rang don
NK065(cu)001:13191: du sku lnga'i bdag nyid du sangs rgyas pa ni
NK065(cu)001:13192: / gsum pa mthar phyin 'bras bu'i sems bskyed do //
NK065(cu)001:13195: sku lnga la snyoms par zhugs shing gleng bslang ba dang /
NK065(cu)001:13196: dbang bskur zhing rgyud bshad pa dang /
NK065(cu)001:13197: sgrib pa dag nas sangs rgyas pa la dam pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:13198: lhan cig pa rnams sku lnga'i ngo bor sangs rgyas
NK065(cu)001:13199: pas ston 'khor dgongs pa gcig tu gyur pa de
NK065(cu)001:13200: go phye ba'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa'i phyir
NK065(cu)001:13202: skyes ma skyes dbyer med chos kyi sku dang //
NK065(cu)001:13203: 'gag mi 'gag gnyis med mngon byang gi sku dang /
NK065(cu)001:13204: gnas mi gnas gnyis med longs sku dang /
NK065(cu)001:13205: dmigs mi dmigs gnyis med rdo rje'i sku dang /
NK065(cu)001:13206: 'gro 'ong med pa las der snang ba gnyis med sprul skur sems bskyed pa dang lnga'o //
NK065(cu)001:13207: zhes brjod pas dbang thob pa'i yon tan ston 'khor
NK065(cu)001:13208: dgongs pa tha mi dad du gyur pa la mnyes
NK065(cu)001:13209: pa'o // de dag kyang khog gzhung las /
NK065(cu)001:13210: 'gro ba chags can spang med la //
NK065(cu)001:13211: longs spyod rdzogs sku btsun mo dang //
NK065(cu)001:13212: gnyis med rol sogs bstan pa ste //
NK065(cu)001:13213: mthun pas mthun pa sgrol phyir ro //
NK065(cu)001:13219: lhan cig pa rnams rang don du sangs rgyas pa'i phyir rgyud zhu mi dgos kyang /
NK065(cu)001:13220: gzhan don go phye ba'i 'khor gsang ba bzhis chod
NK065(cu)001:13221: pa rnams kyi ched du rgyud bshad par zhus pas
NK065(cu)001:13222: / ston pa'i thugs rje skyes te dgyes pa'i tshul drug gi sgo nas rgyud bshad cing /
NK065(cu)001:13223: 'di nyid rtogs pa'i skal pa dang mi ldan pa
NK065(cu)001:13224: rnams la lam stegs kyi theg pa gzhan ston pa'i
NK065(cu)001:13225: phyir thub pa drug sprul te chos sgo bsam gyis
NK065(cu)001:13226: mi khyab pa spro bar zhal gyis bzhes pa ni
NK065(cu)001:13227: thun mong gi gleng bslang ste /
NK065(cu)001:13229: thun mong gleng bslang ston dang 'khor //
NK065(cu)001:13230: tha dad snang nas dbang thob ste //
NK065(cu)001:13231: nyid kyis rtogs nas 'gro don du //
NK065(cu)001:13232: bka' stsal don gyis zhus dang lan //
NK065(cu)001:13233: gnang bar don gyis tshig tu phyung //
NK065(cu)001:13234: sku gsung thugs kyi spro ba mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:13240: gsang ba bzhis chod pa'i gdul bya'i ched du rgyud bshad par zhus pa ste /
NK065(cu)001:13241: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad btsun mo'i
NK065(cu)001:13242: tshogs dang bcas pas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod
NK065(cu)001:13243: do // e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK065(cu)001:13244: sogs kyi phyir thugs rjes bzung bar rigs so zhes brjod pas so //
NK065(cu)001:13246: de bas na chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i phyir dbyer med na'ang /
NK065(cu)001:13247: de ma rtogs pa la thugs rje skyes te /
NK065(cu)001:13248: lhun gyis grub pa'i chos bstan par dgyes nas ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do zhes sbyar ro //
NK065(cu)001:13250: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las //
NK065(cu)001:13252: sems can thams cad bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po can yin pa las /
NK065(cu)001:13253: ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis bcings grol ltar snang yang /
NK065(cu)001:13254: gshis la bcings grol gnyis ka ma grub ste /
NK065(cu)001:13256: bcing bya 'ching byed bcings pa po //
NK065(cu)001:13257: bdag 'dzin sems can sdug bsngal dngos //
NK065(cu)001:13258: thams cad sems kyi ngo bo'i phyir //
NK065(cu)001:13259: bdag 'dzin zhes bya'i ming yang med //
NK065(cu)001:13260: des na gnyis po'ang med pa la //
NK065(cu)001:13261: 'gro ba po yang yod ma yin //
NK065(cu)001:13264: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK065(cu)001:13265: bstan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK065(cu)001:13271: 'od dang sprul pa 'gyed pa ste dgyes tshul drug
NK065(cu)001:13272: gi sgo nas gdul bya khyad par can gyi ched
NK065(cu)001:13273: du rgyud bshad pa ni le'u gsum pa'i smad man
NK065(cu)001:13274: chad dang / gdul bya thun mong pa'i ched du
NK065(cu)001:13275: ji ltar spro ba ni le'u gsum pa'i stod dang
